NK106(me)001:1: // ma h+aa sa n+d+hi tsi t+t+aa bi sra n+ta pri
NK106(me)001:2: t+ti ma h+aa ra tha n+aa ma bi h+aa ra
NK106(me)001:3: ti smad //// rdzogs pa chen pa sems nyid ngal
NK106(me)001:4: gso'i 'grel pa shing rta chen po zhes bya ba
NK106(me)001:5: glegs bam phyi ma bzhugs so //
NK106(me)001:6: de ltar gsang sngags kyi rim pa gnyis po legs par bstan nas /
NK106(me)001:7: da ni chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin gnyug ma
NK106(me)001:8: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes gzod ma nas ngo
NK106(me)001:9: bo nyid med pa chos thams cad kyi snying po'i
NK106(me)001:10: don bstan pa la 'jug par bya ste /
NK106(me)001:12: de ltar bskyed rdzogs zung 'brel rnal 'byor pas //
NK106(me)001:13: chos rnams ma skyes stong pa'i tshul la 'jug /'di
NK106(me)001:14: ltar dang po'i sgo nas brtsams te yongs su rdzogs
NK106(me)001:15: pa'i bar gyi chos rnams rang bzhin la mkhas par
NK106(me)001:16: bya ba las rang bzhin ni ma skyes pa ste
NK106(me)001:18: 'phags pa dkon mchog 'byung gnas kyi mdo las /
NK106(me)001:19: gang na'ang stong pa rig pa med na ni //
NK106(me)001:20: nam mkha' bar snang bya yi rjes dang mtshungs //
NK106(me)001:21: gang na'ang ngo bo nyid 'ga' yod min pa //
NK106(me)001:22: de ni nam yang gzhan gyi rgyur mi 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:23: gang gi ngo bo nyid ni mi rnyed pa //
NK106(me)001:24: rang bzhin med de ji ltar gzhan gyis rnyed //
NK106(me)001:25: rang bzhin med pa gzhan gyis ci zhig bskyed //
NK106(me)001:26: rgyu de bde bar gshegs pas bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)001:27: thams cad chos kyang mi g.yo brtan par gnas //
NK106(me)001:28: mi 'gyur 'tshe ba med cing zhi ba ste //
NK106(me)001:29: ji ltar nam mkha' shes pa med pa bzhin //
NK106(me)001:30: de la mi shes 'gro ba rmongs par 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:31: ji ltar ri bo dag ni mi 'gul ba //
NK106(me)001:32: de bzhin chos rnams rtag tu bskyod mi nus //
NK106(me)001:33: 'chi 'pho med cing skye ba med pa yi //
NK106(me)001:34: chos rnams de ltar rgyal bas rab tu bstan //
NK106(me)001:37: chos gang skye ba med cing 'byung ba med //
NK106(me)001:38: 'chi 'pho med cing rga bar mi 'gyur ba //
NK106(me)001:39: mi yi seng ge yis ni der ston cing //
NK106(me)001:40: sems can brgya phrag dag ni de la bkod //
NK106(me)001:41: gang la ngo bo nyid ni gang yang med //
NK106(me)001:42: gzhan yang ma yin sus kyang ma rnyed pa //
NK106(me)001:43: nang na ma yin phyi rol dag na yang //
NK106(me)001:44: mi rnyed de dag la ni mgon pos bkod //
NK106(me)001:47: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)001:48: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK106(me)001:49: stong pa ma yin mi stong min //
NK106(me)001:50: dbu ma'ang dmigs su yod ma yin //
NK106(me)001:52: de'ang phyi don du zhen pa ni rang gi sems su shes pa la sogs pa'am /
NK106(me)001:53: lha dang gzhal yas khang du shes pas spong la /
NK106(me)001:54: de'ang skye ba med par shes pas ni gnyen po
NK106(me)001:55: de nyid kyang ngo bo nyid med pas chos thams
NK106(me)001:56: cad kyi rang bzhin la 'jug par 'gyur te /
NK106(me)001:58: sems tsam la ni brten nas ni //
NK106(me)001:59: phyi rol don du rtog pa spong //
NK106(me)001:60: ci yang med ces bstan pa yis //
NK106(me)001:61: phyi nas de yang rab tu spong //
NK106(me)001:64: sems tsam la ni gnas nas ni //
NK106(me)001:65: phyi rol don la mi rtog go //
NK106(me)001:66: yang dag nyid la gnas nas ni //
NK106(me)001:67: sems tsam las ni 'da' bar bya //
NK106(me)001:68: snang med gnas pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK106(me)001:69: de yis theg pa chen po mthong //
NK106(me)001:70: zhes pa'i tshul gyis stong pa nyid shes pa la 'jug go //
NK106(me)001:71: spyi don gnyis pa de nyid rtogs pa'i lta ba bstan pa la lnga ste /
NK106(me)001:74: de yang snang srid 'khor 'das chos rnams kun //
NK106(me)001:75: ye nas bdag med spros dang bral ba la //
NK106(me)001:76: ma rig 'dzin pas srid pa 'dir 'khyams te //
NK106(me)001:77: 'khor 'das bde sdug sna tshogs snang mod kyang //
NK106(me)001:78: snang dus nyid nas rang bzhin stong pa'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:79: sgyu ma rmi lam 'dra bar mkhyen par mdzod //
NK106(me)001:80: de'ang chos thams cad ni stong zhing bdag med pa yin yang /
NK106(me)001:81: de ma shes pas nga dang nga yir 'dzin pa'i
NK106(me)001:82: dbang gis rmi lam dang 'dra ba'i 'khor bar 'khrul
NK106(me)001:83: te bde sdug so so la spyod kyang rang bzhin
NK106(me)001:84: bden pa med par shes par bya ste /
NK106(me)001:86: ye nas lhun 'byams sangs rgyas chos //
NK106(me)001:87: thog ma tha ma dbus med pas //
NK106(me)001:88: nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin la //
NK106(me)001:89: mi shes byis pa rnam par 'khor //
NK106(me)001:90: 'on kyang bcings med bkrol med pa //
NK106(me)001:91: sgyu ma lta bu'i rang bzhin no //
NK106(me)001:94: rnam rtog bdag tu 'dzin pa yis //
NK106(me)001:95: nan gyis mkha' la mdud pa 'dor //
NK106(me)001:96: bcings med rnam par grol med pa'i //
NK106(me)001:97: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK106(me)001:98: bstan phyir spro ba sna tshogs mdzod //
NK106(me)001:100: de'ang don med pa la bdag tu bzung bas 'khrul ba ni /
NK106(me)001:102: 'di dag ni bdag med pa yin mod kyi /
NK106(me)001:103: 'on kyang byis pa so so'i skye bo bdag tu
NK106(me)001:104: 'dzin pa la zhen pa dag ni bdag gi phung
NK106(me)001:105: po rnams la bdag yod do zhes mngon par zhen
NK106(me)001:106: pas de kho na nyid khong du mi chud do
NK106(me)001:107: // khong du ma chud pas mgal me'i 'khor lo ltar 'khor ba'i 'khor lor 'khyam mo zhes so //
NK106(me)001:108: de ltar sems kyi bag chags dag tu zhen pas
NK106(me)001:109: rnam pa sna tshogs pa'i 'khrul snang 'di dag grub
NK106(me)001:110: tshul yang / pad+ma rnam par rol ba'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:111: lha'i bu pad+ma rnam par rol pas 'jam dpal la smras pa /
NK106(me)001:113: phyi rol gyi yul 'di dag byed pa pos byas pa'am ji ltar blta bar bgyi /
NK106(me)001:116: phyi rol gyi yul 'di rnams ni byed pa pos
NK106(me)001:117: byas pa ma yin te sems sam rtog pa'i bag
NK106(me)001:118: chags kyi snang ba yin no //
NK106(me)001:120: bag chags ji ltar brtas kyang ri dang rgya mtsho
NK106(me)001:121: dang nyi ma dang zla ba la sogs pa sra
NK106(me)001:122: zhing 'thas pa ltar gyur pa snang du ga la
NK106(me)001:126: grong khyer chen po w+aa r+aa na s+ai na bram
NK106(me)001:127: ze me sbyin zhes bya bas rang gi lus stag
NK106(me)001:128: tu bsgoms pas / grong khyer gyi mi rnams kyis
NK106(me)001:129: stag tu mthong nas bros pas grong khyer stongs pa
NK106(me)001:130: tu bsgoms pas / byung ngo // zad par sa
NK106(me)001:131: dang chu bsgoms pas sa dang chur snang ba dang
NK106(me)001:132: tu bsgoms pas / byung ngo // / rnal 'byor
NK106(me)001:133: spyod pa'i dge slong gis mi gtsang ba dang rus
NK106(me)001:134: gong gi 'du shes bsgoms pas der snang ba yin
NK106(me)001:135: na thog ma med pa'i bag chags brtas pas ci
NK106(me)001:136: tu bsgoms pas / byung ngo // / ste mi snang / lha'i bus smras pa /
NK106(me)001:137: bag chags brtas pa'i dbang gis rnam pa sna tshogs
NK106(me)001:138: bdag ci'i phyir snang ba yin 'jam dpal gyis smras
NK106(me)001:139: pa / snang ba thams cad ma nges pa yin te /
NK106(me)001:140: la la'i snang ba ni la la'i mun pa yin no //
NK106(me)001:142: sa la sar 'du shes pa'ang yod /
NK106(me)001:143: sa la mer 'du shes pa'ang yod /
NK106(me)001:144: sa la longs spyod du 'du shes pa'ang yod /
NK106(me)001:145: sa la sdug bsngal du 'du shes pa'ang yod /
NK106(me)001:146: me la mer 'du shes pa'ang yod /
NK106(me)001:147: me la longs spyod du 'du shes pa'ang yod /
NK106(me)001:148: me la gnas su 'du shes pa'ang yod /
NK106(me)001:149: me la zas su 'du shes pa'ang yod /
NK106(me)001:150: chu la chur 'du shes pa'ang yod /
NK106(me)001:151: chu la mer 'du shes pa'ang yod /
NK106(me)001:152: chu la sar 'du shes pa'ang yod /
NK106(me)001:153: chu la bdud rtsir 'du shes pa'ang yod /
NK106(me)001:154: chu la gnas su 'du shes pa'ang yod /
NK106(me)001:155: nam mkha' la nam mkhar 'du shes pa'ang yod /
NK106(me)001:156: nam mkha' la gnas su 'du shes pa'ang yod /
NK106(me)001:157: nam mkha' la sar 'du shes pa'ang yod /
NK106(me)001:158: de bas na nges pa med pa'i phyir bag chags
NK106(me)001:159: kyi dbang gis gang ltar yang snang ba yin no
NK106(me)001:160: zhes so // tshul des kyang gcig tu ma nges
NK106(me)001:161: pa rmi lam lta bur rang bzhin med pa yin
NK106(me)001:162: zhes so // no // der ma zad mi gcig
NK106(me)001:163: la bltas pa na'ang cha shas kyis du mar snang
NK106(me)001:164: zhes so // no // ste / gnyen dang /
NK106(me)001:168: skyes pa la sogs par snang ba mi 'gal ba bzhin du /
NK106(me)001:169: chos sna tshogs su snang la rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i ngo bor shes par bya ste /
NK106(me)001:171: ji ltar rlung gis brgyab pas mi g.yo ba'i //
NK106(me)001:172: chu yang g.yo ba'i dba' rlabs rnams su 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:173: de ltar rgyal po mda' bsnun snang ba yang //
NK106(me)001:174: gcig nyid na yang rnam pa sna tshogs byed //
NK106(me)001:175: ji ltar rmongs pas log nas bltas pa yis //
NK106(me)001:176: mar me gcig nyid gnyis su snang bar 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:177: de ltar blta bya lta byed gnyis med la //
NK106(me)001:178: kye ma blo ni gnyis kyi dngos por snang //
NK106(me)001:180: de'ang chu gcig nyid rlung gis dba' rlabs mang por snang ba dang /
NK106(me)001:181: mar me gcig nyid mig btsir bas gnyis su snang ba dang /
NK106(me)001:182: sa ra ha gcig nyid bzang ngan gnyis su mthong
NK106(me)001:183: ba ltar chos thams cad don la gnyis su med
NK106(me)001:184: pa la gnyis su 'dzin pas bslad pa de dang
NK106(me)001:185: 'dra'o zhes so // des na chos thams cad med
NK106(me)001:186: la snang ba rmi lam ltar gnyis su med par
NK106(me)001:187: 'dra'o zhes so // shes par bya'o // snang ba sems su 'dod pa dgag pa ni /
NK106(me)001:188: da ni rnam pa sems la snang yang snang yul sems ma yin no zhes bshad pa ni /
NK106(me)001:190: 'di ltar phyi rol snang ba'i dngos po kun //
NK106(me)001:191: sems la snang yang sems su grub pa med //
NK106(me)001:192: sems las gzhan du'ang grub pa 'ga' med de //
NK106(me)001:193: bag chags dbang gis gzung 'dzin gnyis snang yang //
NK106(me)001:194: snang dus nyid nas gzung 'dzin gnyis med pa //
NK106(me)001:195: bzhin dang me long nang gi gzugs bzhin no //
NK106(me)001:196: 'di ltar me long du bzhin gyi gzugs brnyan shar ba na /
NK106(me)001:197: me long dngas pa'i ngos gzugs brnyan 'char ba'i rten du rung ba dang /
NK106(me)001:198: bzhin la rnam pa 'char ba'am btod byed kyi nus
NK106(me)001:199: pa yod pa'i rkyen las rang gi bzhin ji lta
NK106(me)001:200: bar snang dus / bzhin gyi gzugs brnyan de byad kyang ma yin /
NK106(me)001:201: byad las gzhan gyi rnam pa btod byed kyang med
NK106(me)001:202: pa bzhin du sna tshogs su 'khrul ngor snang ba
NK106(me)001:203: 'di dag rgyu rkyen 'khrul pa'i rten cing 'brel bar
NK106(me)001:205: snang yul ri la sogs pa sna tshogs pa 'di dag sems kyang ma yin /
NK106(me)001:206: sems kyi bag chags 'khrul pa las snang ba ma
NK106(me)001:207: gtogs don gzhan bden par grub pa yang med pas
NK106(me)001:209: rab rib can la skra shad 'dzag pa ltar snang ba dang mtshungs pa med bzhin snang ba'o //
NK106(me)001:210: da dung kha cig na re /
NK106(me)001:211: sa rdo la sogs par snang ba 'di dag phyi
NK106(me)001:212: nang gnyis gang yang ma yin na ci yin zhe
NK106(me)001:213: na / gnyis 'dzin las grub pa kho nar zhen
NK106(me)001:214: pa khyod la phag yin no zhes brjod par bya'o
NK106(me)001:215: na / // de lta mod kyi snang srid 'khor
NK106(me)001:216: 'das kyi chos thams cad snang dus nas phyi nang
NK106(me)001:217: bar gsum gang du'ang ma grub la snang ba sgyu
NK106(me)001:218: ma'i dpe brgyad dang mtshungs par bshad de /
NK106(me)001:219: 'phags pa ting nge 'dzin rgyal po las /
NK106(me)001:220: me long ngos sam 'bru mar snod dag tu //
NK106(me)001:221: bud med kha bzhin brgyan pas bltas pa na //
NK106(me)001:222: de na bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor kun snang yang //
NK106(me)001:223: yod pa ma yin med pa'ang ma yin ltar //
NK106(me)001:224: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin shes par bya //
NK106(me)001:226: de'ang med bzhin du snang ba 'di dag las der
NK106(me)001:227: 'dzin pa'i gzung 'dzin 'khrul pa skye bar byed do
NK106(me)001:228: // 'dir gzung ba ni gzung yul las skad cig
NK106(me)001:229: dang por skyes pa'i rtog pa ste sems nyid gzung
NK106(me)001:230: bar skyes pa can yin la /
NK106(me)001:231: 'dzin pa ni rjes las skyes kyi dpyod pa sems las byung ba rnams yin te /
NK106(me)001:232: spyan ras gzigs brtul zhugs las /
NK106(me)001:233: de la gzung ba ni yul du 'dzin pa'i sems dang /
NK106(me)001:234: 'dzin pa ni de la dpyod pa'i sems las byung ba'o zhes /
NK106(me)001:235: shes par bya ba yin na grang zhes so //
NK106(me)001:236: 'dir mi mkhas shing rmongs la mngon pa'i nga rgyal can phal na re /
NK106(me)001:237: gzung ba ni ri la sogs pa'i snang ba yin la /
NK106(me)001:238: 'dzin pa rang gi shes pa'o zhes 'dzer te /
NK106(me)001:239: ba lang rdzi khyod kyi log par rtog pa des
NK106(me)001:240: chog /'o na gzung 'dzin spangs pa'i 'phags pa rnams
NK106(me)001:241: la yul 'di dag snang ngam mi snang /
NK106(me)001:242: snang na gzung 'dzin snang bar 'gyur te /
NK106(me)001:243: yul gzung ba dang der shes pa de nyid 'dzin par khas blangs pas de snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)001:244: mi snang na 'phags pa'i snang ba sgyu ma lta bur bshad pa dang /
NK106(me)001:245: nyan thos dgra bcom gyis ri dang gtsug lag khang mthong ba dang /
NK106(me)001:246: sangs rgyas kyis ji snyed pa mkhyen pa'i yul la
NK106(me)001:247: snang ba la sogs pa'i shes byed dpag tu med
NK106(me)001:248: do // de la sogs pa'i rigs pa dang lung
NK106(me)001:249: mang yang ha cang log par rtog pa la mtha'
NK106(me)001:252: log pa'i lam la mtha' med phyir //
NK106(me)001:253: de dag 'dir ni spro bya min //
NK106(me)001:255: snang ba sems su 'dod pa'ang sngar bkag zin mod /
NK106(me)001:256: 'on kyang ri la sogs pa 'di dag yul du byas nas /
NK106(me)001:257: de 'dzin pa'i blo dang po la snang ba zhes bshad de /
NK106(me)001:258: snang ba dang snang yul ma phyed pa re bden /
NK106(me)001:259: 'on kyang skyod byed dag gi blo gros de ni mdzangs pa zhig ste /
NK106(me)001:260: don phyin ci log la'ang sgro btags nas bden par zhen pas 'dzin pa'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)001:261: snang yul ni sems kyang ma yin te /
NK106(me)001:262: rang med pa na'ang yod pa dang /
NK106(me)001:263: rang gzhan du song dus mi 'pho ba dang /
NK106(me)001:264: kha dog la sogs par snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)001:265: rang gi sems yin na rang dang rjes su 'gro ldog nges pas /
NK106(me)001:267: med na med par 'gyur dgos pa dang /
NK106(me)001:268: sems la kha dog dang dbyibs med pa ltar /
NK106(me)001:269: de dag la'ang der 'gyur ba la sogs sngar brjod zin pa bzhin no //
NK106(me)001:270: snang mi snang du nges pa ni /
NK106(me)001:271: sems yin pas na snang ba tsam sems su bzhag pas chog mod /
NK106(me)001:272: snang yul sems su rlom pa ni ha cang yang
NK106(me)001:273: rmongs pas rngams po che mi rigs par smra ba
NK106(me)001:274: dag yin no // snang srid sgyu ma ltar bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:275: 'di ltar me long du gzugs brnyan shar bar snang dus me long gi nang /
NK106(me)001:276: der ni byad nyid snang yang ma grub la //
NK106(me)001:277: byad las gzhan gyi rnam pa btod byed med //
NK106(me)001:278: med bzhin gnyis su snang ba mngon sum ltar //
NK106(me)001:279: sna tshogs chos rnams de bzhin shes par bya //
NK106(me)001:280: 'di ltar me long du byad ma 'phos kyang snang la /
NK106(me)001:281: snang dus nas byad las gzhan pa'i chos su grub pa med pa ltar /
NK106(me)001:282: snang srid kyi chos thams cad sems la snang dus
NK106(me)001:283: nyid nas sems dang sems las gzhan du'ang ma grub
NK106(me)001:284: pa sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad du shes par bya ste
NK106(me)001:286: rmi lam ji bzhin sgyu ma bzhin //
NK106(me)001:287: dri za'i grong khyer ji bzhin du //
NK106(me)001:288: de bzhin skye dang de bzhin gnas //
NK106(me)001:289: de bzhin du ni 'jig pa'ang gsungs //
NK106(me)001:292: ji ltar nam mkha' dngas la zla shar ba //
NK106(me)001:293: de yi gzugs brnyan dngas pa'i mtshor snang yang //
NK106(me)001:294: zla ba chu yi nang du 'phos pa med //
NK106(me)001:295: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin shes par gyis //
NK106(me)001:296: ji ltar mi dag brag ri'i khrod 'dug ste //
NK106(me)001:297: glu len smra dang ngu dang dgod pa las //
NK106(me)001:298: rkyen la brten nas brag ca 'byung mod kyi //
NK106(me)001:299: sgra las dbyangs de nam yang 'phos pa med //
NK106(me)001:300: chos rnams thams cad de ltar shes par gyis //
NK106(me)001:301: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK106(me)001:302: sems ngo bo med par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:303: 'di ltar sna tshogs su snang ba 'di dag rigs pas /
NK106(me)001:304: ma brtags nyams dga' brtags na ngos gzung med //
NK106(me)001:305: shin tu brtags na smra bsam brjod las 'das //
NK106(me)001:306: yod med mi dmigs mtha' bral ma bral med //
NK106(me)001:307: de'ang chos thams cad ma brtags na bden pa ltar snang yang /
NK106(me)001:308: phyi snang ba rdul phran du brtags na rang bzhin med pas gzung ba'i yul mi dmigs /
NK106(me)001:309: nang 'dzin pa skad cig cha med pas ngo bo
NK106(me)001:310: ngos gzung las 'das pas 'dzin pa'i sems mi dmigs
NK106(me)001:311: / gnyis med spros pa dang bral bas brjod bya brjod byed las 'das pa ste /
NK106(me)001:314: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i ye shes kyi sman gang yin zhe na /
NK106(me)001:315: sems yongs su tshol ba'i brtson 'grus so //
NK106(me)001:316: de ni 'di ltar sems yongs su tshol te /
NK106(me)001:319: gti mug par gyur pa'i sems de gang yin /
NK106(me)001:322: da ltar byung ba zhig yin nam /
NK106(me)001:323: de la sems 'das pa gang yin pa de ni 'gags shing zad pa'o //
NK106(me)001:324: ma 'ongs pa gang yin pa de ni ma skyes shing ma phyin pa'o //
NK106(me)001:325: da ltar byung ba gang yin pa de ni rten dang gnas med pa'o //
NK106(me)001:327: sems ni nang na yang med /
NK106(me)001:329: de gnyis ka'i bar na yang med /
NK106(me)001:330: gnyis ka med par yang mi dmigs so //
NK106(me)001:332: sems kyi dpyad du med pa /
NK106(me)001:335: rnam par rig pa med pa /
NK106(me)001:338: sems ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyis kyang ma gzigs gzigs par mi 'gyur ro //
NK106(me)001:340: sems ni kun tu btsal na mi rnyed do //
NK106(me)001:341: gang mi rnyed pa de ni mi dmigs so //
NK106(me)001:342: gar mi dmigs pa de ni 'das pa yang ma yin /
NK106(me)001:344: da ltar byung ba yang ma yin te /
NK106(me)001:347: da ltar byung ba yang ma yin pa de ni
NK106(me)001:348: dus gsum las yang dag par 'das pa'o zhes dang
NK106(me)001:349: / sems ji lta ba de bzhin du chos thams
NK106(me)001:350: cad kyang mi dmigs pas gang na yang yod pa
NK106(me)001:351: ma yin no zhes pa dang /
NK106(me)001:356: nam mkha' lta bu'o zhes dang /
NK106(me)001:358: rgyal ba'i spyod yul 'di la gang zhig 'jug 'dod pa //
NK106(me)001:359: des ni bsam pa nam mkha' lta bur rnam par sbyongs //
NK106(me)001:360: rtog dang rnam par rtog dang 'du shes 'dzin spongs la //
NK106(me)001:361: nam mkha' lta bu'i yid kyis 'di la 'jug par gyis //
NK106(me)001:364: brjod par bya ba ldog pa ste //
NK106(me)001:365: sems kyi spyod yul ldog pas so //
NK106(me)001:366: ma skyes pa dang ma 'gags pa //
NK106(me)001:367: chos nyid mya ngan 'das dang mtshungs //
NK106(me)001:370: bstan du mtshan ma'i dngos por med //
NK106(me)001:371: mthong du dmigs pa'i yul dang bral //
NK106(me)001:372: shes su tshig tu brjod du med //
NK106(me)001:373: rgyu las ma byung snying po 'di //
NK106(me)001:374: sgro yis btags pa kun dang bral //
NK106(me)001:376: dpe ni nam mkha' lta bur rtag /
NK106(me)001:377: don ni chos nyid skye ba med //
NK106(me)001:378: rtags ni sems nyid 'gag pa med //
NK106(me)001:379: nam mkha' lta bu'i chos nyid la //
NK106(me)001:380: nam mkha' lta bu'i dpe yis mtshon //
NK106(me)001:382: rang bzhin med pa'i dpes bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:383: 'di ltar med bzhin du snang ba'i cha nas /
NK106(me)001:384: sgyu ma'i tshul du skye sogs snang na yang //
NK106(me)001:385: snang dus nyid nas skye sogs rang bzhin med //
NK106(me)001:386: smig rgyu'i chu dang rdzing bu'i zla gzugs bzhin //
NK106(me)001:387: 'di ltar chu'i zla ba dang smig rgyu'i chu ltar
NK106(me)001:388: skye bar snang dus nyid nas skye ba med pa
NK106(me)001:389: la sogs par rtogs par bya ste /
NK106(me)001:391: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)001:392: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK106(me)001:393: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK106(me)001:394: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK106(me)001:395: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)001:396: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK106(me)001:397: 'gag pa med las thams cad 'gag /'gag pa nyid na 'gag pa med //
NK106(me)001:398: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)001:399: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK106(me)001:400: gnas pa med las thams cad gnas //
NK106(me)001:401: gnas pa nyid na gnas pa med //
NK106(me)001:402: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)001:403: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK106(me)001:404: dmigs pa med las thams cad dmigs //
NK106(me)001:405: dmigs pa nyid na dmigs pa med //
NK106(me)001:406: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)001:407: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK106(me)001:412: chu bo sna tshogs pa yang rgya mtshor gcig pa ltar //
NK106(me)001:413: brdzun pa du ma dag kyang bden pa gcig gis 'joms //
NK106(me)001:414: nyi ma gcig pu snang bar gyur pa yis //
NK106(me)001:415: mun pa du ma dag kyang 'joms par byed //
NK106(me)001:416: ji ltar chu 'dzin gyis ni rgya mtsho las //
NK106(me)001:417: chu blangs nas ni sa gzhi gang byas kyang //
NK106(me)001:418: de ni ma nyams nam mkha' dag dang mnyam //
NK106(me)001:419: 'phel ba med cing 'grib pa dag kyang med //
NK106(me)001:420: rgyal ba phun sum tshogs pas yongs gang ba //
NK106(me)001:421: lhan cig skyes pa gcig gi rang bzhin nyid //
NK106(me)001:422: de las 'gro ba skye zhing 'gag pa ste //
NK106(me)001:423: de la dngos dang dngos med pa yang med //
NK106(me)001:425: chu phran rnams rgya mtshor gcig pa ltar /
NK106(me)001:426: skye sogs su snang ba rnams skye med du gcig pa dang /
NK106(me)001:427: nyi ma'am mar me gcig gis mun pa du ma 'joms pa ltar /
NK106(me)001:428: skye med gcig shes pas 'khrul snang thams cad skye med du shes pa dang /
NK106(me)001:429: sprin las char sa gzhi thams cad khyab par bab
NK106(me)001:430: dus sprin la che chung 'phel 'grib med pa ltar
NK106(me)001:431: / chos nyid skye med kyi ngang las chos can
NK106(me)001:432: skye 'gag tu snang yang skye med kyi ngang la
NK106(me)001:434: sems nyid rang bzhin gyis dag pa'i ngang la 'gro ba thams cad zhen 'dzin gyis 'khrul yang /
NK106(me)001:435: sems nyid las g.yos pa med pa'i rang bzhin du shes par bya ste /
NK106(me)001:436: sems nyid ye nas dag pa'i rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir ro zhes dang /
NK106(me)001:437: dgongs pa nges par 'grel pa las /
NK106(me)001:439: sngon bdag dgon pa nags khrod gcig na mchis pa'i tshe /
NK106(me)001:440: dge sbyong zhig kyang mchis te /
NK106(me)001:441: chos rnam pa sna tshogs la dmigs pas brda sprod par bgyid de /
NK106(me)001:442: kha cig ni phung po la dmigs pas so //
NK106(me)001:443: kha cig ni khams la dmigs pas so //
NK106(me)001:444: kha cig ni skye mched la dmigs pas so //
NK106(me)001:445: kha cig ni rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba dang
NK106(me)001:446: dran pa nye bar gzhag pa rnams la dmigs pas
NK106(me)001:447: so // bdag gis ni chos gcig gi mtshan nyid
NK106(me)001:448: bdag med par shes pas thams cad kyang de bzhin
NK106(me)001:450: spyi don gsum pa sbyang bya bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:451: de ltar med bzhin snang ba'i chos rnams gzod ma nas ngo bo nyid med pa las /
NK106(me)001:452: khyad par ma dag 'gro drug snang ba 'di //
NK106(me)001:453: med bzhin snang ba bag chags 'khrul pa'i gzugs //
NK106(me)001:454: rab rib can la skra shad snang ba bzhin //
NK106(me)001:455: de bsal 'dod pas bad kan sbyong ba ltar //
NK106(me)001:456: 'khrul snang dag 'dod ma rig ling tog bsal //
NK106(me)001:457: 'di ltar bad kan gyis bsgribs pas skra shad 'dzag
NK106(me)001:458: pa la sogs par snang ba na bad kan sel
NK106(me)001:459: ba'i sbyor ba la brtson pa ltar /
NK106(me)001:460: sems can rnams ni thog ma med pa nas bdag
NK106(me)001:461: dang bdag gir 'dzin pa'i bag chags dang ma rig
NK106(me)001:462: pa'i ling tog gis bsgribs pas sems nyid 'od gsal
NK106(me)001:463: ba sangs rgyas kyi snying po ji ltar rang la
NK106(me)001:464: yod kyang ma mthong bar ma zad /
NK106(me)001:465: phyi sa rdo ri brag nang nyon mongs pa'i zhen
NK106(me)001:466: rtog la sogs pa skra shad 'bab pa dang mtshungs
NK106(me)001:467: par snang dus nyid nas yod ma myong ba slu
NK106(me)001:468: ba byis pa 'brid pa'i rang bzhin du bshad de
NK106(me)001:470: ma rig pa'i phyin ci log rjes su song ba'i phyir /
NK106(me)001:471: 'jig rten pas ni dngos po'i rnam pa rang bzhin
NK106(me)001:472: med pa nyid la rang bzhin dang bcas pa nyid
NK106(me)001:474: ji ltar rab rib can rnams kyis skra shad la
NK106(me)001:475: sogs pa'i rang bzhin med pa nyid la rab rib
NK106(me)001:476: can gyi rkyen gyis rang bzhin nyid du mngon par
NK106(me)001:477: zhen pa de bzhin du byis pa rnams ma rig
NK106(me)001:478: pa'i rab rib kyis blo gros kyi mig nyams pa
NK106(me)001:479: nyid kyis dngos po'i rnam pa rang bzhin med pa
NK106(me)001:480: la rang bzhin dang bcas pa nyid du mngon par
NK106(me)001:481: zhen par gyur nas zhes pa dang /
NK106(me)001:483: ji ltar rab rib can dag gis //
NK106(me)001:484: skra shad log par 'dzin par ltar //
NK106(me)001:485: de bzhin dngos por rtog pa 'di //
NK106(me)001:486: byis pas log par rnam par brtags //
NK106(me)001:488: de'ang 'phags pa rnams kyis rang bzhin med par gzigs
NK106(me)001:489: pas snying po'i rang bzhin dang mthun par dag pa
NK106(me)001:490: dang ngo bo nyid med pa 'ba' zhig tu dgongs
NK106(me)001:492: gang gi tshe ma rig pa'i rab rib dang bral
NK106(me)001:493: bas dri ma med pa'i shes rab kyi spyan mnga'
NK106(me)001:494: ba rnams kyis gzigs pa la ltos na ni /
NK106(me)001:495: de'i tshe rab rib dang bral bdag gis rab rib
NK106(me)001:496: can gyis dmigs pa'i skra shad ma mthong ba ltar
NK106(me)001:497: 'phags pas byis pa'i skye bo'i blos brtags pa bzhin
NK106(me)001:498: ma gzigs pa rnams kyis 'di ni dngos po rnams
NK106(me)001:499: kyi rang bzhin ma yin no zhes gsal bar gsung
NK106(me)001:500: bar mdzad pa yin te zhes gsungs pa dang /
NK106(me)001:501: de la slu ba'i chos can ni byis pa rnams
NK106(me)001:502: 'brid par byed cing phyin ci log tu snang ba
NK106(me)001:503: ste mgal me'i 'khor lo bzhin no //
NK106(me)001:504: de'i phyir rang bzhin ma yin pa nyid kyis na /
NK106(me)001:505: 'du byed thams cad brdzun pa ste slu ba'i chos can yin pa'i phyir smig rgyu'i chu bzhin no //
NK106(me)001:506: gang zhig bden pa de ni slu ba'i chos can ma yin te /
NK106(me)001:507: dper na mya ngan las 'das pa bzhin no //
NK106(me)001:508: de'i phyir bstan pa'i rigs pa dang lung 'di las
NK106(me)001:509: dngos po rnams rang bzhin med par grub ste zhes
NK106(me)001:510: so // spyi don bzhi pa sbyong byed bstan pa la bdun las /
NK106(me)001:511: mtha' bral dbu mar bslab tshul bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:512: de lta bu'i ma rig pa'i ling tog de gang gis sel zhe na /
NK106(me)001:514: de yi gnyen por rig pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK106(me)001:515: 'khor ba'i bag chags stong par la bzla zhing //
NK106(me)001:516: stong pa'i rang bzhin sna nga bar thag bcad de //
NK106(me)001:517: snang stong gnyis med bden pa gnyis don shes //
NK106(me)001:518: mtha' gnyis gnas bsal dbu mar bslabs pa yis //
NK106(me)001:519: srid zhir mi gnas nam mkha'i ngang du grol //
NK106(me)001:520: 'di ni nges don snying po'i dam pa ste //
NK106(me)001:521: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i gnas lugs yin //
NK106(me)001:522: 'di ltar yang dag pa'i shes rab ni so so rang gi rig pa'i ye shes te /
NK106(me)001:523: de nyid kyis chos rnams kyi rang bzhin la blta ba na /
NK106(me)001:524: las dang nyon mongs pa dang bag chags thams cad
NK106(me)001:525: kyang med bzhin snang ba sprul pa la sogs pa'i
NK106(me)001:526: rang bzhin du khong du chud pa'i stong pa nyid
NK106(me)001:529: nyon mongs las dang lus rnams dang //
NK106(me)001:530: byed pa po dang 'bras bu dag /
NK106(me)001:531: dri za'i grong khyer lta bu dang //
NK106(me)001:532: smig rgyu rmi lam 'dra ba yin //
NK106(me)001:534: las thams cad rnam par sbyong ba'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:535: las de ni rang bzhin gyis ngo bo nyid med
NK106(me)001:536: pa stong pa nyid kyi rjes su blta bar bya
NK106(me)001:537: ste zhes so // de'ang rkyen las skyes pa'i phyir yang stong ste /
NK106(me)001:538: ma dros pas zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:539: gang zhig rkyen las skyes pa de ma skyes //
NK106(me)001:540: de la skye ba'i rang bzhin yod ma yin //
NK106(me)001:541: rkyen la rag las gang de stong par bshad //
NK106(me)001:542: gang gis stong nyid shes de bag yod yin //
NK106(me)001:544: stong pa'ang snang ba nyid de bden pas stong pa'i cha tsam du shes par bya ste /
NK106(me)001:545: 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i don bsdus pa las /
NK106(me)001:548: gzugs las stong pa nyid gzhan ma yin no //
NK106(me)001:549: stong pa nyid las kyang gzugs gzhan ma yin no zhes pa dang /
NK106(me)001:551: gzugs kyi rang bzhin gang yin pa //
NK106(me)001:552: de ni stong pa nyid bzhin du //
NK106(me)001:553: stong pa nyid kyang gzugs su brjod //
NK106(me)001:554: rang bzhin gdod nas ma skyes pa'o //
NK106(me)001:556: 'dod chags zhe sdang rang bzhin stong pa nyid //
NK106(me)001:557: gti mug nga rgyal yongs su rtog pas bskyed //
NK106(me)001:558: rtog pa de yang ma byung byung med par //
NK106(me)001:559: de ltar shes na 'dren pa rnams su 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:561: chos thams cad 'byung ba med pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:562: 'dod chags mi dmigs de bzhin zhe sdang dang //
NK106(me)001:563: gti mug 'di la nam yang mi dmigs te //
NK106(me)001:564: chos rnams kun dang nam mkha'  'dra'o zhes //
NK106(me)001:565: de ltar gang shes de ni rgyal bar 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:566: lha dang lha min gnyis ka tshul gcig ste //
NK106(me)001:567: mnyam dang mi mnyam de bzhin mnyam pa yin //
NK106(me)001:568: sangs rgyas med cing chos dang dge 'dun med //
NK106(me)001:569: de ltar sus shes de ni mkhas pa yin //
NK106(me)001:570: sems can rang bzhin byang chub nyid du gsungs //
NK106(me)001:571: byang chub rang bzhin sems can thams cad de //
NK106(me)001:572: sems can rnams dang byang chub gnyis ma yin //
NK106(me)001:573: de ltar shes na skyes bu mchog tu 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:575: de'ang kun rdzob dang don dam pa gnyis su med
NK106(me)001:576: pa ni bden pa dbyer med pa ste dbu ma'i
NK106(me)001:577: de kho na nyid dngos po med pa'i ngo bo
NK106(me)001:578: nyid du ye gdod ma nas dag pa la bslabs
NK106(me)001:579: pas / rtag chad 'khor 'das kyi cha las grol
NK106(me)001:580: ba'i mya ngan las 'das pa thob par 'gyur ro
NK106(me)001:581: pas / // de kho na rang bzhin rdzogs pa
NK106(me)001:582: chen po'i don chos nyid bya btsal las 'das pa
NK106(me)001:583: pas / // zhes bya ste / kun byed las /
NK106(me)001:584: sangs rgyas sems can snang srid snod bcud kun //
NK106(me)001:585: snying po byang chub nga las byung ba'i phyir //
NK106(me)001:586: ye nas gnyis su med par la yang bzla //
NK106(me)001:589: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)001:590: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK106(me)001:591: ma bcos ma bslad byas pa med //
NK106(me)001:592: ji bzhin rang bzhin rnam par dag /
NK106(me)001:593: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)001:594: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK106(me)001:595: gzhi rtsa med pas sems nyid ni //
NK106(me)001:596: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba yin //
NK106(me)001:597: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)001:598: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK106(me)001:599: rang bzhin med pa'i rang bzhin las //
NK106(me)001:600: bde ba chen por lhun gyis grub //
NK106(me)001:601: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)001:602: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK106(me)001:603: stong pa ma yin mi stong min //
NK106(me)001:604: dbu ma'ang dmigs su yod ma yin //
NK106(me)001:606: sems kyi rtsa ba gcad pa ni /
NK106(me)001:608: snang ba'i dngos kyis phan gnod gnyis su med //
NK106(me)001:609: der 'dzin zhen pas srid par 'ching bas na //
NK106(me)001:610: sna tshogs snang la brtag dpyad mi dgos kyi //
NK106(me)001:611: 'dzin pa'i sems kyi rtsa ba gcad par mdzod //
NK106(me)001:612: 'di ltar snang bas 'ching ba ma yin te dgag
NK106(me)001:613: sgrub tu phar ma zhen na tshur mi gos pa'i
NK106(me)001:614: phyir te / 'brel pa ma grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)001:615: de bas na zhen pas 'ching ba yin pas zhen pa spang ba ni /
NK106(me)001:617: gang la zhen pa yod na de yang thong //
NK106(me)001:618: rtogs par gyur na thams cad de yin te //
NK106(me)001:619: de las gzhan zhig sus kyang shes mi 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:620: klog pa de yin 'dzin dang bsgom pa'ang de //
NK106(me)001:621: bstan bcos snying la 'chad pa'ang de yin no //
NK106(me)001:623: de'ang snang ba'i gzugs sgra dri ro reg la phar rtog dpyod kyis rang bzhin med pa dang /
NK106(me)001:624: mi gtsang ba la sogs par zhen pas spong yang
NK106(me)001:625: sems kyi zhen mkhan ma grol bas 'dzin pa'i rtsa
NK106(me)001:626: ba mchod de khyi la rdo 'phangs pa na rdo
NK106(me)001:627: rdeg mkhan la mi 'ju bar rdo la rmugs pa
NK106(me)001:628: lta bu'i chos spyod pa ni nyon mongs pa las
NK106(me)001:629: mi grol bas / seng ge la rdo 'phangs dus
NK106(me)001:630: 'phen mkhan gsod pa ltar nyon mongs pa dang chags
NK106(me)001:631: sdang thams cad kyi rtsa ba rang gi sems yin
NK106(me)001:632: pas de nang du brtags la rang bzhin med pas
NK106(me)001:633: shes rab kyis zhi bar bya ste /
NK106(me)001:636: nang du yongs su tshol la phyi rol du ma rgyu gcig /'od srungs /
NK106(me)001:637: ma 'ongs pa'i dus na dge slong mngon pa'i nga
NK106(me)001:638: rgyal can khyi rdo la snyeg pa dang mtshungs pa
NK106(me)001:640: ji ltar khyi rdo la snyeg pa dang mtshungs pa dag gang yin zhe na /
NK106(me)001:641: khyi rdo de nyid kyis 'jigs pa las /
NK106(me)001:642: rdo de nyid kyi phyir snyeg gi rdo de sus 'phangs pa la mi snyeg go //
NK106(me)001:644: 'di ltar dge sbyong dang bram ze kha cig gzugs dang /
NK106(me)001:648: reg bya rnams kyi nang du so sor rtog pa la mngon par brtson te /
NK106(me)001:649: mi rtag pa dang slu ba dang /
NK106(me)001:650: 'jig pa'i chos su rtog kyang de dag gang las byung ba mi shes pas /
NK106(me)001:656: rgyal po'i pho brang 'khor du song na yang gzugs dang /
NK106(me)001:660: reg bya rnams kyis gnod par 'gyur ro //
NK106(me)001:661: gal te de dag dgon par gnas pa las 'chi ba'i dus byed par gyur na yang /
NK106(me)001:662: 'jig rten gyi sdom pa la gnas pa de dag
NK106(me)001:663: mtho ris kyi 'jig rten du skye bar 'gyur te
NK106(me)001:664: / der yang de dag gi 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga po dag gis gnod par 'gyur ro //
NK106(me)001:665: de dag las shi 'phos nas kyang ngan song las yongs su mi grol bar 'gyur te /
NK106(me)001:672: de ltar na dge sbyong khyi rdo la snyeg pa dang mtshungs pa yin no //
NK106(me)001:673: de la 'di skad ces bya ste /
NK106(me)001:674: dper na khyi ni rdo bas skrag gyur kyang //
NK106(me)001:675: sus 'phangs mi snyeg rdo la snyeg par byed //
NK106(me)001:676: de bzhin dge sbyong bram ze la la dag /
NK106(me)001:677: gzugs la sogs pas skrag nas dgon par gnas //
NK106(me)001:678: de dag dgon pa de na gnas gyur kyang //
NK106(me)001:679: gzugs la sogs pa'i yul rnams mthong gyur na //
NK106(me)001:680: btang snyoms 'dug cing nang gi tshul mi shes //
NK106(me)001:681: de yi nyes las byung ba gang yin pa //
NK106(me)001:682: mi shes pa ni slar yang grong du gnas //
NK106(me)001:683: gzugs la sogs pas der yang gnod par 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:684: der yang lha yi longs spyod spyad gyur te //
NK106(me)001:685: lha dang mi las kha cig shi 'phos nas //
NK106(me)001:686: de dag ngan song sar ni ltung bar 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:687: blun po de dag shi 'phos sdug bsngal 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:688: de ltar sdug bsngal brgya ldan de dag ni //
NK106(me)001:689: khyi rdo snyeg pa 'dra zhes bde gshegs gsungs //
NK106(me)001:691: phyi ma'i dus na dge slong rnal 'byor spyod pa
NK106(me)001:692: pa khyi rdo la snyeg pa mi 'dra ba dag
NK106(me)001:693: ni / dper na seng ge la rdo 'phangs na /
NK106(me)001:694: rdo gang nas byung shes pas rdo la mi snyeg
NK106(me)001:695: par rdo 'phang bar byed pa dag la snyeg pas
NK106(me)001:697: de bzhin du dge slong rnal 'byor spyod pa pa
NK106(me)001:698: phyi rol gyi 'dod pa'i yon tan mthong ba de'i
NK106(me)001:699: tshe sems las byung bar shes nas sems la brtags
NK106(me)001:700: pas dngos po med par shes nas grol bar 'gyur
NK106(me)001:701: ro // de la 'di skad ces bya ste /
NK106(me)001:702: seng ge mi la za ba ltar //
NK106(me)001:703: dge slong rnal 'byor spyod pa yis //
NK106(me)001:704: phyi rol 'dod yon mthong gyur na //
NK106(me)001:705: sems las byung bar shes nas ni //
NK106(me)001:706: sems nyid stong par shes pa yis //
NK106(me)001:710: dper na rta'i 'dul spyod la mkhas pas rta de
NK106(me)001:711: gang dang gang du g.yo bar byed cing ma byang
NK106(me)001:712: ba de srid du spyod do //
NK106(me)001:714: de bzhin du dge slong rnal 'byor spyod pa pa
NK106(me)001:715: yang gang dang gang du sems 'gyur bar mthong ba
NK106(me)001:716: de dang der rab tu spyod pa la 'jug ste
NK106(me)001:717: / de ci nas 'khrug par mi 'gyur ba de ltar sems rab tu 'chos so //
NK106(me)001:718: de la 'di skad ces bya ste /
NK106(me)001:719: dper na rta yi 'dul spyod mkhas pa zhig /
NK106(me)001:720: byang zhing g.yo med tshul du rab tu 'dul //
NK106(me)001:721: rnal 'byor pa yang sems ni 'gyur mthong nas //
NK106(me)001:722: de ltar phyis 'khrug mi 'gyur de ltar 'chos //
NK106(me)001:725: dper na lkog nad lha gor gyis ni srog gi dbang po 'gag par byed do //
NK106(me)001:727: de bzhin du lta bar gyur thams cad kyi nang
NK106(me)001:728: nas bdag tu 'dzin pas ni chos kyi srog gi
NK106(me)001:730: de la 'di skad ces bya ste /
NK106(me)001:731: dper na lha gor srog gi dbang po la //
NK106(me)001:732: gnod cing de yis bde ba sbyin pa med //
NK106(me)001:733: de bzhin lta gyur nang nas bdag blta ba //
NK106(me)001:734: des ni chos srog rnam par 'jig par byed //
NK106(me)001:737: dper na mi ni gang dang gang du bcings pa de nyid las dgrol bar bya ba yin no //
NK106(me)001:739: de bzhin du rnal 'byor spyod pa pa'i sems gang
NK106(me)001:740: dang gang la chags pa de de dang des dgrol
NK106(me)001:742: de la 'di skad ces bya ste /
NK106(me)001:743: dper na mi ni gang du bcings gyur pa //
NK106(me)001:744: de dang de las dgrol bar bya ba yin //
NK106(me)001:745: de bzhin sems rmongs gang dang gang chags pa //
NK106(me)001:746: rnal 'byor spyod pas de dang de las dgrol //
NK106(me)001:748: de nyid sems kyi gsang yin te /
NK106(me)001:750: sems kyi gsang 'di ma shes na //
NK106(me)001:751: de dag don med gyi nar 'khyam //
NK106(me)001:753: tshogs drug la 'char ba'i sems dngos med du bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:754: de'ang tshogs drug yul la 'char ba'i /
NK106(me)001:755: sems ni snang la rang bzhin 'ga' med de //
NK106(me)001:756: btsal bas mi rnyed bltas pas mthong ba med //
NK106(me)001:757: kha dog dbyibs med ngo bo ngos gzung med //
NK106(me)001:758: phyi dang nang med dus gsum skye 'gag med //
NK106(me)001:759: phyogs dang ris med gzhi rtsa dngos po med //
NK106(me)001:760: 'di zhes mi mtshon bsam yul 'das pa'i sems //
NK106(me)001:762: sems la sems kyis rjes su bltas na ngo bo
NK106(me)001:763: ngos gzung gang du'ang med par shes pa ni gnyug
NK106(me)001:764: ma'i de nyid shes pa ste /
NK106(me)001:766: sems kyi rtsa ba mi mtshon te //
NK106(me)001:767: lhan cig skyes pa rnam gsum gyis //
NK106(me)001:768: gang las de skyes gang du nub //
NK106(me)001:769: gang du gnas gyur mi shes so //
NK106(me)001:771: dam pa soms dang cig shos mi shes na //
NK106(me)001:772: gang nas shar zhing gang du nub 'gyur ba //
NK106(me)001:773: ji ltar phyi rol ji bzhin nang de bzhin //
NK106(me)001:775: gdod nas dag pa nam mkha'i rang bzhin la //
NK106(me)001:776: bltas shing bltas shing mthong ba 'gag par 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:777: de lta bu nyid dus su 'gog par 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:779: de'ang dmigs bsam spros pa thams cad las 'das pa nyid /
NK106(me)001:780: 'phags pa dkon mchog 'byung gnas kyi mdo las /
NK106(me)001:781: chos gang skye ba med cing 'byung ba med //
NK106(me)001:782: 'chi 'pho med cing dga' bar mi 'gyur ba //
NK106(me)001:783: mi yi seng ge yis ni de bstan zhing //
NK106(me)001:784: sems can brgya phrag dag ni de la bkod //
NK106(me)001:785: gang yang gang la ngo bo nyid gang med //
NK106(me)001:786: gzhan yang ma yin sus kyang mi rnyed pa //
NK106(me)001:787: nang na ma yin phyi rol dag na yang //
NK106(me)001:788: ma rnyed de dag la ni mgon pos bkod //
NK106(me)001:789: bde bar gshegs pa'i zhi ba'i 'gro gsungs kyang //
NK106(me)001:790: 'gro ba gang yang rnyed par mi 'gyur te //
NK106(me)001:791: de dag 'gro las grol bar rnam par gsung //
NK106(me)001:792: grol nas sems can mang po dgrol bar mdzad //
NK106(me)001:793: bdag med par ni chos kun ston mdzad cing //
NK106(me)001:794: sems can 'dzin las 'jig rten rnam par grol //
NK106(me)001:795: bdag nyid 'gro las grol zhing 'gro sgrol bas //
NK106(me)001:796: de yis pha rol gshegs kyang brgal ba med //
NK106(me)001:797: drang srong chen pos srid pa'i pha rol phyin //
NK106(me)001:798: pha rol gshegs pa gang yang rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:799: pha rol yod ma yin zhing tshur log med //
NK106(me)001:800: pha rol song ngo zhes kyang tshig tu gsung //
NK106(me)001:801: gang gis tshig tu smra ba de yang med //
NK106(me)001:802: gang smras de yi tshig kyang yod ma yin //
NK106(me)001:803: gang la smra ba de yang rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:804: gang gis shes pa de yang yod ma yin //
NK106(me)001:805: log par rtog pas chags pa'i dbang gis su //
NK106(me)001:807: skyes bu gang zhig zhi ba'i chos rig pa //
NK106(me)001:808: des ni rang byung de bzhin gshegs pa mthong //
NK106(me)001:809: chos mchog zhi ba rnams kyang rab tu shes //
NK106(me)001:811: gzhi rtsa med par yang gsang snying las /
NK106(me)001:812: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK106(me)001:813: pho mo ma yin ma ning min //
NK106(me)001:814: mtshan med ma yin rigs rgyud min //
NK106(me)001:815: kha dog ma yin dbyibs ma yin //
NK106(me)001:816: gnas su ma yin gang yang min //
NK106(me)001:818: sems ma bcos par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:819: de lta bu ni dus gsum 'phel 'grib med pas
NK106(me)001:820: 'char 'char 'dra yang ngo bo med pa ni yul
NK106(me)001:823: 'gag pa mi dmigs ma skyes phyogs na med //
NK106(me)001:824: da ltar mi gnas rang bzhin mnyam pa'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:825: sems kyis sems ma tshol bar dal du chug /
NK106(me)001:828: da ltar gyi sems la skyes cha gnas cha 'gag cha gsum du med de /
NK106(me)001:829: skad cig ma med pa tsam du'ang ma grub pas /
NK106(me)001:830: lta ba dang blta mkhan gnyis su ma grub pa'i phyir rang babs su bzhag pa nyid /
NK106(me)001:832: sems kyis sems la blta ru med pa'i phyir //
NK106(me)001:833: bltas pas mi mthong ji bzhin nyid du zhog /
NK106(me)001:835: sems skad cig mar bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:837: dgag sgrub dran rig skad cig yid kyi yul //
NK106(me)001:838: snang tsam nyid nas phyi dang nang na'ang med //
NK106(me)001:839: btsal bya'i don gyis tshol mkhan byas pas bslang //
NK106(me)001:840: rang gis rang btsal nam yang rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:841: 'di ltar sems kyi rtog pa ji 'dra ba zhig skyes nas de btsal kyang mi rnyed de /
NK106(me)001:842: tshol mkhan de nyid yin pas /
NK106(me)001:843: rang gis rang btsal bas mi rnyed pa ni gnyis med pas so //
NK106(me)001:844: nges par brtags na rang yang med de gang du'ang
NK106(me)001:845: dmigs pa tha dad nye bar zhi ba'i phyir te
NK106(me)001:847: ngang la gnas pas g.yo med lhun gyis grub //
NK106(me)001:848: rang bzhin gnas pas sus kyang bcos su med //
NK106(me)001:849: ma bcos ji bzhin pa ru gnas pa de //
NK106(me)001:850: bya ba med pa las kyi mchog tu bstan //
NK106(me)001:852: gcig la gnyis su bltas pas sgom pa nor //
NK106(me)001:853: ngo bo gcig la gnyis kyis thob pa med //
NK106(me)001:855: gdod nas dag cing skye 'gag med par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:857: ye nas skye med rang bzhin gnyug ma'i don //
NK106(me)001:858: mi gnas 'gag pa med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK106(me)001:859: dus gsum gzhi rtsa med pas stong pa'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:860: sna tshogs 'char gzhi ma 'gags snang ba la //
NK106(me)001:861: dngos po mtshan mar med pas rtag pa med //
NK106(me)001:862: rang shar 'gag pa med pas chad pa med //
NK106(me)001:863: gnyis dang gnyis med med pas brjod du med //
NK106(me)001:864: 'di zhes grub pa med pas ngos gzung med //
NK106(me)001:865: rang bzhin gdod nas dag par shes par bya //
NK106(me)001:866: de'ang sems nyid rang bzhin gyis dag pa la gzhi
NK106(me)001:867: dang rtsa ba med pas stong pa zhes brjod la
NK106(me)001:868: / 'char tshul cir yang ma 'gags pas snang ba zhes brjod cing /
NK106(me)001:869: brtags kyang dngos po dang mtshan mar med pas rtag pa'i mtha' dang bral /
NK106(me)001:870: rig tsam du ma 'gags pas chad pa'i mtha' dang bral /
NK106(me)001:871: de gnyis dang gnyis ka ma yin pa'i phung po
NK106(me)001:872: gsum pa gzhan med pas 'adi'o zhes ngos gzung med
NK106(me)001:873: pa'i phyir / rang bzhin gyis dag pa zhes bya
NK106(me)001:874: ba tsam las brjod par med pa ni mtha' yis
NK106(me)001:875: ma gos pa'i ye shes te /
NK106(me)001:877: mtha' yis ma gos dri ma med pa'i ye shes ni //
NK106(me)001:878: byas pa rnams dang bral zhing bsags pa'i las min zhes //
NK106(me)001:880: de'i tshe 'pho 'gyur med pas rtag pa dang /
NK106(me)001:881: log par rtog pa'i dra ba chad pa dang /
NK106(me)001:882: sangs rgyas pa la sogs pa'i cha shas dbye ba yang /
NK106(me)001:884: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)001:885: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK106(me)001:886: nges par rtag na rtag pa nyid //
NK106(me)001:887: rtag chen de nyid gnyen po med //
NK106(me)001:888: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)001:889: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK106(me)001:890: nges par chad na chad la nyid //
NK106(me)001:891: byang chub nyid de log rgyun chad //
NK106(me)001:892: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)001:893: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK106(me)001:894: rab 'byams mtha' yas gang nas kyang //
NK106(me)001:895: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:896: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)001:897: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK106(me)001:898: sems nyid rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas te //
NK106(me)001:899: de las gzhan du yod ma yin //
NK106(me)001:900: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)001:901: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK106(me)001:902: srid gsum ye nas snying po nyid //
NK106(me)001:903: ma nor ma bcos lhun gyis grub //
NK106(me)001:904: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)001:905: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK106(me)001:906: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dbyings //
NK106(me)001:907: btsal ba med par rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK106(me)001:908: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)001:909: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK106(me)001:910: kun nas kun tu ngang bzang po //
NK106(me)001:911: thams cad ye 'byams rmad du grags //
NK106(me)001:912: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)001:913: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK106(me)001:914: snying po byang chub de nyid las //
NK106(me)001:915: ma rtogs gang yang yod ma yin //
NK106(me)001:916: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)001:917: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK106(me)001:918: thams cad sangs rgyas yin pa la //
NK106(me)001:919: rtog pas bsgribs pa ngo ma shes //
NK106(me)001:920: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)001:921: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK106(me)001:922: rtog pa nyid nas rtog med phyir //
NK106(me)001:923: bde gshegs snying po gzhan na med //
NK106(me)001:924: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)001:925: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK106(me)001:926: kun gyi snying po byang chub la //
NK106(me)001:927: ye nas dgongs pa lhun gyis grub //
NK106(me)001:929: gang du'ang blang dor med par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:930: de lta bu'i sems nyid de yang rig pas gzhig cing /
NK106(me)001:931: brtags pas med ltar ma brtags dus na'ang med //
NK106(me)001:932: rang bzhin gnyis med gdod ma'i ngo bo la //
NK106(me)001:933: bzang ngan blang dor re dogs mi dmigs pas //
NK106(me)001:934: brtag dang dpyad pas 'di la ci byar yod //
NK106(me)001:935: dus gsum yid kyi tshol khro ma byed zhog /'di
NK106(me)001:936: ltar brtag dpyad du mas sems brtags na ma grub
NK106(me)001:937: pa ltar ma brtags pa'i dus na'ang ma grub pa
NK106(me)001:938: yin pas rang bzhin med pa /
NK106(me)001:939: blang dor dang re dogs med pa bram ze bkren
NK106(me)001:940: pas glang po che lom pas blo bde ba ltar
NK106(me)001:941: ngang gis rtog dpyod dran bsam tshol khro med pa'i
NK106(me)001:944: glang chen lom nas sems tshags chud pa na //
NK106(me)001:945: der ni 'gro 'ong bcad na dal ba ste //
NK106(me)001:946: 'di ltar rtogs na gang du'ang 'dri sa med //
NK106(me)001:947: mkhas pa ngo tsha med pas de ma rtogs //
NK106(me)001:949: sems kyi glang po che ni yan du chug /
NK106(me)001:950: de nyid kyis ni bdag nyid la dris shig /
NK106(me)001:951: nam mkha'i ri mo la ni chu 'thung dang //
NK106(me)001:952: de yi 'gram du zhog cig rang ga bar //
NK106(me)001:953: yul gyi glang po'i dbang po lag pas blangs nas su //
NK106(me)001:954: ji ltar gsod par rang dbang snang bar 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:955: rnal 'byor pas ni glang po skyong ba bzhin //
NK106(me)001:957: spyi don lnga pa grub matha'i tshig gis mi rtogs par bstan pa la bzhi ste /
NK106(me)001:958: mngon pa'i nga rgyal can gyis mi rtogs par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:959: da ni grub pa'i matha'i tshig 'ba' zhig 'jal ba
NK106(me)001:960: rnams kyis yang dag pa'i don ji lta ba nyid
NK106(me)001:961: mi rtogs par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:962: phyogs chos dang rjes su 'gro ldog gi khyab pa brtsi zhing /
NK106(me)001:963: rtags mthun phyogs dang mi mthun phyogs la zhugs sam
NK106(me)001:964: ma zhugs zhes pa la sogs pa rang rang gi
NK106(me)001:965: kun rtog g.yo zhing nyon mongs pa'i bud shing phyin
NK106(me)001:966: ci log gi sbud pas sbar bas sdug bsngal du
NK106(me)001:967: ma'i me dpung rab tu 'bar zhing /
NK106(me)001:968: rang dang gzhan gyi rgyud bsreg pa la mkhas pa
NK106(me)001:969: mngon pa'i nga rgyal ri bo dang mnyam pa'i gang
NK106(me)001:970: zag / rtog ge spros pa'i spun pas bskyod pa'i sems //
NK106(me)001:971: rnam g.yeng rlung ltar g.yo bas mi rtogs kyi //
NK106(me)001:972: bsal gzhag 'gro 'ong med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK106(me)001:973: kun byed ye shes dri med ngo bo nyid //
NK106(me)001:974: ji bzhin bzhag pas de bzhin mthong ba yin //
NK106(me)001:975: zhes bya ba ni gshis sam babs kyi rang bzhin gang yin pa de /
NK106(me)001:977: byis pa ngan pa rtog ge ba //
NK106(me)001:978: ro dang 'dra bas de dag brtags //
NK106(me)001:979: zhes pa dag gis brtags pa'i kun tu spros pa'i
NK106(me)001:980: dra ba chen po stong du mched pa'i chos ltar
NK106(me)001:981: ma yin gyi / chos dang sems kyi gnas lugs
NK106(me)001:982: ye nas rnam par dag pas grub bsal med pa
NK106(me)001:983: ma yin gyi / ste / nam mkha' rin po
NK106(me)001:984: che'i mdo dang gshed dmar gyi rgyud las ji ltar
NK106(me)001:985: gsungs pa nyid byams pas mngon rtogs rgyan dang rgyud
NK106(me)001:987: 'di la bsal bya ci yang med //
NK106(me)001:988: gzhag par bya ba cung zad med //
NK106(me)001:989: yang dag nyid la yang dag blta //
NK106(me)001:990: yang dag mthong na rnam par grol //
NK106(me)001:992: dri ma ye nas med pas byang ba dang /
NK106(me)001:993: yon tan ye nas rdzogs pas chub pa dang /
NK106(me)001:994: 'char tshul cir yang ma 'gags pas byang chub kyi sems zhes bya ste /
NK106(me)001:995: sku gsum ye nas lhun grub tu bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:997: byang ba'i don ni 'di lta ste //
NK106(me)001:998: snying po byang chub sems de ni //
NK106(me)001:999: rang byung ye nas rnam dag pas //
NK106(me)001:1000: kun byed rgyal pos byas pa kun //
NK106(me)001:1001: kun bzang nyid du rnam dag pas //
NK106(me)001:1002: byang zhes bya bar bshad pa yin //
NK106(me)001:1003: chub ces bya ba 'di lta ste //
NK106(me)001:1004: snying po rang byung ye shes des //
NK106(me)001:1005: snang ba dang ni srid pa dang //
NK106(me)001:1006: snod dang bcud kyis bsdus pa dang //
NK106(me)001:1007: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK106(me)001:1008: khams gsum rgyud drug sems can dang //
NK106(me)001:1009: de bzhin nyid ni thams cad la //
NK106(me)001:1010: kun la chub ste khyab par gnas //
NK106(me)001:1011: des na chub ces bya bar bshad //
NK106(me)001:1012: sems kyi don ni 'di lta ste //
NK106(me)001:1013: snying po rang byung ye shes des //
NK106(me)001:1014: snang srid snod bcud thams cad la //
NK106(me)001:1015: 'jug cing dbang sgyur gsal bar spyod //
NK106(me)001:1016: des na sems zhes bya bar bshad //
NK106(me)001:1018: de'ang chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis gnyis su med cing dag pas /
NK106(me)001:1019: ngo bo nyid kyi rang bzhin med pa'i dgongs pa
NK106(me)001:1020: shes na gshis kyi gnas lugs shes pa yin la
NK106(me)001:1021: / sems nyid kyang 'ong ba dang 'gro ba med
NK106(me)001:1022: par rtogs nas nyon mongs pa gang la'ang skye 'gag
NK106(me)001:1023: med pas spang gnyen gnyis su med par rtogs nas
NK106(me)001:1024: ma spangs rang sar dag pa ste /
NK106(me)001:1025: mi zad pa'i gter mdzod man ngag gi glu las /
NK106(me)001:1026: nyon mongs gnyen po gnyis su byed pa ga la yod //
NK106(me)001:1027: de ltar rtsol ba'i skyes bu de ni 'khor bar 'ching //
NK106(me)001:1029: gnad mthong bas grol ba ni yul spangs pa la mi ltos par grol te /
NK106(me)001:1030: rmi lam gyi yul dang der 'dzin pa rang ngo
NK106(me)001:1031: shes pas skad cig gis rang grol ba yin no
NK106(me)001:1032: // gzhan dag yul spangs nas grol bar 'dod pa yin kyang /
NK106(me)001:1033: yul dang sems su snang ba tsam gyis mi 'ching gi /
NK106(me)001:1034: de la zhen na 'ching bas 'dzin zhen spang bar gdams pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1037: zhen pa chod cig n+aa ro pa //
NK106(me)001:1040: gal te yid du 'ong ngo mnyam pa'i sems //
NK106(me)001:1041: snying la 'bab cing gces par byas na ni //
NK106(me)001:1042: til gyi shun pa tsam gyi zug rngus kyang //
NK106(me)001:1043: nam yang sdug bsngal 'ba' zhig bskyed par zad //
NK106(me)001:1045: snang tsam ni dgag sgrub kyi ngo bor med pas zhen 'dzin mi bya'o //
NK106(me)001:1046: de'ang sems nyid ma skyes pa'i ngo bor dang po nyid du rtogs par bya ba tsam las /
NK106(me)001:1047: dus thams cad du blos rtog dpyod 'ba' zhig bya ba ma yin te /
NK106(me)001:1048: rtog dpyod byas kyang rang bzhin snga ma las lhag pa med la /
NK106(me)001:1049: spros pas kun tu 'chel bar 'gyur ba'i phyir te /
NK106(me)001:1051: rang bzhin ma bcos nam mkha' lta bu la //
NK106(me)001:1052: brtag dang dpyad pa mang pos ci zhig bya //
NK106(me)001:1054: chos kyi rgyal po'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:1055: dper na mi gcig la dug mda' phog na de myur du phyung na nad las thar ro //
NK106(me)001:1056: de lta ma yin par sgro las byung ngam /
NK106(me)001:1058: made'u las byung ngam zhes rtog na nad de rgyas nas 'chi bar 'gyur ro //
NK106(me)001:1059: de bzhin du gtan tshigs mang po la rtog dpyod byas pas sems rtog pa'i dbang du song bas /
NK106(me)001:1060: des ni nyon mongs pa mched cing ldang bar 'gyur ro //
NK106(me)001:1061: de lta bas na rnam par mi rtog par sems gnas par bya'o zhes so //
NK106(me)001:1062: de'ang tshig tsam gyis don la rtog cing go yul
NK106(me)001:1063: cung zad tsam gyis gnas lugs rtogs par rlom la
NK106(me)001:1064: / shes pas su zhig 'tshengs shing mi shes pas
NK106(me)001:1065: gang zhig 'phung ba'i chos la rtsod pa dang spros
NK106(me)001:1066: pa 'chel bar yang dag pa'i de nyid las ring
NK106(me)001:1068: skye bo ma lus lhag par sun 'byin zhing //
NK106(me)001:1069: nga rgyal skyon gyis de nyid mtshon mi nus //
NK106(me)001:1071: kye ho bu nyon rtsod pa'i ro ni dga' bas yang dag gnas shes pa //
NK106(me)001:1072: 'gro la 'chad cing 'don pa la sogs pas ni rtogs par nus min te //
NK106(me)001:1075: byang chub sems dpa' chos 'phags kyis gsol ba /
NK106(me)001:1076: bdag gis de bzhin gshegs pa grags pa rgya chen
NK106(me)001:1077: gyi zhing khams dregs pa can zhes bya ba phyin
NK106(me)001:1078: pa'i tshe mu stegs can rnam pa mang po don
NK106(me)001:1079: med pa'i mtshan nyid sems par bgyid /
NK106(me)001:1083: yang dag pa'i don ma rtogs nas blo gros ngan pa de dag gcig la gcig rtsod par gyur /
NK106(me)001:1086: tshar gcod pa dag mthong nas /
NK106(me)001:1088: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi don dam pa ni
NK106(me)001:1089: rtog ge thams cad las yang dag par 'das pa
NK106(me)001:1093: da ni yang dag par rtog ge thams cad las 'das par sangs rgyas so //
NK106(me)001:1094: sangs rgyas nas rnam par phye'o //
NK106(me)001:1096: don dam pa ni 'phags pa rnams kyis so so rang gis rig par ngas bshad la /
NK106(me)001:1097: so so'i skye bo rnams kyis rig par bya ba ni rtog ge'i yul yin no //
NK106(me)001:1098: rtog ge ni mtshan ma'i spyod yul yin no //
NK106(me)001:1099: don dam pa ni brjod du med pa yin no //
NK106(me)001:1100: rtog ge ni rtsod pa mngon par 'phel ba yin no //
NK106(me)001:1101: don dam pa ni rtsod pa nye bar zhi ba yin no //
NK106(me)001:1102: yang dag pa ni rtog ges brtag pa'am /
NK106(me)001:1105: so so rang rig mtshan med spyod yul ni //
NK106(me)001:1106: brjod du med cing tha snyad yongs chad pas //
NK106(me)001:1107: rtsod dang bral ba don dam chos yin te //
NK106(me)001:1108: de ni rtog ge'i yul las 'das pa'o //
NK106(me)001:1110: ltag pa'i bsam pa la bskul ba'i mdo las kyang /
NK106(me)001:1112: 'di la mang du thos pas rgyags shing dregs pa dag ni /
NK106(me)001:1113: yang dag pa'i tshul bzhin yid la byed pa dang
NK106(me)001:1114: bral nas sems kyi rgyud dmu rgod du gyur pa
NK106(me)001:1115: yin te / zhi gnas dang lhag mthong dang bral
NK106(me)001:1116: zhing sangs rgyas kyi chos rab tu zab mo las
NK106(me)001:1117: ring ba yin no zhes so //
NK106(me)001:1118: de'ang tshig tsam gyis shes pas nam du'ang phan pa chen po mi 'grub ste /
NK106(me)001:1120: dper na 'on pa rol mo mkhan //
NK106(me)001:1121: gzhan dag de yis dga' byed kyang //
NK106(me)001:1122: bdag nyid kyis ni mi thos pa //
NK106(me)001:1123: ma bsgoms chos kyang de bzhin no //
NK106(me)001:1124: chu bo dang ni rgya mtsho la //
NK106(me)001:1125: gru dang gzings bcas mnyen pa zhig /
NK106(me)001:1126: gzhan dag de yis sgrol byed kyang //
NK106(me)001:1127: bdag nyid de na 'chi ba bzhin //
NK106(me)001:1128: ma bsgoms chos kyang de bzhin no //
NK106(me)001:1129: dper na bu ram mngar ba'i ro //
NK106(me)001:1130: brjod pas ro ni mi myong ste //
NK106(me)001:1131: myangs pas ro ni myong bar 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:1132: de bzhin stong pa nyid kyi ro //
NK106(me)001:1133: brjod pas ro ni mi myong ste //
NK106(me)001:1134: bsgoms pas ro ni myong bar 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:1136: de lta bas na tshig gis don 'tshol bas rtog
NK106(me)001:1137: dpyod 'ba' zhig lhur len pa'ang yang dag pa'i ye
NK106(me)001:1138: shes kyi rgyu ma yin no //
NK106(me)001:1140: gang zhig bla ma'i man ngag bdud rtsi'i chu //
NK106(me)001:1141: gdung sel bsil ba ngoms par mi 'thung ba //
NK106(me)001:1142: de ni bstan bcos don mang mya ngam gyi //
NK106(me)001:1143: thang la skom pas gdungs te 'chi bar zad //
NK106(me)001:1145: de'ang bla ma dam pas chos nyid zab mo'i don mtshon pas chog pa nyid /
NK106(me)001:1147: rtsa ba bral ba'i de nyid gang sems pa //
NK106(me)001:1148: bla ma'i man ngag thob pa de yis chog /
NK106(me)001:1150: de'ang zab mo snying po'i don la 'jug gi /
NK106(me)001:1151: tshig tsam grub matha'i chos sam rtog ge'i spun kogs tsam la byang chub re bar mi bya'o //
NK106(me)001:1152: rtog ge zhes pa'ang gnyis las /
NK106(me)001:1153: sa mtshams kyi rtog ge ni so so'i skye bo
NK106(me)001:1154: ste mi bden pa phyin ci log tu bden par
NK106(me)001:1155: zhen pas de skad ces bya'o //
NK106(me)001:1156: grub mtha' rtog ge ni dngos por smra ba'i gzhung
NK106(me)001:1157: thams cad de gshis la med kyang rnam par sgro
NK106(me)001:1159: grub matha'i dbye bas mi rtogs par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1161: 'dir ni sna tshogs grub mtha' mang po dang //
NK106(me)001:1162: bsam brjod rtog pa du mas ci zhig bya //
NK106(me)001:1163: nges pa'i don la grub dang ma grub med //
NK106(me)001:1164: mtha' dang dbus med theg pa'i rnam dbye med //
NK106(me)001:1165: mkha' bzhin rnam dag rgya chad phyogs lhung med //
NK106(me)001:1166: de la yod med blos brtags 'khrul pas na //
NK106(me)001:1167: brjod du med gang ji ltar bshad du yod //
NK106(me)001:1168: don med gnas la rab tu ngal bar zad //
NK106(me)001:1169: gshis sems nyid rnal ma'i don ni smra bsam brjod
NK106(me)001:1170: pa las 'das pas bsam brjod kyi grub mthas mi
NK106(me)001:1171: rtogs te / grub ma grub dang mtha' dbus gnyis
NK106(me)001:1172: su med pas grub mtha' zhes gdags su med pa
NK106(me)001:1173: rtogs te / dang / nam mkha' lta bu'i rang
NK106(me)001:1174: bzhin gang du'ang rgya ma chad pa 'di'i lugs so
NK106(me)001:1175: zhes phyogs su ma lhung ba ste /
NK106(me)001:1177: chos kun nam mkha'i mtshan nyid de //
NK106(me)001:1178: nam mkha'i mtshan nyid de bzhin nyid //
NK106(me)001:1180: don de lta bu blos bsam du med pa la
NK106(me)001:1181: bsam pas 'khrul pa'i phyir tshig dang yi ge med
NK106(me)001:1183: tshig dang yi ge'i don brtags pas //
NK106(me)001:1184: tshig yig don la brtags med pas //
NK106(me)001:1185: rtog med mnyam pa de bzhin nyid //
NK106(me)001:1186: de yang nam mkha'i dgongs par gnas //
NK106(me)001:1187: bsam du med pa'i don 'di ni //
NK106(me)001:1188: nam mkha' bzhin du ye gnas so //
NK106(me)001:1190: brjod du med pa de ni bshad du mi shes
NK106(me)001:1191: pas sgras brjod pa dag gi rang bzhin ldog pa
NK106(me)001:1193: brjod du med gang ji ltar bshad du yod //
NK106(me)001:1195: nga dang bdag tu rtog pa mu stegs 'khrul pa'i lam //
NK106(me)001:1196: byis pas bslus pa'i chos spyod rtog pa'i lam btsud pas //
NK106(me)001:1197: phyin pa'i dus med rtogs pa'i dus kyang med pas na //
NK106(me)001:1198: chos nyid chos tshol ba yis rnyed par ga la 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:1200: de bas na chos thams cad zhi ba rang bzhin
NK106(me)001:1201: gyis dag pa spros pa'i rang bzhin las 'das par
NK106(me)001:1203: dkon mchog ta la la'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:1204: de bzhin gshegs pa rtag tu skye med chos //
NK106(me)001:1205: chos rnams thams cad bde bar gshegs dang 'dra //
NK106(me)001:1206: byis pa'i blo can mtshan mar 'dzin pa rnams //
NK106(me)001:1207: 'jig rten dag na med pa'i chos la spyod //
NK106(me)001:1209: gzhi ma grub la dpyad pas mi rtogs par dpes bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1210: des na nam mkha'i ut+pala sngon po dang ser po yin pa so sor rtsod pa ltar /
NK106(me)001:1211: gshis mtha' dbus med pa'i don la rtsod pas ci zhig bya'o //
NK106(me)001:1214: ji ltar mkha' dbus dngas pa'i skyed mos tshal //
NK106(me)001:1215: me tog 'bras mang 'bab chus brgyan pa zhig /
NK106(me)001:1216: mngon du bsams nas de yi rnam dbye dang //
NK106(me)001:1217: mthun phyogs mi mthun phyogs gang rtsod pa bzhin //
NK106(me)001:1218: rang rang gi grub mthas 'jal ba thams cad nam mkha'i skyed mos tshal blo mthun du bzhag nas /
NK106(me)001:1219: de'i mthun phyogs mi mthun phyogs rtsod pa ltar /
NK106(me)001:1220: shes bya zhes pa lta bu'i spyir rloms nas dngos
NK106(me)001:1221: po dngos med la sogs pa rang rang gi rtog
NK106(me)001:1222: pas rloms pa'i spyi bye brag gi phung po dbye
NK106(me)001:1223: gzhi gzugs la sogs pa bye brag tu byed pa
NK106(me)001:1224: thams cad pha rol gyi gshis la ma grub par
NK106(me)001:1225: blos sgro btags nas 'jal ba ste /
NK106(me)001:1226: 'khrul snang gzhi med pa la rnam dbye gzhi bcas
NK106(me)001:1227: kyi grub mthas sgrib pa kun brtags la sogs pa
NK106(me)001:1228: las gzhan med pas dgos pa med de /
NK106(me)001:1229: rigs pa drug cu pa'i 'grel par /
NK106(me)001:1230: khyed cag thog ma med pa'i kun nas nyon mongs pa'i 'ching bas bcings par ma zad /
NK106(me)001:1231: da dung yang rang gi grub mtha' ngan pas sbyar
NK106(me)001:1232: ba'i 'ching bas bcings pa dar gyi srin bu rang
NK106(me)001:1233: gi kha chus 'ching ba bzhin du zhes pa ltar
NK106(me)001:1234: yin no // de'ang gshis nam mkha' 'dra bas rnam
NK106(me)001:1235: dbye ngo bo nyid kyis med par rtogs par bya
NK106(me)001:1236: yin no // ste / kun byed las /
NK106(me)001:1237: chos kun byang chub sems yin de dpe ni //
NK106(me)001:1238: kun dpe nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin du //
NK106(me)001:1239: byang chub sems kyi don yang de bzhin no //
NK106(me)001:1241: blos byas kyi sgom pas bslad par gdams pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1242: des na glo bur gyi sgrib pa'am /
NK106(me)001:1243: rang bzhin gyi sgrib pa la sogs pa'i rnam pa /
NK106(me)001:1244: gang yang dri med sems nyid dag pa la //
NK106(me)001:1245: bcos bsgyur dri mas nam yang mthong ba med //
NK106(me)001:1246: de la bskyed dang rdzogs pas ci zhig bya //
NK106(me)001:1247: dang ba'i bsam gtan bsgoms pas bslad par zad //
NK106(me)001:1248: 'di ltar gzod nas lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin
NK106(me)001:1249: la ni bskyed pa dang rdzogs pas spros pa 'chel
NK106(me)001:1250: ba las blang dor med pa'i ngo bo mi mthong
NK106(me)001:1251: bas lhun mnyam rdzogs pa chen por la bzla ba
NK106(me)001:1253: mtshan ma grangs la dga' ba'i gdul bya la //
NK106(me)001:1254: tshogs dang dkyil 'khor bskyed du yod par bstan //
NK106(me)001:1255: gang zhig sku gsum lam la brten byas nas //
NK106(me)001:1256: mtshan ma grangs kyi go nas rtog byed pa //
NK106(me)001:1257: bskal pa bye ba brgya phrag yun ring du //
NK106(me)001:1258: dkyil 'khor bskyed du med pa'i don mi rtogs //
NK106(me)001:1259: kye de bas ston pa kun byed rgyal po ngas //
NK106(me)001:1260: tshogs dang dkyil 'khor rang bzhin lhun rdzogs pas //
NK106(me)001:1261: ma byas rang bzhin grub pa'i chos nyid la //
NK106(me)001:1262: bskyed cing bsam du med pa'i don rtogs na //
NK106(me)001:1263: kun byed rgyal po'i dkyil 'khor rtogs pa yin //
NK106(me)001:1265: de bzhin du gshis la lam bsgom pa la sogs pa yang med de /
NK106(me)001:1267: byang chub sems ni nam mkha' lta bu ste //
NK106(me)001:1268: nam mkha' lta bu'i sems nyid chos nyid la //
NK106(me)001:1269: lta dang bsgom med dam tshig bsrung du med //
NK106(me)001:1270: 'phrin las rtsol med ye shes sgrib pa med //
NK106(me)001:1271: sa la sbyang med bgrod pa'i lam yang med //
NK106(me)001:1272: phra ba'i chos med gnyis med 'brel pa med //
NK106(me)001:1273: sems la lung med gtan la 'bebs pa med //
NK106(me)001:1274: sgro skur 'das pas yang dag la bzlar med //
NK106(me)001:1275: rdzogs chen byang chub sems kyi lta ba'o //
NK106(me)001:1278: bsam gtan bral bas ci zhig bsam byar yod //
NK106(me)001:1279: brjod du med gang ji ltar bshad du yod //
NK106(me)001:1280: srid pa'i phyag rgyas 'gro ba ma lus bslus //
NK106(me)001:1281: rang bzhin gnyug ma sus kyang bslad pa med //
NK106(me)001:1282: rgyud sde sngags med bsam bya bsam gtan med //
NK106(me)001:1283: de kun rang yid 'khrul par byed pa'i rgyu //
NK106(me)001:1284: rang bzhin dag pa'i sems la bsam gtan dag gis mi bslad de //
NK106(me)001:1285: bdag nyid bde la gnas bzhin gdung bar ma byed cig /
NK106(me)001:1288: ma yengs ting nge 'dzin pa'i rtod phur yin //
NK106(me)001:1289: ye nas yin la yeng med shor ba med //
NK106(me)001:1290: ma yengs ting 'dzin re ba'i bslu mkhan te //
NK106(me)001:1291: rgyu 'bras theg chen drang ba'i lung bstan yin //
NK106(me)001:1292: ye nas yin pas yeng med shor med de //
NK106(me)001:1293: rtsol sgrub gnyen po rang bzhin lhun gyis zhog /
NK106(me)001:1295: spyi don drug pa la bzla ba la bzhi ste /
NK106(me)001:1296: gshis mkha' mnyam du la bzla ba ni /
NK106(me)001:1297: de'i phyir gshis mkha' mnyam gcig tu la bzla ba ni /
NK106(me)001:1298: gdod nas rang bzhin dag pa'i sems nyid la //
NK106(me)001:1299: spang gnyen bral thob med kyis dmigs gtad shol //
NK106(me)001:1300: phyi nang gzung 'dzin med kyis ched 'dzin thong //
NK106(me)001:1301: 'di zhes ngos gzung med kyis zhen pa chod //
NK106(me)001:1302: thob dang ma thob med kyis re dogs spongs //
NK106(me)001:1303: de'ang sems nyid ye nas sangs rgyas pa la da
NK106(me)001:1304: gzod dag par byar med pas blang dor gyi zhen
NK106(me)001:1307: kye sems dpa' chen po rang sems grub 'dod na //
NK106(me)001:1308: 'dod pa med pas grub pa yin pa'i phyir //
NK106(me)001:1309: rtog med mnyam pa nyid la gnas par gyis //
NK106(me)001:1310: blang dor med pa'i yul la rang bzhin gnas //
NK106(me)001:1311: g.yos pa med pa'i ngang la ngang gis gnas //
NK106(me)001:1313: phyi nang gzung 'dzin gang yang med pas ched du 'dzin pa mi bya ba yang /
NK106(me)001:1315: phyi dang nang med chos kyi dbyings //
NK106(me)001:1316: zab mo cha shas rtog yul med //
NK106(me)001:1318: 'adi'o zhes gcig tu med pas zhen pa'i 'khris gzhom pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1320: sems ni ji bzhin pa yi ngo bo ste //
NK106(me)001:1321: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin nyid du grub //
NK106(me)001:1322: ji bzhin pa la 'chos par ma byed cig /
NK106(me)001:1324: thob pa dang ma thob pa med pa yang /
NK106(me)001:1326: thob dang ma thob gnyis su byar med pas //
NK106(me)001:1327: re dang dogs pa'i gzeb tu ma 'ching zhig /
NK106(me)001:1329: rtogs dus nges pas phyam gcig tu la bzla ba ni /
NK106(me)001:1330: da ni rang gis rtogs pa'i dus nges pas phyam gcig nam mkha'i ngang du la bzla ba ni /
NK106(me)001:1331: gzhi nas 'pho 'gyur med pa'i rig pa la //
NK106(me)001:1332: sna tshogs rkyen gyi rnam pa ci shar yang //
NK106(me)001:1333: shar ba de nyid rang gi thog tu grol //
NK106(me)001:1334: chu dang rlabs bzhin chos skur phyam gcig go //
NK106(me)001:1335: rang gi sems 'pho 'gyur med pa'i ngang du dga'
NK106(me)001:1336: mi dga' dang bde sdug la sogs pa'i rnam pa
NK106(me)001:1337: ci shar yang skad cig de la der 'dzin med
NK106(me)001:1338: par rang gis rang grol bas gnyen po gzhan med
NK106(me)001:1339: cing dus la snga phyi med pas skad cig rang
NK106(me)001:1340: grol ba ni / kun byed las /
NK106(me)001:1341: grol ba rang grol gzhan las min //
NK106(me)001:1343: mi zad pa'i gter mdzod man ngag gi glu las /
NK106(me)001:1344: skad cig grol ba de la chos kyi sku zhes bya //
NK106(me)001:1345: grol ba de las gzhan pa'i bde chen sa yod ces //
NK106(me)001:1346: byis pa rnams kyis smras kyang smig rgyu'i chu dang mtshungs //
NK106(me)001:1348: ji srid sems las rnam 'phros pas //
NK106(me)001:1349: de srid mgon po'i bdag nyid de //
NK106(me)001:1350: chu dang rlabs dag gzhan yin nam //
NK106(me)001:1352: blta bya lta byed dang bral bar la bzla ba ni /
NK106(me)001:1353: de'ang nyams su myong ba 'di ltar shar ro //
NK106(me)001:1354: dgag sgrub kyi blo rtog shar ba /
NK106(me)001:1355: gang du bltas tshe blta mkhan ngo bo stor //
NK106(me)001:1356: btsal bas mi rnyed yul dang phyogs na med //
NK106(me)001:1357: 'tshol mkhan nyid kyang mi dmigs spros dang bral //
NK106(me)001:1358: byed po mi gnas bya ba'i yul gyis stong //
NK106(me)001:1359: ji ltar shar ba de la bltas pas blta mkhan
NK106(me)001:1360: rang sar bor nas gang du bor btsal bas phyogs
NK106(me)001:1361: dang yul na med par ma zad 'tshol mkhan de
NK106(me)001:1362: nyid kyang mi dmigs par phyam gdal bas tshol bar
NK106(me)001:1364: btsal bya'i dgag sgrub gnyis ka rjes med du //
NK106(me)001:1365: song nas ci yin ngos gzung med pa ni kho bo'i sems te nam mkha' lta bu ni /
NK106(me)001:1367: ma gnas mi rtogs cir yang dgongs med pas //
NK106(me)001:1368: mi rtog mnyam pa'i yul la rang bzhin gnas //
NK106(me)001:1369: ye nas byas zin rtsol ba'i sems mi 'byung //
NK106(me)001:1370: bde chen de la gang su gnas pa ni //
NK106(me)001:1371: chos rnams kun gyi snying por de 'gyur ro //
NK106(me)001:1372: zhes pa thog tu phebs so //
NK106(me)001:1373: gzhi thog tu phebs pas blta ba'i gnas med par la bzla ba ni /
NK106(me)001:1374: de'i tshe sems nyid nam mkha' dang dbyer mi phyed
NK106(me)001:1375: pa'i dgongs par lhun gyis grub pas chos sku rang
NK106(me)001:1376: gnas kyi btsan sa zin tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:1378: mkha' bzhin dri med gdod ma'i ngang du phyin //
NK106(me)001:1379: ldog pa'i gnas med da ni gang du 'gro //
NK106(me)001:1380: zad sar thug ste 'ong ba 'ga' yang med //
NK106(me)001:1381: sus kyang mi mthong kho bo gang na 'dug /
NK106(me)001:1382: ces rtogs pa mtha' dbus med pa rdo rje'i glus ngom pa'o //
NK106(me)001:1383: de'ang gang shar gzhi thog tu grol ba mkha' la
NK106(me)001:1384: sprin dengs pa 'dra ba'i rtogs pa skyes pa de'i
NK106(me)001:1385: tshe / sems nyid gdod ma'i dbyings dang rang shar rang grol gyi ye shes 'dres pas /
NK106(me)001:1386: sems nyid gnas lugs kyi ngang las phyir ldog pa'i
NK106(me)001:1387: sa'am gnas med pa ni chos zad pa'i sa la
NK106(me)001:1388: thug pas 'phral byung dgag sgrub kyi shes pa dngos
NK106(me)001:1389: po mtshan 'dzin gyi 'phrang las grol te /
NK106(me)001:1390: da ni 'gro 'ong med pa'i chos nyid klungs su
NK106(me)001:1391: phebs pas gang du 'gro bar bya ste 'gro sa
NK106(me)001:1392: med ces bya'o // de lta bu'i ngang du phyin
NK106(me)001:1393: pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams ni 'khrul pa'i yul las
NK106(me)001:1394: 'das pas 'khor ba'i grong du 'ong ba 'ga' yang
NK106(me)001:1395: med de nam mkha' lta bu'i gzhi la phyin pa'i
NK106(me)001:1396: med ces bya'o // phyir ro // des na kho
NK106(me)001:1397: bo'i sems nyid dbyings su phyin pa'i dus 'di na
NK106(me)001:1398: sprin mkha' la zhi ba bzhin 'dzin rtog gdod ma'i
NK106(me)001:1399: gzhir dag pas sgo gsum rtsol med du grol te
NK106(me)001:1400: kho bo gang na 'dug pa'i don mthong ngam ste
NK106(me)001:1401: med ces bya'o // phyir ro // / skal pa
NK106(me)001:1402: dman pa dag la bshad kyang ji lta ba bzhin
NK106(me)001:1403: mi mthong ba'i don rang gis nges pa'i dus so
NK106(me)001:1404: med ces bya'o // phyir ro // / // kun byed las /
NK106(me)001:1405: bde chen chos sku sems su rdzogs pa'i phyir //
NK106(me)001:1406: snga phyi dus gsum med de khyab par cig /
NK106(me)001:1409: kye lags dbang pos ltos shig dang //
NK106(me)001:1410: ngas ni 'di las ma rtogs so //
NK106(me)001:1411: las zin pa yi skyes bu yi //
NK106(me)001:1412: drung du sems thag gcad par byos //
NK106(me)001:1413: zhes pa thog tu phebs pa'i dus so //
NK106(me)001:1414: spyi don bdun pa rtogs pas thag gcad pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1416: de nyid shes na gzhan zhig dgos mi 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:1417: grol ba rnams ni nga bzhin 'khrul pa chad //
NK106(me)001:1418: da ni mi 'dri sems kyi gzhi rtsa stor //
NK106(me)001:1419: gtad med 'dzin med nges med 'di yin med //
NK106(me)001:1420: phyal ba lhug pa yengs pa phyam gcig pa //
NK106(me)001:1421: 'di ltar rtogs nas da ni glu len te //
NK106(me)001:1422: dri med 'od zer shar bas bstan nas song //
NK106(me)001:1423: zhes pa ni gnas lugs kyi phu thag 'khrus pas gzhan la smon pa med pa'idusa te /
NK106(me)001:1424: rnal 'byor pa gzhan dag grol ba rnams kyang ngas
NK106(me)001:1425: ji ltar rtogs pa'i tshul 'di rtogs pas grol bas
NK106(me)001:1426: na / da ni 'dri ba'i the tshom med de
NK106(me)001:1427: de las lhag pa sus kyang bstan rgyu med pa'i
NK106(me)001:1428: na / phyir ro // do ha las /
NK106(me)001:1429: mdun dang rgyab dang phyogs bcu ru //
NK106(me)001:1430: gang gang mthong ba de de nyid //
NK106(me)001:1431: di ring mgon po nga ltar 'khrul pa chad //
NK106(me)001:1432: nga ni su la'ang dri bar mi bya'o //
NK106(me)001:1433: zhes pa dang tshul gcig go //
NK106(me)001:1434: sngon lta sgom spyod pa'i go rims dang khrigs shin
NK106(me)001:1435: tu legs pas sa lam gong 'og gi rim pa
NK106(me)001:1436: skas kyi gdang bu lta bu la brten zhing /
NK106(me)001:1437: rnal 'byor gong 'og gi skye tshul la blo goms
NK106(me)001:1438: 'dris su byed pa rnams dus 'dir sems kyi gzhi
NK106(me)001:1439: rtsa stor ba dang mnyam du stor bas /
NK106(me)001:1440: da ni gang la'ang gtad so dang 'dir rgyag med de /
NK106(me)001:1441: ji ltar shar yang 'dzin pa med pa smyon pa chang gis bzi ba lta bu dang /
NK106(me)001:1442: snang la ngos gzung med pa bu chung lta bu dang /
NK106(me)001:1443: bya cha'i rim pa rnams khrigs su med pas phyal ba dang /
NK106(me)001:1446: gtad so med pas zhe 'dzin las 'das par phyam
NK106(me)001:1447: gcig pa ste ya cha ba'i rnam pa zhig bdag
NK106(me)001:1450: yid bzhin nor bu lta bu'i dgongs pa bzhin //
NK106(me)001:1451: 'khrul pa zhig pa'i mkhas pa ngo mtshar che //
NK106(me)001:1453: gang shar chos nyid du shar bas 'khrul pa gzhi
NK106(me)001:1454: la sangs pa yul med nam mkha' lta bu'i dgongs
NK106(me)001:1455: par phyin pas las dang 'du byed thams cad grol
NK106(me)001:1457: 'gro rnams las kyis so sor bcings gyur te //
NK106(me)001:1458: las las grol na yid ni thar pa yin //
NK106(me)001:1459: rang rgyud grol na nges par gzhan med de //
NK106(me)001:1460: mchog gi mya ngan 'das pa thob par 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:1462: de'ang ci byed gtan med du grol bas 'dzin med shugs la byung bas 'ching grol med pa yang /
NK106(me)001:1464: bya ba byed dang bya ba mi byed pa //
NK106(me)001:1465: nges par rtogs na 'ching dang grol ba med //
NK106(me)001:1466: ces pa thog tu phebs dus bla ma'i dgongs pa 'phos pas grol ba yang //
NK106(me)001:1468: gdod nas skye med rang bzhin yin pa la //
NK106(me)001:1469: di ring dpal ldan bla mas bstan pas rtogs //
NK106(me)001:1471: tshul 'di ltar gyur pas sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes gnyug ma don gyi glu len zhing /
NK106(me)001:1472: gnas lugs yin min las 'das pa rgya chad phyogs
NK106(me)001:1473: bral chen po'i gnad rtogs pa nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor
NK106(me)001:1474: dri ma med pa'i 'od zer stong shar bas skal
NK106(me)001:1475: bzang gi 'jig rten du snang bar byas te blo
NK106(me)001:1476: gsal thar pa 'dod pa'i pad tshal du bstan nas
NK106(me)001:1477: bed chen kun du bzang po'i sa la song ngo
NK106(me)001:1479: spyi don brgyad pa snang sems ye grol du bshad pa la /
NK106(me)001:1480: rdzogs pa chen por la bzla ba /
NK106(me)001:1481: rmad byung chen por 'ub chub pa /
NK106(me)001:1482: de dag gi mjug bsdu ba gsum gyi /
NK106(me)001:1484: snang ba'i yul stong par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1485: da ni snang sems ye grol du gdams pa 'chad de /
NK106(me)001:1486: de'ang gshis rdzogs pa chen por la bzla ba /
NK106(me)001:1487: kye ho grogs dag snang ba'i yul la ltos //
NK106(me)001:1488: thams cad ma skyes stong par mnyam pa nyid //
NK106(me)001:1489: me long gzugs brnyan sna tshogs ci shar yang //
NK106(me)001:1490: me long ngos yin dngas par gcig pa bzhin //
NK106(me)001:1491: 'di ltar me long du shar ba'i gzugs brnyan me long gi ngos su dngas par gcig gi /
NK106(me)001:1492: don la me long gi mdangs las gzugs med pa
NK106(me)001:1493: bzhin du snang srid kyi chos thams cad kyang rang
NK106(me)001:1494: bzhin stong pa nyid las gzhan med de /
NK106(me)001:1495: ljon pas zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:1496: me long dkyil 'khor yongs dag la //
NK106(me)001:1497: bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor snang ba ltar //
NK106(me)001:1498: de ltar rang bzhin ma grub pa'i //
NK106(me)001:1499: chos rnams ljon pas shes par gyis //
NK106(me)001:1501: 'byed pa'i sems stong par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1502: snang ba rang bzhin med par spyod dus /
NK106(me)001:1504: de nyid 'byed pa' yid la tshur ltos dang //
NK106(me)001:1505: sems ni mkha' 'dra dgag sgrub kun dang bral //
NK106(me)001:1506: mkha' la sprin rnams byung nas zhig na yang //
NK106(me)001:1507: nam mkha'i cho 'phrul gnyis med dag pa bzhin //
NK106(me)001:1508: rang bzhin dri med gdod ma'i sangs rgyas te //
NK106(me)001:1509: ma byas lhun gyis grub pa'i chos nyid do //
NK106(me)001:1510: de'ang lta byed kyi shes pa yul thog tu grol
NK106(me)001:1511: zhing yul snang gi rnam pa 'dzin med du sangs
NK106(me)001:1512: pa ni / nam mkha' la sprin byung nas dengs
NK106(me)001:1513: pa na sprin nam mkha'i dbyings las gud du ma
NK106(me)001:1514: song bzhin du rang thim nas mi snang ba ltar
NK106(me)001:1515: pa ni / / shes pa yul thog tu grol
NK106(me)001:1516: bas dus gsum nam mkha'i dgongs par phyin pa ste
NK106(me)001:1517: pa ni / / / ting nge 'dzin rgyal po las /
NK106(me)001:1518: ji ltar bar snang cung zad sprin med la //
NK106(me)001:1519: skad cig tu ni sprin gyi dkyil 'khor snang //
NK106(me)001:1520: byung nas zhig ste sprin gyi dkyil 'khor med //
NK106(me)001:1521: thog mar gang las byung ba brtag par bya //
NK106(me)001:1522: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin shes par gyis //
NK106(me)001:1524: rnam pa gcig tu chos thams cad dang po yang dbyings skye med las byung /
NK106(me)001:1527: gang shar gyi shes pa de yang dang po sems nyid stong pa'i ngang nas byung /
