NK106(me)001:1529: mthar yang der 'gag ces shes par bya'o //
NK106(me)001:1530: de lta bu'i rang bzhin ye nas sangs rgyas yin par /
NK106(me)001:1532: sems nyid nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin ni //
NK106(me)001:1533: ye nas sangs rgyas snying po byang chub la //
NK106(me)001:1534: rtsol zhing bsgrubs pas sangs rgyas 'grub pa med //
NK106(me)001:1535: ma byas rang bzhin dag pa'i ngang der zhog /
NK106(me)001:1537: yul sems gnyis med stong par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1539: yul sems gnyis med ye nas dag pa la //
NK106(me)001:1540: spang blang gnyis med phyogs ris dgag sgrub med //
NK106(me)001:1541: gang snang bden med gang shar stong pa nyid //
NK106(me)001:1542: thams cad mnyam nyid gza' gtad kun dang bral //
NK106(me)001:1543: de'ang snang ba'i yul dang 'dzin byed kyi shes pa'ang
NK106(me)001:1544: rmi lam gyi nang ltar don la gnyis su med
NK106(me)001:1545: la snang bas na spang blang dang dgag sgrub med
NK106(me)001:1548: de bzhin nyid du gcig pa yis //
NK106(me)001:1549: chos nyid yul ni lnga snang la //
NK106(me)001:1551: de bzhin nyid la blang dor byed //
NK106(me)001:1552: rang byung ye shes snang ba ste //
NK106(me)001:1553: rang gi rkyen gyis dor mi btub //
NK106(me)001:1554: mi btub dor bar byed pas 'khor //
NK106(me)001:1556: des na gang snang yang bden pas stong pa smig
NK106(me)001:1557: rgyu'i chu ltar shes nas chos thams cad snang mnyam
NK106(me)001:1558: gzugs brnyan lta bu'i ngo bor blo gza' gtad dang
NK106(me)001:1559: bral ba la sbyang bar bya'o //
NK106(me)001:1560: yul nges med dang blo gtad med du bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1562: yul la nges med snang ba sna tshogs ltar //
NK106(me)001:1563: blo la gtad med phyogs bral chen po nyid //
NK106(me)001:1564: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen por shes par bya //
NK106(me)001:1565: 'di ltar snang ba gcig tu ma nges par sna tshogs pa ltar //
NK106(me)001:1566: de 'dzin pa'i shes pa'ang gza' gtad med pa phyogs
NK106(me)001:1567: bral nyag gcig tu grol ba rang bzhin rdzogs pa
NK106(me)001:1570: ji ltar snang ba nges med lta //
NK106(me)001:1571: blo yang gtad med phyogs lhung bral //
NK106(me)001:1572: bzo med nam mkha' chen po ni //
NK106(me)001:1573: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'o //
NK106(me)001:1575: de dag gi rgyu mtshan bshad pa /
NK106(me)001:1577: 'di ltar snang srid 'khor 'das chos rnams la //
NK106(me)001:1578: 'das pa'i chos rnams mi dmigs mnyam pa nyid //
NK106(me)001:1579: ma 'ongs chos rnams ma skyes mnyam pa nyid //
NK106(me)001:1580: da lta'i chos rnams mi gnas mnyam pa nyid //
NK106(me)001:1581: dus gsum dus med gzhi bral mnyam pa nyid //
NK106(me)001:1582: thams cad ye nas rdzogs pa'i ngang nyid do //
NK106(me)001:1583: 'di ltar mnyam pa nyid lngar chos thams cad mnyam
NK106(me)001:1584: pas blang dor bzang ngan med par shes par bya
NK106(me)001:1585: ste / snang srid kyi chos 'di dag sngar 'das
NK106(me)001:1586: 'gags pas 'ong ba'am phyir log nas mi 'ong bar
NK106(me)001:1587: ste / mnyam / ma 'ongs pa ma skyes pas phyogs na med par mnyam /
NK106(me)001:1588: da lta ba phyi nang ngo bo ngos gzung rig
NK106(me)001:1589: pas brtags na mi rnyed la ma brtags na snang
NK106(me)001:1590: bar mnyam ste / mtshan brjod las /
NK106(me)001:1591: dus gsum dus med rtogs par gnas //
NK106(me)001:1593: dus gsum yang dus su ma grub par 'brel pa gzhi nas med pas stong par mnyam /
NK106(me)001:1594: thams cad skye ba med cing skye med kyi ngang las byung /
NK106(me)001:1596: ngang du 'gag pa ltar snang dus nyid nas gang du'ang ma grub par mnyam pa nyid do //
NK106(me)001:1599: chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid pas shes rab kyi
NK106(me)001:1600: pha rol tu phyin pa yang mnyam pa nyid do
NK106(me)001:1601: zhes pa dang / chos nyid mi g.yo ba'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:1602: chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis ma skyes pa /
NK106(me)001:1603: ngo bo nyid kyis mi g.yo ba /
NK106(me)001:1604: bya ba'i mtha' dang bral ba /
NK106(me)001:1606: gzod ma nas mnyam pa nyid do zhes so //
NK106(me)001:1607: sems nyid 'gyur med du bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1609: snang srid 'khor 'das sems kyi gzugs brnyan te //
NK106(me)001:1610: sems kyi rang bzhin chos dbyings nam mkha' che //
NK106(me)001:1611: nam mkha'i rang bzhin dus gsum 'pho 'gyur med //
NK106(me)001:1612: 'gyur med rang bzhin gzod nas mya ngan 'das //
NK106(me)001:1613: gzhi nas byang chub kun tu bzang po yin //
NK106(me)001:1614: de'ang ji ltar snang ba bag chags 'khrul pa'i gzugs
NK106(me)001:1615: brnyan me long gi ngos la shar ba lta bu
NK106(me)001:1617: sems ni ri mo mkhan dang 'dra //
NK106(me)001:1618: sems kyis phung por byas pa ste //
NK106(me)001:1619: 'jig rten khams ni ji snyed pa //
NK106(me)001:1620: de dag sems kyis bris pa yin //
NK106(me)001:1622: snod 'jig pa la bcud 'jig pa brten pa'i snang
NK106(me)001:1623: srid thams cad 'khrul pa'i sems kyi bag chags goms
NK106(me)001:1624: pas rmi lam ltar snang ba thams cad snang dus
NK106(me)001:1625: nyid nas ma grub pa yin no //
NK106(me)001:1626: des na snang ba sems kyi 'khrul snang du thag bcad pa'o //
NK106(me)001:1627: snang ba 'dzin pa'i sems stong par thag bcad pa ni nam mkha' lta bu ste /
NK106(me)001:1629: sems ni nam mkha' lta bur gzung bya ste //
NK106(me)001:1630: nam mkha'i rang bzhin nyid du sems gzung bya //
NK106(me)001:1632: nam mkha' 'gyur med du thag gcad pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1634: ji ltar nam mkha' 'pho 'gyur med pa bzhin //
NK106(me)001:1635: sems nyid nam mkha'i rang bzhin 'gyur ba med //
NK106(me)001:1637: 'gyur ba med pa'i don de nyid gzod ma nas
NK106(me)001:1638: zhi zhing mya ngan las 'das pa kun tu bzang
NK106(me)001:1639: po'i rang bzhin yin pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1641: sems nyid mi 'gyur gdod nas dag pa 'di //
NK106(me)001:1642: snying po byang chub kun byed lhun gyis grub //
NK106(me)001:1645: snang stong dbyer med gdod mar mnyam par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1646: de bas na chos thams cad ye 'byams rmad du
NK106(me)001:1647: byung ba rdzogs pa chen por 'ub chub pa ni
NK106(me)001:1648: / snang dang stong pa dbyer med gdod ma'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:1649: gcig dang du mar mi dmigs spros dang bral //
NK106(me)001:1650: phyogs dang ris med thams cad mnyam pa nyid //
NK106(me)001:1651: snang mnyam stong mnyam bden mnyam brdzun par mnyam //
NK106(me)001:1652: yod mnyam med mnyam mtha' las 'das par mnyam //
NK106(me)001:1653: dbyings gcig gdod nas dag pa'i ngang nyid do //
NK106(me)001:1654: 'di ltar chos thams cad snang stong gnyis su med
NK106(me)001:1655: pa gcig dang du ma'i spros pa las 'das pas
NK106(me)001:1656: phyogs char chad pa med de nam mkha' lta bu'i
NK106(me)001:1659: chos kun nam mkha'i rang bzhin te //
NK106(me)001:1660: nam mkha' la ni rang bzhin med //
NK106(me)001:1661: nam mkha' la ni dpe yang med //
NK106(me)001:1662: nam mkha' la ni tshad kyang med //
NK106(me)001:1663: chos rnams thams cad ma lus pa'i //
NK106(me)001:1664: don ni 'di ltar shes par gyis //
NK106(me)001:1666: de ltar nam mkha' don du mnyam pa ltar snang
NK106(me)001:1667: bar mnyam pa me long nang gi gzugs brnyan lta
NK106(me)001:1668: bu / stong par mnyam pa de la gzugs rang mtshan du med pa lta bu /
NK106(me)001:1669: blo 'khrul ngor don byed nus tsam du bden par
NK106(me)001:1670: mnyam pa gzugs dang gzugs brnyan gnyis ka mig shes
NK106(me)001:1671: la gzugs 'dzin gyi shes pa bskyed nus lta bu
NK106(me)001:1672: / brdzun par mnyam pa gshis med pa'i ngang der
NK106(me)001:1673: 'khrul snang d+ha du ra zos pa'i snang ba lta
NK106(me)001:1674: / bu / yod par mnyam pa snang tsam dor ba sprul pa lta bu /
NK106(me)001:1675: med par mnyam pa rang bzhin ma grub pas smig rgyu'i chu lta bu /
NK106(me)001:1676: mtha' 'das su mnyam pa nam mkha' yangs pa'i ngang lta bu /
NK106(me)001:1677: gdod nas mnyam pa chos nyid dbye bsal las 'das
NK106(me)001:1678: pa'i dbyings dpe dang bral ba ste gzod ma nas
NK106(me)001:1679: stong pa ni / 'phags pa dkon mchog sprin gyi mdo las /
NK106(me)001:1680: gzod ma nyid nas stong zhing ma 'ongs chos //
NK106(me)001:1681: song ba med cing gnas med gnas kyis dben //
NK106(me)001:1682: sgyu ma'i rang bzhin rtag tu snying po med //
NK106(me)001:1683: thams cad dag cing rnam dag nam mkha' bzhin //
NK106(me)001:1684: rgyal ba'i chos ni gang dag rab ston pa //
NK106(me)001:1685: de yang mi zad pas na mi mthong ste //
NK106(me)001:1686: chos 'di snga nas bdag med sems can med //
NK106(me)001:1687: de dag rab tu ston kyang zad mi 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:1688: rtag pa tsam du brtags nas bstan pa yin //
NK106(me)001:1689: 'khor ba la ni tha snyad mi rnyed de //
NK106(me)001:1690: gang dag sngon byung mtha' ni mtshan nyid med //
NK106(me)001:1691: ma 'ongs dus kyang shes par bya ba'i phyir //
NK106(me)001:1692: las dang bya ba de ltar zhugs gyur te //
NK106(me)001:1693: rab dang tha ma dag tu'ang 'byung bar 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:1694: chos rnams rtag tu zhi zhing rang bzhin stong //
NK106(me)001:1695: thams cad bdag med par yang shes par gyis //
NK106(me)001:1697: tshul 'di zla ba sgron ma las kyang bshad do //
NK106(me)001:1698: blos btags thams cad ngo bos stong par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1700: blo yis btags pa thams cad ngo bos stong //
NK106(me)001:1701: ming rnams glo bur rang mtshan sgro btags nyid //
NK106(me)001:1702: bden brdzun gnyis med yul sems 'brel pa med //
NK106(me)001:1703: gcig gis gcig la ma gos gzung 'dzin med //
NK106(me)001:1704: de yang phung po dang khams la sogs pa'i grub mtha' ni blos btags nas bshad de /
NK106(me)001:1705: blos btags pa de nyid chos rnams la med pas kyang ngo bos stong la /
NK106(me)001:1706: ming du btags pa thams cad don de'i phyi nang
NK106(me)001:1707: gang na'ang med pas glo bur ba ste ma grub
NK106(me)001:1708: la / don rang mtshan no zhes btags pa'ang ming dang rtog pa'i ri mor zad cing /
NK106(me)001:1709: 'dogs yul bud shing las skyes pa'i me lta bu
NK106(me)001:1710: la 'dod kyang rmi lam gyi me ltar bag chags
NK106(me)001:1711: 'khrul pa'i snang gzugs las gshis la ma grub pas
NK106(me)001:1712: snang srid 'khrul ngor snang ba thams cad sgro btags
NK106(me)001:1714: yul ji ltar snang dus nas brdzun mnyam 'ba' zhig las /
NK106(me)001:1715: bden pa dang brdzun pa gnyis su med cing /
NK106(me)001:1716: snang ba'i yul dang der 'dzin gyi shes pa'ang dpyad
NK106(me)001:1717: na gcig gis gcig la ma gos pas 'brel pa
NK106(me)001:1718: med de / yul dang yul can dpyad na nam
NK106(me)001:1719: mkha' lta bu yin pas 'brel yul dang 'brel por
NK106(me)001:1720: med pa'i phyir 'brel pa don la med do //
NK106(me)001:1721: 'brel pa med par ma zad spyi dang bye brag
NK106(me)001:1722: ces blos bkod pa'ang don rang mtshan la med de
NK106(me)001:1723: spyi bye brag tu ma brtags sam brtags pas 'phel
NK106(me)001:1724: 'grib mi byed par mnyam pa'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)001:1725: de ltar dpyad pas brjod don 'brel med la gzung
NK106(me)001:1726: 'dzin gnyis bcas su 'dzin don med pa la rmongs
NK106(me)001:1727: pas 'dzin pa thams cad 'khrul par bstan pa yin
NK106(me)001:1728: no // de'ang bu chung gi dus na de lta
NK106(me)001:1729: bu'i grub mtha' dang rnam dbye sgro btags med pa
NK106(me)001:1730: no // las / phyis sgro btags goms pa ni
NK106(me)001:1731: grub mtha' ngan pa'i don thos pa las byung ba'i
NK106(me)001:1732: no // las / sgrib pa ste / rnam nges las /
NK106(me)001:1733: skye bo reng bur skye 'gyur zhing //
NK106(me)001:1734: yon tan nyes pa ma mthong la //
NK106(me)001:1735: kye ma grub mtha' mi bzad pa'i //
NK106(me)001:1736: gdon 'di su yis bgos pa yin //
NK106(me)001:1740: chos thams cad ni brda tsam btags pa tsam mo //
NK106(me)001:1741: brda tsam btags pa tsam gang yin pa de ni
NK106(me)001:1742: glo bur ba ste ngo bo nyid kyis stong pa
NK106(me)001:1744: sems 'phos pa med cing yul shar ba med par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1745: 'brel pa med pa la ma 'dzin cig par gdams pa'i dpe ni /
NK106(me)001:1746: ji ltar me long gzugs bzhin snang ba ni //
NK106(me)001:1747: yul gyi rnam pa dbang po'i shes la shar //
NK106(me)001:1748: de nyid gzung bas chags sdang srid par 'khrul //
NK106(me)001:1749: nan ltar gtugs na sems ni ma 'phos shing //
NK106(me)001:1750: yul gyi rnam pa'ang sems la shar ba med //
NK106(me)001:1751: ngo bo med phyir gnyis su ma grub bo //
NK106(me)001:1752: re zhig go sla bas grags pa dang sbyar na /
NK106(me)001:1753: me long du bzhin gyi gzugs brnyan snang dus rang
NK106(me)001:1754: gi byad dang gzugs brnyan gnyis su song ba'am byad
NK106(me)001:1755: las gzugs brnyan yul la ma 'phos bzhin du snang
NK106(me)001:1756: ba ltar sna tshogs su dbang po'i yul tshogs drug
NK106(me)001:1757: so sor snang ba la ni /
NK106(me)001:1758: sems de phar yul de la 'phos pa ma yin gyi /
NK106(me)001:1759: yul gyi rnam pa dbang shes la snang ba ste /
NK106(me)001:1760: byad me long du snang ba'ang 'phos pa ma yin gyi /
NK106(me)001:1761: byad kyi gzugs brnyan nam rnam pa der snang ba dang 'dra bar shes par bya'o //
NK106(me)001:1762: des na rnam pa shar dus blos gzung bas srid par 'khrul lo //
NK106(me)001:1763: de'ang don du dpyad na sems phar ma 'phos rnam pa tshur la shar zhes pa'ang ma grub ste /
NK106(me)001:1764: shar ba'i sems phyi nang bar gsum du ma grub pas kyang rnam pa 'dzin byed med pa dang /
NK106(me)001:1765: rnam pa de'ang dpyad na ngo bo med pas shar mkhan ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)001:1766: yul dang yul can gnyis bcas su ma grub pa 'thad pa dang bcas pa ste /
NK106(me)001:1768: gang la brten te gang 'byung ba //
NK106(me)001:1769: de ni re zhig de nyid min //
NK106(me)001:1770: de las gzhan yang ma yin phyir //
NK106(me)001:1771: de phyir chad min rtag ma yin //
NK106(me)001:1773: yul sems rang bzhin med pas rang grol du bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1774: tshul de ltar na snang ba'i /
NK106(me)001:1775: yul rnams thams cad rang bzhin med par gcig /
NK106(me)001:1776: blo rnams thams cad ngos gzung med par gcig /
NK106(me)001:1777: snang sems gnyis med gdod nas dag par gcig /
NK106(me)001:1778: brtag dpyad mi dgos gzhi nas grol bar gcig /'di
NK106(me)001:1779: ltar sna tshogs su snang ba thams cad rang bzhin
NK106(me)001:1780: med pa'i ngang du gcig pa rmi lam sna tshogs
NK106(me)001:1781: gnyid kyi ngang du gcig pa lta bu dang /
NK106(me)001:1782: snang ba la 'char 'char 'dra ba'i blo rnams ngo
NK106(me)001:1783: bo ngos gzung med pa'i ngang du gcig pa dba'
NK106(me)001:1784: rlabs chu'i ngang du gcig pa lta bu dang /
NK106(me)001:1785: snang sems gnyis su med pa chos nyid kyi ngang
NK106(me)001:1786: du gcig pa rab rib dang de 'dzin pa'i mig
NK106(me)001:1787: shes 'khrul par gcig pa lta bu dang /
NK106(me)001:1788: gang la'ang brtag dpyad mi dgos pa nam mkha'i skyed
NK106(me)001:1789: tshal brtag dpyad kyi yul las 'das pa lta bu
NK106(me)001:1790: rnams ni gshis nam mkha'i ngang du bstan pa nyid
NK106(me)001:1792: ji ltar khyod kyi bdag gi 'du shes ni //
NK106(me)001:1793: shes pa de bzhin kun la blo sbyang bya //
NK106(me)001:1794: chos rnams thams cad stong pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK106(me)001:1795: rnam par dag pa nam mkha' lta bu yin //
NK106(me)001:1798: 'di ltar snang srid chos rnams thams cad kun //
NK106(me)001:1799: skye ba med pa'i ngang du gcig pas na //
NK106(me)001:1800: gzung 'dzin mi dmigs rtog pa'i smra bsam 'das //
NK106(me)001:1801: dbyings gcig nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin no //
NK106(me)001:1803: gang shar rang grol du rtogs na mkhas par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1805: 'khor 'das gnyis med sems kyi ngang du gcig /
NK106(me)001:1806: chu bo sna tshogs rgya mtsho'i ngang du gcig /
NK106(me)001:1807: thams cad ro mnyam lhan cig skyes par gcig /'byung bzhi'i 'pho 'gyur nam mkha'i ngang du gcig /
NK106(me)001:1808: sems kyi dgag sgrub stong pa'i ngang du gcig /
NK106(me)001:1809: gang shar rang grol gnyis med dag par gcig /
NK106(me)001:1810: dba' rlabs rol pa chu bo'i ngang du gcig /
NK106(me)001:1811: de ltar rtogs na skyes bu mkhas pa yin //
NK106(me)001:1812: de'ang phyogs bzhi nas 'bab pa'i chu rnams rgya mtshor gcig pa ltar /
NK106(me)001:1813: 'khor 'das sems kyi ngang du gcig pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1815: snang srid snod bcud sangs rgyas sems can kun //
NK106(me)001:1816: sems kyis byas shing sems kyi ngang du gcig /
NK106(me)001:1818: 'byung bzhi'i 'pho 'gyur thams cad nam mkha'i ngang las ma g.yos pa ltar /
NK106(me)001:1819: lta sgom spyod 'bras nyams myong gi rnam pa ci
NK106(me)001:1820: shar gnyug ma lhan cig skyes par gcig pa ste
NK106(me)001:1822: gang las gnyug ma lhan cig skyes //
NK106(me)001:1823: thams cad ro mnyam ngang der gcig /
NK106(me)001:1825: sems la dgag sgrub shar ba stong par gcig pa'ang
NK106(me)001:1826: de nyid lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes las la
NK106(me)001:1828: dba' rlabs chur gcig pa ltar gang shar skye med
NK106(me)001:1829: du gcig pa yang sems kyi spros pa sems nyid
NK106(me)001:1830: kyi ngang / sems nyid ye nas spro bsdu med pa'i ngang ste /
NK106(me)001:1832: spros pa nyid nas spros med //
NK106(me)001:1834: de'ang rnam rtog gzhi thim la song ba chu la chu 'dres pa lta bu ste /
NK106(me)001:1836: ji ltar chu la chu bzhag na //
NK106(me)001:1837: de snyed chu ru ro mnyam 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:1838: skyon dang yon tan rnam ldan sems //
NK106(me)001:1839: mgon po sus kyang mthong mi 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:1841: mgon po sems nyid spros pa med pa ste mthong yul las 'das pa'o //
NK106(me)001:1842: tshul de ltar shes na mkhas pa zhes bya ste /
NK106(me)001:1844: don la rnam par dpyod pa ni mkhas pa yin
NK106(me)001:1845: gyi tshig la rtog pas ma yin no zhes gsungs
NK106(me)001:1846: pa bzhin no // gsum pa la gnyis las /
NK106(me)001:1847: blang dor med pa'i don la gzung 'dzin med par gdams pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1848: da ni mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK106(me)001:1849: sna tshogs ngos gzung med pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK106(me)001:1850: rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i gzugs brnyan te //
NK106(me)001:1851: bzang ngan blang dor med pa'i rol pa la //
NK106(me)001:1852: blo yis gnyis su ma 'dzin gang bder zhog /
NK106(me)001:1853: ji lta ba ngo bo nyid nas dag pa'i rol
NK106(me)001:1854: par shar bas bya btsal dran bsam las 'das pa
NK106(me)001:1855: gnyis med bde ba chen por gzhag pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1857: ma skyes rnam par dag pa'i chos nyid la //
NK106(me)001:1858: skye ba dngos por snang ba'i gzugs brnyan shar //
NK106(me)001:1859: ji ltar skyes pa rang bzhin gnyis med pas //
NK106(me)001:1860: ji bzhin rtsol bral bde ba chen por zhog /
NK106(me)001:1862: 'dzin med rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen por bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1864: gtad med yul la nges med snang ba shar //
NK106(me)001:1865: 'dzin med rig pa rnam yan chen po ni //
NK106(me)001:1866: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i gnas lugs yin //
NK106(me)001:1867: gang la'ang dgag pa dang bsgrub pa de'i tshe 'dzin
NK106(me)001:1868: med kyi rig pa rang yan du shar bas rdzogs
NK106(me)001:1869: pa chen po'i ngang du lhun gyis grub ste /
NK106(me)001:1871: kye nga ni kun byed rgyal po byang chub sems //
NK106(me)001:1872: nga la sgro dang skur pa'i yul med pas //
NK106(me)001:1873: gang la sems par ma byed sgom ma byed //
NK106(me)001:1874: sgo gsum ma bcos ji bzhin lhug par zhog /
NK106(me)001:1875: ji ltar shar ba rang bzhin ngang gis grol //
NK106(me)001:1876: skye med nam mkha' lta bur phyogs 'das pas //
NK106(me)001:1877: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen por shes par gyis //
NK106(me)001:1879: spyi don dgu pa skabs kyi dge ba bsngo ba ni /
NK106(me)001:1880: da ni dge ba bsngo ba /
NK106(me)001:1881: de ltar chos kun mnyam pa'i rang bzhin gyis //
NK106(me)001:1882: blo bral ngang du 'dzin med la bzlas nas //
NK106(me)001:1883: phyogs bral rig pa khol bur bcings pa yis //
NK106(me)001:1884: dub pa'i sems nyid di ring ngal sos shig /
NK106(me)001:1886: snying po'i don cig car du grol ba'i chos rmad
NK106(me)001:1887: du byung ba'i phreng ba bkod legs pa'i dge bas
NK106(me)001:1888: / 'gro ba gang dag dbyings phyogs bral chen po
NK106(me)001:1889: yin par khong du ma chud pas rang rang gi
NK106(me)001:1890: grub pa'i mtha' dang lta sgom gyi ra bar bcings
NK106(me)001:1891: / te / gshis bcings grol med pa'i dgongs par
NK106(me)001:1892: ma reg pas dgag sgrub la sogs pa'i 'ching ba
NK106(me)001:1893: / te / dang / bden zhen gyis dub pa
NK106(me)001:1894: dag gis blo bral gyi rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen
NK106(me)001:1895: po kun byed byang chub sems kyi nam mkha' yangs
NK106(me)001:1896: par ngal sos par shog cig ces pa'o //
NK106(me)001:1897: skye med mkha' la snying po'i sprin 'khrigs te //
NK106(me)001:1898: ji bzhin rtsol bral stong nyid 'brug sgrogs pas //
NK106(me)001:1899: sems nyid mi g.yo byang chub mchog gi sa //
NK106(me)001:1900: brjod med mnyam rdzogs snying po'i don mthong shog /'gro ba'i sems gang gzung 'dzin rgyar chud de //
NK106(me)001:1901: mkha' mnyam yangs pa chen po'i gnas bral ba //
NK106(me)001:1902: de kun ye rdzogs kun tu bzang po'i zhing //
NK106(me)001:1903: ma lus rang bzhin dag pa bgrod par shog /
NK106(me)001:1904: rtog pas sbyar ba'i rlung gis dkrugs pa'i chu //
NK106(me)001:1905: zab mo'i gzugs brnyan 'dzin pas ring ba kun //
NK106(me)001:1906: mi rtog rang byung ye shes mtsho bsil bas //
NK106(me)001:1907: dngas la mi g.yo lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK106(me)001:1908: rdzogs pa chen po sems nyid ngal gso las /
NK106(me)001:1909: gzhi rtogs pa'i shes rab mtha' gnyis la mi gnas pa'i le'u ste bcu pa'i 'grel pa'o ////
NK106(me)001:1910: de ltar chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin lta ba mtha' bral chen por gdeng bcas nas /
NK106(me)001:1911: bcu gcig pa sgom pa bsam gtan dri ma med pa'i le'u la spyi don bzhi ste /
NK106(me)001:1912: lta bas gtan la phab nas bsgom par bstan pa /
NK106(me)001:1913: gang gis bsgom pa'i dbang po'i rim pa bstan pa /
NK106(me)001:1914: ji ltar bsgom pa'i lam gyi rim pa bshad pa /
NK106(me)001:1915: skabs kyi dge ba bsngo ba'o //
NK106(me)001:1916: spyi don dang po lta bas gtan la phab nas bsgom par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1917: de ltar chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis ma skyes
NK106(me)001:1918: pa nam mkha' lta bu'i gnas lugs kyi rang bzhin
NK106(me)001:1919: lta ba mtha' bral chen po bshad nas /
NK106(me)001:1920: da ni sgom pa rang byung gi ye shes 'od gsal nyi zla lta bu ston pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1922: de ltar chos kun mnyam pa'i don mthong nas //
NK106(me)001:1923: gnas lugs ngang la ji bzhin gzhag pa gces //
NK106(me)001:1925: dang por lta bas mtha' chod nas sgom pas de'i ngang la mnyam par gzhag dgos te /
NK106(me)001:1926: de lta ma yin na nyon mongs pa'i tshogs las
NK106(me)001:1927: mi grol zhing sa dang lam gyi yon tan mi
NK106(me)001:1928: rdzogs pa'i phyir na nges par bsgom par bya'o //
NK106(me)001:1929: de'ang gnas lugs rang bzhin gyis dag pa nam mkha'
NK106(me)001:1930: lta bu'i ngang la blo re dogs kyi spros pa
NK106(me)001:1931: chod pa'i tshul gyis bzhag ste /
NK106(me)001:1933: kye sems dpa' rdo rje don la da sgoms shig /
NK106(me)001:1934: bsgom du med pa'i chos nyid byang chub la //
NK106(me)001:1935: bsgom dang bsgom par bya ba gnyis med pas //
NK106(me)001:1936: ma bsgoms rang bzhin bzhag na sgom pa yin //
NK106(me)001:1937: don ni kun don skye ba med pa ste //
NK106(me)001:1938: rnam rtog mtshan ma de bzhin rig byas na //
NK106(me)001:1939: dran bsam yid la 'gyu ba ma lus kun //
NK106(me)001:1940: skye ba med pa'i ngang las mi yengs pa //
NK106(me)001:1941: gang ltar bsams kyang sgom pa yin shes na //
NK106(me)001:1942: ma bsgoms gang ltar bzhag kyang yengs pa med //
NK106(me)001:1944: kye sems dpa' rdo rje legs par da sgoms shig /
NK106(me)001:1945: ji ltar snang grags chos rnams thams cad la //
NK106(me)001:1946: snying po rtogs goms don nyid gcig las med //
NK106(me)001:1947: snying po mngon du phyung nas gang bstan pa //
NK106(me)001:1948: rang bzhin skye ba med pa'i don du rtogs //
NK106(me)001:1949: ma yengs re dogs med na sgom pa yin //
NK106(me)001:1951: de'ang thos nas bsam pa dang de'i don bsgom pa la 'jug dgos te /
NK106(me)001:1952: snying po'i don rgyud la skye dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)001:1953: de kho na nyid nges par bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:1955: gang gis bskal pa bcu'i bar du mnyan pa bas /
NK106(me)001:1956: gang gis se gol gtogs pa tsam du de kho
NK106(me)001:1957: na nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin 'di bsgoms na de
NK106(me)001:1958: bas ches bsod nams mang du 'phel lo zhes so
NK106(me)001:1959: // spyi don gnyis pa gang gis bsgom pa'i dbang
NK106(me)001:1960: po'i rim pa bstan pa la rab 'bring tha gsum
NK106(me)001:1961: // gyi / dbang po rab la drug ste /
NK106(me)001:1962: yang rab rtogs pas grol bar bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1964: de yang dbang po'i rim pas bstan pa ste /
NK106(me)001:1965: dbang po yang rab gnas lugs rtogs pas grol //
NK106(me)001:1966: bsgom dang bsgom bya gnyis med don mthong nas //
NK106(me)001:1967: snang srid gzhi grol sems nyid bya rtsol med //
NK106(me)001:1968: phyogs bral rig pa chu bo'i rgyun bzhin 'char //
NK106(me)001:1969: 'di ltar sngon bsod nams bsags pa'i skal ldan dbang
NK106(me)001:1970: po yang rab pa rnams kyis sems nyid rnal ma'i
NK106(me)001:1971: don bsgom bya dang bsgom byed las 'das pa nam
NK106(me)001:1972: mkha' lta bu'i don bla ma dam pa'i rkyen gyis
NK106(me)001:1973: rtogs pa tsam gyis grol te /
NK106(me)001:1974: 'bad pa dang bcas nas bsgom mi dgos par sems
NK106(me)001:1975: nyid chu bo rgyun gyi rnal 'byor la dus thams
NK106(me)001:1976: cad du ngang gis gnas pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1978: kye ston pa kun byed nga yis lung bstan pa //
NK106(me)001:1979: ma lus skye med rnam dag ting 'dzin te //
NK106(me)001:1980: bsgom dang mi bsgom rkyen la rag ma lus //
NK106(me)001:1981: bsgom bya ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams kun //
NK106(me)001:1982: gang du ji ltar bzhag pa'i tshul med par //
NK106(me)001:1983: ma btsal rang sar grol bas bsgom pa yin //
NK106(me)001:1984: kye bsgom du med pa'i man ngag 'di dag la //
NK106(me)001:1985: tshig dang sgra las 'das pa'i don yin phyir //
NK106(me)001:1986: snga rabs kun byed rgyal pos lung ma bstan //
NK106(me)001:1987: phyi rabs kun byed rgyal pos lung mi ston //
NK106(me)001:1988: da lta kun byed rgyal pos lung bstan med //
NK106(me)001:1989: kye ston pa'i ston pa kun byed rgyal po yis //
NK106(me)001:1990: ma nor dgongs pa'i don la lung bstan pa //
NK106(me)001:1991: sgro skur 'das pa don gyi snying po la //
NK106(me)001:1992: bsgom dang mi bsgom mkha' la rtsod pa 'dra //
NK106(me)001:1994: klong gyur la bsgom bya bsgom byed dang bral bar bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:1995: de lta bu'i dgongs pa klong du gyur dus /
NK106(me)001:1997: thun mtshams ris med 'di yin ngos gzung med //
NK106(me)001:1998: thams cad rang grol kun tu bzang po'i zhing //
NK106(me)001:1999: rtags dang tshad med rang byung gzhi klong yangs //
NK106(me)001:2000: ji bzhin ngang la ye bzhin gnas pas na //
NK106(me)001:2001: gol dang gol sa rtsal sbyong bogs 'byin med //
NK106(me)001:2002: thob dang ma thob med par thag chod pas //
NK106(me)001:2003: 'bras bur smon med da lta rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK106(me)001:2004: de 'dra'i rnal 'byor nam mkha' rab 'byams yin //
NK106(me)001:2006: bden zhen grol nas gnyen po bsgom du med pas kyang sgom pa med la /
NK106(me)001:2007: bden zhen med pa'i ngang la rgyun du gnas pas
NK106(me)001:2008: thun mtshams med pa'i rol pa nges med phyogs las
NK106(me)001:2009: 'das pa rang grol kun tu bzang po'i zhing la
NK106(me)001:2010: spyod pa ni / kun byed las /
NK106(me)001:2011: kye kun byed rgyal po'i dbang thob rig pa na //
NK106(me)001:2012: dngos po ma bcos ji bzhin rtag tu shar //
NK106(me)001:2013: rgyu dang rkyen med zhi ba mchog gi lam //
NK106(me)001:2014: gzhi gzhag gang ltar bzhag kyang de nyid ngang //
NK106(me)001:2015: kun byed rgyal po'i thabs chen rtogs pa'i dbang //
NK106(me)001:2016: kun kyang ji bzhin yul la 'jug pa na //
NK106(me)001:2017: skyon dang yon tan gnyis ka mnyam shes pas //
NK106(me)001:2018: 'jug dang mi 'jug don las shin tu 'das //
NK106(me)001:2019: mi 'gyur lhun grub kun byed rgyal po'i zhing //
NK106(me)001:2020: ma bgrod ma sbyangs rang bzhin ngang gis rdzogs //
NK106(me)001:2022: de'ang dngos po dang mtshan ma'i sgom pa ltar ngos gzung gi rtags dang tshad kyang med de /
NK106(me)001:2024: dngos po mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i chos bzhin du //
NK106(me)001:2025: tshad dang rtags med nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK106(me)001:2027: de'ang gang du'ang ma phyin pas gol ba'i sa med cing /
NK106(me)001:2028: gang la'ang ma bltas pas mthong byed sgrib pa med de /
NK106(me)001:2030: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin 'di nyid ni //
NK106(me)001:2031: chos kun ma lus pa yi snying po ste //
NK106(me)001:2032: ma skyes rnam par dag pas sgrib pa med //
NK106(me)001:2033: bgrod pa'i lam dang bral bas gol sa med //
NK106(me)001:2035: gol sgrib ni sbyang bgrod lta sgom pa rnams kyis
NK106(me)001:2036: sems nyid bltas pas mthong ba med pa la bltas
NK106(me)001:2037: pa na de nyid sgrib par byung zhing /
NK106(me)001:2038: bgrod du med pa la bgrod pa de nyid gol sar gyur pa'ang /
NK106(me)001:2040: chos kun snying po byang chub sems gcig la //
NK106(me)001:2041: gcig la rnam par bgrangs pas gol sgrib byung //
NK106(me)001:2042: bgrod du med la bgrod pas gol sa byung //
NK106(me)001:2043: dmigs med bltas pas ma mthong sgrib pa byung //
NK106(me)001:2045: de'ang rang sems don gyi sangs rgyas su ye nas lhun grub tu thag chod pas /
NK106(me)001:2046: phyis de las gzhan pa'i sangs rgyas la smon pa
NK106(me)001:2047: med par shes te dus de nyid nas sangs rgyas
NK106(me)001:2048: kyi sa la gnas pa'i don yang /
NK106(me)001:2050: sems nyid ye nas mngon par byang chub pas //
NK106(me)001:2051: thob dang ma thob re dogs gnyis su med //
NK106(me)001:2053: kun byed nga la thams cad tshogs pa'i phyir //
NK106(me)001:2054: de phyir phun sum tshogs zhes bya bar bshad //
NK106(me)001:2055: kun byed nga yi rang bzhin rnam gsum las //
NK106(me)001:2056: ston pa bstan pa 'khor rnams 'byung ba'i phyir //
NK106(me)001:2057: kun byed ces ni de la btags pa yin //
NK106(me)001:2058: dang por ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ni //
NK106(me)001:2059: kun byed nga yi rang byung ye shes las //
NK106(me)001:2060: rang bzhin rnam pa gsum du 'byung ba ste //
NK106(me)001:2061: sku gsum ston pa gsum du bstan pa yin //
NK106(me)001:2063: de lta bu'i rnal 'byor pa la basngagasa pa yang /
NK106(me)001:2065: lus ni gang zag lha mi yang //
NK106(me)001:2066: dgongs pa chos nyid sangs rgyas yin //
NK106(me)001:2068: 'bring dang tha mas bsgom dgos par gdams pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2070: 'bring dang tha mas goms la brtson dgos te //
NK106(me)001:2071: ji srid bdag 'dzin dbyings su ma nub par //
NK106(me)001:2072: de srid sna tshogs thabs kyis bsgom par bya //
NK106(me)001:2073: 'di ltar dbang po 'bring dang tha mas ni shin tu brtson pa chen pos bsgom dgos te /
NK106(me)001:2074: 'khor ba'i rgyu bdag 'dzin las ma grol ba'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)001:2075: de'ang sgom mi sgom gyi sa mtshams kyang sems la
NK106(me)001:2076: gzung 'dzin dbyings su nub ma nub la byed de
NK106(me)001:2078: gnyis dang gnyis med dag pa'i ye shes ni //
NK106(me)001:2079: sgom dang mi sgom ming du btags pa ste //
NK106(me)001:2081: sgom pa'i 'thad pa bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2082: sgom pa'i 'thad pa yang rang shar rang grol du
NK106(me)001:2083: ma song ba'i tshe tha mal rang ga'i rtog pa
NK106(me)001:2084: yin pas na / khyad par rnam rtog ngan pas srid par 'khrid //
NK106(me)001:2085: de nyid grol phyir bsam gtan thabs la bstan //
NK106(me)001:2086: phyi nas shes rab mtha' grol klong yangs 'char //
NK106(me)001:2087: de'ang rnam par rtog pas 'khor bar ltung ba ni /
NK106(me)001:2088: phyogs kyi glang pos 'jam dpal la bstod pa las /
NK106(me)001:2089: rnam rtog ma rig chen po ste //
NK106(me)001:2090: 'khor ba'i rgya mtshor ltung byed yin //
NK106(me)001:2091: rnam rtog de dang bral bas na //
NK106(me)001:2092: khyod ni rtag tu mya ngan 'das //
NK106(me)001:2095: rtog pa'i khor mos srid pa'i dgon par 'khyams //
NK106(me)001:2096: rtag tu las dang nyon mongs 'du byed cing //
NK106(me)001:2097: sdug bsngal brgya phrag mngon par sgrub par byed //
NK106(me)001:2099: de lta bu nye bar zhi bar bya ba'i phyir
NK106(me)001:2100: bsgoms pas dus phyis chos thams cad yongs su grol
NK106(me)001:2101: ba'i shes rab 'char bar nges pa yin no //
NK106(me)001:2102: zhi lhag zung 'brel du dgos par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2104: zhi gnas kyis ni nyon mongs mgo gnon la //
NK106(me)001:2105: lhag mthong gis ni nyon mongs rtsa ba 'byin //
NK106(me)001:2108: zhi gnas kyis ni nyon mongs pa gnon par byed do //
NK106(me)001:2109: lhag mthong gis ni nyon mongs pa yongs su sbyong bar byed do zhes pa dang /
NK106(me)001:2111: zhi gnas rab tu ldan pa'i lhag mthong gis //
NK106(me)001:2112: nyon mongs rnam par 'joms par shes byas nas //
NK106(me)001:2113: thog mar zhi gnas btsal bya de yang ni //
NK106(me)001:2114: 'jig rten chags pa med la mngon dgas 'grub //
NK106(me)001:2116: de'ang ngo bo gcig pa dang /
NK106(me)001:2118: dang po ni gnas pa'i cha nas zhi gnas /
NK106(me)001:2119: gsal ba'i cha nas lhag mthong ste /
NK106(me)001:2120: gsal stong mtha' bral du rtogs pa'i zhi lhag zung 'brel gyis ni srid pa las sgrol ba nyid /
NK106(me)001:2122: shes rab med na bsam gtan yod min te //
NK106(me)001:2123: bsam gtan med par yang ni shes rab med //
NK106(me)001:2124: gang la de gnyis yod pas srid pa yi //
NK106(me)001:2125: rgya mtsho gnag rjes lta bur 'chal bar bgyi //
NK106(me)001:2127: tha dad pa la gnyis te /
NK106(me)001:2128: sgra'i rjes su mthun pa dang /
NK106(me)001:2129: don gyi rjes su mthun pa'o //
NK106(me)001:2130: dang po ni thos pa'i don la sems rtse gcig pa zhi gnas dang /
NK106(me)001:2131: de las don rtogs pa lhag mthong ngo //
NK106(me)001:2132: gnyis pa ni bsgoms pas dang por rtse gcig tu zin pa tsam zhi gnas la /
NK106(me)001:2133: phyis de yang rang bzhin med par rtogs pa lhag mthong ste /
NK106(me)001:2135: zhi gnas ni sems rtse gcig pa'o //
NK106(me)001:2136: lhag mthong ni yang dag par ji lta ba bzhin du chos la so sor rtog pa'o zhes dang /
NK106(me)001:2137: dgongs pa nges par 'grel pa las /
NK106(me)001:2138: zhi gnas dang lhag mthong ni gnyis te /
NK106(me)001:2139: shes rab las byung ba dang /
NK106(me)001:2141: shes rab las byung ba ni /
NK106(me)001:2142: mdo sde bcu gnyis kyi tshig yid la byed pa ni zhi gnas so //
NK106(me)001:2143: de'i don rtogs pa ni lhag mthong ngo //
NK106(me)001:2144: gdams ngag las byung ba ni /
NK106(me)001:2145: man ngag gis sems mi g.yo bar byed pa ni zhi gnas so //
NK106(me)001:2146: de'i don rtogs pa ni lhag mthong ngo zhes so //
NK106(me)001:2147: de'i rgyu mtshan bshad pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2149: des na rab kyis ngan rtog chos skur lhongs //
NK106(me)001:2150: bzang ngan med na gnyen po sgom mi dgos //
NK106(me)001:2151: 'bring gis ngang dngas zung 'brel bsgoms pa yis //
NK106(me)001:2152: bzang ngan rtog pa dbyings su nub gyur nas //
NK106(me)001:2153: zung 'brel rtogs pa nam mkha' lta bu 'char //
NK106(me)001:2154: tha mas thog mar zhi gnas btsal ba yis //
NK106(me)001:2155: gang dmigs de la brtan pa thob par sla //
NK106(me)001:2156: de nas lhag mthong so sor rtog bsgoms pas //
NK106(me)001:2157: phyi nang snang sems gzhi grol chen por 'char //
NK106(me)001:2158: des na dbang po'i rim pa shes pa gces //
NK106(me)001:2159: 'di ltar dbang po rab kyis gser gling du phyin
NK106(me)001:2160: pa na sa rdo btsal gyis mi rnyed pa ltar
NK106(me)001:2161: gang shar chos nyid du grol bas gnyen po dbyings
NK106(me)001:2162: su dag nas / bsam gtan thun 'jog tu sgom mi dgos te /
NK106(me)001:2164: ji bzhin ma bcos rgyal ba'i dgongs pa la //
NK106(me)001:2165: sems dang sems byung rtog pa ci skyes kyang //
NK106(me)001:2166: de nyid skye med nyid du gnas shes pas //
NK106(me)001:2167: bya btsal mtshan ma'i 'du shes kun dang bral //
NK106(me)001:2169: 'bring gis lta ba rtogs pas skye ba med pa'i ngang /
NK106(me)001:2171: rdzing bu rnyog pa dang bral ba mi g.yo ba ltar bzhag pas /
NK106(me)001:2172: zhi lhag zung du 'brel te rnam rtog dbyings su
NK106(me)001:2173: nub nas nam mkha' lta bu'i rtogs pa 'char te
NK106(me)001:2174: / ting nge 'dzin dam pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:2175: ji bzhin pa yi chos nyid la //
NK106(me)001:2176: de bzhin pa yi blo bzhag na //
NK106(me)001:2177: ming du mi thogs nyams myong 'byung //
NK106(me)001:2178: des na ting nge 'dzin zhes bya //
NK106(me)001:2180: tha ma sems 'phyar zhing mi bsrun pa spre'u lta
NK106(me)001:2181: bu cung zad kyang mi gnas pa de rtse gcig
NK106(me)001:2182: tu 'dzin pa'i zhi gnas kyis brlan te bsgoms pas
NK106(me)001:2183: zin dus / de'i gnyen por chos thams cad rang bzhin med pa stong pa nyid dang /
NK106(me)001:2184: snang ba thams cad sgyu ma la sogs pa so
NK106(me)001:2185: sor rtog pa'i lhag mthong bsgoms pas skye ba med
NK106(me)001:2188: zhi gnas grub pas lhag mthong la bslab par bya'o zhes so //
NK106(me)001:2189: dbang po 'bring la sgom tshul bzhag thabs lam bgrod tshul gsum gyi /
NK106(me)001:2191: mi rtog par bzhag par gdams pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2192: de ltar dbang po dang sbyar te sgom tshul yang rim pa gsum las /
NK106(me)001:2194: da ni dbang po 'bring gi sgom pa bstan //
NK106(me)001:2195: ji ltar chu ni dba' rlabs rnyog pa na /
NK106(me)001:2196: dngas pa'i gzugs brnyan mi gsal g.yo ba ltar //
NK106(me)001:2197: yid ni mi bsrun kun rtog 'phyar zhing g.yo //
NK106(me)001:2198: sna tshogs spros la kun du 'chel ba na //
NK106(me)001:2199: sems nyid 'od gsal dngas pa'i ye shes dang //
NK106(me)001:2200: spyan dang mngon shes gza' skar mi 'char bas //
NK106(me)001:2201: gcig tu mi g.yo mnyam par gzhag pa gces //
NK106(me)001:2202: 'di ltar chu'i dba' rlabs g.yo ba'i dus na gzugs
NK106(me)001:2203: brnyan 'dzin rung du skyes pa'ang gzugs brnyan mi 'dzin
NK106(me)001:2204: pa ltar / sems kyang mngon shes la sogs pa'i
NK106(me)001:2205: yon tan lhun grub tu yod kyang kun tu rtog
NK106(me)001:2206: pa g.yo ba'i rlabs kyis brel bas yon tan mi
NK106(me)001:2207: mngon pa'i phyir gcig tu mnyam par gzhag pa gces
NK106(me)001:2208: pa ltar / te / do ha las /
NK106(me)001:2209: 'di ni yid 'dus pa la rlung gi rlabs //
NK106(me)001:2210: g.yo zhing 'phyar la shin tu mi bsrun 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:2211: lhan cig skyes pa'i rang bzhin rtogs gyur na //
NK106(me)001:2212: de yis bdag nyid brtan par 'gyur ba yin //
NK106(me)001:2214: ji ltar bzhag na rtog pa'i dba' rlabs rnyog pa
NK106(me)001:2215: med dus sems nyid 'od gsal ba'i mar me rang
NK106(me)001:2216: gsal bas sems kyi chu mi g.yo bar zhog cig
NK106(me)001:2218: dba' rlabs med pa'i dbang phyug mchog /
NK106(me)001:2219: rnyog pa med pa'i bsam gtan 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:2220: chu dang mar me rang gsal gcig pur zhog /'gro 'ong nga yis mi len mi 'dor ro //
NK106(me)001:2222: lus gnad dang bzhag thabs bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2223: mnyam par bzhag tshul rgyas par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2224: mtha' gsum dang bral ba mi g.yo ba gsum gyi rang bzhin du bzhag ste /
NK106(me)001:2226: lus ni chos bdun ri rgyal lta bu la //
NK106(me)001:2227: dbang po mtha' bral rdzing bu'i gza' skar 'dra //
NK106(me)001:2228: sems nyid stong gsal dngas pa'i nam mkha' bzhin //
NK106(me)001:2229: bying rgod gnyis med spros dang bral bar bzhag /
NK106(me)001:2230: lus mi g.yo ba chos bdun te //
NK106(me)001:2237: mgrin pa yid tsam dgug par mnyam par gzhag go //
NK106(me)001:2238: dbang po mi g.yo ba ni /
NK106(me)001:2244: yid rnams dgag kyang mi dgag ste /
NK106(me)001:2250: rtog pa gang byung yang de'i sgo mi dgag /
NK106(me)001:2252: sgo bgags na lha'i mig la sogs pa spyan lnga /
NK106(me)001:2253: yid kyi mngon shes drug rnams dbang po dngas par
NK106(me)001:2254: bzhag pa'i yon tan yin pa la de mi thob
NK106(me)001:2255: / rjes phyir 'brangs na rtog pa lu gu rgyud mi chod pa tha mal pa dang khyad med /
NK106(me)001:2256: des na dbang po rdzing bu'i chu mi g.yo ba la /
NK106(me)001:2257: so so'i snang yul gza' skar gyi gzugs brnyan 'char ba ma 'gags pa ltar mnyam par gzhag go //
NK106(me)001:2258: de'ang yul so so la rtog pas der ma bzung
NK106(me)001:2259: na mi gnod kyi steng du so so'i yon tan
NK106(me)001:2260: du 'char zhing / rnam par snang la mi rtog
NK106(me)001:2261: pas rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes zhes bya'o
NK106(me)001:2262: du 'char zhing / // rnam pa med na de'i
NK106(me)001:2263: blo med pas rnam par rtog mi rtog gi dpyad
NK106(me)001:2264: ra med pa'i phyir rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye
NK106(me)001:2266: des na dbang po la yul snang dus mi rtog pa'i ngang la bzhag pas /
NK106(me)001:2267: so so rang gi rig pa'i bla mas /
NK106(me)001:2268: rtog pa 'gro 'ong chad pa la rlung 'gags par bshad pa mngon sum du rtogs te /
NK106(me)001:2269: kha sna'i rlung 'gyu yang rtog pa mi g.yo ste
NK106(me)001:2270: spros pa chad pa la rtog pa shi bar btags
NK106(me)001:2271: pas / spros pa med dus de'i gnyen po bsgom mi dgos pas /
NK106(me)001:2272: spros pa'i gnyen po spros med kyi rnal 'byor ma
NK106(me)001:2273: ste shes rab kyis ci bya ste mi dgos par
NK106(me)001:2275: mig ni mi 'dzums sems kyang mi 'gog dang //
NK106(me)001:2276: rlung 'gags pa ni dpal ldan bla mas rtogs //
NK106(me)001:2277: gang tshe rlung rgyu de ni mi g.yo ste //
NK106(me)001:2278: 'chi ba'i tshe na rnal 'byor mas ci bya //
NK106(me)001:2280: gnad de nyid thog tu phebs dus tshogs drug lhug pa'am ma bcos pa zhes bya ste /
NK106(me)001:2281: yul dbang po la snang bas dbang shes yul la mi rtog ste /
NK106(me)001:2282: dbang po yul la lhung ba ste gsal yang ting
NK106(me)001:2283: nge 'dzin 'od gsal ba'i dgongs pa la mi gnod
NK106(me)001:2284: kyi steng du grogs byed pas rgyas pa zhes bya
NK106(me)001:2286: ji srid dbang po yul gyi grong la lhung //
NK106(me)001:2287: de srid rang nyid las med rab tu rgyas //
NK106(me)001:2289: sems mi g.yo ba spros pa'i mtha' dang bral bar
NK106(me)001:2290: bzhag pa ni lus dang dbang po mi g.yo ba
NK106(me)001:2292: de'ang spro bsdu med pa'i sems dngas la 'od gsal
NK106(me)001:2293: ba de nyid las mi g.yo bar bzhag pa ni
NK106(me)001:2295: dngos dang dngos med bde bar gshegs pa'i 'ching ba ste //
NK106(me)001:2296: srid dang mnyam nyid tha dad dag tu ma byed par //
NK106(me)001:2297: gnyug ma'i yid ni gcig tu sdod dang rnal 'byor pa //
NK106(me)001:2298: ji ltar chu la chu bzhag bzhin du shes par byos //
NK106(me)001:2300: de'ang de'i dus su dngos po phyi snang ba'i yul /
NK106(me)001:2301: dngos med nang rig pa'i sems la rtog pas 'chel
NK106(me)001:2302: na sems nyid lhan cig skyes pa bde bar gshegs
NK106(me)001:2303: pa'i snying po la 'ching zhing sgrib pas 'khor 'das
NK106(me)001:2304: bzang ngan nam / tha na rang gi ting nge
NK106(me)001:2305: 'dzin la zhen 'dzin gyi blo cung zad kyang mi
NK106(me)001:2306: bzang ngan nam / bya'o // de ltar dngos po
NK106(me)001:2307: dngos med gang la'ang mi rtog pas de las gzhan
NK106(me)001:2308: gang yang mi bsam pa byung dus /
NK106(me)001:2309: kun rtog gi 'gro ba ma lus pa sems nyid
NK106(me)001:2310: gzhi'i ngang du thim pas sems mi g.yo zhing brtan
NK106(me)001:2311: pa na 'khor ba las grol te gnyis 'dzin bdag
NK106(me)001:2312: gzhan du zhen pa med pas bla na med pa'i
NK106(me)001:2313: chos sku'i lus spros bsam brjod 'das chen po thob
NK106(me)001:2315: dngos dang dngos med yongs su dpyad pas na //
NK106(me)001:2316: der ni 'gro ba ma lus rab thim 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:2317: gang tshe yid ni mi g.yo rang gnas brtan pa der //
NK106(me)001:2318: de tshe 'khor ba'i dngos po las ni rang grol 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:2319: gang tshe bdag gzhan yongs su shes med na //
NK106(me)001:2320: de tshe bla med lus ni thob par 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:2323: kye ji bzhin rtsol bral bde ba chen po la //
NK106(me)001:2324: sgo gsum mi rtsol bcos shing dmigs mi byed //
NK106(me)001:2325: yid la mi byed mtshan ma'i rjes mi 'brang //
NK106(me)001:2326: rang byung ye shes bde ba'i don la bzhag /'di ni rang byung 'od gsal dgongs pa ste //
NK106(me)001:2327: kun byed rgyal po'i dgongs pa'i phrin las so //
NK106(me)001:2329: yon tan gyi 'char tshul bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2330: de ltar mnyam par gzhag pa na shin tu spros pa dang bral ba /
NK106(me)001:2331: de tshe rang bzhin gcig ste gdod ma'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:2332: gzung dang 'dzin pa mi dmigs chos kyi sku //
NK106(me)001:2333: dri med 'od gsal nyi ma'i snying po ni //
NK106(me)001:2334: bde gsal mi rtog mtha' dbus med pa 'char //
NK106(me)001:2335: de'ang dmigs bsam chos nyid du 'das pas kun rtog
NK106(me)001:2336: dbyings su thim nas chos skur ro mnyam gyi dgongs
NK106(me)001:2337: pa 'od gsal rdzogs pa chen po bde gsal mi
NK106(me)001:2338: rtog pa'i nyams dang bcas pa dpe don mtshon 'das
NK106(me)001:2341: dus gsum gcig ste khyad par med //
NK106(me)001:2342: sngon med phyis med gdod nas byung //
NK106(me)001:2343: chos skus khyab pa gcig pa'i phyir //
NK106(me)001:2344: che ba'i chen por rang bzhin gnas //
NK106(me)001:2346: ngo mtshar rmad byung rol pa 'di //
NK106(me)001:2347: bya bral nam mkha' bzhin du gnas //
NK106(me)001:2348: cir yang mi dmigs gti mug las //
NK106(me)001:2349: de ma thag tu rang las byung //
NK106(me)001:2352: bla ma'i lung la bsgrims te rab 'bad na //
NK106(me)001:2353: lhan cig skyes pa 'byung bar the tshom med //
NK106(me)001:2354: kha dog yon tan yi ge dpe bral ba //
NK106(me)001:2355: smra ru mi btub de ni gyi na mtshon //
NK106(me)001:2356: gzhon nu ma yi bde ba snying la zhen pa bzhin //
NK106(me)001:2357: dbang phyug dam pa de ni su la'ang bstan nus sam //
NK106(me)001:2359: ting nge 'dzin dam pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:2360: bsam gyis mi khyab chos nyid la //
NK106(me)001:2361: bsam du med pa'i blo bzhag na //
NK106(me)001:2362: phyogs ris med pa'i nyams myong 'byung //
NK106(me)001:2363: des na ting nge 'dzin zhes bya //
NK106(me)001:2365: chos nyid rtogs pa'i tshul bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2366: de ltar rang byung lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes shar ba de'i tshe /
NK106(me)001:2368: snang dang stong pa thams cad phyam gcig la //
NK106(me)001:2369: yod dang med pa kun gyi mtha' las 'das //
NK106(me)001:2370: srid dang zhi ba gnyis su mi rtog pa //
NK106(me)001:2371: shes dang shes bya gcig pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK106(me)001:2372: mnyam dang mi mnyam med pa'i chos nyid mthong //
NK106(me)001:2373: phyi nang gi chos can sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad dang
NK106(me)001:2374: de'i chos nyid rang bzhin gyis ma skyes pa'i ngo
NK106(me)001:2375: bo tha mi dad pas snang stong phyam gcig tu
NK106(me)001:2376: mthong ba nyid / kun byed las /
NK106(me)001:2377: ji ltar snang ba de bzhin nyid du gcig /
NK106(me)001:2378: ma bcos mnyam pa'i rgyal po de la ni //
NK106(me)001:2379: mi rtog chos sku'i dgongs pa khong nas 'char //
NK106(me)001:2381: sems nyid yod med kyi mtha' las 'das pa dngas
NK106(me)001:2382: gsal g.yo ba med pa'i ye shes srid zhi gnyis
NK106(me)001:2385: thog ma tha ma dbus zhi zhing //
NK106(me)001:2386: srid dang mya ngan 'das zhi ba //
NK106(me)001:2387: lhun gyis grub pa'i bde chen te //
NK106(me)001:2388: mtshungs pa med pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK106(me)001:2389: rang gi mthu yis rig pa las //
NK106(me)001:2392: de'i tshe shes bya yul dang shes byed blo gnyis
NK106(me)001:2393: su med pa'i ye shes mnyam pa nyid du 'char
NK106(me)001:2395: phyi nang gnyis ka phyi nyid nang //
NK106(me)001:2396: zab mo cha shas rtog yul med //
NK106(me)001:2398: 'phags pa'i ye shes kyi dngos rgyur bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2400: 'di ni 'phags pa'i bden mthong ye shes rgyu //
NK106(me)001:2401: phyi nas de bzhin nyid mthong blo mig gis //
NK106(me)001:2402: rgyal ba'i chos sku phun tshogs bsgrub pas na //
NK106(me)001:2403: skal bzang rnams kyis rtag tu mnyam par zhog /
NK106(me)001:2404: de'ang spros pa med pa'i ye shes ches cher goms
NK106(me)001:2405: rjes su byas pa las mthong ba'i lam la sogs
NK106(me)001:2406: pa gong ma rnams ngang gis 'grub pa'i tshul yang
NK106(me)001:2408: de phyir yang dag yang dag min //
NK106(me)001:2409: gang gang shin tu goms gyur pa //
NK106(me)001:2410: sgom pa yongs su rdzogs pa na //
NK106(me)001:2411: bde gsal mi rtog blo 'bras bu //
NK106(me)001:2414: yeng med spros bral du bzhag pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2415: da ni bzhag tshul brgyad kyi rang bzhin rgyas par bstan pa las /
NK106(me)001:2416: yeng med spro bsdu bral bar bzhag pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2417: sems nyid ma skyes mkha' ltar dag pa'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:2418: sems byung mi dmigs sprin tshogs dengs pa bzhin //
NK106(me)001:2419: yeng med spros dang bral ba'i shes pa yis //
NK106(me)001:2420: ji bzhin ngang la ye bzhin mnyam par gzhag /
NK106(me)001:2421: de yang sems nyid nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang la
NK106(me)001:2422: sems byung gi rtog pa rang sor bzhag pas dengs
NK106(me)001:2423: pa sprin yal ba lta bu lta ba'i ngang der
NK106(me)001:2424: ma g.yengs par dpe'i rang bzhin la mnyam par gzhag
NK106(me)001:2426: kye sems dpa' rdo rje ji bzhin nyid sgoms shig /
NK106(me)001:2427: rtogs pas rang sar grol ba'i lta ba la //
NK106(me)001:2428: ma yengs rang bzhin bzhag pas bya rtsol med //
NK106(me)001:2429: kun kyang rang byung rang sar grol ba yin //
NK106(me)001:2431: ma skyes nam mkha' lta bu'i sems nyid 'di //
NK106(me)001:2432: mi skye 'gag pa med pa'i ngang du zhog /
NK106(me)001:2434: dngas gsal rnyog bral du bzhag pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2435: dngas gsal rnyog pa med par bzhag pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2436: dngas shing stongs pa rgya mtsho lta bu la //
NK106(me)001:2437: gzung 'dzin rnyog bral dba' rlabs med par zhog /
NK106(me)001:2438: sems ma bying bas dngas la /
NK106(me)001:2439: mi rgod pas stengs pa rgya mtsho rang sor gnas
NK106(me)001:2440: pa lta bu'i ngang du gzung 'dzin rnam rtog gi
NK106(me)001:2441: rnyog pas ma bslad par dngas seng nga bzhag pa
NK106(me)001:2443: rgya mtsho dngas pa'i ting nge 'dzin //
NK106(me)001:2444: sgra rten yid la byed min par //
NK106(me)001:2445: ji bzhin rnyog pa kun dang bral //
NK106(me)001:2447: shes nas ma yengs don la gnas pa las //
NK106(me)001:2448: rtsol bas mi 'jug mnyen pos sems mi sbyong //
NK106(me)001:2449: yul la mi 'jog dran pa'i sems mi sdud //
NK106(me)001:2450: gang ltar byung ba de nyid don yin pas //
NK106(me)001:2451: kun byed nga yi don la 'jug par gyis //
NK106(me)001:2453: mkha' ltar phyogs bral du bzhag pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2454: phyogs bral nam mkha' lta bur bzhag pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2455: stong zhing gsal ba nam mkha' lta bu la //
NK106(me)001:2456: kun rtog sprin med phyogs lhung bral bar shog /
NK106(me)001:2457: sems nyid ye stong nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang du
NK106(me)001:2458: rnam rtog gi spro bsdu med par bzhag pa nyid
NK106(me)001:2460: kye sems dpa' rdo rje chen po da sgoms shig /
NK106(me)001:2461: blang dor med pa'i chos nyid byang chub la //
NK106(me)001:2462: mkha' ltar gnas pas lus sems bcos su med //
NK106(me)001:2463: 'du shes zhen 'dzin med pas sgom du med //
NK106(me)001:2464: mkha' ltar rab zhi rnyog pa kun bral ba //
NK106(me)001:2465: yul la mi 'jug dgongs pa'i dmigs 'jug bral //
NK106(me)001:2467: byar med byung rgyal du bzhag pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2468: dgag sgrub re dogs dang bral bar bzhag pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2469: brtan zhing mi g.yo ri rgyal lta bu la //
NK106(me)001:2470: dgag sgrub gnyis med re dogs bral bar zhog /
NK106(me)001:2471: sems mi g.yo ba ri rgyal lta bu'i ngang du dgag sgrub kyi rnam rtog med par bzhag ste /
NK106(me)001:2473: kye ston pa'i ston pa kun byed rgyal po yis //
NK106(me)001:2474: rtogs pas gnyis ka'i 'ching ba rab bcad nas //
NK106(me)001:2475: mi 'gal mnyam pa'i don la gnas byas pas //
NK106(me)001:2476: kun byed nga yi dgongs par lhun gyis grub //
NK106(me)001:2477: gang gis 'ching ba ni rtog bcad byas shing //
NK106(me)001:2478: grol bar mi 'jug mya ngan 'das mi len //
NK106(me)001:2479: snying po'i don la phyogs ris dmigs mi 'dzin //
NK106(me)001:2480: don la mi sgom snying rje'i yul mi 'jug /
NK106(me)001:2482: snang yul 'gag med du bzhag pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2483: sgo lnga rang gsal du bzhag pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2484: dag cing gsal ba me long lta bu la //
NK106(me)001:2485: snang yul ma 'gags gzugs brnyan lta bur zhog /
NK106(me)001:2486: sems gsal dngas phyed pa'i ngang du dbang po'i snang
NK106(me)001:2487: yul khra bun ne shigs se 'dzin rtog med la
NK106(me)001:2490: kye de phyir sems dpa' rdo rje da sgoms shig /
NK106(me)001:2491: rang byung ye shes dmigs pa kun las 'das //
NK106(me)001:2492: rtogs pas dmigs pa'i don du 'jog mi byed //
NK106(me)001:2493: yul las 'das pas rnam shes srung mi byed //
NK106(me)001:2494: dngos po snying por gsal bas sgom mi byed //
NK106(me)001:2495: rnam pa snying por gsal bas re dogs med //
NK106(me)001:2497: ye grol dag gsal du bzhag pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2498: dag gsal gnyen pos ma bslad par bzhag pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2499: ye grol sor gzhag 'ja' tshon lta bu la //
NK106(me)001:2500: bying rgod gnyis med dag cing gsal bar zhog /
NK106(me)001:2501: sems gsal dngas phyed pa'i ngang du bying rgod med par bzhag pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2503: kye sems dpa' rdo rje legs par da sgoms shig /
NK106(me)001:2504: ma skyes rnam par dag pa'i don snang bas //
NK106(me)001:2505: snang ba dngos por mi lta 'jig mi byed //
NK106(me)001:2506: snang ba skye ba med par rang grol bas //
NK106(me)001:2507: stong pa mi sgom ji bzhin rtogs pas grol //
NK106(me)001:2508: zhes pa ltar bzhag pas snang ba stong par shes pa 'ja' tshon ltar shes so //
NK106(me)001:2509: rtse gcig mda' mkhan ltar bzhag pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2510: rtse gcig ma yengs par bzhag pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2511: gzhan du ma yengs mda' mkhan lta bu la //
NK106(me)001:2512: gnyug ma'i ye shes spro bsdu bral bar shog /
NK106(me)001:2513: sems chos nyid kyi ngang las ma yengs par tsen
NK106(me)001:2514: ne ce re ba mda' bsrangs pa ltar mig tu
NK106(me)001:2517: de ltar sgom du med pa'i snying po la //
NK106(me)001:2518: ma yengs dran pas gzung ba man ngag yin //
NK106(me)001:2520: byar med lhun grub tu bzhag pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2521: blo bde las zin du bzhag pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2522: thag chod shes pa las zin lta bu la //
NK106(me)001:2523: re dogs gnyis med lhun gyis grub par zhog /
NK106(me)001:2524: sems rang sor bzhag pa las chos sku rang gnas
NK106(me)001:2525: su thag chod pas phyi nas re ba dang dogs
NK106(me)001:2526: pa med pa'i ngang der rang babs su glod nas
NK106(me)001:2528: kye lam 'dir 'jug cing bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK106(me)001:2529: da lta nyid nas rgyal ba'i sa la gnas //
NK106(me)001:2530: dgongs pa mi 'dzin phyogs ris gzung du med //
NK106(me)001:2531: snying po'i lam la 'jug dang mi 'jug 'das //
NK106(me)001:2533: de'ang sgo gsum gyi nar glod nas ma yengs tsam du 'jog gi /
NK106(me)001:2534: ha cang dran pa bsgrims pa'ang mi dgos so //
NK106(me)001:2535: yang rgya yan du yengs na'ang tha mal du ltung bas na /
NK106(me)001:2536: tha mal gyi shes pa rang babs ma yengs pa'i ngang la bzhag par yang /
NK106(me)001:2538: kye ston pa'i ston pa kun byed rgyal po yis //
NK106(me)001:2539: sgom zhing bsam du med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK106(me)001:2540: ma bsams yal bar gnas pas 'khor ba nyid //
NK106(me)001:2541: btsa' zhing bsgoms pas rnam rtog mtshan ma'i lam //
NK106(me)001:2545: kye sems dpa' rdo rje ji bzhin nyid sgoms shig /
NK106(me)001:2546: rang lus mi bcos dbang po mi brtul te //
NK106(me)001:2547: ngag kyang mi bsdam bya btsal gang yang med //
NK106(me)001:2548: sems kyang gar gtad mi g.yo'i ngang la bzhag /
NK106(me)001:2549: bya ba med pa'i phrin las 'di bsgoms pas //
NK106(me)001:2550: byas pa med par don kun rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:2552: kye rnal 'byor dus gcig 'jug pa'i skal ldan la //
NK106(me)001:2553: kun byed rgyal po'i dgongs pa bstan byas na //
NK106(me)001:2554: rtogs pa'i klong la dran zhing 'dris pa las //
NK106(me)001:2555: sgom zhing 'jug tu med par lung ston cig /
NK106(me)001:2557: bzhag thabs brgyad kyis don bsdu ba ni /
NK106(me)001:2558: de ltar bzhag thabs brgyad kyi tshul /
NK106(me)001:2559: 'di ni rang bzhin dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin //
NK106(me)001:2560: zhi gnas lhag mthong zung du 'brel pa yin //
NK106(me)001:2561: skye med ngang der gnas pas zhi gnas la //
NK106(me)001:2562: gsal stong spros dang bral bas lhag mthong nyid //
NK106(me)001:2563: dbyer med ngo bo gcig pas zung du 'brel //
NK106(me)001:2564: de'ang gzung 'dzin med pas rang bzhin dag pa'i ting
NK106(me)001:2565: nge 'dzin te zhi lhag zung du 'brel tshul yang
NK106(me)001:2566: / yin thog tu gnas pa'i cha zhi gnas la /
NK106(me)001:2567: de dus gsal cha lhag mthong zhes brjod kyang dbyer
NK106(me)001:2568: med pas zung du 'jug pa zhes btags dus nas
NK106(me)001:2569: gnyis ka gang du'ang dbye bsal med pas /
NK106(me)001:2570: zhi gnas zhi gnas kyi 'du shes zhi /
NK106(me)001:2571: lhag mthong lhag mthong du rtog pa med pas dbyer med gnyug ma'i zung 'jug ste /
NK106(me)001:2572: byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod kyi mdo las /
NK106(me)001:2573: byang chub sems dpa'i zhi gnas ni yang dag pa'i
NK106(me)001:2574: bsam pa de zhi ba'i 'du shes la yang mi
NK106(me)001:2575: gnas pa'o // lhag mthong ni lta ba mthong ba
NK106(me)001:2576: ste lta ba nyid kyang rjes su mi mthong ba'o
NK106(me)001:2577: gnas pa'o // // gang gis de ltar mthong ba de nyid yang dag par mthong ba'o zhes so //
NK106(me)001:2578: lam bgrod tshul la yang bdun las /
NK106(me)001:2579: bzhag thabs brgyad kyis brjod med mthong tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:2580: da ni de ltar bzhag pas ye shes bzhi'i rim pas lam gyi bgrod tshul yang bshad de /
NK106(me)001:2582: dang po snang ba'i ye shes bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:2583: bzhag thabs brgyad kyis sems gnyug mar gnas pa /
NK106(me)001:2584: de tshe zab zhi spros dang bral ba'i sems //
NK106(me)001:2585: smra bsam brjod du med pa'i don mthong bas //
NK106(me)001:2586: snang ba'i ye shes shin tu mi rtog pa //
NK106(me)001:2587: 'od gsal shes rab pha rol phyin zhes bya //
NK106(me)001:2588: sems nyid smra bsam brjod las 'das pa'i ngang du
NK106(me)001:2589: blo'i 'jug pa zhi nas dngas gsal g.yo ba med
NK106(me)001:2590: pa'i ye shes thog mar skyes pa gang yin pa
NK106(me)001:2591: de ni snang ba'i ye shes te 'od gsal shes
NK106(me)001:2592: rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i don te /
NK106(me)001:2594: 'od gsal ba ni rnam pa bzhi //
NK106(me)001:2595: rdzogs nas ye shes chen po'i sa //
NK106(me)001:2596: snang ba rnam par mi rtog pa //
NK106(me)001:2597: mched pa ye shes sgyu ma ste //
NK106(me)001:2598: thob pa dam pa 'phags pa'i lam //
NK106(me)001:2599: nye bar thob pas rdzogs pa'o //
NK106(me)001:2601: 'di dag gnyis med rnam rgyal du bar do'i skad cig bzhi la sbyar te grol tshul bshad pa'ang /
NK106(me)001:2602: da lta 'di bzhin yod pa ngo shes shing thob pa rnams der grol ba yin no //
NK106(me)001:2603: thar lam zin pa'i rtags ni /
NK106(me)001:2604: de'ang snang ba'i ye shes 'od gsal ba dang por
NK106(me)001:2605: skyes pas sems nyid gnyug ma'i ye shes ngos zin
NK106(me)001:2606: / thar pa'i lam sna zin pas byang chub kyi sa bon thebs pa'o //
NK106(me)001:2608: de nyid mthong bas sems ni rab zhi zhing //
NK106(me)001:2609: phyi nang chos la dgag sgrub zhen pa chung //
NK106(me)001:2610: stong pa'i ngang nas snying rje phyogs med 'char //
NK106(me)001:2611: rang gzhan don du dge la spyod cing bskul //
NK106(me)001:2612: dben par dga' zhing rnam g.yeng 'du 'dzi nyung //
NK106(me)001:2613: rmi lam na yang dge ba'i chos la spyod //
NK106(me)001:2614: des ni thar pa'i lam sna zin pa yin //
NK106(me)001:2615: sems nyid 'od gsal gzhi'i ye shes ngos zin dus
NK106(me)001:2616: glo bur kun rtog rang sar grol bas 'od gsal
NK106(me)001:2618: kun spyod gcig tu dge bas phyi sna tshogs kyi chos yul lnga /
NK106(me)001:2619: nang dran rig gi sems dgag sgrub dang bcas pa thams cad la zhen pa bral zhing /
NK106(me)001:2620: sems rang gsal stong pa'i ngang nas sems can la
NK106(me)001:2621: nye ring phyogs cha med pa'i snying rje skye bas
NK106(me)001:2622: rang yang dge ba la spyod /
NK106(me)001:2623: gzhan yang dge ba 'ba' zhig la bskul /
NK106(me)001:2624: rab tu dben pa'i ri sul dang nags 'dab la
NK106(me)001:2625: sogs par dga' zhing rnam g.yeng dang 'du 'dzi spongs
NK106(me)001:2626: te / tha na rmi lam du'ang mi dge ba'i
NK106(me)001:2627: sems med par dkar po dge ba'i snang ba 'ba'
NK106(me)001:2628: te / zhig 'char zhing / lus dang ngag dang
NK106(me)001:2629: yid gsum shin tu sbyangs pa la gnas pas tshogs
NK106(me)001:2630: lam gyi yon tan rgyud la skye zhing sgom khang
NK106(me)001:2631: du 'od gsal gyi snang ba sna tshogs pa mthong
NK106(me)001:2632: te / zhig 'char zhing / bar 'gyur te / lang+kara gshegs pa las /
NK106(me)001:2633: bsam pa med par lus bsrangs nas //
NK106(me)001:2634: sangs rgyas dang ni byang chub la //
NK106(me)001:2635: yang dang yang du phyag btsal nas //
NK106(me)001:2636: bdag med pa ni rnam par bsgom //
NK106(me)001:2637: rnal 'byor can gyis de bsgoms na //
NK106(me)001:2639: 'gro ba kun la bskyab pa'i yid //
NK106(me)001:2640: rnal 'byor can gyis brtson byas na //
NK106(me)001:2641: nyi ma zla ba'i dbyibs 'dra dang //
NK106(me)001:2643: ri mo nam mkha'i me 'dra mthong //
NK106(me)001:2645: de tshe sangs rgyas lha yi phyag /
NK106(me)001:2646: thams cad zhing nas byung ba yis //
NK106(me)001:2647: de yi mgo la nyug mdzad de //
NK106(me)001:2648: yang dag rjes su 'gro ba'i ltas //
NK106(me)001:2652: de nas ches cher gong du goms pa yis //
NK106(me)001:2653: sems gsal ye shes sngon pas rgya che zhing //
NK106(me)001:2654: snang ba rmi lam sgyu mar rab tu rtogs //
NK106(me)001:2655: chos rnams gnyis med ngang du ro gcig pas //
NK106(me)001:2656: skyes dang ma skyes med par mthong ba'i tshe //
NK106(me)001:2657: mched pa'i ye shes shin tu mi rtog pa //
NK106(me)001:2658: bsam gtan dga' bas brgyan pa thob pa yin //
NK106(me)001:2659: sngar gyi don la ches cher goms nas sems stong
NK106(me)001:2660: gsal rang byung gi ye shes la sgrib pa'i shas
NK106(me)001:2661: chung ngu song bas shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin
NK106(me)001:2662: dang nyams su myong ba rlabs che zhing /
NK106(me)001:2663: phyi'i snang ba'ang ngang gis zhar la rmi lam sgyu mar mthong la /
NK106(me)001:2664: chos thams cad rang bzhin du ma ro gcig gi
NK106(me)001:2665: rtogs pa 'char zhing nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang la
NK106(me)001:2666: gnas pa ni mched pa'i ye shes zhes bya ste
NK106(me)001:2668: rmi lam na yang sgyu mar mthong //
NK106(me)001:2673: de tshe lus sems sngon pas rab dag cing //
NK106(me)001:2674: thabs dang shes rab dri med rtogs pa 'char //
NK106(me)001:2675: mngon shes ldan zhing snying rjes phan pa 'grub //
NK106(me)001:2676: srid la skyo bas sems ni nges par 'byung //
NK106(me)001:2677: rmi lam na yang chos kun de 'drar rtogs //
NK106(me)001:2678: lus kyi phyi nang shig sro 'bu srin med //
NK106(me)001:2679: bying rgod bral zhing nyin mtshan ting 'dzin 'grub //
NK106(me)001:2680: skye bo des ni 'phags lam myur du mthong //
NK106(me)001:2681: rtogs pa dri ma med pas lus sems shin tu sbyangs pa'i rtags khyad par can yang /
NK106(me)001:2682: zung 'brel khyad par can gyi ting nge 'dzin la
NK106(me)001:2683: nyin mtshan du gnas pas de las 'bral mi phod
NK106(me)001:2684: cing / snying rjes sems can la phan pa spyod
NK106(me)001:2685: cing 'khor ba la skyo shas dang nges 'byung thun
NK106(me)001:2686: mong ma yin pa skye ba dang /
NK106(me)001:2687: rmi lam du'ang chos thams cad rmi lam dang sgyu ma la sogs par mthong zhing /
NK106(me)001:2688: lus kyi nang du srin bu med la phyi'i shig
NK106(me)001:2689: sro med pa la sogs pa sbyor lam gyi rtags
NK106(me)001:2690: rnams thob cing / myur du mthong lam la rag par 'gyur te /
NK106(me)001:2693: rab tu thob par dka' ba med //
NK106(me)001:2695: thob pa 'phags pa'i ye shes ni /
NK106(me)001:2697: de nas ches cher goms pas sngon pas lhag /
NK106(me)001:2698: ting 'dzin rtogs pa'i nyi ma sngon med 'char //
NK106(me)001:2699: chos kun tshul gcig mnyam pa'i don mthong nas //
NK106(me)001:2700: spyan dang mngon shes sgrib pa med mnga' bas //
NK106(me)001:2701: zhing khams brgya stong bye ba dpag med mthong //
NK106(me)001:2702: de tshe zag med 'phags pa'i ye shes te //
NK106(me)001:2703: thob pa zhes bya mngon du gyur pa yin //
NK106(me)001:2704: 'dir sems nyid 'od gsal ba'i ye shes zag pa
NK106(me)001:2705: med pa dang por mthong bas thob pa zhes bya
NK106(me)001:2707: nang gi snying ga'i rtsa 'khor la brten pa'i 'dab ma'i rlung brgya phrag gcig dag /
NK106(me)001:2708: khams dngas ma'i ye shes de cher 'od gsal zhing
NK106(me)001:2709: 'khor lo gzhan rnams su'ang gsal bas rlung sems khyad
NK106(me)001:2710: par can brgya phrag bcu gnyis brtan zhing nyon mongs
NK106(me)001:2711: pa'i rlung brgya phrag bcu gnyis 'gags pas /
NK106(me)001:2712: sngags ltar na nang gi khams la ye ldan gyi zhing khams snang la /
NK106(me)001:2713: mtshan nyid ltar na sangs rgyas brgya'i zhal blta ba la sogs pa phyi'i zhing snang bar bshad de /
NK106(me)001:2714: so so'i skye bo'i sa'i spyan dang mngon shes ltar
NK106(me)001:2715: sgrib pa dang thogs pa can las ches dag cing
NK106(me)001:2716: sgrib pa med pa thob ste kun brtags pa mthong
NK106(me)001:2717: bas spang bar bya ba'i nyon mongs pa las rnam
NK106(me)001:2718: par grol zhing ye shes 'od gsal ba'i dgongs pa
NK106(me)001:2721: 'tshe ba chad dang mi basngagasa ngan 'gro dang //
NK106(me)001:2722: 'khor gyi 'jigs bral nyam nga'i gnod pa med //
NK106(me)001:2723: ces 'jigs pa lnga las grol ba yin no //
NK106(me)001:2724: mthong zin goms pas gzungs sprin ye shes 'char tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:2725: 'phags pa'i ye shes dang po thob pa /
NK106(me)001:2726: de las ches cher gong du 'phel ba yis //
NK106(me)001:2727: rtogs pa'i ting 'dzin yon tan grangs med cing //
NK106(me)001:2728: rtog dang mi rtog mnyam pa'i chos nyid las //
NK106(me)001:2729: gzungs sprin ye shes dri med rgya che zhing //
NK106(me)001:2730: mnyam par gzhag dang ma bzhag gnyis med par //
NK106(me)001:2731: rtag tu mnyam gzhag sprul pa bsam yas ston //
NK106(me)001:2732: tshad med zhing dang ye shes gzigs pa 'jug /
NK106(me)001:2733: de'ang mthong zin gyi don goms par byed pas sgom pa'i lam ste /
NK106(me)001:2734: chung 'bring chen po thob pas sa re rer yon
NK106(me)001:2735: tan sngar bshad pa de dag grangs med pa thob
NK106(me)001:2736: cing sprul pas sems can gyi don byed la /
NK106(me)001:2737: sa dang po nas bdun pa'i bar du rjes thob
NK106(me)001:2738: na rtog pa yod pas mnyam rjes tha dad pa'ang
NK106(me)001:2739: yod la / dag pa sa gsum nas mngon gyur
NK106(me)001:2740: gyi rtog pa med pas 'dres pa ni ye shes
NK106(me)001:2741: nyid du ro gcig pa'i phyir te /
NK106(me)001:2743: bya ba sgrub la rtag tu blo //
NK106(me)001:2744: me bzhin du ni 'bar ba dang //
NK106(me)001:2745: zhes pa la sogs pa sngar bstan pa bzhin no //
NK106(me)001:2746: nye bar thob pa 'phags las rdzogs tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:2747: yon tan khyad par can de dag kyang rdo rje'i lus kyi /
NK106(me)001:2748: rtsa khams dag cing rlung sems yon tan mchog /
NK106(me)001:2749: shin tu rgya che dri ma med pa na //
NK106(me)001:2750: nye bar thob pa zhes bya'i ye shes te //
NK106(me)001:2751: 'phags lam rdzogs nas myur du byang chub 'thob //
NK106(me)001:2752: 'di ni 'od gsal snying po'i theg pa ste //
NK106(me)001:2753: skal bzang 'bras bu tshe 'dir grol ba yin //
NK106(me)001:2754: de'ang sgom lam gyi ye shes ni nye bar thob
NK106(me)001:2755: pa zhes bya ste 'phags lam brgyad bsgoms pas lhan
NK106(me)001:2756: cig skyes pa sa dgu'i dri ma rnams sbyong ba
NK106(me)001:2757: yin no // spyir gyi sa dang lam gyi yon
NK106(me)001:2758: tan rnams rtsa rlung thig le las su rung ba
NK106(me)001:2759: yin no // las snang ste / bsod nams dang
NK106(me)001:2760: ye shes kyi tshogs bsags kyang de dag las su
NK106(me)001:2761: rung zhing rtsol bas sbyangs pa las kyang rung ba
NK106(me)001:2762: yin no // las snang ste / yin no //
NK106(me)001:2763: de'ang dbu ma la mdud pa nyi shu rtsa gcig
NK106(me)001:2764: yod pa'i dang po gnyis grol bas sa dang po
NK106(me)001:2765: yin no // las snang ste / yin no //
NK106(me)001:2766: nas / nyi shu ba grol bas bcu pa'i bar
NK106(me)001:2768: sbyang gzhi'i rtsa 'dab rnams sbyong byed kyi rtsa 'dab
NK106(me)001:2769: kyi ye shes mched pas bskams dus rlung zhabs 'khrul
NK106(me)001:2770: snang stongs te / sbyong byed ye shes kyi rtsar
NK106(me)001:2771: ye shes kyi dngas ma dang rlung rnam par mi
NK106(me)001:2772: rtog pa rgyu ba med pa tshud pa las sa
NK106(me)001:2774: de'ang sprul pa'i 'khor lo'i rtsa 'dab las su rung bas tshogs sbyor gyi yon tan 'char /
NK106(me)001:2775: sangs rgyas sprul sku'i zhal mthong /
NK106(me)001:2776: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi las su rung bas longs sku'i zhing snang /
NK106(me)001:2777: snying ga'i las su rung bas mthong lam skye /
NK106(me)001:2778: mgrin pas sa dang po nas bdun pa'i bar longs sku'i yon tan snang /
NK106(me)001:2779: spyi bo'i las su rung bas dag pa sa gsum gyi yon tan 'char /
NK106(me)001:2780: nyi shu rtsa gcig pa dbu ma'i mdud pa grol
NK106(me)001:2781: dus rtsa 'khor thams cad shin tu dag pas sku
NK106(me)001:2785: sa dang sa yi yon tan rnams //
NK106(me)001:2786: rtsa rnams kyi ni skye 'bri las //
NK106(me)001:2787: rlung dang bde chen las 'dod de //
NK106(me)001:2790: rnam bzhi'am gsum mam lnga 'khor lo //
NK106(me)001:2791: gnyis gnyis kyi ni gcig ma rdzogs //
NK106(me)001:2792: sa bcu tha mas ye shes sa //
NK106(me)001:2793: bzho bas steng dang 'og tu grags //
NK106(me)001:2795: de'ang sngar bshad pa ltar 'khor lo gsum ltar na sku gsum /
NK106(me)001:2796: bzhi ltar na bde ba chen po dang bzhi /
NK106(me)001:2797: lnga ltar na ye shes chen po dang lnga rdzogs shing /
NK106(me)001:2798: mdud pa nyi shus sa bcu'o //
NK106(me)001:2799: gcig gis sangs rgyas kyi sa ste /
NK106(me)001:2800: de dag gong nas gong du grol nas 'od gsal du 'jug pa'o //
NK106(me)001:2801: skabs 'dir rang bzhin gyis rtsa mdud grol ba las
NK106(me)001:2802: grol ba'i tshul bar do 'phros su bshad par bya
NK106(me)001:2804: gnas skabs gang du 'char ba ngos bzung na /
NK106(me)001:2805: sngar bstan pa ltar dbu ma'i dbus kyi ye shes 'od gsal gyi rtsa /
NK106(me)001:2806: snying dbus dngas ma chen po'i rang bzhin la 'byung ba thim dus 'char ro //
NK106(me)001:2808: ye shes mngon par 'byung ba'i rgyud phyi ma las /
NK106(me)001:2809: lus can rnams ni 'chi ba'i tshe //
NK106(me)001:2810: gzugs ni sgra la thim par 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:2811: sgra dri ro ni reg la thim //
NK106(me)001:2812: reg ni chos la thim par 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:2815: dang po sa ni chu la thim //
NK106(me)001:2816: chu yang me la thim 'gyur te //
NK106(me)001:2817: me ni rlung la thim gyur nas //
NK106(me)001:2818: rlung yang rnam par shes la thim //
NK106(me)001:2819: rnam shes gzung ba 'di nyid ni //
NK106(me)001:2822: de'ang gzugs sgra la thim pas gzugs mi gsal bar
NK106(me)001:2823: song dus sa cha la thim pas lus kyi stobs
NK106(me)001:2824: nyams / sgra dri la thim pas rna ba mi
NK106(me)001:2825: gsang du song dus chu me la thim pas gsher
NK106(me)001:2826: ba'i cha bskam zhing khrag rnams kyi dngas ma rtsa
NK106(me)001:2828: dri ro la thim pas snas dri mi tshor dus
NK106(me)001:2829: me rlung la thim pas drod mtha' nas sdud cing
NK106(me)001:2830: 'khor lo bzhi'i 'dab ma rnams kyi dngas ma dbus
NK106(me)001:2831: su 'jug / ro reg la thim pas lces ro
NK106(me)001:2832: mi tshor dus rlung rnam shes la thim pas dbugs
NK106(me)001:2834: dngas ma thams cad yar sna mar sna'i rtser sleb
NK106(me)001:2836: la thim dus lus kyis reg bya mi tshor zhing
NK106(me)001:2837: mdangs nyams dus rnam shes 'od gsal la 'jug ste
NK106(me)001:2839: ma'i yar sna'i ham la ro ma'i dngas ma dkar
NK106(me)001:2841: thim / mar snar a la brkyang ma'i dngas ma
NK106(me)001:2842: dmar po thim pa snying ga'i ye shes 'od gsal
NK106(me)001:2843: gyi dngas ma chen po'i nang du thim pas phra
NK106(me)001:2844: rags kyi rtog pa 'gags nas ye shes 'od gsal
NK106(me)001:2846: thim / ba 'char ro // de'ang sems la sangs
NK106(me)001:2847: rgyas rang chas su yod pa nyid rang la snang
NK106(me)001:2850: sems nyid stong pa'i ngang las chos kyi sku'i 'od
NK106(me)001:2852: snang ba'i cha las lhun grub gzugs kyi sku'i 'od gsal rnam pa lnga 'char ro //
NK106(me)001:2853: dang po ni snang ba dang /
NK106(me)001:2856: nye bar thob pa'i ye shes so //
NK106(me)001:2857: dang po ni rnam shes 'od gsal la thim pa'i skad cig la /
NK106(me)001:2858: phyi rtags sam snang ba la 'od zer lnga smig
NK106(me)001:2859: rgyu'i rnam pa tsam ste 'byung ba'i dngas ma lnga
NK106(me)001:2860: snying po la thim pa'i gnad kyis 'char ro //
NK106(me)001:2861: nang rtags sam ngo bo la bde gsal mi rtog pa'i ye shes me long lta bu 'char te /
NK106(me)001:2863: dang po smig rgyu de nyid kyang //
NK106(me)001:2864: 'od zer lnga dang ldan pa mthong //
NK106(me)001:2866: snang ba zhes bya rnam par mi rtog pa //
NK106(me)001:2867: gsal ba'i cha de gzung rtog spangs pa las //
NK106(me)001:2868: 'byung ba mi 'byung rlung dang bcas pa gang //
NK106(me)001:2869: lhang nger gnas pa skad cig dang po yin //
NK106(me)001:2871: ye shes des zhe sdang las gyur pa'i rtog pa sum cu rtsa gsum 'gag ste /
NK106(me)001:2873: rnam rtog sum cu rtsa gsum po'i ming gang zhe na /
NK106(me)001:2875: 'dod chags dang bral ba bar ma dang /
NK106(me)001:2876: shin tu 'dod chags dang bral ba dang /
NK106(me)001:2904: dogs pa dang bcas pa dang /
NK106(me)001:2906: phrag dog ste rang bzhin gyi rtog pa sum cu rtsa gsum mo zhes so //
NK106(me)001:2907: gnyis pa snang ba mched pa la thim pa'i ye shes kyi dus su /
NK106(me)001:2908: phyi rtags skya wal ba zla ba shar ba lta
NK106(me)001:2909: bu ni yid kun gzhi la 'jug pas shar rtsa'i
NK106(me)001:2911: nang rtags sngar bas gsal ba der 'dzin med pa ste /
NK106(me)001:2913: gnyis pa zla ba lta bu dang //
NK106(me)001:2915: mched pa rnam par rab tu mi rtog ste //
NK106(me)001:2916: ches gsal ba la 'dzin rtog ma zhugs pa //
NK106(me)001:2917: ye shes phra ba rlung bral mi rtog pa //
NK106(me)001:2918: lhan ner gnas pa skad cig gnyis pa yin //
NK106(me)001:2920: ye shes des 'dod chags las byung ba'i rtog pa bzhi bcu 'gag ste /
NK106(me)001:2922: 'dod chags las byung ba'i rtog pa bzhi bcu gang zhe na /
NK106(me)001:2945: lhan cig byed pa'i dga' ba la sbyor ba dang /
NK106(me)001:2946: shin tu dga' ba la sbyor ba dang /
NK106(me)001:2959: ngo tsha ba med pa dang /
NK106(me)001:2963: gya gyu che ba ste 'dod chags las gyur pa'i rtog pa bzhi bcu'o zhes so //
NK106(me)001:2964: gsum pa mched pa thob pa la thim pa'i ye shes ni /
NK106(me)001:2965: phyi rtags su nyi ma shar ba'am me'i snang ba
NK106(me)001:2966: ltar dmar ser du snang ste nyon yid kun gzhir
NK106(me)001:2967: thim pa so sor rtog pa'i ye shes kyi rtsa'i
NK106(me)001:2968: gdangs so // nang rtags su bde gsal 'dzin pa
NK106(me)001:2969: med pa'i ye shes sngon pas lhag pa 'char te
NK106(me)001:2971: gsum pa nyi ma lta bu dang /
NK106(me)001:2973: thob pa'i ye shes shin tu mi rtog pa //
NK106(me)001:2974: gsal ba tsam du'ang mi gnas shin tu phra //
NK106(me)001:2975: rlung sems mi phyed gsal bar 'char ba ste //
NK106(me)001:2976: lham mer gnas pa skad cig gsum pa yin //
NK106(me)001:2978: ye shes des gti mug las gyur pa'i rtog pa bdun 'gag ste /
NK106(me)001:2980: gti mug las gyur pa'i rtog pa bdun gang zhe na /
NK106(me)001:2988: thams cad gti mug las gyur pa'i rtog pa bdun po de dag 'gag go zhes so //
NK106(me)001:2989: bzhi pa thob pa nye bar thob pa la thim pa'i ye shes ni /
NK106(me)001:2990: phyi rtags mthing nag gam ljang nag mun sros pa lta bu ste /
NK106(me)001:2991: gti mug kun gzhi'i cha chos kyi dbyings su thim pas dbus rtsa'i gdangs so //
NK106(me)001:2992: nang rtags sngon pas dngas la 'od gsal bas zhen rtog gi dri ma mtha' dag dag pa ste /
NK106(me)001:2994: bzhi pa mun pa lta bu dang //
NK106(me)001:2996: nye ba thob dri ma med pa ste //
NK106(me)001:2997: rang byung rang gsal bde ba dmigs su med //
NK106(me)001:2998: phra rags rang bzhin ting 'dzin mchog mi 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:2999: skad cig bzhi par mi 'gyur khyab byed yin //
NK106(me)001:3001: de'i dus su snying ga'i rtsa dar dkar gyi skud
NK106(me)001:3002: pa 'dra ba'i nang gi khrag dbugs kyi dngas ma
NK106(me)001:3003: la thig le a ham rdzogs par thim nas shin
NK106(me)001:3004: tu spros pa dang bral ba'i ye shes sangs rgyas
NK106(me)001:3005: kyi chos sku mngon du 'char ro //
NK106(me)001:3006: 'od gsal bzhi rim gyis 'char ba yang a ham
NK106(me)001:3007: snying ga'i rtsa 'dab tu 'dus pa dngas ma'i rtsa
NK106(me)001:3008: nang gi dngas ma chen po la rim gyis thim
NK106(me)001:3010: de'ang 'od gsal dang po gsum gyi dus su sgrib pa rags pa rnams dbyings su thim la /
NK106(me)001:3011: bzhi pa'i dus su phra ba thim pas sgrib pa
NK106(me)001:3012: mtha' dag dang bral ba'i skabs shig der 'byung bas
NK106(me)001:3013: ye thog tu grol ba'i 'thad pa ste /
NK106(me)001:3014: sangs rgyas mngon du byed dus bzhin no //
NK106(me)001:3015: de'ang sangs rgyas kyi spangs pas mi ldog la /
NK106(me)001:3016: 'di ngo ma shes na ldog pa ni /
NK106(me)001:3017: sangs rgyas kyis lam du spangs pa yin la /
NK106(me)001:3018: 'di spangs pa med pas ldog go //
NK106(me)001:3019: ngo shes nas mi ldog pa ni /
NK106(me)001:3020: ngo shes dus grol nas mngon shes la sogs zag
NK106(me)001:3021: med brnyes pas ldog pa'i gnas med pa yin pa'i
NK106(me)001:3022: phyir ro // chos sku'i 'od gsal lo //
NK106(me)001:3023: de nas lhun grub gzugs sku'i 'od gsal ni skad cig bzhi pa'i rjes de nyid la 'char te /
NK106(me)001:3025: lnga pa sprin med nam mkha' la //
NK106(me)001:3026: mi rtog mtha' dbus med pa 'char //
NK106(me)001:3028: dang por ston ka'i nam mkha' sprin med pa lta
NK106(me)001:3029: bu la 'od mthing ga las rnam par snang mdzad
NK106(me)001:3031: de'ang snying ga'i 'od gsal la rigs lnga'i sku dang zhing khams yod pa'i gnad kyis so //
NK106(me)001:3032: de nas mi bskyod pa dang /
NK106(me)001:3035: don yod grub pa'i gtso 'khor rnams tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor du 'char ro //
NK106(me)001:3036: de dag kyang snying nang gi gdangs las rang shar
NK106(me)001:3037: bas 'og min rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor dus
NK106(me)001:3039: sngar ngo 'phrod cing brtan pa yod pa rnams dus der grol lo //
NK106(me)001:3040: de'ang 'od gsal gyi skad cig rnams bsam gtan gyi zhag yin pas /
NK106(me)001:3041: da lta ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par bzhag nas
NK106(me)001:3042: rnam rtog phyi ma ma 'phros snga ma 'gags pa'i
NK106(me)001:3043: bar gyi gsal dngas la ji tsam gnas yun ring
NK106(me)001:3044: ba bar do'i skad cig ma bsam gtan gyi rim
NK106(me)001:3046: da lta nyid nas brtan pa che ba gal che'o //
NK106(me)001:3047: der ngo ma shes na srid pa'i bar do la
NK106(me)001:3048: rmi lam ltar yad yud du snang ba'i phyed snga
NK106(me)001:3050: phyed phyi ma'i gnas dang yul gyi snang bar 'char dus /
NK106(me)001:3052: 'bring gis bskyed rdzogs sgyu ma lta bu /
NK106(me)001:3053: tha mas skyabs 'gro la sogs pas bar do'i 'jigs
NK106(me)001:3054: pa las log nas mtho ris su skyes te phyi
NK106(me)001:3055: ma la grol bar gsungs so //
NK106(me)001:3056: 'phros dang bcas pas 'od gsal rnam pa bzhis lam bgrod pa'i tshul bshad zin to //
NK106(me)001:3057: dbang po tha ma la sgom rim bzhag thabs goms pas rigs 'dzin 'grub tshul gsum yod pa'i /
NK106(me)001:3058: bsgom pa'i rim pa la yang mdor bstan zhi lhag gsum gyi /
NK106(me)001:3061: dbang po tha mas bsgom pa'i rim pa yang //
NK106(me)001:3062: dang por zhi lhag so sor rtsal sbyang ste //
NK106(me)001:3063: brtan par gyur nas zung 'jug dbyer med bsgom //
NK106(me)001:3064: de yang thabs tshul dpag med tshul la bslab //
NK106(me)001:3066: rnam rtog 'dul bar bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:3068: thog mar zhi gnas btsal ba'i rim pa ni //
NK106(me)001:3069: dben pa'i phyogs su stan la rab 'dug nas //
NK106(me)001:3070: dbugs dbyung rngub pa'i kha dog grangs rnams kyis //
NK106(me)001:3071: nyin 'gar rnam rtog 'dul zhing gnas par bya //
NK106(me)001:3072: de'ang bsam gtan gyi tsher ma skye bo'i 'tshe ba
NK106(me)001:3073: dang 'du 'dzi dang klag cor la sogs pa med
NK106(me)001:3074: pa'i gnas rang bzhin gyis yid 'dzin par stan bde
NK106(me)001:3075: ba la 'dug ste skyil krung bcas nas lag pa
NK106(me)001:3077: rtsa gsum gsal ba'i ro ma dkar po nas sna
NK106(me)001:3078: bug g.yas la rlung phyir song bas nad gdon sdig
NK106(me)001:3079: sgrib thams cad sro khang nas du ba song ba
NK106(me)001:3080: ltar sangs / nang du 'jug dus sangs rgyas la
NK106(me)001:3081: sogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin 'od du gyur pa sna
NK106(me)001:3082: bug g.yon nas brkyang ma dmar po'i nang du zhugs
NK106(me)001:3083: te dbu ma'i nang du thim par bsams la dar
NK106(me)001:3084: cig thub thang du steng 'og gi rlung kha sbyar
NK106(me)001:3085: ltar sangs / la gzung / yang dal bus snga ma bzhin btang la lhag cung zad re gzung /
NK106(me)001:3086: rlung gi kha dog ni dpyid gsum sa rlung bad
NK106(me)001:3087: kan gyis 'thibs pa'i dus te de'i gnyen por rlung
NK106(me)001:3089: dbyar gsum me'i tsha ba bsal ba'i phyir chu rlung dkar po /
NK106(me)001:3090: ston gsum mkhris pa g.yo ba bsal ba'i phyir sa rlung ser po /
NK106(me)001:3091: dgun gsum grang ba chu'i gnyen por me'i rlung dmar po bsgom mo //
NK106(me)001:3092: dbyibs ni snying nang du rlung sems kyi dngas ma gzhu lta bu dang /
NK106(me)001:3095: gru bzhi pa rnams bsgom zhing /
