NK106(me)001:3096: de dang mthun pa'i reg bya can no //
NK106(me)001:3097: grangs ni khug pa bdun tshun chad yid kyis bya'o //
NK106(me)001:3098: de'ang las dang po pas rlung de sna bug nas
NK106(me)001:3099: khru bzhi la sogs pa nas je che je ring
NK106(me)001:3100: stong gsum la sogs pa'i bar du spro zhing /
NK106(me)001:3101: de las gzhan gang la'ang yid ma yengs par bya'o //
NK106(me)001:3102: khams 'dus pa'i tshe nang du ma lus par ha drag pos phyir 'phangs pas sel la /
NK106(me)001:3103: bde ba dang dad pa skyes pa la sogs pa'i dus su nang du gzung ngo //
NK106(me)001:3104: de'ang rlung la nyin zhag 'gar sbyangs pas sems gsal
NK106(me)001:3105: dngas gang du'ang mi rtog pa'i zhi gnas skye ste
NK106(me)001:3106: / de'i tshe rags pa'i rlung rgyu ba med cing
NK106(me)001:3107: sems rtog pa med pa na ro brkyang gi dngas
NK106(me)001:3108: ma dkar dmar nyi zla'i cha mi g.yo zhing /
NK106(me)001:3109: de'i nang du rlung zhabs rgyu ba med de dbu
NK106(me)001:3110: mar mi rtog pa'i ngang la gnas pas lhan cig
NK106(me)001:3111: skyes pa'i ye shes ngos zin par 'gyur te /
NK106(me)001:3113: gang du rlung dang sems ni mi rgyu zhing //
NK106(me)001:3114: nyi ma zla ba 'jug pa med gyur pa //
NK106(me)001:3115: mi shes pa dag gnas der sems ni dbugs phyung zhig /
NK106(me)001:3117: dmigs pa rtse gcig pa ni /
NK106(me)001:3118: de nas rnam rtog rags pa rnams mgo non pa dang /
NK106(me)001:3119: de ltar bsgoms pa'i rjes thogs /
NK106(me)001:3120: de nas byams sogs bzhi dang sems gnyis dang //
NK106(me)001:3121: bskyed rim dang ni bris sku glegs bam sogs //
NK106(me)001:3122: dge ba'i yul ni gang yang rung zhig la //
NK106(me)001:3123: dmigs pa rtse gcig ma yengs mnyam par gzhag /
NK106(me)001:3124: de'ang byams sogs tshad med bzhi'am /
NK106(me)001:3127: rnam rtog nye bar zhi ba dang //
NK106(me)001:3128: byang chub sems ni bsgom par bya //
NK106(me)001:3132: ri mo la sogs pa lha'i sku la sems gzung bar /
NK106(me)001:3134: gser gyi kha dog lta bu'i sku lus kyis //
NK106(me)001:3135: 'jig rten mgon po kun nas rab mdzes pa //
NK106(me)001:3136: dmigs pa 'di la gang gi sems 'jug pa //
NK106(me)001:3137: byang chub sems dpa' de ni mnyam gzhag yin //
NK106(me)001:3139: mdor na sngon nas dmigs med la ma goms pas
NK106(me)001:3140: dmigs yul dge ba gang rung zhig las gzhan du
NK106(me)001:3143: dmigs yul la ni sems gtad nas //
NK106(me)001:3144: de rgyun rnam par g.yeng mi bya //
NK106(me)001:3146: zhi gnas kyi ting 'dzin dngos ni /
NK106(me)001:3148: de ltar bzhag pas sems ni las rung zhing //
NK106(me)001:3149: gzhan du mi 'phro gar gtad yul la zin //
NK106(me)001:3150: ji tsam bzhag pa de tsam mnyam par gnas //
NK106(me)001:3151: lus ngag sems ni dga' bdes khyab pa na //
NK106(me)001:3152: rtse gcig mi g.yo'i zhi gnas grub pa yin //
NK106(me)001:3153: yul gang la sems gzung sar mnyam gzhag ma btang ring la rtog pa mi 'phro zhing /
NK106(me)001:3154: sems bde lus bde ngag smra ba nyung zhing tshig
NK106(me)001:3155: 'jam la mdog snum pa ni zhi gnas rtse gcig
NK106(me)001:3158: dge slong rnal 'byor spyod pa bdag gi lus sems las su rung ba yin //
NK106(me)001:3159: zas kyi 'du shes chung ba yin /
NK106(me)001:3160: smra ba nyung zhing tshig 'jam pa yin /
NK106(me)001:3161: pags pa'i mdog kyang rab tu snum pa yin zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK106(me)001:3164: zhi gnas las su rung ba /
NK106(me)001:3165: de nas lhag mthong don la bslab pa ni //
NK106(me)001:3166: phyi rol snang srid 'khor 'das chos 'di rnams //
NK106(me)001:3167: sna tshogs snang bas rmi lam sgyu 'dra zhing //
NK106(me)001:3168: gzugs brnyan sprul pa sgra brnyan dri za'i grong //
NK106(me)001:3169: mig yor smig rgyu 'dra zhing snying po med //
NK106(me)001:3170: snang bas stong ste rang bzhin stong pa'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:3171: gzod ma nas med bzhin snang ba sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad ltar bsgom par bya ste /
NK106(me)001:3172: 'phags pa ting nge 'dzin rgyal po las /
NK106(me)001:3173: chos 'di rnams ni dbu ba chu shing 'dra //
NK106(me)001:3174: sgyu ma lta bu nam mkha'i glog 'dra ste //
NK106(me)001:3175: chu yi zla ba 'dra zhing smig rgyu bzhin //
NK106(me)001:3177: ji ltar dri za'i grong khyer smig rgyu dang //
NK106(me)001:3178: sgyu ma ji bzhin rmi lam ci 'dra bar //
NK106(me)001:3179: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin shes bya ste //
NK106(me)001:3180: mtshan mar bsgom pa ngo bo nyid kyis stong //
NK106(me)001:3182: nam mkha' mdzod kyi mdo las /
NK106(me)001:3183: chos gcig gis ni chos rnams thams cad sgyu ma dang //
NK106(me)001:3184: smig rgyu dang 'dra gzung byar med cing gsog dang ni //
NK106(me)001:3185: brdzun zhing ther zug min pa rjes su rtogs gyur pa //
NK106(me)001:3186: de ni ring por mi thogs byang chub snying por 'gro //
NK106(me)001:3188: 'di ltar blo 'khrul ngor snang ba'i ma dag pa snod bcud thams cad dang /
NK106(me)001:3189: dag pa dkon mchog gi snang ba thams cad kyang rmi lam ltar don la ma grub la /
NK106(me)001:3190: 'khrul ngor bag chags sam bsags pa'i dbang gis sang ba ste //
NK106(me)001:3191: de'i snang ba la shar ba de kun dag dag
NK106(me)001:3192: 'dra yang gnyis bcas kyi snang ngor shar bas brdzun
NK106(me)001:3194: mya ngan las 'das pa yang rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu zhes gsungs pa yin no //
NK106(me)001:3195: 'khrul ngor snang ba'i sangs rgyas brdzun pa sprul pa'i rang bzhin chu'i zla ba ltar /
NK106(me)001:3196: dbyings chos sku dang longs sku las ma 'phos bzhin snang ba brdzun gyi /
NK106(me)001:3197: dag pa sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin 'og min na
NK106(me)001:3198: bzhugs pa med pa'i brdzun pa ni ma yin no
NK106(me)001:3199: // de'ang 'khrul rtog gis 'khor ba dang de'i bde
NK106(me)001:3200: sdug gcig nas gcig tu brgyud cing tshe rabs bgrangs
NK106(me)001:3201: // pa 'dra yang / dus de nyid nas sems
NK106(me)001:3202: nyid skye ba med pa'i ngang la ltos na 'khor
NK106(me)001:3203: ma 'khor med pa rmi lam ltar 'khrul pa bag
NK106(me)001:3204: chags kyi gnyid la shar dus nas 'khrul snang yod
NK106(me)001:3206: 'phags pa nye bar 'khor gyis zhus pa las /
NK106(me)001:3207: sems dmyal 'jigs pa nga yis bstan byas te //
NK106(me)001:3208: sems can stong phrag du ma skyo byas kyang //
NK106(me)001:3209: gang dag shi 'phos ngan song dag 'gro ba'i //
NK106(me)001:3210: 'gro ba de dag nam yang yod ma yin //
NK106(me)001:3211: gang dag ral gri mda' chen mtshon 'byin pa'i //
NK106(me)001:3212: gnod pa byed pa'ang yod pa ma yin te //
NK106(me)001:3213: lus la 'bab mthong de na mtshon cha med //
NK106(me)001:3214: sna tshogs yid dga' me tog kha bye zhing //
NK106(me)001:3215: gser gyi khang mchog 'bar ba yid 'ong ba //
NK106(me)001:3216: 'di na de la'ang byed pa 'ga' med de //
NK106(me)001:3217: de dag rtog pa'i dbang gis bzhag pa yin //
NK106(me)001:3218: rtog pa'i dbang gis 'jig rten rnam btags te //
NK106(me)001:3219: 'du shes 'dzin pas byis pa rnam par phye //
NK106(me)001:3220: 'dzin dang 'dzin med de yang byung med de //
NK106(me)001:3221: yongs su rtog pa sgyu ma smig rgyu bzhin //
NK106(me)001:3223: mdor na snang btags kyi chos 'di dag sgyu ma'i
NK106(me)001:3224: dpe brgyad ltar med la snang ba sang seng 'al
NK106(me)001:3225: 'ol du bsgom pa la brtson par bya'o //
NK106(me)001:3227: de ltar sgyu mar 'dzin pa tsam yang mi dmigs pas nam mkha' ltar bsgom pa ni /
NK106(me)001:3229: thams cad nam mkha' 'dra zhing bdag med pas //
NK106(me)001:3230: skye med spros dang bral bar mnyam par gzhag /
NK106(me)001:3231: de yis phyi rol chos la bdag med cing //
NK106(me)001:3232: gzung dang gzung yul rang bzhin med par rtogs //
NK106(me)001:3233: de'ang snang la bden par med pa de yang btags pa tsam las /
NK106(me)001:3234: don la rang bzhin gyis yod med spros pa'i yul ma yin pa'i ngang la mnyam par gzhag go //
NK106(me)001:3235: des ni phyi bden pa'am bden med sgyu mar 'dzin pa'i rtog pa'ang ldog pas /
NK106(me)001:3236: de'i tshe gzung ba'i yul mi dmigs par rtogs dus
NK106(me)001:3237: de la zhen cha gzung rtog gi blo ma grub
NK106(me)001:3238: pas zhar la 'dzin pa'ang ma grub par shes te
NK106(me)001:3239: / gang gi ngo bor med cing dmigs pa las
NK106(me)001:3240: 'das pa'i chos nyid du rtogs shing bsgom par bya'o
NK106(me)001:3242: 'phags pa ting nge 'dzin gyi rgyal po las /
NK106(me)001:3243: sngon 'das dus kyi bskal pa bsam yas na //
NK106(me)001:3244: mi yi gtso bo byung bar ngas dran te //
NK106(me)001:3245: drang srong chen po gzings kyi don mdzad pa //
NK106(me)001:3246: ming ni dngos po med las byung zhes bya //
NK106(me)001:3247: skyes ma thag tu mkha' la rab tu gnas //
NK106(me)001:3248: chos rnams thams cad dngos po med par bstan //
NK106(me)001:3249: de tshe de dang mthun par mtshan btags pa'i //
NK106(me)001:3250: sgra ni 'jig rten kun tu grags par byas //
NK106(me)001:3251: lha rnams thams cad rab tu sgra 'byin pa //
NK106(me)001:3252: dngos po med ces bya ba'i rgyal bar gyur //
NK106(me)001:3253: skyes ma thag tu gom pa bdun por te //
NK106(me)001:3254: rgyal bas chos rnams dngos po med par bshad //
NK106(me)001:3255: thub pa chos rnams thams cad ston pa yi //
NK106(me)001:3256: sangs rgyas chos kyi rgyal por nam gyur tshe //
NK106(me)001:3257: r+ts+wa shing gel pa sman ri brag rnams las //
NK106(me)001:3258: chos rnams dngos po med ces sgra yang byung //
NK106(me)001:3259: 'jig rten de na ji snyed sgra yod pa //
NK106(me)001:3260: thams cad dngos med ci yang med pa zhes //
NK106(me)001:3261: de lta bu ni 'jig rten 'dren pa yi //
NK106(me)001:3262: sgra dbyangs rnam pa shin tu byung bar gyur //
NK106(me)001:3264: bzhag thabs la bcu gsum las /
NK106(me)001:3266: de ltar bsgoms pa'i rjes thogs /
NK106(me)001:3267: de nas nang gi sems la 'di ltar brtag /
NK106(me)001:3268: sna tshogs rtog la ngo bo med pa'i sems //
NK106(me)001:3269: dgag sgrub bden brdzun bde sdug btang snyoms sogs //
NK106(me)001:3270: yul la 'phro zhing ngos gzung med pa khyod //
NK106(me)001:3271: dang pa gang 'ongs da lta gang na gnas //
NK106(me)001:3272: tha ma gar 'gro dbyibs dang kha dog ci //
NK106(me)001:3273: snyam du brtags tshe 'di ltar mthong bar 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:3275: de'ang yul sna tshogs la dga' mi dga' yin ma
NK106(me)001:3276: yin bden brdzun bde sdug la sogs par sha ra
NK106(me)001:3282: dbyibs dang mtshan ma ci 'dra zhes skad cig kyang
NK106(me)001:3283: ma yengs par brtags shing gzhig ras dpyad pa la
NK106(me)001:3287: 'di la chos rnams kyi so sor rtog pa'i shes
NK106(me)001:3288: rab gang zhe na sems yongs su tshol ba'i brtson
NK106(me)001:3289: 'grus so zhes gsungs pa'i don to //
NK106(me)001:3290: de ltar brtags pas rtog pa'i yul dang so sor
NK106(me)001:3291: rtog pa'i shes rab de nyid kyang mi dmigs pa
NK106(me)001:3292: shing las me byung dus shing nyid kyang tshig pa
NK106(me)001:3293: las / bud shing zad nas gnyis ka ngo bo med pa ltar rtogs pa ni /
NK106(me)001:3295: dper na shing nyid rlung gis drud pa las //
NK106(me)001:3296: me byung nas ni de nyid sreg par byed //
NK106(me)001:3297: de bzhin shes rab dbang po skyes nas ni //
NK106(me)001:3298: so sor rtog pa de nyid sreg par byed //
NK106(me)001:3301: 'dzin pa ma grub par rtogs pa ni /
NK106(me)001:3303: de la so sor dpyod pa'i /
NK106(me)001:3304: sems ni dang por skye ba'i rgyus stong zhing //
NK106(me)001:3305: bar du gnas dang tha mar 'gag pas stong //
NK106(me)001:3306: kha dog dbyibs med ngo bo ngos gzung med //
NK106(me)001:3307: 'das pa 'gags shing ma 'ongs ma skyes la //
NK106(me)001:3308: da lta mi gnas phyi nang gang na'ang med //
NK106(me)001:3309: nam mkha' 'dra zhing spros dang bral bar shes //
NK106(me)001:3310: 'di ltar sems de ni yod pa ltar snang ba rtog pas bslad pa ste /
NK106(me)001:3311: don la ngo bo gang yang med pa la skye rgyu med pas dang por skye ba'i rgyus stong /
NK106(me)001:3312: ma skyes pa la gnas mkhan med pas gnas pa ngo bos stong /
NK106(me)001:3313: mi gnas pa la 'gag rgyu med pas 'gag pa rang gi mtshan nyid kyis stong /
NK106(me)001:3317: phyi nang bar gsum du btsal zhing dpyad kyang mi rnyed de /
NK106(me)001:3318: ma rnyed pa'i ngang de dpe nam mkha' ltar ngos
NK106(me)001:3319: gzung dpyad ra med par sang nge ba yangs phyam
NK106(me)001:3320: me ba bya byed dang bral ba zhig 'byung ba
NK106(me)001:3321: ni chos sku rang lugs kyi dgongs pa ste /
NK106(me)001:3323: rtsa ba med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK106(me)001:3324: btsal bas ma rnyed ngos gzung med //
NK106(me)001:3325: ji bzhin ye bzhin stong pa'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:3326: brjod bral rang byung ye shes so //
NK106(me)001:3330: de tshe sems la gang yang mi bsam par //
NK106(me)001:3331: chad pa ngal gso bzhin du lhod kyis glod //
NK106(me)001:3332: ci yang mi bsam yid la byed pa bor //
NK106(me)001:3333: thams cad gnyis med mnyam pa'i ngang la gzhag /
NK106(me)001:3334: khur gyis dub pa ngal gso ba ltar sngar rtog
NK106(me)001:3335: dpyod kyi rnam pas dpyad dpyad pa'i gom pa dor
NK106(me)001:3336: bas ngal ba na mtha' gtugs pa'am ngal sar sleb
NK106(me)001:3337: pa ltar phyam gyis song ba ste /
NK106(me)001:3338: rang lugs su lhod kyis glod pas dran bsam gang
NK106(me)001:3339: yang med la rig pa'i mdangs bde ba dang bcas
NK106(me)001:3340: pa ma 'gags par snang ba thams cad khrol le
NK106(me)001:3341: shigs se bun ne ba'i ngang gzhag go //
NK106(me)001:3343: 'jur bus bcings pa'i sems de ni //
NK106(me)001:3344: glod na grol bar the tshom med //
NK106(me)001:3345: rmongs rnams gang gis 'ching gyur pa //
NK106(me)001:3346: mkhas rnams de yis rnam par grol //
NK106(me)001:3348: spyir yang sems ni bsgrims te rtse gcig tu bzung na 'phro rang 'phro la /
NK106(me)001:3349: gang dgar song zhig ces glod na rang sor gnas
NK106(me)001:3350: pa chos nyid yin te rnga mo dang 'dra bar
NK106(me)001:3352: bcings pa dag ni phyogs bcur 'gro bar rtsom //
NK106(me)001:3353: thongs par gyur na mi g.yo brtan par gnas //
NK106(me)001:3354: go log rnga mo lta bur bdag gis rtogs //
NK106(me)001:3355: bu khyod rnams kyang rang la cer te ltos //
NK106(me)001:3357: de'ang gzings kyi bya rog ltar sems kyang 'phro ru bcug nas /
NK106(me)001:3358: da cung zad kyang nang du ma 'ong zhig ces byas na /
NK106(me)001:3359: phyi yul la 'phro ba bzhin byas kyang nang du
NK106(me)001:3360: log nas stong pa rang gnas kyi dgongs pa la
NK106(me)001:3363: yul nyid rnam par dag ste bston bya min //
NK106(me)001:3364: stong pa 'ba' zhig gis ni spyad par bya //
NK106(me)001:3365: ji ltar gzings las 'phur ba'i bya rog ni //
NK106(me)001:3366: bskor zhing bskor zhing slar yang de ru babs //
NK106(me)001:3368: gzugs sogs kyi yul rnams la sems 'phro ba'i dus su /
NK106(me)001:3369: yul bden par med pas blo yang skad cig gis
NK106(me)001:3370: de la brten par mi byed de rang log nas
NK106(me)001:3371: dpyad ra med pa'i stong pa nyid du gnas so
NK106(me)001:3372: // dpe phyi'i rgya mtsho la gzings kha nas 'phur
NK106(me)001:3373: ba'i bya rog phyi'i yul la mi brten par gzings
NK106(me)001:3374: de nyid du babs pa bzhin no //
NK106(me)001:3377: de yis ngar 'dzin gang zag bdag med cing //
NK106(me)001:3378: 'dzin pa'i sems la rang bzhin med par rtogs //
NK106(me)001:3379: de ltar nga dang bdag tu zhen pa'i rnam rtog
NK106(me)001:3380: rtsad bcad pas ma rnyed pa'i don la goms pas
NK106(me)001:3381: 'dzin byed gang zag gi bdag med pas 'dzin pa
NK106(me)001:3383: sngar gzung yul ngo bo med pas gzung ba bdag med par rtogs te /
NK106(me)001:3384: bdag gnyis kyis stong par rtogs pas 'khor bar skye
NK106(me)001:3385: ba'i yul dang skye mkhan gnyis ma grub ste 'khor
NK106(me)001:3386: ba rang bzhin med par grol ba ni mya ngan
NK106(me)001:3387: las 'das pa'i dgongs par phyin pa'o //
NK106(me)001:3388: de'ang 'khor ba sems las gzhan ma yin pas de'i phyir te /
NK106(me)001:3390: 'khor ba'i rang bzhin sems kyi ngo bo nyid yin zhes //
NK106(me)001:3391: rmongs rnams mda' bsnun gyis smras tsen na shes par gyis //
NK106(me)001:3393: de ltar rtogs dus tshe 'dir ma grol yang phyi mar grol nges te /
NK106(me)001:3394: dbu ma bzhi brgya pa las /
NK106(me)001:3395: de nyid shes pas gal te 'dir //
NK106(me)001:3396: mya ngan 'das pa ma thob kyang //
NK106(me)001:3397: skye ba phyi mar 'bad med par //
NK106(me)001:3400: dpe dge ba'am mi dge ba rlabs che bas mi
NK106(me)001:3401: myong mi srid par phyi ma la myong bar 'gyur
NK106(me)001:3402: ba'i las bzhin te nges par myong 'gyur gyi las
NK106(me)001:3403: bzhin zhes so // brtan pa thob tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:3404: zhi lhag so sor brtan pa thob pa /
NK106(me)001:3405: de nas zung 'jug gnyug ma'i ye shes ni //
NK106(me)001:3406: snang sems gnyis med chu dang chu zla bzhin //
NK106(me)001:3407: rdzing bur chu zla shar dus chu dang zla gzugs
NK106(me)001:3408: tha dad med pa ltar snang ba dang snang ba
NK106(me)001:3409: 'dzin pa'i dus de'i blo gnyis su med pa'o //
NK106(me)001:3411: snang yul la mi zer ba yin par go bar bya'o //
NK106(me)001:3412: snang yul dang de'i stong pa gnyis chu dang chu zla ltar gnyis med du gnas so //
NK106(me)001:3413: gnyis med kyi don la bslab tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:3414: de ltar yin yang ma rig pas /
NK106(me)001:3415: gnyis su gzung bas srid par 'khrul na yang //
NK106(me)001:3416: gnyis med shes pas mya ngan 'das zhir 'gro //
NK106(me)001:3417: de bas gnyis med don la 'di ltar bslab //
NK106(me)001:3418: chos rnams ma skyes sems kyi ngo bo nyid //
NK106(me)001:3419: sems kyi rang bzhin dag cing dri ma med //
NK106(me)001:3420: dri med stong gsal spros dang bral bar gzhag /
NK106(me)001:3421: don med pa la bdag tu gzung bas srid par
NK106(me)001:3422: 'khrul pa rmi lam gyi chu la 'jigs par gzung
NK106(me)001:3423: bas slar 'jigs sngangs je cher gyur pa ltar song
NK106(me)001:3424: ba'i 'khrul snang gi bag chags brtan pa bas bskyed
NK106(me)001:3425: pa ni sems kyi 'khrul snang las gzhan du ma
NK106(me)001:3427: 'khrul snang 'char ba'i gzhi sems de yang rang bzhin
NK106(me)001:3428: gyis dag cing ngo bo med pas nyon mongs pa'i
NK106(me)001:3429: dri mas gos ma myong bar shes te /
NK106(me)001:3431: sems de'i rang bzhin 'od gsal bas na nyon mongs ngo bo med gzigs nas //
NK106(me)001:3433: dri ma med pa'i ye shes /
NK106(me)001:3434: mtha' yis ma gos pa'i snying po /
NK106(me)001:3435: spros pa dang bral ba'i ngo bo nyid nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang la bzhag ste /
NK106(me)001:3436: rtog dpyod kyi tshol khro gang yang mi bya'o //
NK106(me)001:3437: byas na sems nyid brnyogs pas 'khor ba'i kun rtog
NK106(me)001:3438: 'phel ba dug sbrul gzeb na yod pa de nyid
NK106(me)001:3439: rang sor bzhag na gnod pa med la gtses na
NK106(me)001:3440: gnod pa ltar / sems kyang rtsol sgrub dang blang dor med par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:3441: mi zad pa'i gter mdzod man ngag gi glu las /
NK106(me)001:3442: sems nyid rnal ma'i don ni kun gyis rtogs dka' ba //
NK106(me)001:3443: mtha' yis ma gos dri ma med pa'i snying po ni //
NK106(me)001:3444: rang bzhin gdod nas dag pas kun gyis dpyad bya min //
NK106(me)001:3445: gal te dpyad na dug sbrul gtses pa kho nar zad //
NK106(me)001:3448: ji ltar snang ba de bzhin nyid du gcig /'di la sus kyang 'chos par ma byed cig /
NK106(me)001:3449: ma bcos mnyam pa'i rgyal po de la ni //
NK106(me)001:3450: mi rtog chos sku'i dgongs pa ngang gis gnas //
NK106(me)001:3452: mtha' bral dbu mar rtogs tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:3454: de yis nyon mongs rnyogs pa rab zhi zhing //
NK106(me)001:3455: rnam par mi rtog ye shes chen por gnas //
NK106(me)001:3456: rig dang mngon shes ting 'dzin 'grub 'gyur zhing //
NK106(me)001:3457: gzung 'dzin gnyis med mtha' bral dbu mar rtogs //
NK106(me)001:3458: nyon mongs pa'i rnyog pa zhi zhing gzung 'dzin gnyis
NK106(me)001:3459: su med pa'i ye shes rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK106(me)001:3460: ting nge 'dzin gyis rig pa dang grol ba'i yon
NK106(me)001:3461: tan spyan dang mngon shes 'grub ste /
NK106(me)001:3463: bsam gtan gyis ni 'dod pa'i yon tan smad pa 'dor //
NK106(me)001:3464: rig dang mngon par shes dang ting 'dzin mngon par 'grub //
NK106(me)001:3466: bsgom bya sgom byed dang bral ba sangs rgyas kyi dgongs par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:3468: de tshe sems ni nam mkha' lta bu la //
NK106(me)001:3469: yul ni mi dmigs rang bzhin spros dang bral //
NK106(me)001:3470: bsgom dang bsgom bya med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK106(me)001:3471: bya rgyu byed mkhan med pas gdod ma'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:3472: dri med rang bzhin dag pa'i sangs rgyas yin //
NK106(me)001:3473: mnyam par bzhag pa de'i tshe sems ni spro bsdu
NK106(me)001:3474: dang bral ba nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang las snang
NK106(me)001:3475: yul snang yang 'dzin pa mi dmigs pas rang bzhin
NK106(me)001:3476: gnyis kyi 'du shes 'jug pa med pa'i gnyis med
NK106(me)001:3477: kyi ye shes / sgom dang bsgom mkhan gnyis su
NK106(me)001:3478: med pas bya rgyu dang byed mkhan rang sar grol
NK106(me)001:3479: ba ni sems sems byung gi 'jug pa dbyings su
NK106(me)001:3480: thim pas rang bzhin gdod ma'i dbyings su dus der
NK106(me)001:3481: kyi ye shes / phyin te / sems nyid don
NK106(me)001:3482: gyi sangs rgyas chos sku rang gnas kyi dgongs pa
NK106(me)001:3485: ma lus rgyun du gnas pa'i sangs rgyas de //
NK106(me)001:3486: sems ni ngo bo nyid kyis dag pas na //
NK106(me)001:3487: de nyid dri med mchog gi go 'phang ngo //
NK106(me)001:3489: de'i tshe sems sems byung sems nyid rang bzhin gyis
NK106(me)001:3490: dag pa la thim pas rnam rtog mi g.yo ba
NK106(me)001:3491: lan tsh+wa chu la thim pa lta bu yang /
NK106(me)001:3493: rnam rtog yid ni mi g.yo brtan par gnas //
NK106(me)001:3494: ji ltar lan tsh+wa chu la thim pa ltar //
NK106(me)001:3495: de ltar sems ni rang bzhin la thim 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:3496: de tshe bdag dang gzhan ni mnyam par mthong //
NK106(me)001:3498: chos nyid rtogs pa'i tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:3500: gzung yul mi dmigs chu zla mig yor la //
NK106(me)001:3501: 'dzin mkhan mi dmigs g.yo med phyogs ltung bral //
NK106(me)001:3502: snang sems gnyis med pha rol phyin pa'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:3503: zab zhi spros bral 'od gsal 'dus ma byas //
NK106(me)001:3504: bdud rtsi lta bu'i chos nyid khong du chud //
NK106(me)001:3505: phyi gzung ba'i yul lnga chu zla lam mig yor
NK106(me)001:3506: ltar rtogs pas gzung ba'i rtog pas bden par zhen
NK106(me)001:3507: pa'i dmigs pa cung zad kyang med cing /
NK106(me)001:3508: nang 'dzin pa'i shes pa cha med nam mkha' ltar
NK106(me)001:3509: rtogs pas der 'dzin ngo bo nyid kyis stong ste
NK106(me)001:3510: / gzung 'dzin gnyis su med pa'i shes pa rang
NK106(me)001:3511: so spro bsdu med pa ni shes rab kyi pha
NK106(me)001:3517: so so rang gi ye shes bdud rtsi lta bu ste /
NK106(me)001:3518: zab zhi spros bral 'od gsal 'dus ma byas //
NK106(me)001:3519: bdud rtsi lta bu'i chos shig bdag gis rnyed //
NK106(me)001:3522: pha rol mya ngan las 'das pa /
NK106(me)001:3523: de gnyis kyi bar slob pa'i lam gsum mi dmigs
NK106(me)001:3524: pas shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa yang
NK106(me)001:3526: tshu rol pha rol mtha' la min //
NK106(me)001:3527: de dag par na mi gnas pa //
NK106(me)001:3528: dus rnams mnyam pa nyid shes phyir //
NK106(me)001:3529: shes rab pha rol phyin par 'dod //
NK106(me)001:3531: lta ba mthar phyin pa'i tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:3532: de lta bu'i ngang la gnas pa ni /
NK106(me)001:3533: 'dzin med yangs pa'i ting 'dzin gru chen gyis //
NK106(me)001:3534: srid gsum rgya mtsho'i pha rol brgal bas na //
NK106(me)001:3535: bzhi bde'i steng du blo bde rgyun mi 'chad //
NK106(me)001:3536: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang du phyin //
NK106(me)001:3537: lta ba yangs pa chen po'i don rtogs pa'i ngang
NK106(me)001:3538: la gnas pa gru lta bus 'khor ba spros pa'i
NK106(me)001:3540: gzhi ye nas spros pa med par /
NK106(me)001:3541: glod dus der spros pa med par 'dres te dbyings
NK106(me)001:3542: ye shes gnyis su med pa la rdzogs pa chen
NK106(me)001:3543: po'i ngang zhes btags pas der phyin zhes bya ste
NK106(me)001:3544: / rang byung byas pa med pa'i don kun rdzogs pa'i rtogs pa 'char ba yang /
NK106(me)001:3546: kye de phyir kun byed nga yis lung bstan pa //
NK106(me)001:3547: thos pa'i don la ma nor brtan par byos //
NK106(me)001:3548: bya btsal kun dang bral ba'i 'phrin las kyis //
NK106(me)001:3549: ma byas don kun rdzogs pa'i rtogs pa 'char //
NK106(me)001:3551: zhi lhag mtshan nyid pa ngos gzung ba ni /
NK106(me)001:3552: de ltar mnyam par bzhag dus sems spro bsdu med par lhan ner /
NK106(me)001:3553: gnas pas zhi gnas chos sku stong pa la //
NK106(me)001:3554: gsal bas lhag mthong gzugs sku snang ba nyid //
NK106(me)001:3555: thabs dang shes rab tshogs gnyis bskyed rdzogs grub //
NK106(me)001:3556: de'ang gnas pas mi rtog pa stong pa'i cha ni
NK106(me)001:3557: zhi gnas chos kyi sku'i rgyu can ye shes kyi
NK106(me)001:3558: tshogs shes rab rdzogs pa'i rim pa la /
NK106(me)001:3559: gsal bas snang ba'i cha ni lhag mthong gzugs sku'i
NK106(me)001:3560: rgyu can bsod nams kyi tshogs thabs bskyed pa'i rim
NK106(me)001:3562: de'i dus su dmigs pa med pa don gyi pha rol tu phyin pa drug rdzogs par yang /
NK106(me)001:3563: tshangs pa khyad par sems kyis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:3565: mi bsrung bar ni tshul khrims so //
NK106(me)001:3566: mi gnas pa ni bzod pa'o //
NK106(me)001:3567: mi brtson pa ni brtson 'grus so //
NK106(me)001:3568: mi sems pa ni bsam gtan no //
NK106(me)001:3569: mi dmigs pa ni shes rab bo //
NK106(me)001:3571: de'ang sbyin sogs drug spyod pa ni de la gnas
NK106(me)001:3572: pas de dag gi pha rol tu ma phyin la
NK106(me)001:3573: / de dag gi sems dpa' thams cad las 'das pa na pha rol tu phyin par gyur pa'o //
NK106(me)001:3574: de'i dus su don gyi tshul khrims kyang rdzogs te /
NK106(me)001:3575: lha'i bu blo gros rab gnas kyis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:3576: gang tshul khrims dang tshul khrims 'chal pa mi dmigs
NK106(me)001:3577: pa 'di ni tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin
NK106(me)001:3578: pa'o zhes so // tshogs gnyis kyang rdzogs par /
NK106(me)001:3579: sa'i snying po 'khor lo bcu pa las /
NK106(me)001:3580: de la mi dmigs pa ni bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs so zhes pa dang /
NK106(me)001:3581: ye shes dam pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:3582: byang chub sems dpa' ye shes tog gis gsol ba /
NK106(me)001:3583: dge slong rnal 'byor spyod pa pa rnams kyis tshogs ji ltar bsag par bgyi /
NK106(me)001:3585: tshogs ni bsod nams dang ye shes so //
NK106(me)001:3586: bsag pa ni mang du spel ba'o //
NK106(me)001:3588: bsod nams kyi tshogs ji ltar lags /
NK106(me)001:3590: sbyin pa la sogs pa dkar po'i chos mtshan ma dang bcas pa'o //
NK106(me)001:3592: ye shes kyi tshogs gang lags /
NK106(me)001:3594: shes rab la sogs pa mtshan ma med pa'o //
NK106(me)001:3596: de gnyis ji ltar gsog pa lags //
NK106(me)001:3598: bsod nams kyi tshogs ni 'khor ba'i tshogs zhes bya ste /
NK106(me)001:3599: dper na ba lang gi rmig rjes kyi chu dang mtshungs so //
NK106(me)001:3604: lha dang mi'i bde ba myong nas slar ngan song du 'khor ba yin no //
NK106(me)001:3605: ye shes kyi tshogs ni mya ngan las 'das pa'i tshogs zhes bya ste /
NK106(me)001:3606: dper na rgya mtsho chen po'i chu lta bu /
NK106(me)001:3610: mya ngan las 'das pa thob par byed pa'o //
NK106(me)001:3611: ye shes tog ye shes kyi tshogs kho na bsag par bya'o zhes so //
NK106(me)001:3612: de'ang bsod nams cha mthun rnams thar pa cha mthun
NK106(me)001:3613: du bsgyur zhing bsam gtan pas bsam gtan gtso bor
NK106(me)001:3615: zhi lhag gnyis kyi byed las ni /
NK106(me)001:3617: lhag mthong rtogs pa'i shes rab bskyed byas nas //
NK106(me)001:3618: zhi gnas kyis ni de yi ngang la gnas //
NK106(me)001:3619: yang sngar lhag mthong gis rtogs pa'i don la 'dris
NK106(me)001:3620: pa ni zhi gnas la rag las pas kyang zung
NK106(me)001:3621: 'brel du 'grub par bya ba la nges par 'bad
NK106(me)001:3622: do // de ltar goms pas dmigs med rtogs pa'i dus ni /
NK106(me)001:3623: ji ltar zhe na mnyam par 'jog pa'i dus /
NK106(me)001:3624: gang tshe gzung 'dzin dngos dang dngos med du //
NK106(me)001:3625: blo yi rnam pa rab tu mi gnas pa //
NK106(me)001:3626: de tshe dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med par //
NK106(me)001:3627: sems dang sems byung dmigs pa med par zhi //
NK106(me)001:3628: yang dag pa'i don bsgom dus gzung 'dzin dngos po
NK106(me)001:3629: dang dngos med rang bzhin med par rtogs pa ni
NK106(me)001:3630: dang por bya ba'i lhag mthong yin la /
NK106(me)001:3631: de ltar rtogs pa'i ngang la blo'i rnam pa skye
NK106(me)001:3632: ba med par gnas pa ni phyi nas bya ba'i
NK106(me)001:3633: zhi gnas te / dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su
NK106(me)001:3634: med pa na de gnyis dbyer med pa ni zung
NK106(me)001:3635: du 'brel ba'i 'bras bu grub pas kyang shes par
NK106(me)001:3636: zhi gnas te / bya ste / spyod 'jug las /
NK106(me)001:3637: gang tshe dngos dang dngos med dag /
NK106(me)001:3638: blo yi mdun na mi gnas pa //
NK106(me)001:3639: de tshe rnam pa gzhan med pas //
NK106(me)001:3640: dmigs pa med par rab tu zhi //
NK106(me)001:3642: goms pas ting 'dzin 'grub tshul la yang drug las /
NK106(me)001:3643: ting nge 'dzin gyi yon tan ni /
NK106(me)001:3644: de ltar goms pa las ting nge 'dzin gyi yon tan ji ltar 'grub pa'i tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:3645: sems la yon tan ye ldan du yod kyang dri mas bsgribs pa'i tshe mi snang bas /
NK106(me)001:3646: zhi gnas dang lhag mthong bsgoms pas sgrib pa ci
NK106(me)001:3647: rigs su dag pa las gnas skabs su thob pa'i
NK106(me)001:3648: tshul te sems kyi kun rtog dbyings su nub pa'i
NK106(me)001:3649: tshe / rang bzhin gdod nas dag pa'i sems nyid la //
NK106(me)001:3650: gnas skabs glo bur kun rtog dag pa na //
NK106(me)001:3651: snyoms 'jug dgu dang rdzu 'phrul mngon shes 'grub //
NK106(me)001:3652: ting 'dzin grangs med gzungs sprin lhun gyis grub //
NK106(me)001:3653: de yang gnas skabs su sems kyi kun rtog dag
NK106(me)001:3654: pas snyoms 'jug la sogs pa yon tan gyi tshogs
NK106(me)001:3659: rang sa 'dod pa'i sems gang rtse gcig pa //
NK106(me)001:3660: de las rtog dang dpyod pa'i ting nge 'dzin //
NK106(me)001:3661: dga' bde'i yan lag bsam gtan dang po skye //
NK106(me)001:3662: de las rtog med dpyod pa'i ting nge 'dzin //
NK106(me)001:3663: sems gsal dga' bde'i rang bzhin gnyis pa skye //
NK106(me)001:3664: de las rtog dpyod gnyis med ting nge 'dzin //
NK106(me)001:3665: dga' bdes brlan pa'i yan lag gsum pa skye //
NK106(me)001:3666: de las dga' ba sdud pa'i ting nge 'dzin //
NK106(me)001:3667: bzhi pa phan yon yan lag bcas pa skye //
NK106(me)001:3668: de la 'gog pa'i sems dang bsam gtan bzhi gzugs
NK106(me)001:3669: med bzhi ste dgu'i ting nge 'dzin ni mthar gyis
NK106(me)001:3670: gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dagu'o //
NK106(me)001:3671: de yang 'dod pa'i sems rtse gcig pa ni sngar
NK106(me)001:3672: bshad pa'i zhi lhag zung 'brel du bsgoms pas sems
NK106(me)001:3673: bde gsal rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes mi
NK106(me)001:3674: la sogs pa 'dod pa'i rten las thob pa ste
NK106(me)001:3675: / skabs 'dir rang gi rten dal 'byor las thog pas mi la sbyar ro //
NK106(me)001:3676: de nas bsam gtan gyi sems ni /
NK106(me)001:3677: nyer bsdogs dang dngos gzhi gnyis las /
NK106(me)001:3678: nyer bsdogs ni sbyor ba ste kha cig las dngos gzhi tsam mo zhes bshad do //
NK106(me)001:3679: de'ang snga ma snga ma'i bsam gtan gyi dngos gzhi
NK106(me)001:3680: phyi ma phyi ma'i nyer bsdogs su bshad par rig
NK106(me)001:3681: par bya'o // dang po sems rtse gcig tu 'jog
NK106(me)001:3682: dus bsam gtan dang po'i nyer bsdogs mi lcogs pa
NK106(me)001:3683: par bya'o // med pa ste / de'ang mnyam par 'jog dgos snyam du rtog pa dang bcas shing /
NK106(me)001:3684: de nyid gang du'ang mi rtog pa'i ngang du 'jog
NK106(me)001:3685: pa'i dran rtsi'i dpyod pa dang bcas pa'i sbyor ba
NK106(me)001:3686: las dngos gzhi mi rtog pa'i ye shes skye'o //
NK106(me)001:3687: thun rjes dang mtshams su rtog dpyod dang ldan pa'o //
NK106(me)001:3689: dang po'i sems kyi nyer bsdogs las rtog pa med la dpyod pa tsam dang bcas pa sbyor ba /
NK106(me)001:3690: dngos gzhi gsal la mi rtog pa'o //
NK106(me)001:3692: gnyis pa'i sems kyi nyer bsdogs las rtog dpyod gang yang med par khrong gis /
NK106(me)001:3693: dngos gzhi khyad par can mi rtog pa skye'o //
NK106(me)001:3695: gsum pa'i sems kyi nyer bsdogs las ting nge 'dzin gyis thob pa'i dga' bde dang bcas pa'i /
NK106(me)001:3696: dngos gzhi khyad par can skye'o //
NK106(me)001:3698: rtog pa dang bcas shing dpyod pa dang bcas pa ni bsam gtan dang po'o //
NK106(me)001:3699: rtog pa med la dpyod pa tsam dang bcas pa ni bsam gtan gnyis pa'o //
NK106(me)001:3700: rtog pa yang med dpyod pa yang med pa'i yid la byed pa ni bsam gtan gsum pa'o //
NK106(me)001:3701: dga' ba sdud pa yid la byed pa ni bsam gtan bzhi pa'o zhes so //
NK106(me)001:3702: bsam gtan gyi sems thob tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:3704: de las mkha' ltar dag cing dngas pa'i sems //
NK106(me)001:3705: nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched thob par 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:3706: de las chos kun sems nyid spros pa med //
NK106(me)001:3707: rnam shes mtha' yas skye mched thob par 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:3708: de las snang sems mi dmigs spros dang bral //
NK106(me)001:3709: ci yang med pa'i skye mched 'grub par 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:3710: de las yod med spros kun bral ba'i sems //
NK106(me)001:3711: yod min med min skye mched 'grub par 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:3712: de las sna tshogs nyon mongs spros pa'i sems //
NK106(me)001:3713: rang bzhin 'gog pa zhi ba thob par 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:3714: 'dir bsam gtan gyi sems thob pa'i rten las gzugs med kyi sems khyad par can skye bas /
NK106(me)001:3715: dang po nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched ni /
NK106(me)001:3716: chos thams cad nam mkha' ltar dag cing dri ma
NK106(me)001:3717: med pa'i ngo bo nyid du yid la byed pa
NK106(me)001:3718: brtan pa'o // rnam shes mtha' yas ni /
NK106(me)001:3720: sems de yang thog mtha' thams cad dang bral zhing mtha' yas par sems pa'i yid la byed pa'o //
NK106(me)001:3722: de yang mi dmigs pas gang du'ang mi mthong ba'i sems so //
NK106(me)001:3724: yod med gang gi'ang mtha' las 'das pa'i yid la byed pa'o //
NK106(me)001:3726: sems kyi spros pa ma lus pa 'gog pa ste /
NK106(me)001:3728: 'dir 'gog pa ni sems kyi spros pa 'gog pa'i phyir te zhes so //
NK106(me)001:3729: dbye na blos gzhigs shing dpyad nas so sor brtags pa'i 'gog pa dang /
NK106(me)001:3730: ma gzhigs par chos nyid kyi ngang la 'jog pa so sor brtags min gyi 'gog pa gnyis so //
NK106(me)001:3731: de'ang byang chub sems dpa'i 'gog pa ni snying rjes sems can rjes su 'dzin pa yin te /
NK106(me)001:3733: rtag tu 'gog par gtogs pa'i bsam gtan yin mod kyi //
NK106(me)001:3734: 'gro ba mgon med pa la snying rje lhag par skye //
NK106(me)001:3736: de lta na spros pa ma bkag go zhe na /
NK106(me)001:3737: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes kyi snying rje skye bas spros pa yod pa ma yin no //
NK106(me)001:3740: mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dgu la snyoms par 'jug par bya'o zhes pa'i don to //
NK106(me)001:3741: spyir so so'i skye bo dang 'phags pa'i bsam gtan
NK106(me)001:3742: ni 'bras bu che ba'i sems kyi bar mnyam du
NK106(me)001:3743: thob pa las / de nas zhi gnas kyi bde
NK106(me)001:3744: ba la phyogs te chos thams cad nam mkha' lta
NK106(me)001:3745: bu'o snyam nas de'i ngang du blo'i 'jug pa nub
NK106(me)001:3746: pa las gzugs med kyi sems kyis srid rtsi'i bar
NK106(me)001:3747: thob pa las / du 'phen la / 'phags pa
NK106(me)001:3748: ni lhag mthong gi ye shes kyis chos thams cad
NK106(me)001:3749: bdag dang bdag gir gzung du med pa'i rang bzhin
NK106(me)001:3750: zung 'brel khyad par can bsgrubs pas /
NK106(me)001:3751: mi che ba'i sems thob nas 'og min gyi bar
NK106(me)001:3752: du mthong sgom gyi ye shes gong ma thob pas
NK106(me)001:3754: de'i sems la bsam gtan gzugs med kyi cha'i yon
NK106(me)001:3755: tan tshang bas ting nge 'dzin de dag la 'jug
NK106(me)001:3756: gi / khams de dag gi sems rang mtshan pa
NK106(me)001:3757: ma yin te theg chen 'phags pa rnams khams gong
NK106(me)001:3758: mar skye ba mi 'dzin pa'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)001:3761: de ltar mthar gyis snyoms 'jug dgu po yang //
NK106(me)001:3762: rim dang rim min thod rgal rtsal sbyangs pas //
NK106(me)001:3763: rang gzhan snga phyi'i tshe rabs las rnams dang //
NK106(me)001:3764: sems kyi spyod yul gang yin shes pa dang //
NK106(me)001:3765: 'chi 'pho skye dang sgrib pas chod kyang mthong //
NK106(me)001:3766: gcig dang du mar rdzu zhing rnam par 'phrul //
NK106(me)001:3767: nyon mongs med cing ji snyed ji bzhin shes //
NK106(me)001:3768: zhing rnams bde gshegs sras kyis gang ba mthong //
NK106(me)001:3769: de la mthar gyis gnas pa'i ting nge 'dzin bsgoms
NK106(me)001:3770: pas sngar mi shes pa'i spyan dang mngon par shes
NK106(me)001:3771: pa sgrib pa med pas rnam par 'phrul zhing /
NK106(me)001:3772: sa gong nas gong du 'phar ba'i yon tan dang
NK106(me)001:3773: zhing khams mthong nas chos nyan pa dang tshogs rdzogs
NK106(me)001:3774: pa la sogs pa byed do //
NK106(me)001:3775: mthar gyis gnas pa de'i sgom tshul la gsum las /
NK106(me)001:3776: seng ge rnam bsgyings ni bsam gtan bzhi dang gzugs
NK106(me)001:3777: med bzhi la yar rim par bsgoms nas mar la
NK106(me)001:3778: yang rim par bsgom pa skas gdang bu dgu pa
NK106(me)001:3779: la yar 'dzeg mar 'bebs byed pa bzhin no //
NK106(me)001:3781: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po'i ting nge
NK106(me)001:3782: 'dzin seng ge rnam par bsgyings pa de gang zhe
NK106(me)001:3784: bsam gtan dang po nye bar bsgrubs te gnas so
NK106(me)001:3785: zhes pa nas 'gog pa dang srid rtse nas bsam
NK106(me)001:3786: gtan dang po'i bar du gsungs so //
NK106(me)001:3787: thod rgal chung ngu ni bsam gtan gzugs med 'gog
NK106(me)001:3788: pa dgu la yar rim gyis bsgoms nas mar bsam
NK106(me)001:3789: gtan dang po mchongs nas bsgom pa'o //
NK106(me)001:3790: thod rgal chen po ni gnyis las /
NK106(me)001:3791: lugs mthun 'gog pa bar du bcug pa ni bsam gtan dang po bsgom /
NK106(me)001:3792: 'gog pa bsgom pa nas 'gog pa'i bar du de bzhin du byed pas mtshon te /
NK106(me)001:3793: nang tshan re bar du bcug nas re mos su bsgom pa'o //
NK106(me)001:3794: mnyam par bzhag pa'i sems bar du bcug pa ni
NK106(me)001:3795: 'gog pa las langs nas mnyam par ma bzhag pa'i
NK106(me)001:3796: sems su byed do zhes mar bsam gtan dang po'i
NK106(me)001:3797: bar du rim gyis bsgom pa'o //
NK106(me)001:3798: de bzhin du bsam gtan dang po nas gsum pa
NK106(me)001:3799: la 'jug pa nas 'gog pa'i bar du yar 'gro
NK106(me)001:3800: mar 'ong re re bar du bor nas bsgom pa
NK106(me)001:3807: brgyad brgyad bar du bor zhing yar 'gro mar 'ong res kyis bsgom pa'i tshul gsungs te /
NK106(me)001:3810: rnam pa gnyis su song 'ongs nas //
NK106(me)001:3811: 'dod par gtogs pa'i rnam par shes //
NK106(me)001:3812: mnyam gzhag min pa'i mtshams bzung ste //
NK106(me)001:3813: thod rgal du ni snyoms 'jug pa //
NK106(me)001:3814: gcig dang gnyis gsum bzhi dang lnga //
NK106(me)001:3815: drug dang bdun dang brgyad brgal nas //
NK106(me)001:3818: spyan lnga dang mngon shes drug ni sngar smos zin to //
NK106(me)001:3819: ting 'dzin gsum thob pa'i dus ni /
NK106(me)001:3820: ting nge 'dzin khyad par can thob pa'i dus /
NK106(me)001:3821: de tshe snang ba sgyur mar rab rtogs pas //
NK106(me)001:3822: sgyu ma lta bu'i ting 'dzin nyid dang ni //
NK106(me)001:3823: sems kyii gdung bral rnyog pa rab zhi'i phyir //
NK106(me)001:3824: zla ba dri ma med pa'i ting 'dzin dang //
NK106(me)001:3825: chos kun mi dmigs mnyam pa'i ngang gcig pas //
NK106(me)001:3826: mkha' ltar gos pa med pa'i ting 'dzin sogs //
NK106(me)001:3827: brgya stong grangs med rab tu 'grub par 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:3828: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gcig nyid mun pa sel bas snang byed dang /
NK106(me)001:3830: pad+mo kha 'byed pas pad+mo'i gnyen la sogs pa tha dad par btags pa de bzhin du /
NK106(me)001:3831: snang ba sgyu mar rtogs nas de'i ngang la rtse
NK106(me)001:3832: gcig pa'i cha nas sgyu ma lta bu'i ting nge
NK106(me)001:3833: 'dzin dang / nyon mongs pa'i mun nag dang gdung
NK106(me)001:3834: ba zhi ba'i cha nas zla ba dri ma med
NK106(me)001:3835: 'dzin dang / pa dang / chos thams cad nam
NK106(me)001:3836: mkha' ltar rtogs pas nam mkha' ltar gos pa med
NK106(me)001:3837: pa la sogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin blo rdzas gcig
NK106(me)001:3838: la cha'i yon tan je mang du gong du 'phel
NK106(me)001:3839: bas brgya stong grangs med pa yang 'thob bo //
NK106(me)001:3840: mdo las sgyu ma lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK106(me)001:3841: ting nge 'dzin zung 'brel thob tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:3843: lhag mthong gis ni rab tu rtogs pa'i don //
NK106(me)001:3844: zhi gnas dam pas rtse gcig gzung ba'i phyir //
NK106(me)001:3845: gzungs dang ting 'dzin zung 'brel lhun gyis grub //
NK106(me)001:3846: so sor rtog pa'i lhag mthong gis chos kyi tshig
NK106(me)001:3847: don legs par rtogs pa rnams zhi gnas kyis rtse
NK106(me)001:3848: gcig tu rgyud la 'dzin pa'i phyir na /
NK106(me)001:3850: zhi gnas ni ting nge 'dzin du gnas te /
NK106(me)001:3852: lhag mthong ni chos kyi sgo'i gzungs so //
NK106(me)001:3853: zhi gnas ni ting nge 'dzin to zhes so //
NK106(me)001:3855: legs par grub pa'i rgyud las /
NK106(me)001:3856: gzungs ni gang phyir rnam gsum gzungs //
NK106(me)001:3857: tshig dang don dang gnyis ka dang //
NK106(me)001:3858: legs pa las ni nyams pa las //
NK106(me)001:3859: 'dzin pa'i phyir na gzungs zhes bya //
NK106(me)001:3861: de dag gis spyi'i rim pa brjod zin to //
NK106(me)001:3862: spyi don gsum pa ji ltar bsgom pa'i lam gyi
NK106(me)001:3863: rim pa bshad pa la tshogs sbyor mthong sgom mi
NK106(me)001:3864: slob lam lnga dgos pa bshad pas mjug bsdu ba
NK106(me)001:3865: drug gi / tshogs lam la gsum ste /
NK106(me)001:3867: da ni bye brag lam gyi rim pa'i dbye ba shes par bya ba ni /
NK106(me)001:3869: lam lnga'i rim pa bgrod las grol ba ste //
NK106(me)001:3870: tshogs lam chung ngur lus tshor sems dang chos //
NK106(me)001:3871: dran pa nye bar gzhag pa bzhi bsgom zhing //
NK106(me)001:3873: sangs rgyas thams cad kyang lam lnga bgrod nas sangs rgyas pas na /
NK106(me)001:3876: dang po tshogs kyi lam ni theg chen byang chub
NK106(me)001:3877: mchog tu sems bskyed de lam dang po bsgom pa
NK106(me)001:3878: nas bzung ste drod rgyud la ma skyes kyi bar
NK106(me)001:3879: gyi thos bsam sgom gsum la sogs pa'i rtogs pa
NK106(me)001:3880: dang ting nge 'dzin dge ba'i tshogs dang bcas pa'i
NK106(me)001:3881: rang bzhin thar pa'i gling du bgrod pa'i lam mo
NK106(me)001:3882: // lam de'i rgyu ni theg chen sems bskyed gsar
NK106(me)001:3883: du skye ba'i rten gang yin pa'i rigs sad pa'o
NK106(me)001:3884: // // 'bras bu ni lam phyi ma bzhi'o //
NK106(me)001:3885: nges tshig ni thos bsam dang bsod nams kyi tshogs gtso bor gyur pas na tshogs lam mo //
NK106(me)001:3887: chung ngur dran pa nye bar gzhag pa bzhi mnyam rjes gnyis kyis bsgom pa ste /
NK106(me)001:3888: de'ang rang dang gzhan gyi lus la mnyam gzhag tu nam mkha' ltar bsgom zhing /
NK106(me)001:3889: rjes thob tu sgyu ma lta bu dang /
NK106(me)001:3890: chags pa'i gnyen por mi gtsang ba'i 'du shes bsgom pa'o //
NK106(me)001:3891: tshor ba'ang mnyam gzhag tu mi dmigs pa dang /
NK106(me)001:3892: rjes thob tu chu shing ltar bsgom mo //
NK106(me)001:3893: sdug bsngal ba nyid du yid la byed do //
NK106(me)001:3894: sems kyang ma skyes pa dang /
NK106(me)001:3895: mi rtag pa nyid du bsgom pa dang /
NK106(me)001:3897: sgyu ma tsam du mnyam rjes su bsgom pa'o //
NK106(me)001:3898: byang chub kyi phyogs bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:3900: gang gis lus nam mkha' dang mtshungs par mthong ba
NK106(me)001:3901: de ni lus la lus kyis rjes su blta ba'i
NK106(me)001:3902: dran pa nye bar gzhag pa'o //
NK106(me)001:3903: tshor ba nang na yang ma yin /
NK106(me)001:3904: phyi rol na yang ma yin /
NK106(me)001:3905: gnyis ka med par yang mi dmigs pa 'di ni
NK106(me)001:3906: tshor ba la rjes su blta ba'i dran pa nye
NK106(me)001:3907: bar gzhag pa'o // sems de ni ming tsam ste
NK106(me)001:3908: rang bzhin gyis ma skyes par mthong ba de ni
NK106(me)001:3909: sems dran pa nye bar gzhag pa'o //
NK106(me)001:3910: chos thams cad gnyis su med par mthong ba de
NK106(me)001:3911: ni chos dran pa nye bar gzhag pa'o zhes so
NK106(me)001:3913: 'bring du snga ma goms pa las phul du byung
NK106(me)001:3914: ba'i yang dag par spong ba bzhi bsgom par bstan
NK106(me)001:3917: dge dang mi dge'i zhen bzhi yang dag spong //
NK106(me)001:3918: de'ang mi dge ba ma skyes pa mi bskyed pa'i phyir 'dun pa bskyed /
NK106(me)001:3921: skyes pa spang ba'i phyir 'bad pa la sogs pa bzhi /
NK106(me)001:3922: dge ba ma skyes pa bskyed pa dang /
NK106(me)001:3923: skyes pa spel ba'i phyir 'bad pa la sogs pa bzhi byed de /
NK106(me)001:3926: de la yang dag par spong ba bzhi gang zhe na /
NK106(me)001:3928: mi dge ba ma skyes pa mi bskyed pa'i phyir 'dun pa bskyed do //
NK106(me)001:3931: brtson 'grus rab tu brtsam mo zhes pa la sogs pa bzhi gsungs so //
NK106(me)001:3934: chen por 'dun sems dpyod dang dran pa bzhis //
NK106(me)001:3935: rdzu 'phrul rten 'grub rkang pa bzhi po bsgom //
NK106(me)001:3939: dran pa'i ting nge 'dzin rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi bsgom ste /
NK106(me)001:3941: 'dun pa'i ting nge 'dzin rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa dang zhes pa bzhi gsungs so //
NK106(me)001:3942: de ltar tshogs lam gyi dus 'dir ni byang chub la dmigs pa'i tshul khrims dang /
NK106(me)001:3943: dbang po'i sgo bsdam pa dang /
NK106(me)001:3944: zas kyi tshod rig pa dang /
NK106(me)001:3945: nam gyi cha stod dang cha smad la mi nyal bas rnal 'byor la brtson pa dang /
NK106(me)001:3946: blang dor gyi bya ba shes bzhin du gnas pas mngon par dga' ba dang /
NK106(me)001:3947: dge ba la mi 'gyod pa dang /
NK106(me)001:3950: mos pa la sogs pa thar pa'i rgyur 'gyur ba'i dge ba gzhan dang /
NK106(me)001:3951: thos bsam sgom gsum la brtson pas sbyor lam la sbyor ba yin no //
NK106(me)001:3952: de'ang tshogs lam chung ngu nas grangs med gsum la
NK106(me)001:3953: sogs pa'i tshogs gsog pa'i 'go rtsom pa yin te
NK106(me)001:3955: bzang dang smon pa'i stobs can dag /
NK106(me)001:3956: sems brtan khyad par 'gro ba yi //
NK106(me)001:3957: byang chub sems dpas grangs med gsum //
NK106(me)001:3958: kun du brtson par mdzad ces brjod //
NK106(me)001:3960: dran pa nyer gzhag bzhi bsgom pa'i dus sbyor lam skye ba'i dus ma nges pa'o //
NK106(me)001:3961: yang dag spong bzhi bsgom pa'i dus ni sbyor lam tshe phyi ma la skye ba dus nges pa'o //
NK106(me)001:3962: rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhi bsgom pa'i dus sbyor lam tshe de nyid la skye bar nges pa'o //
NK106(me)001:3963: lam 'di'i gnyen po'i khyad ni 'du byed rnams la
NK106(me)001:3964: nyes dmigs su lta bas rnam par sun 'byin pa'i
NK106(me)001:3965: gnyen po'o // spangs pa ni zag bcas kyi chos
NK106(me)001:3966: la skyon du mthong bas mngon zhen mngon gyur pa'i
NK106(me)001:3967: ngo skal du gyur ched spangs pa'o //
NK106(me)001:3968: rtogs pa ni bdag med gnyis thos bsam gyis don spyi'i tshul du rtogs pa shas che /
NK106(me)001:3969: sgom byung gis rtogs pa'ang yod de /
NK106(me)001:3971: bsgoms pa las byung ba'i shes rab kyang rung ste zhes so //
NK106(me)001:3972: yon tan ni spyan dang mngon shes la sogs pa ci rigs yod de /
NK106(me)001:3974: de tshe chos kyi rgyun las ni //
NK106(me)001:3975: sangs rgyas rnams las zhi gnas dang //
NK106(me)001:3976: ye shes yangs pa thob bya'i phyir //
NK106(me)001:3977: gdams ngag rgya chen rnyed par 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:3979: chos kyi sgo la rnam par gsan pa la //
NK106(me)001:3980: de bzhin gshegs pa mngon sum 'doms mdzad cing //
NK106(me)001:3981: co nas 'dren bzhin nyes pa'i tshang tshing gi //
NK106(me)001:3982: tshan las drangs te byang chub la 'god do //
NK106(me)001:3984: tshogs lam chen po thob dus mngon shes dang spyan dang rdzu 'phrul ci rigs su yod do //
NK106(me)001:3985: bsgom bya'i gdams ngag kyang lus ngag gi 'jug ldog la dmigs pa'i tshul khrims dang /
NK106(me)001:3986: gsung rab kyi tshig don la dmigs pa'i thos bsam sgom gsum gyi shes rab dang /
NK106(me)001:3987: dkon mchog gsum rjes su dran pa dang /
NK106(me)001:3988: 'dus byas thams cad mi rtag pa /
NK106(me)001:3989: zag pa dang bcas pa sdug bsngal ba /
NK106(me)001:3990: chos thams cad stong zhing bdag med pa /
NK106(me)001:3991: mya ngan las 'das pa zhi ba ste chos kyi phyag rgya bzhi dang /
NK106(me)001:3996: shes rab khyad par can dbang po'i ngo bo nyid
NK106(me)001:3997: du ma skyes pa'i thar pa cha mthun lnga dang
NK106(me)001:4003: dbugs phyi nang du rgyu ba rjes su dran pa rnams bsgom zhing /
NK106(me)001:4004: spyod pa rnam par spyod pa na mi gtsang ba'i 'du shes dang /
NK106(me)001:4005: skyes bu chen po'i rnam rtog brgyad bsgom par bya'o //
NK106(me)001:4006: de'ang sbyor ba skyabs 'gro sems bskyed sngon du song bas bsgom zhing /
NK106(me)001:4007: rjes bsngo bas zin pa'i tshul gyis mi gtsang ba'i 'du shes dgu bsgom pa'ang /
NK106(me)001:4008: rang dang gzhan gyi lus la /
NK106(me)001:4017: rul ba'i 'du shes bsgom par bya'o //
NK106(me)001:4018: de'ang 'dod chags la mi gtsang ba dang /
NK106(me)001:4019: zhe sdang la byams pa dang /
NK106(me)001:4020: gti mug la rten 'brel bsgom par /
NK106(me)001:4021: dpung bzang gis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:4022: 'dod chags shas che mi gtsang sha tshil dang //
NK106(me)001:4023: pags pa keng rus blta bas rnam par bzlog /
NK106(me)001:4024: byams dang snying rje'i chus gdab zhe sdang la //
NK106(me)001:4025: gti mug la ni rten 'brel lam gyis so //
NK106(me)001:4027: skyes bu chen po'i rnam par rtog pa brgyad ni /
NK106(me)001:4029: bdag gis nam zhig sems can gyi sdug bsngal sel nus snyam pa dang /
NK106(me)001:4030: nam zhig dbul bas nyen pa'i sems can rnams 'byor pa chen po la 'jog nus snyam pa dang /
NK106(me)001:4031: nam zhig sha khrag dang bcas pa'i lus kyis sems can gyi don nus snyam pa dang /
NK106(me)001:4032: nam zhig dmyal bar yun ring du gnas nas kyang sems can la phan 'dogs nus snyam pa dang /
NK106(me)001:4033: nam zhig 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i
NK106(me)001:4034: 'byor pa chen pos sems can gyi re ba rdzogs
NK106(me)001:4035: par byed nus snyam pa dang /
NK106(me)001:4036: nam zhig sangs rgyas su gyur nas sems can gyi sdug bsngal nges par 'byin nus snyam pa dang /
NK106(me)001:4037: nam zhig sems can la mi phan pa'i skye ba dang /
NK106(me)001:4038: don dam pa'i ro la gcig tu dpyod pa dang /
NK106(me)001:4039: skye bo thams cad sems par mi byed pa'i tshig dang /
NK106(me)001:4040: gzhan la mi phan pa'i 'tsho ba dang /
NK106(me)001:4044: dbang phyug dang ldan pa dang /
NK106(me)001:4045: gzhan la gnod pa byed pa la dga' bar tshe
NK106(me)001:4046: rabs thams cad du ma gyur cig snyam pa dang
NK106(me)001:4047: / nam zhig sems can gyi sdig pa'i 'bras bu
NK106(me)001:4048: bdag la smin cing bdag gi dge ba'i 'bras bu
NK106(me)001:4049: de dag la smin pas bde bar gyur cig snyam
NK106(me)001:4050: du sems pa yin no zhes so //
NK106(me)001:4051: 'di dag kyang skyabs 'gro sems bskyed dang ldan pas bsgom par bya'o //
NK106(me)001:4052: gzhan yang sngar bstan pa'i tshul gyis spyod yul yongs su dag pa'ang bsgom par bya'o //
NK106(me)001:4056: sbyor lam bzhi ste drod dang rtse mo ru //
NK106(me)001:4057: dad brtson dran dang ting 'dzin shes rab kyis //
NK106(me)001:4058: dbang po lnga dang bzod pa chos mchog tu //
NK106(me)001:4059: dad sogs stobs lnga rab tu sgom par byed //
NK106(me)001:4060: de la sbyor lam gyi rten ni tshogs lam chen
NK106(me)001:4061: po gang la skyes pa mthar thug gi gang zag
NK106(me)001:4063: de'ang lha klu lha ma yin la sogs pa grangs med pa la skye bar mdo las bshad do //
NK106(me)001:4064: bsam pa'i rten ni 'dod pa'am bsam gtan sa drug gang rung yin no //
NK106(me)001:4065: rgyu ni tshogs lam chen po mthar thug ste /
NK106(me)001:4067: thar pa'i cha dang mthun pa skyes pa'i spro ba
NK106(me)001:4068: can la nges par 'byed pa'i cha dang mthun pa
NK106(me)001:4070: ngo bo ni sgom byung 'jig rten pa'i ye shes so //
NK106(me)001:4080: shes rab kyi dbang po lnga bsgom pa'o //
NK106(me)001:4081: de'ang rnam byang bskyed pa la dngos su dbang byed pas dbang po zhes bya'o //
NK106(me)001:4083: dad pa'i dbang po dang zhes pa lnga bshad do //
NK106(me)001:4084: de'ang sbyor lam bzhir ye shes bzhi las /
NK106(me)001:4085: dang po theg chen gyi drod snang ba thob pa'i
NK106(me)001:4086: ye shes ni chos thams cad yid kyi snang ba
NK106(me)001:4087: tsam du mthong ba 'jig rten pa'i sgom byung gi
NK106(me)001:4088: snang ba cung zad thob pas don bden par 'dzin
NK106(me)001:4089: pa'i gnyen po byed pa yin te /
NK106(me)001:4091: de nas de 'drar gyur pa yi //
NK106(me)001:4092: byang chub sems dpa'i mnyam gzhag pas //
NK106(me)001:4093: yid kyis brjod pa ma gtogs par //
NK106(me)001:4094: don kun rab tu mi mthong ngo //
NK106(me)001:4096: skabs 'di'i snang ba ni chos la nges par sems pa'i bzod pa la bya ste /
NK106(me)001:4097: chu bo tsh+wa sgo can gyi mdo las /
NK106(me)001:4098: snang ba zhes bya ba ni chos la nges par
NK106(me)001:4099: sems pa'i bzod pa'i tshig bla dgas so zhes mdo
NK106(me)001:4100: sde'i rgyan gyi 'grel par drangs pa'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)001:4101: rtse mo snang ba mched pa'i ye shes ni chos
NK106(me)001:4102: kyi snang ba de nyid spel ba'i phyir bdag med
NK106(me)001:4103: pa bsgom pa la brtson pas 'jig rten pa'i sgom
NK106(me)001:4104: byung gi snang ba 'bring du thob pa yin te
NK106(me)001:4106: chos kyi snang ba 'phel bya'i phyir //
NK106(me)001:4107: brtson 'grus brtan pa kun tu rtsom //
NK106(me)001:4109: bzod pa de kho na nyid kyi phyogs gcig la
NK106(me)001:4110: zhugs pa'i ye shes ni sems tsam du gnas pa'i
NK106(me)001:4111: 'dzin pa'i sgom byung gi snang ba rab tu thob
NK106(me)001:4112: pas phyi rol don du zhen pa'i gnyen po byed
NK106(me)001:4113: pa yin te / de nyid las /
NK106(me)001:4114: chos kyi snang ba 'phel nas ni //
NK106(me)001:4115: sems tsam la ni gnas par 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:4116: de nas don du snang ba kun //
NK106(me)001:4117: sems su rab tu snang bar 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:4118: de tshe de yi gzung ba yi //
NK106(me)001:4119: rnam par g.yeng ba de spongs 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:4120: de nas de la 'dzin pa yi //
NK106(me)001:4121: rnam par g.yeng ba 'ba' zhig lus //
NK106(me)001:4123: chos mchog de ma thag pa'i ye shes ni don
NK106(me)001:4124: du 'dzin pa'i rnam g.yeng med pa'i 'jig rten pa'i
NK106(me)001:4125: sgom byung gi snang ba yongs su rdzogs pas theg
NK106(me)001:4126: chen mthong lam thob pa la gzhan gyis bar mchod
NK106(me)001:4127: pa yin te / de nyid las /
NK106(me)001:4128: de tshe bar chad med pa yi //
NK106(me)001:4129: ting nge 'dzin la myur du reg /
NK106(me)001:4131: de ltar nges 'byed cha bzhi po re re la'ang
NK106(me)001:4132: chung 'bring che gsum du dbye bas bcu gnyis su
NK106(me)001:4133: yod de / mngon rtogs rgyan las /
NK106(me)001:4134: de ltar nges 'byed cha mthun ni //
NK106(me)001:4135: chung dang 'bring dang chen po yin //
NK106(me)001:4137: 'di dag la gnyen po'i khyad ni mgo gnon gyis spong ba gnyen po yin no //
NK106(me)001:4138: spyir gnyen po la sun 'byin pa'i gnyen po /
NK106(me)001:4141: thag bsring gi gnyen po dang bzhi yin no //
NK106(me)001:4142: spong ba'i gnyen po la gnyis las /
NK106(me)001:4143: mgo gnon ni mngon gyur nyam smod pas spong ba dang /
NK106(me)001:4144: rtsa ba nas spong bas bon drungs 'byin pa bar chad med lam lta bu'o //
NK106(me)001:4145: spangs pa'i khyad par ni sgrib pa'i sa bon dang mngon gyur nyam smad pa dang /
NK106(me)001:4146: so so'i skye bo'i phongs pa dang rgud pa las grol ba yin no //
NK106(me)001:4147: rtogs pa'i khyad par ni 'jig rten pa'i sgom byung
NK106(me)001:4148: gi ye shes kyis bdag med gnyis don spyi'i tshul
NK106(me)001:4149: gyis rtogs pa'o // yon tan ni dkon mchog sprin
NK106(me)001:4150: las ting nge 'dzin dang gzungs dang mngon shes la
NK106(me)001:4151: sogs pa du ma gsungs so //
NK106(me)001:4152: tshogs lam 'phags pa'i khyad ni tshogs lam chen po
NK106(me)001:4153: dang sgom byung du khyad med kyang rnam par mi
NK106(me)001:4154: rtog pa'i ye shes cung zad gsal bas mthong lam
NK106(me)001:4155: la nye ring gi khyad yod de /
NK106(me)001:4157: bar chad med na mthong ba'i lam ches nye bar
NK106(me)001:4158: 'byung ba zhes bya ba ni thar pa'i cha dang
NK106(me)001:4159: mthun pa las 'di'i khyad par yin par rig par
NK106(me)001:4160: bya'o zhes so // mthong lam ni /
NK106(me)001:4161: de nas 'phags pa'i ye shes dang por /
NK106(me)001:4162: mthong ba'i lam ste rab tu dga' ba'i sar //
NK106(me)001:4163: dad brtson dran pa shes rab ting 'dzin dga' //
NK106(me)001:4164: shin tu sbyangs pa yang dag byang chub kyi //
NK106(me)001:4165: yan lag bdun po dag ni legs bsgom zhing //
NK106(me)001:4167: chos mchog chen po mthar thug pa'i mjug thogs su
NK106(me)001:4168: mthong ba'i lam gyi ye shes skye ba ni skad
NK106(me)001:4169: cig ma bcu drug gi bdag nyid de /
NK106(me)001:4173: lam gyi bden pa re re bzhin chos shes pa'i bzod pa dang /
NK106(me)001:4175: rjes su shes pa'i bzod pa dang /
NK106(me)001:4176: rjes su shes pa ste bzhi bzhi'i bdag nyid ni /
NK106(me)001:4178: sdug bsngal la sogs bden pa la //
NK106(me)001:4179: chos shes rjes su shes pa dang //
NK106(me)001:4180: bzod shes skad cig bdag nyid 'di //
NK106(me)001:4181: kun shes tshul la mthong ba'i las //
NK106(me)001:4184: bden pa so so la chos shes pa'i bzod pa dang /
NK106(me)001:4186: rjes su shes pa'i bzod pa dang /
NK106(me)001:4187: rjes su shes pa ste de ltar skad cig ma
NK106(me)001:4188: bcu drug gi bdag nyid ni thams cad shes pa
NK106(me)001:4189: nyid kyi skabs su mthong ba'i lam yin no zhes
NK106(me)001:4190: so // de'ang ye shes 'di skye ba'i lus kyi
NK106(me)001:4191: rten chos mchog chen po dang gcig pas 'gro ba
NK106(me)001:4193: nyan thos pa'i ltar ma yin no //
NK106(me)001:4194: bsam pa'i rten bsam gtan bzhi pa'o //
NK106(me)001:4195: rgyu ni chos mchog mthar thug ni dngos rgyu dang tshogs sbyor gzhan brgyud pa'i rgyu'o //
NK106(me)001:4196: 'bras bu lam phyi ma gnyis bskyed pa'o //
NK106(me)001:4197: ngo bo la bden bzhi'i dbye bas khams kyi dri
NK106(me)001:4198: ma spong ba la ltos nas skad cig bcu drug
NK106(me)001:4199: go // de yang dri ma dang /
NK106(me)001:4201: dang po ni 'jig tshogs la lta ba /
NK106(me)001:4204: lta ba la mchog tu 'dzin pa'i lta ba /
NK106(me)001:4205: tshul khrims dang brtul zhugs la mchog tu 'dzin pa'i lta ba ste lta ba lnga dang /
NK106(me)001:4210: the tshom ste lta min lnga dang bcus 'dod pa'i
NK106(me)001:4211: khams su bden pa bzhi po re re la'ang nyon
NK106(me)001:4212: mongs pa bcu char log por 'jug pas bzhi bcu
NK106(me)001:4213: / khams gong ma gnyis su bden pa bzhi po
NK106(me)001:4214: re re la khong khro ma gtogs pa dgu dgu
NK106(me)001:4215: log por 'jug pas bdun cu rtsa gnyis te mthong
NK106(me)001:4216: spang gis bsdus pa'i nyon mongs pa brgya dang bcu
NK106(me)001:4217: / gnyis ni / kun las btus las /
NK106(me)001:4218: nyon mongs pa brgya rtsa bcu gnyis ni mthong bas
NK106(me)001:4219: spang bar bya ba'i nyon mongs pa'i rigs so zhes
NK106(me)001:4220: so // bsam gtan sa bzhi dang gzugs med pa
NK106(me)001:4221: bzhir khong khro mi 'jug pa ni rgyud zhi gnas
NK106(me)001:4222: kyis brlan par byas pas kun nas mnar med sems
NK106(me)001:4223: pa khong khro'i gzhi dgu med pa'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)001:4224: dgu ni bdag la sngar yang gnod pa byas /
NK106(me)001:4226: ma 'ongs pa na'ang byed par 'gyur snyam pa gsum /
NK106(me)001:4227: de bzhin du gnyen la'ang gsum /
NK106(me)001:4228: bdag gi dgra la phan btags snyam pa la sogs pa gsum ste dagu'o //
NK106(me)001:4229: de'ang nyon mongs pa de dag gis log par 'jug
NK106(me)001:4230: tshul ni sdug bsngal gyi bden pa la mtshon na
NK106(me)001:4231: / 'jig tshogs la lta bas sdug bsngal gyi bden pa la bdag dang bdag gi bar 'dzin to //
NK106(me)001:4232: mthar 'dzin pa'i lta bas sdug bsngal gyi bden pa la yod med rtag chad du 'dzin to //
NK106(me)001:4233: log par lta bas sdug bsngal gyi bden pa med par 'dzin to //
NK106(me)001:4234: ma rig pas sdug bden gyi mtshan nyid mi shes bzhin du 'jug go //
NK106(me)001:4235: the tshom gyis phung po lnga po de sdug bsngal
NK106(me)001:4236: gyi bden pa yin ma yin the tshom za bzhin
NK106(me)001:4237: du 'jug go // 'jug tshul lnga po de la 'dod chags kyis zhen cing chags par byed do //
NK106(me)001:4238: nga rgyal gyis rlom zhing khengs par byed do //
NK106(me)001:4239: lta ba mchog 'dzin gyis mchog dam par 'dzin to //
NK106(me)001:4240: tshul khrims dang brtul zhugs mchog 'dzin gyis dag grol gyi lam du 'dzin to //
NK106(me)001:4241: khong khros 'jug tshul lnga po de dang mi mthun pa la khro ba'i sems su byed do //
NK106(me)001:4242: sdug bsngal la ji lta bar bden pa lhag ma
NK106(me)001:4243: rnams la'ang de bzhin du 'jug par rig pa bya'o
NK106(me)001:4244: // de'ang 'gog bden gyi ming la dmigs nas 'jug gi don la dmigs pa ma yin no //
NK106(me)001:4246: khams gsum ka'i nyon mongs pa mthong bas spang bya dril nas spong bas /
NK106(me)001:4251: chos shes pa'i bzod pa bzhi rdzas gcig ldog pa
NK106(me)001:4252: bden bzhi so so la ltos pa'i cha bzhi yin
NK106(me)001:4253: pas na skad cig gcig la skyes dus mthong spang
NK106(me)001:4254: gi sa bon rtsa ba nas spong ba'i gnyen po
NK106(me)001:4255: bar chad med lam yin pas /
NK106(me)001:4256: mthong spang brgya rtsa bcu gnyis po rnams skad cig gis spongs so //
NK106(me)001:4257: de'ang bden bzhi so so'i chos shes pa'i bzod pa'i
NK106(me)001:4258: nye rgyu dang de'i ngo skal gyi spang bya nus
NK106(me)001:4260: dus gnyis pa la dngos rgyu dang de'i ngo skal gyi spang bya nus med gnyis po de phrad /
NK106(me)001:4261: dus gsum pa la chos bzod bzhi po skye ba
NK106(me)001:4262: dang de'i ngo skal gyi spang bya'i sa bon phra
NK106(me)001:4263: mo mtha' dag 'gag pa dus mnyam du byas pa'i
NK106(me)001:4266: ji ltar myug sogs rim skyes pas //
NK106(me)001:4267: sa bon shun pa gcod pa ltar //
NK106(me)001:4268: de bzhin de nyid mthong ba yis //
NK106(me)001:4269: mthong spang rnams ni bzlog par 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:4271: de nas bden bzhi so so'i chos bzhi blo rdzas
NK106(me)001:4272: gcig pas khams gsum gyi bden pa bzhi'i rnam pa'i
NK106(me)001:4273: nyon mongs pa las grol ba gnyen po rnam grol
NK106(me)001:4274: gyi lam mo // de bzhin du rjes bzod bzhi
NK106(me)001:4275: dang rjes shes bzhi ni thag bsring gi gnyen po
NK106(me)001:4277: de ltar spangs pa de dag kyang sgrib pa gnyis yin la /
NK106(me)001:4278: de gnyis las grol ba yin te /
NK106(me)001:4280: nyon mongs pa yi sgrib pa dang //
NK106(me)001:4281: shes bya'i sgrib pa gnyis su bstan //
NK106(me)001:4282: der ni sgrib pa thams cad de //
NK106(me)001:4283: de zad nas ni grol bar 'dod //
NK106(me)001:4287: ser sna la sogs rnam rtog gang //
NK106(me)001:4288: de ni nyon mongs sgrib par 'dod //
NK106(me)001:4289: 'khor gsum rnam par rtog pa gang //
NK106(me)001:4290: de ni shes bya'i sgrib par 'dod //
NK106(me)001:4292: sems rab tu ma zhi bar byed pa gang mi
NK106(me)001:4293: dge ba'am sgrib pa lung du ma bstan pa'i ngo
NK106(me)001:4294: bor ser sna la sogs pa ni nyon sgrib yin
NK106(me)001:4295: la / 'khor gsum la bden zhen dang ma bral
NK106(me)001:4296: ba gang dge ba zag bcas sam ma bsgribs lung
NK106(me)001:4297: ma bstan gyi ngo bo gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa
NK106(me)001:4298: yul yul can ni shes sgrib yin no //
NK106(me)001:4299: de'ang nyon sgrib kun brtags rnams ni mthong spang yin la /
NK106(me)001:4300: lhan skyes ni sgom spang yin no //
NK106(me)001:4301: shes sgrib gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa rags pa ni mthong spang yin la /
NK106(me)001:4302: phra ba ni sgom spang yin no //
NK106(me)001:4303: rtogs pa'i khyad par ni 'jig rten las 'das pa'i
NK106(me)001:4304: shes rab kyis bdag med gnyis mngon sum du rtogs
NK106(me)001:4305: pa yin no // yon tan ni sngar smos pa'i
NK106(me)001:4306: sa dang po'i brgya phrag bcu gnyis la sogs pa
NK106(me)001:4307: pa yin no // rnams so // dus kyi khyad
NK106(me)001:4308: par ni dang por bden pa bzhis phye ba'i chos
NK106(me)001:4309: bzod bzhi dus gcig la skye /
NK106(me)001:4310: de'i 'og tu chos shes bzhi dus gcig la skye /
NK106(me)001:4311: de'i 'og tu rjes bzod bzhi dus gcig la skye /
NK106(me)001:4312: de'i 'og tu rjes shes bzhi dus gcig la skye
NK106(me)001:4313: bas bya rdzogs kyi skad cig bzhi la ngo bo
NK106(me)001:4314: rigs bzhi ldog pa bcu drug tu skye ba yin
NK106(me)001:4315: te / bden bzhi cig car du rtogs shing bzod shes bzhi rim gyis skye ba'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)001:4316: de'ang mthong spang rnams chos bzod kyis skad cig la
NK106(me)001:4317: spong la mthong lam cha bzhi'i rim pas skye ba
NK106(me)001:4318: yin no // de'ang sa dang po'i tshe byang chub kyi yan lag bdun bsgom pa'o //
NK106(me)001:4321: dran dang chos rab 'byed dang brtson 'grus dang //
NK106(me)001:4322: dga' dang shin tu sbyangs dang ting 'dzin dang //
NK106(me)001:4323: btang snyoms 'di bdun byang chub yan lag ste //
NK106(me)001:4324: mya ngan 'das thob bgyid pa'i dge tshogs lags //
NK106(me)001:4327: byang chub kyi phyogs bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:4329: sus dran pa med cing yid la byed pa med
NK106(me)001:4330: pa'i phyir chos thams cad dngos po med par mthong
NK106(me)001:4331: ba 'di ni dran pa yang dag byang chub kyi
NK106(me)001:4333: sus dge ba dang mi dge ba dang lung du
NK106(me)001:4334: ma bstan pa yongs su mi bsgrub pa'i phyir chos
NK106(me)001:4335: thams cad dben zhing mi dmigs pa 'di ni chos
NK106(me)001:4336: rnam par 'byed pa yang dag byang chub kyi yan
NK106(me)001:4338: sus lus kyi 'du shes bshig pa'i phyir khams gsum
NK106(me)001:4339: mi len mi 'dor ba 'di ni brtson 'grus yang
NK106(me)001:4340: dag byang chub kyi yan lag go //
NK106(me)001:4342: sus dga' ba dang mi dga' ba bshig pa'i phyir
NK106(me)001:4343: 'du byed thams cad la dga' ba mi bskyed pa
NK106(me)001:4344: 'di ni dga' ba yang dag byang chub kyi yan
NK106(me)001:4346: sus dmigs pa'i dngos po mi dmigs pa'i phyir chos
NK106(me)001:4347: thams cad la sems shin tu sbyangs par gyur pa
NK106(me)001:4348: 'di ni shin tu sbyangs pa yang dag byang chub
NK106(me)001:4351: sus chos thams cad rnam par bshig pa rjes su
NK106(me)001:4352: rtog pa'i phyir sems mi dmigs pa 'di ni ting
NK106(me)001:4353: nge 'dzin yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag go
NK106(me)001:4355: sus chos thams cad la gnas par mi byed brten
NK106(me)001:4356: par mi byed chags par mi byed 'ching bar mi
NK106(me)001:4357: byed cing chos thams cad yang dag par rjes su
NK106(me)001:4358: mi mthong ba'i btang snyoms can du gyur te dga'
NK106(me)001:4359: ba thob pa 'di ni btang snyoms yang dag byang
NK106(me)001:4360: chub kyi yan lag go zhes so //
NK106(me)001:4362: de nas mthong zin goms par byed pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)001:4363: sgom lam chung 'bring chen po re re bzhin //
NK106(me)001:4364: chung ngu'i chung ngu chung ngu'i 'bring dang ni //
NK106(me)001:4365: chung ngu'i che sogs sa dgu rim pa bzhin //
NK106(me)001:4366: dri ma med dang 'od byed 'od 'phro can //
NK106(me)001:4367: sbyang dka' mngon gyur ring song mi g.yo ba //
NK106(me)001:4368: legs pa'i blo gros chos kyi sprin rnams su //
NK106(me)001:4369: yang dag lta dang rtog pa ngag dang las //
NK106(me)001:4370: 'tsho rtsol dran pa ting 'dzin 'phags lam brgyad //
NK106(me)001:4371: de'ang nges 'byed cha mthun dang mthong lam du mthong
NK106(me)001:4372: zin gyi don gong nas gong du goms par byed
NK106(me)001:4373: pa la sgom lam zhes brjod de /
NK106(me)001:4375: nges 'byed yan lag dang mthong ba'i //
NK106(me)001:4376: lam dang sgom pa'i lam nyid la //
NK106(me)001:4377: yang dang yang du sems pa dang //
NK106(me)001:4378: 'jal dang nges rtog sgom pa'i lam //
NK106(me)001:4382: chen po gsum la'ang chung 'bring chen po gsum gsum ste sa dagu'o //
NK106(me)001:4384: chung ngu'i chung ngus gnyis pa dri ma med pa /
NK106(me)001:4385: chung ngu'i 'bring sa gsum pa 'od byed pa /
NK106(me)001:4386: chung ngu'i chen po sa bzhi pa 'od 'phro ba can no //
NK106(me)001:4387: 'bring gi chung ngu sa lnga pa sbyang dka' ba /
NK106(me)001:4388: 'bring gi 'bring sa drug pa mngon du gyur pa /
NK106(me)001:4389: 'bring gi chen po sa bdun pa ring du song ba'o //
NK106(me)001:4390: chen po'i chung ngus brgyad pa mi g.yo ba /
NK106(me)001:4391: chen po'i 'bring sa dgu pa legs pa'i blo gros /
NK106(me)001:4392: chen po'i chen pos bcu pa chos kyi sprin no //
NK106(me)001:4395: sa dgu la ni chen po yi //
NK106(me)001:4396: chen po la sogs dri ma yi //
NK106(me)001:4397: gnyen po chung ngu'i chung ngu la //
NK106(me)001:4398: sogs pa'i lam ni dag pa yin //
NK106(me)001:4400: de la sgom spang yang chen po /
NK106(me)001:4411: chung ngu'i chung ngu ste dagu'o //
NK106(me)001:4412: dri ma med pa la sogs pa'i sa dgu la rim pa bzhin spong ngo //
NK106(me)001:4413: de'ang sgom lam chung ngu'i chung ngu sa gnyis pa
NK106(me)001:4414: dri ma med pas sgom spang chen po'i chen po
NK106(me)001:4415: spong ba nas / sgom spang chung ngu'i chung ngu
NK106(me)001:4416: sgom lam chen po'i chen po sa bcu pas spong
NK106(me)001:4417: spong ba nas / ba yin no // de'ang dri ma rags pa la che bar btags /
NK106(me)001:4418: phra ba la chung bar btags pa'i dbang du mdzad nas de skad ces brjod do //
NK106(me)001:4419: de ltar sgom pa'i lam 'di dag skye ba'i lus kyi rten mthong lam dang gcig ste /
NK106(me)001:4420: gling gsum gyi skyes pa bud med dang 'dod gzugs kyi lha la skye ba shas che la /
NK106(me)001:4422: skyes zin gnas pa'i rten du ni thams cad rung ste /
NK106(me)001:4424: zhing spyod sgyu ma ltar gnas dang //
NK106(me)001:4425: bsams bzhin srid pa len pa dang //
NK106(me)001:4427: sems kyi rten ni bsam gtan bzhi pa la brten
NK106(me)001:4428: pa shas che zhing gzhan la'ang rten du rung bar
NK106(me)001:4429: 'chad do // rgyu ni lam dang po gsum mo //
NK106(me)001:4430: 'bras bu ni mi slob pa'i lam mo //
NK106(me)001:4431: ngo bo ni sa dgu'i rang rang gi dri ma spong ba'i gnyen po la ltos nas /
NK106(me)001:4433: bar chad med pa'i lam dang /
NK106(me)001:4435: khyad par gyi lam dang bzhi'o //
NK106(me)001:4436: de dag kyang de'i sgrib pa spong ba la /
NK106(me)001:4437: sbyor ba dang bar chad med lam ni spong ba'i gnyen po'o //
NK106(me)001:4438: rnam grol gyi lam ni rten gnyen po'o //
NK106(me)001:4439: khyad par gyi lam ni thag bsring gi gnyen po'o //
NK106(me)001:4440: dper na sa gnyis pa'i ye shes skye ba'i skad
NK106(me)001:4441: cig snga logs sa dang po'i mjug gis gnyis pa
NK106(me)001:4442: skye ba la sgrib pa'i mngon gyur gyi nyon mongs
NK106(me)001:4444: gnyis pa'i ye shes skye bzhin pa bar chad med
NK106(me)001:4445: lam nges rang gi ngo skal du gyur pa'i tshul
NK106(me)001:4446: khrims 'chal pa'i sa bon lta bu rtsa ba nas
NK106(me)001:4447: spong / skad cig gnyis pa nas sa'i dngos gzhi rnam grol gyi lam gyis rten gnyen po byed /
NK106(me)001:4448: sa'i mjug gi khyad par gyi lam gyis thag bsring gi gnyen po byed do //
NK106(me)001:4449: sa de'i skad cig dang po nas rdzogs kyi bar
NK106(me)001:4450: rang rang gi dri ma thams cad tshul des spong
NK106(me)001:4451: zhing / de dag gi dri ma yongs su rdzogs
NK106(me)001:4452: pa ni sa de 'gag pa dang dus mnyam pas
NK106(me)001:4453: zhing / spong ba'o // de la deng sang gi
NK106(me)001:4454: phar phyin pa rtsing po kha cig mthong spang thams
NK106(me)001:4455: cad skye 'gyur lam gyis spong la /
NK106(me)001:4456: sgom spang thams cad 'gag 'gyur lam gyis spong zhes
NK106(me)001:4457: 'dod pa ni gnyen po'i tshul la rab tu rmongs
NK106(me)001:4458: pas skyong byed dag dang chos mtshungs par mthong ngo
NK106(me)001:4460: de la byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi sa dri
NK106(me)001:4461: ma med pa 'di yongs su skyes pa de'i tshe
NK106(me)001:4462: tshul khrims 'chal ba'i dri ma rnams yongs su spangs
NK106(me)001:4463: pa yin te zhes pa nas /
NK106(me)001:4464: sa bcu'i mi mthun phyogs dri ma bcu sa de
NK106(me)001:4465: dag skyes dus bar chad med lam la spangs nas
NK106(me)001:4466: / rnam grol lam gyis rten gnyen po byas /
NK106(me)001:4467: khyad par gnyen pos thag bsring bar byas te spong ba yin no //
NK106(me)001:4468: de'ang mthong spang ma lus pa spangs pa dang /
NK106(me)001:4469: sgom spang rang sa'i ci rigs su spangs pa yin no //
NK106(me)001:4470: yon tan ni sngar sa'i skabs su bshad zin to //
NK106(me)001:4471: sa dgu'i dri ma dgu ji ltar spong ba ni /
NK106(me)001:4472: lhan cig skyes pa'i dri ma drug ste /
NK106(me)001:4479: de dag khams kyi dbye bas 'dod pa na drug /
NK106(me)001:4480: bsam gtan dang gzugs med pa na khong khro ma gtogs pa lnga lnga ste bcu drug go //
NK106(me)001:4481: sa'i sgo nas dbye na 'dod pa na drug /
NK106(me)001:4483: gzugs med bzhi ste brgyad na lnga lnga bgrangs pas nyi shu rtsa drug go //
NK106(me)001:4484: de dag kyang che 'bring gis dbye na 'dod pa'i drug las /
NK106(me)001:4486: gzhan lnga la dgu dgu ste lnga bcu rtsa bzhi /
NK106(me)001:4487: bsam gtan sa bzhi na khong khro bor bas nyon
NK106(me)001:4488: mongs pa lnga la che 'bring dgu dgu ste bzhi
NK106(me)001:4489: bcu rtsa lnga pa tshan pa lnga /
NK106(me)001:4490: de bzhin du gzugs med na'ang bzhi bcu rtsa lnga
NK106(me)001:4491: pa tshan pa lnga ste bsdoms pas sgom spang bzhi
NK106(me)001:4492: brgya dang bcu bzhi yod do //
NK106(me)001:4493: spong tshul sbyor bas mgo smad /
NK106(me)001:4494: bar chad med pas dngos su spangs /
NK106(me)001:4495: rnam grol gyis rten gnyen po byas /
NK106(me)001:4496: khyad par lam gyis thag bsring gi gnyen po byas
NK106(me)001:4497: pa'i tshul gyis sa dgu po rnams su mngon gyur
NK106(me)001:4498: dang sa bon rnams spangs pa yin no //
NK106(me)001:4499: sa de dag tu 'phags lam brgyad yongs su bsgom pa'ang /
NK106(me)001:4501: yang dag lta dang 'tsho dang rtsol ba dang //
NK106(me)001:4502: dran dang ting 'dzin dag dang las mtha' dang //
NK106(me)001:4503: yang dag rtog nyid lam gyi yan lag brgyad //
NK106(me)001:4504: 'di ni zhi bar bgyi slad bsgom par bgyi //
NK106(me)001:4507: byang chub kyi phyogs bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:4509: gang gis chos thams cad mi mnyam pa med cing
NK106(me)001:4510: gnyis su med par mthong ba 'di ni yang dag
NK106(me)001:4512: chos thams cad mthong ba med pa'i tshul gyis rtag
NK106(me)001:4513: tu med rnam par rtag tu med la yongs su
NK106(me)001:4514: rtag tu med pa'i tshul gyis mthong ba 'di ni
NK106(me)001:4517: chos thams cad brjod du med par mthong ba 'di ni yang dag pa'i ngag go //
NK106(me)001:4519: chos thams cad bya ba med cing byed pa med
NK106(me)001:4520: par mthong ba 'di ni yang dag pa'i las kyi
NK106(me)001:4522: chos thams cad mi gsog mi 'bri bar mthong ba 'di ni yang dag pa'i 'tsho ba'o //
NK106(me)001:4524: chos thams cad rtsol ba med cing bsgrub pa med
NK106(me)001:4525: pa'i tshul gyis chos thams cad yongs su bsgrub pa
NK106(me)001:4526: 'di ni yang dag pa'i rtsol ba'o //
NK106(me)001:4528: chos thams cad yid la mi byed cing dran pa
NK106(me)001:4529: med par mthong ba 'di ni yang dag pa'i dran
NK106(me)001:4531: chos thams cad mi dmigs pa'i phyir rang bzhin gyis
NK106(me)001:4532: mnyam par bzhag cing 'khrugs pa med la mi dmigs
NK106(me)001:4533: par mthong ba 'di ni yang dag pa'i ting nge
NK106(me)001:4535: sa 'di dag rang gi ngo bo la ltos na dmigs bsam las 'das pa ste /
NK106(me)001:4537: rgyal ba'i sras rnams sa 'di rnams ni shin tu
NK106(me)001:4538: rnam dag bar snang bya'i rjes dang mtshungs zhes so
NK106(me)001:4539: // 'on kyang khams la sgrib pa'i rim pa rnams
NK106(me)001:4540: bsal bas khams mthar thug gnas gyur pa byang chub
NK106(me)001:4541: mthong ba la ltos te tha dad du bzhag go
NK106(me)001:4542: // // dri ma so so ba rnams dag pa
NK106(me)001:4543: mthar thug dus gdod ma'i dbyings sam 'od gsal ba'i
NK106(me)001:4544: sangs rgyas rang gsal du mthong ba'ang tshes kyi dbang
NK106(me)001:4545: gis zla ba ltar snang ba ni /
NK106(me)001:4546: chos kyi dbyings su bstod pa las /
NK106(me)001:4547: ji ltar tshes pa'i zla ba la //
NK106(me)001:4548: skad cig skad cig rgyas par mthong //
NK106(me)001:4549: de bzhin sa la zhugs rnams kyang //
NK106(me)001:4550: rim gyi rim gyis 'phel bar mthong //
NK106(me)001:4551: ji ltar yar ngo'i bco lnga la //
NK106(me)001:4552: zla ba rdzogs par gyur pa ltar //
NK106(me)001:4553: de bzhin sa yi mthar thug na //
NK106(me)001:4554: chos kyi sku yang rdzogs pa gsal //
NK106(me)001:4558: de ltar byang chub phyogs chos sum cu bdun //
NK106(me)001:4559: slob pa'i lam bzhir bsgoms pa'i mjug thogs su //
NK106(me)001:4560: mi slob sa la mi gnas mya ngan 'da' //
NK106(me)001:4561: byang phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun slob lam
NK106(me)001:4562: gyis bsdus pa rnams yongs su rdzogs pa'i mthar mi
NK106(me)001:4563: slob pa'i sangs rgyas kyi byang chub mngon du byed
NK106(me)001:4564: do // de'ang lus kyi rten theg pa thun mong
NK106(me)001:4565: ba dang bstun na dzam+bu'i gling gi rgyal rigs sam
NK106(me)001:4566: bram ze gang rung yin la /
NK106(me)001:4567: theg pa chen po ba ltar na longs sku 'og
NK106(me)001:4568: min du thob pas de'i rten la skye bar 'dod
NK106(me)001:4569: de / sa bcu pa'i sems dpa' de'i rten gang yin pa dang gcig go //
NK106(me)001:4570: bsam pa'i rten bsam gtan bzhi pa'o //
NK106(me)001:4571: rgyu ni theg chen slob lam bzhi'o //
NK106(me)001:4572: 'bras bu ni 'phrin las chen pos 'gro ba mtha' yas pa byang chub la dgod pa'o //
NK106(me)001:4573: ngo bo ni sangs rgyas kyi sa'i sku gsung thugs
NK106(me)001:4574: yon tan 'phrin las mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor
NK106(me)001:4575: lo'o // spangs pa ni sgrib gnyis bag chags dang bcas pa spangs pa ste /
NK106(me)001:4577: nyon mongs pa dang de bzhin skye //
NK106(me)001:4578: nyon mongs shes bya'i sgrib de bzhin //
NK106(me)001:4579: gang yang mi mthun phyogs chos bcom //
NK106(me)001:4582: rtogs pa'i khyad ni chos sku yongs rdzogs mngon sum du rtogs te /
NK106(me)001:4584: bcom ldan 'das khyod chos sku rnam dag blo gros mtha' yas pa //
NK106(me)001:4585: shes bya mtha' med mkha' dbyings khyab pa de dag gis kun mthong //
NK106(me)001:4587: yon tan ni 'jig rten las 'das pa'i yon tan mtha' yas pa thams cad rdzogs te /
NK106(me)001:4588: dbu ma rin chen phreng ba las /
NK106(me)001:4589: sangs rgyas rnams kyi sa gzhan te //
NK106(me)001:4590: rnam pa kun tu gzhal yas par //
NK106(me)001:4591: rgya chen de ni stobs bcu dang //
NK106(me)001:4592: ldan pa yin pa tsam zhig brjod //
NK106(me)001:4593: de yi stobs ni re re yang //
NK106(me)001:4594: 'gro ba kun gzhi dpag tu med //
NK106(me)001:4595: sangs rgyas rnams kyi tshad med nyid //
NK106(me)001:4596: phyogs rnams kun gyi nam mkha' dang //
NK106(me)001:4597: sa chu me rlung ji lta bar //
NK106(me)001:4598: de tsam bzhin du brjod par byas //
NK106(me)001:4600: sa lam gyi dgos pa brjod pas mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK106(me)001:4601: da ni de ltar sa dang lam gyi dgos pa brjod pas mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK106(me)001:4603: 'di ltar sa dang lam rnams ma bgrod pa'i //
NK106(me)001:4604: sangs rgyas de 'dra nam yang 'byung ba med //
NK106(me)001:4605: bskal mang tshe rabs du ma tshe gang grol //
NK106(me)001:4606: de dag kun kyang lam 'dir brten pas na //
NK106(me)001:4607: rgyu 'bras theg pa gang la zhugs rnams kyis //
NK106(me)001:4608: sa dang lam rnams mkhyen nas bgrod par mdzod //
NK106(me)001:4609: bla na med pa'i sangs rgyas ni sa dang lam
NK106(me)001:4610: rnams yongs su rdzogs par 'byung ba de ni mi
NK106(me)001:4611: srid de / sangs rgyas 'gro ba'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:4612: gang dag bskal pa'i sangs rgyas byang chub brnyes //
NK106(me)001:4613: mi dbang kha los sgyur ba de dag kun //
NK106(me)001:4614: sa dang lam rnams rim par bgrod las byung //
NK106(me)001:4615: de lta bas na rgyal ba'i mdzod 'dod pas //
NK106(me)001:4616: byang chub dam pa 'dir brten brtson par gyis //
NK106(me)001:4617: lam 'di las ni gzhan las 'byung mi 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:4619: des na bskal pa du mas sangs rgyas thob pa'am /
NK106(me)001:4620: tshe bcu drug la sogs pas thob pa'am /
NK106(me)001:4621: shin tu myur ba tshe gcig gis sangs rgyas thob kyang rung ste /
NK106(me)001:4622: sa lam gyi rim pa ni ji lta ba bzhin bgrod dgos te /
NK106(me)001:4623: de dag gi sgrib pa dag cing yon tan rdzogs par thob dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)001:4624: ding sang ni sa dang lam gyi rim pa la ma brten yang sangs rgyas thob la /
NK106(me)001:4627: sa lam ma rdzogs par byang chub thob par 'dod
NK106(me)001:4628: pa'i lugs smra ba dag ni tshul gzhan zhig gis
NK106(me)001:4629: byin gyis brlabs par mngon no //
NK106(me)001:4632: mdo rgyud chen po rnams dang /
NK106(me)001:4633: bstan bcos chen po rnam pa dang 'gal ba'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)001:4634: de bas na yang dag pa'i sa dang lam la bslab par bya ba la 'bad do //
NK106(me)001:4635: spyi don bzhi pa skabs kyi dge ba bsngo ba ni /
NK106(me)001:4636: da ni dge ba rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu bsngo ba ni /
NK106(me)001:4638: de ltar zab zhi 'od gsal snying po yis //
NK106(me)001:4639: 'gro kun sems kyi rnyog pa rab zhi nas //
NK106(me)001:4640: srid 'dir yun ring spros la 'chel ba yis //
NK106(me)001:4641: dub pa'i sems nyid di ring ngal sos shig /
NK106(me)001:4643: yang dag pa'i lam po che bkod legs pa'i char
NK106(me)001:4644: gyi snang ba bsil bas gang ba'i mtsho chu dal
NK106(me)001:4645: gyis 'bab pa'i dge bas 'gro ba'i nyon mongs pa'i
