NK106(me)001:4646: rnyog pa rab tu zhi nas /
NK106(me)001:4647: thog ma med pa'i 'khor ba'i spros pas dub pa'i
NK106(me)001:4648: sems nyid 'di rang bzhin gyis dag pa'i chos sku
NK106(me)001:4649: bde ba chen po'i dgon par ngal sos par shog
NK106(me)001:4650: cig ces pa'o // me long ye shes chos nyid gang chen mtsho //
NK106(me)001:4651: mi rtog mnyam pa'i ngang du 'gro kun gyi //
NK106(me)001:4652: mu bzhi'i dri bral spangs rtogs mthar phyin nas //
NK106(me)001:4653: ma lus skye dgu'i re ba rdzogs par shog /
NK106(me)001:4654: ma rig 'thibs po'i dgon par 'khyams pa rnams //
NK106(me)001:4655: me gsum gdung ba'i sdug bsngal gyis gtses te //
NK106(me)001:4656: mig med thar pa'i lam dang bral ba rnams //
NK106(me)001:4657: mi gnas mya ngan 'das pa thob par shog /
NK106(me)001:4658: mi lus rin chen dal 'byor 'di thob kyang //
NK106(me)001:4659: mi rtag snying po med cing 'dor bas na //
NK106(me)001:4660: mi dge'i sdig rnams rab tu spang byas te //
NK106(me)001:4661: ma lus rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob par shog /
NK106(me)001:4662: rdzogs pa chen po sems nyid ngal gso las /
NK106(me)001:4663: lam bsam gtan dri ma med pa zhi lhag zung
NK106(me)001:4664: du 'brel pa'i le'u ste bcu gcig pa'i 'grel pa'o
NK106(me)001:4665: //// de ltar nyams su blangs nas 'bras bu'i mthar thug la ni rgyus mtshams sbyor ba /
NK106(me)001:4666: bcu gnyis pa bogs 'don spyod pa'i le'u la spyi don gsum ste /
NK106(me)001:4667: bsam gtan 'grub pa'i rgyu la bslab par gdams pa /
NK106(me)001:4668: ting nge 'dzin mi g.yo ba gsum bstan pa /
NK106(me)001:4669: skabs kyi dge ba bsngo ba'o //
NK106(me)001:4670: spyi don dang po bsam gtan 'grub pa'i rgyu la bslab par gdams pa ni /
NK106(me)001:4671: de ltar lam sgom pa'i tshul rab tu zab mo bshad nas /
NK106(me)001:4672: da ni de'i yan lag nges par 'grub pa'i rang bzhin brjod par bya ste /
NK106(me)001:4674: de ltar zung 'jug bsam gtan 'grub pa'i rgyu //
NK106(me)001:4675: ting 'dzin mi g.yo yan lag gsum la bslab //
NK106(me)001:4676: gang gi tshe yongs su bsgrub par bya ba'i lam
NK106(me)001:4677: gyi ngo bo bsam gtan khyad par can de yang
NK106(me)001:4678: sbyor ba yan lag gsum ldan gyis yongs su 'grub
NK106(me)001:4679: par 'gyur ro // spyi don gnyis pa ting nge
NK106(me)001:4680: 'dzin mi g.yo ba gsum bstan pa la mdor bstan
NK106(me)001:4683: yan lag gsum po de dag gang zhe na /
NK106(me)001:4685: gang gis bsgrub pa cho ga'i yan lag dang //
NK106(me)001:4686: ji ltar bsgrub pa thabs kyi yan lag dang //
NK106(me)001:4687: gnyis med bsgrub pa ngo bo'i yan lag go //
NK106(me)001:4688: 'di ltar yang dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin bsgrub pa thams cad tshul gsum gyis 'grub par 'gyur te /
NK106(me)001:4689: gang zag gang gis bsgrub pa dang /
NK106(me)001:4690: thabs ji lta bus bsgrub pa dang /
NK106(me)001:4692: rgyas par bshad pa la gang gis bsgrub pa cho ga'i /
NK106(me)001:4693: ji ltar bsgrub pa thabs kyi /
NK106(me)001:4694: gnyis med bsgrub pa ngo bo'i yan lag gsum ste /
NK106(me)001:4695: gang gis bsgrub po cho ga'i yan lag la lnga las /
NK106(me)001:4698: gang gis bsgrub pa'i skye bo nges 'byung can //
NK106(me)001:4699: lus ni 'du 'dzi'i grong las rgyang bsrings shing //
NK106(me)001:4700: sems ni spros pa'i tshogs las ring du bsrings //
NK106(me)001:4701: de yis ting 'dzin 'di ni myur du 'grub //
NK106(me)001:4702: 'di ltar lus ngag 'du 'dzis g.yengs shing sems spros
NK106(me)001:4703: pa'i dra ba stong gis g.yengs pas ni zhi gnas
NK106(me)001:4704: tsam yang mi 'grub na yang dag pa'i ting nge
NK106(me)001:4706: de bas na lus 'du 'dzi'i grong las bsrings te
NK106(me)001:4707: dgon par phyogs nas gcig pur rab tu dben pa'i
NK106(me)001:4708: nags sam gnas su 'dug pa dang /
NK106(me)001:4709: sems rtog pa'i tshogs las ring du bsrings te zhi
NK106(me)001:4710: gnas kyis brlan pa'i rgyud la zab mo'i ting nge
NK106(me)001:4713: de lta bas na ting nge 'dzin 'dod pas 'du
NK106(me)001:4714: 'dzi dang rnam par g.yeng ba'i yul 'khor spangs te
NK106(me)001:4715: gcig pur zhi ba'i nags su gnas pa la brtson
NK106(me)001:4717: de'ang khyim du gnas pas mi 'grub par //
NK106(me)001:4719: gang dag khyim phyi nang na 'dug bzhin du //
NK106(me)001:4720: byang chub dam pa yongs dag rnyed pa ni //
NK106(me)001:4721: de 'dra'i sangs rgyas sngon chad ma byung zhing //
NK106(me)001:4722: da lta mi gnas ma 'ongs pa na'ang med //
NK106(me)001:4724: khrims ldan mang du thos pas 'grub pa ni /
NK106(me)001:4726: dad ldan ngo tsha shes shing khrel yod la //
NK106(me)001:4727: bag yod tshul khrims dag cing dge la spro //
NK106(me)001:4728: mang thos 'dod pa chung zhing chog shes ldan //
NK106(me)001:4729: de yis ting 'dzin 'di ni myur du 'grub //
NK106(me)001:4730: dad pa dang ldan pas 'grub ste chos la dad
NK106(me)001:4731: pas 'jug cing zhugs pa na'ang lhag par dad pas
NK106(me)001:4732: ches gong du 'phel ba'i phyir te /
NK106(me)001:4734: dad pa can gyi mi rnams la //
NK106(me)001:4735: dkar po'i chos rnams ngang gis 'byung //
NK106(me)001:4737: ngo tsha shes shing khrel yod pa ni ting nge
NK106(me)001:4738: 'dzin bsgom pa la spro ba dang mi 'dor bas
NK106(me)001:4740: bag yod pas rnam g.yeng las sems bsrung ba'i phyir ting nge 'dzin 'grub ste /
NK106(me)001:4741: ting nge 'dzin dam pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:4742: bag yod ngo tsha shes shing khrel yod pas //
NK106(me)001:4743: zab mo'i ting 'dzin dam pa rnyed par 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:4747: tshul khrims ldan pa'i mgo la de 'dug ste //
NK106(me)001:4748: ting 'dzin zhi ba mchog 'di rnyed par 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:4750: dge ba la spro ba dang /
NK106(me)001:4752: 'dod pa chung zhing chog shes pas ting nge 'dzin 'grub par /
NK106(me)001:4754: yon tan tshogs rab 'dod dang chog shes ldan //
NK106(me)001:4755: mang du thos shing yo byad bsnyungs pa dang //
NK106(me)001:4756: dgon par gnas shing gcig pur dben la dga' //
NK106(me)001:4757: de yis ting 'dzin mchog 'di rnyed mi dka' //
NK106(me)001:4759: sgrub pa lnga spangs pas 'grub pa ni /
NK106(me)001:4761: lus sems bsdams shing dben par gnas la dga' //
NK106(me)001:4762: gnyid dang snyom las smra la dga' ba spangs //
NK106(me)001:4763: rgod 'gyod med cing gzhan dang 'dris pa nyung //
NK106(me)001:4764: de yis ting 'dzin 'di ni myur du 'grub //
NK106(me)001:4765: 'di ltar sems dang lus ma bsdams pa ni rgod
NK106(me)001:4766: bag gi rnam par gyur pas zhi ba'i lam dang
NK106(me)001:4767: 'gal ba dang / grong 'dabs la sogs pa mang
NK106(me)001:4768: po 'du ba'i gnas ni rnam par g.yeng bas nyams
NK106(me)001:4769: 'gal ba dang / pa dang / gnyid dang rmugs
NK106(me)001:4770: pa dang snyom las su gnas pa la dga' ba
NK106(me)001:4771: ni bya ba gzhan yang mi 'grub na ting nge
NK106(me)001:4772: 'dzin lta ci smos te 'gal zla yin pa dang
NK106(me)001:4773: 'gal ba dang / pa dang / / rgod pa
NK106(me)001:4774: dang 'gyod pa ni sems g.yeng ba'i phyir lhag mthong
NK106(me)001:4775: la bar du gcod pa dang /
NK106(me)001:4776: skye bo dang bshes 'dris mang ba ni brel ba
NK106(me)001:4777: du ma dang chags sdang gi gnas su gyur pa'i
NK106(me)001:4778: phyir bsam gtan dang 'gal ba dang /
NK106(me)001:4779: smra la dga' ba ni ting nge 'dzin gyi nyams
NK106(me)001:4780: yod pa dag 'grib cing skye ba'i gegs byed la
NK106(me)001:4781: 'khon dang rtsod pa du ma'i 'byung khungs su gyur
NK106(me)001:4782: pa'i phyir / 'di dag spangs na ting nge 'dzin
NK106(me)001:4783: ngang gis 'phel zhing rgyal ba'i chos 'dzin pa yin
NK106(me)001:4784: pa'i phyir / te / snga ma las /
NK106(me)001:4785: 'du 'dzi med cing dben la dga' ba dang //
NK106(me)001:4786: 'dris pa nyung zhing gnyid dang snyom las spangs //
NK106(me)001:4787: mi zhum rgod pa med cing lus sems bsdams //
NK106(me)001:4788: de yis ting 'dzin mchog 'di rnyed mi dka' //
NK106(me)001:4791: tshogs las bsrings shing rab tu zhi la mos //
NK106(me)001:4792: ri dgas lta bur mdzes shing gnas de rgyu //
NK106(me)001:4793: mkha' la rlung bzhin rnyed la mi chags la //
NK106(me)001:4794: de 'dra de ni rgyal ba'i chos 'dzin yin //
NK106(me)001:4796: dben par gnas shing bya ba nyung bas 'grub pa ni /
NK106(me)001:4798: grong dang grong 'dab skye bo'i 'du 'dzi med //
NK106(me)001:4799: gnas dang dgon par mang po'i rten 'dris med //
NK106(me)001:4800: don dang bya ba sna tshogs brel ba med //
NK106(me)001:4801: de yis ting 'dzin 'di ni myur du 'grub //
NK106(me)001:4802: gang dag grong dang grong 'dab pa'i skye bo rnams
NK106(me)001:4803: dang 'grogs shing sa mdo la sogs pa'i gnas sam
NK106(me)001:4804: / dgon pa'i gnas kyi rab tu byung ba dag dang rten 'dris byed la /
NK106(me)001:4805: tshe 'di'i rnam par g.yeng ba'i don dang bya ba
NK106(me)001:4806: mang ba de dag gis nam yang zhi ba'i ting
NK106(me)001:4808: gang du gnas kyang bshes 'dris nyung zhing don dang
NK106(me)001:4809: bya ba nyung ba dag la ngang gis dge ba
NK106(me)001:4810: 'phel zhing ting nge 'dzin 'grub pa yin te tshul
NK106(me)001:4811: bzhin yid la byed pa mang ba'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)001:4813: ma 'ongs dus na dge slong dag /'phyar zhing g.yeng la ma bsdams pa //
NK106(me)001:4814: rnyed dang bkur stis rgyags pa dag /
NK106(me)001:4815: tshul khrims ldan la khro ba 'byung //
NK106(me)001:4817: de dag rnams la mi brten cing //
NK106(me)001:4818: gcig pur bas matha'i gnas mal du //
NK106(me)001:4819: gnas te dben la dga' bar gyis //
NK106(me)001:4821: tshul bzhin yid la byed pa kho nas 'da' bar bya ste /
NK106(me)001:4823: don dam gzigs par bgyi slad dngos rnams la //
NK106(me)001:4824: tshul bzhin yid la byed pa de goms mdzod //
NK106(me)001:4825: de dang 'dra bar yon tan ldan pa yi //
NK106(me)001:4826: chos gzhan 'ga' yang mchis pa ma lags so //
NK106(me)001:4828: gang zag theg pa chen po'i rigs can gyis 'grub pa ni /
NK106(me)001:4830: tshe 'di'i bde dang phyi ma'i bde 'bras dang //
NK106(me)001:4831: rang don zhi ba gnyer min 'gro ba'i phyir //
NK106(me)001:4832: srid las thar 'dod nges 'byung skyo shas can //
NK106(me)001:4833: de yis ting 'dzin mchog 'di myur du 'grub //
NK106(me)001:4834: 'di ltar gzhan don du zhi ba'i dgon par bsam gtan gnyer bas gnas par bya ba las /
NK106(me)001:4835: rang don du nyan rang gi zhi bde don du
NK106(me)001:4836: gnyer ba ni skyes bu dam pa theg pa chen
NK106(me)001:4837: po la zhugs pa rnams kyi lam la yin pa'i
NK106(me)001:4838: phyir ro // des na tshe 'di'i bde 'bras dang /
NK106(me)001:4839: phyi ma'i bde 'bras lha mi'i dpal thob pa dang /
NK106(me)001:4840: rang don du zhi ba mi 'dod pas 'khor ba'i
NK106(me)001:4841: sems can gyi phyir srid pa la skyo zhing nges
NK106(me)001:4842: par 'byung ba'i blos bsam gtan bsgrub pa ni rten
NK106(me)001:4843: gyi gang zag tu rig par bya'o //
NK106(me)001:4844: ting nge 'dzin mchog dam pa las /
NK106(me)001:4845: srid pa'i bde la rab tu ma chags shing //
NK106(me)001:4846: gcig pur zhi ba tshol ba'i sems bral te //
NK106(me)001:4847: 'dus byas rnams la skyo ba'i yid ldan pa //
NK106(me)001:4848: de yis ting 'dzin mchog rab dam pa 'grub //
NK106(me)001:4850: de la tshe 'di'i bde ba mtha' dag la ma chags shing /
NK106(me)001:4851: khyad par du nor la sred pa dag gis yo byad bsnyungs pa la bslab dgos te /
NK106(me)001:4853: gdug pa dug dang mtshon dang dgra bo dang //
NK106(me)001:4854: me bzhin 'dod pa'i bde la yid dbyung mdzod //
NK106(me)001:4855: 'dod pa rnams ni phung grol bskyed pa ste //
NK106(me)001:4856: thub pa'i dbang pos kim pa'i 'bras 'drar gsungs //
NK106(me)001:4857: de dag spang bgyi de yi lcags sgrog gis //
NK106(me)001:4858: 'khor ba'i brtson rar 'jig rten 'di dag bcings //
NK106(me)001:4860: nang sems can la chags pas gtso bor de dag spang dgos te /
NK106(me)001:4862: bud med gzhon nu'i lus 'di logs shig tu //
NK106(me)001:4863: dri nga ba dang sgo dgu dod pa dang //
NK106(me)001:4864: mi gtsang kun snod 'dra ba dgang dka' dang //
NK106(me)001:4865: pags pas g.yogs dang rgyan yang logs shig gzigs //
NK106(me)001:4868: bud med phung bar byed pa ste //
NK106(me)001:4870: gal te bdag la phan 'dod na //
NK106(me)001:4871: de bas bud med rnam par spang //
NK106(me)001:4873: byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod kyi mdo las /
NK106(me)001:4874: stong gi 'jig rten gyi khams su yongs su brtags
NK106(me)001:4875: na ji ltar bdag gi chung ma ltar dgrar gyur
NK106(me)001:4876: pa gzhan yang gang med do zhes so //
NK106(me)001:4877: mdor na rang gi rgyud la gang shas che ba'i
NK106(me)001:4878: nyon mongs pa de dang por brtags la gtso bor
NK106(me)001:4879: spang zhing / dbang po drug gi yul la zhen pa kun spang dgos te /
NK106(me)001:4881: gang dag dbang po drug yul rnams la ni //
NK106(me)001:4882: rtag tu mi brtan g.yo dang gang dag gcig /
NK106(me)001:4883: g.yul ngor dgra sogs las rgyal de dag la //
NK106(me)001:4884: mkhas rnams dang po dpa' rab lags par 'tshal //
NK106(me)001:4888: rgyan po 'gyed dang lus la blta ba dang //
NK106(me)001:4889: le lo sdig pa'i grogs la brten pa dang //
NK106(me)001:4890: chang dang mtshan mo rgyu ba ngan song ba //
NK106(me)001:4891: grags pa nyams par 'gyur ba de drug spongs //
NK106(me)001:4893: gzhan yang rang gi chos la mchog tu 'dzin pas gzhan la smod pa dang /
NK106(me)001:4894: zab mo'i chos la the tshom za ba dang /
NK106(me)001:4895: mi rtag pa la rtag par 'dzin /
NK106(me)001:4896: mi bden pa la bden par 'dzin /
NK106(me)001:4897: phyin ci log la dam par 'dzin /
NK106(me)001:4898: 'khor ba sdug bsngal ba la bde bar 'dzin pa
NK106(me)001:4899: ste phyin ci log bzhi dang bcas pa srid pa
NK106(me)001:4900: kun tu sbyor ba yin pas gtso bor spang dgos
NK106(me)001:4902: tshul khrims brtul zhugs mchog 'dzin rang lus la //
NK106(me)001:4903: phyin ci log bzhi lta dang the tshom ste //
NK106(me)001:4904: kun du sbyor ba 'di gsum thar pa yi //
NK106(me)001:4905: grong khyer sgo 'gegs lags par mkhyen par gyis //
NK106(me)001:4907: khyad par du rnyed na dga' ba dang /
NK106(me)001:4908: ma rnyed na mi dga' ba dang /
NK106(me)001:4910: sdug na mi dga' ba dang /
NK106(me)001:4911: snyan grags thob na dga' ba dang /
NK106(me)001:4912: skur ba dang mi snyan pa byung dus mi dga' ba dang /
NK106(me)001:4914: smad na mi dga' ba ste 'jig rten chos brgyad nges par spang ba nyid /
NK106(me)001:4916: 'jig rten mkhyen pas rnyed dang ma rnyed dang //
NK106(me)001:4917: bde dang mi bde snyan dang mi snyan dang //
NK106(me)001:4918: bstod smad ces bgyi 'jig rten chos brgyad po //
NK106(me)001:4919: bdag gi yid yul min par mgo snyoms mdzod //
NK106(me)001:4923: dad dang tshul khrims thos dang gtong ba ni //
NK106(me)001:4924: dri med ngo tsha shes dang khrel yod dang //
NK106(me)001:4925: shes rab nor bdun lags par thub pas gsungs //
NK106(me)001:4927: khyim pa la sogs gzhan dag dge ba la bskul zhing gso sbyong la 'god pa'ang /
NK106(me)001:4929: 'tshe dang chom rkun 'khrig pa brdzun dang ni //
NK106(me)001:4930: chang dang dus min zas la chags pa dang //
NK106(me)001:4931: mal stan mtho la dga' dang glu dag dang //
NK106(me)001:4932: gar dang phreng ba'i khyad par rnams spong zhing //
NK106(me)001:4933: dgra bcom tshul khrims rjes su byed pa yi //
NK106(me)001:4934: yan lag brgyad po 'di dag dang ldan na //
NK106(me)001:4935: gso sbyong 'dod spyod lha lus yid 'ong ba //
NK106(me)001:4936: skyes pa bud med dag la stsol bar bgyid //
NK106(me)001:4938: mdor na bsam gtan pa dgon par gnas pas /
NK106(me)001:4939: sdom pa'i tshul khrims kyis nyes spyod cha dang bcas pa las rang gi sems bsdam /
NK106(me)001:4940: dge ba chos sdud kyi tshul khrims kyis sngar med
NK106(me)001:4941: pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang rnam par grol ba la
NK106(me)001:4942: sogs pa bsgrub cing yod pa rnams gong du spel
NK106(me)001:4943: nas dge ba'i phyogs 'ba' zhig gis nyin mtshan 'da'
NK106(me)001:4944: ba dang / sems can don byed kyi tshul khrims
NK106(me)001:4945: kyis der lhags pa'i skye bo dge ba la bskul
NK106(me)001:4946: zhing chos 'dod pa dang gtan khrims nongs pa rnams
NK106(me)001:4947: la gang dang gang 'tshams pa'i chos kyis mgu bar
NK106(me)001:4948: ba dang / bya zhing / tha na bya dang
NK106(me)001:4949: ri dgas dang 'bu srin dang grog ma la sogs
NK106(me)001:4950: pa'i sems can la'ang mi 'tshe zhing zas la sogs
NK106(me)001:4951: pa byin nas de bzhin gshegs pa'i mtshan nas brjod
NK106(me)001:4952: ba dang / bya zhing / / dkon mchog gsum gyi sgra bsgrag /
NK106(me)001:4953: nam zhig na 'di dag kyang sangs rgyas su 'gyur nges snyam pa dang /
NK106(me)001:4954: nam zhig na 'di dag bdag gis 'khor ba las thar bar bya snyam pa dang /
NK106(me)001:4955: 'di dag kyang sprul pa yin pa'ang srid snyam nas
NK106(me)001:4956: gus pa bskyed cing mos gus dang dag snang bya
NK106(me)001:4957: ba dang / da lta yod kyang do mod med
NK106(me)001:4958: pa la sogs pas 'bral ba dang mi rtag pa
NK106(me)001:4959: nyid du yid la bya zhing /
NK106(me)001:4960: skad cig kyang tha mal du ma yin par blo dge ba 'ba' zhig gis 'da' bar bya'o //
NK106(me)001:4961: ji ltar bsgrub pa thabs kyi yan lag la zhi
NK106(me)001:4962: lhag bsgrub pa'i thabs dngos dang so sor bshad pa
NK106(me)001:4963: gnyis las / zhi lhag bsgrub pa'i thabs la'ang gsum ste /
NK106(me)001:4966: ji ltar bsgrub pa thabs kyi yan lag kyang //
NK106(me)001:4967: gnyid rmugs rgod 'gyod the tshom sgrib pa lnga //
NK106(me)001:4968: spangs te zhi lhag zung 'brel tshul gyis bsgrub //
NK106(me)001:4969: gnyid rmugs gnyis kyis zhi gnas rab tu sgrib //
NK106(me)001:4970: rgod 'gyod gnyis kyis lhag mthong rnam par g.yeng //
NK106(me)001:4971: the tshom gnyis ka'i gnod byed mi mthun phyogs //
NK106(me)001:4972: 'dir rnal 'byor spyod pa ba dag gis bsam gtan la sgrib pa ni lnga ste /
NK106(me)001:4973: yang dag pa'i zhi gnas gsal dngas phyed pa la ni gnyid dang rmugs pas bying bar byed la /
NK106(me)001:4974: lhag mthong dngas la rtse gcig pa ni rgod pa dang 'gyod pas 'phro bar byed cing /
NK106(me)001:4975: the tshom gnyis ka'i dus su mi 'grub pa'i rgyu'o //
NK106(me)001:4976: gnyid ni 'jug pa rang dbang med par sems nang du sdud la /
NK106(me)001:4977: rmugs pa ni yul mi gsal ba'i shes pa lung ma bstan dang /
NK106(me)001:4978: rgod pa ni yul gyi phyir sems 'phro ba yin la /
NK106(me)001:4979: 'gyod pa ni bya ba 'ga' zhig yid la gcags pas mngon par mi dga' ba'i shes pa /
NK106(me)001:4980: the tshom ni gnyis bcas kyi blos zin med pas bya ba bsgrub pa la bar du gcod pa'o //
NK106(me)001:4983: rgod dang 'gyod dang gnod sems rmugs pa dang /
NK106(me)001:4984: gnyid dang 'dod la 'dun dang the tshom ste //
NK106(me)001:4985: sgrib pa lnga po 'di dag dge ba'i nor //
NK106(me)001:4986: 'phrog pa'i chom rkun lags par mkhyen par mdzod //
NK106(me)001:4988: de'ang rgod 'gyod gnyis gcig gnyid rmugs gnyis gcig 'dod pa la 'dun pa /
NK106(me)001:4992: de'ang gnyid rmugs la sogs pa /
NK106(me)001:4993: de ltar lnga nyid bying rgod gnyis su 'du //
NK106(me)001:4994: bying na gseng zhing rgod na rtse gcig bsgom //
NK106(me)001:4995: de la gnyid rmugs gnyis ni bying ba yin pas
NK106(me)001:4996: gsengs la yid la byed pa bcu gcig bsgom zhing
NK106(me)001:4997: / gzhan rnams rgod pa yin pas sems gnas pa'i thabs dgu bsgom pa la 'bad par bya'o //
NK106(me)001:4998: gnyen po zung 'brel bsten pa ni /
NK106(me)001:5000: zhi gnas med pa'i lhag mthong spros la rgod //
NK106(me)001:5001: lhag mthong med pa'i zhi gnas lung ma bstan //
NK106(me)001:5002: zung 'brel sgrib pa'i gnyen po mchog gi lam //
NK106(me)001:5003: zhi gnas kyis ma brlan pa'i shes rab ni tshig gi go yul tsam la /
NK106(me)001:5004: lhag mthong gis ma zin pa'i zhi gnas ni lung
NK106(me)001:5005: ma bstan 'khor ba'i sa bon las 'phags par mi
NK106(me)001:5006: nus pa'i phyir zung 'brel la 'bad de /
NK106(me)001:5008: shes rab med par bsam gtan yod min te //
NK106(me)001:5009: bsam gtan med par yang ni shes rab med //
NK106(me)001:5010: gang la de gnyis yod pa srid pa yi //
NK106(me)001:5011: rgya mtsho gnag rjes lta bur 'tshal bar bgyi //
NK106(me)001:5013: so sor bshad pa la zhi gnas dang lhag mthong gnyis kyi /
NK106(me)001:5017: zhi gnas lus ngag yid sems dal bas 'grub //
NK106(me)001:5018: de yang chos kun rang bzhin mnyam pa'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:5019: dmigs pa rab zhi gtso bo'i yan lag yin //
NK106(me)001:5020: dmigs pa gcig la sems 'dzin 'khor gyi tshul //
NK106(me)001:5021: 'di ltar ting nge 'dzin rnam par mi rtog pa ni sgo gsum rab tu dal bas 'grub ste /
NK106(me)001:5024: rlung dal bas khams dal ba 'khor lo bzhi'i 'dab ma la sogs pa rang gnas su sdod pas /
NK106(me)001:5025: sems gnas kyi zhi gnas ngang gis 'grub ste /
NK106(me)001:5026: sems kyi rten khams dngas ma mi g.yo bar sa gcig tu sdod pa'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)001:5027: de ltar dal bus sgom dus sems spro bsdu med
NK106(me)001:5028: pa'i rang bzhin de nyid zhi gnas kyi ngo bo
NK106(me)001:5030: de brtan par bya ba'i don du dmigs yul gcig
NK106(me)001:5031: la sems bzung bas cung zad mi rtog pa 'khor
NK106(me)001:5033: de'ang gshis la sems 'di'i rang bzhin gang nas kyang
NK106(me)001:5034: ma 'ongs mi 'gro mi gnas pa'i rang lugs phyam
NK106(me)001:5035: phyal le ba zhig dus rgyun du yod de /
NK106(me)001:5036: gsal dngas phyed pa'i cha de nas lhag mthong /
NK106(me)001:5037: gnas cha de nas zhi gnas /
NK106(me)001:5038: gnyis su med pas zung 'brel zhes smos te /
NK106(me)001:5039: yod ni sems can kun la dus rtag tu yod cing /
NK106(me)001:5040: gsal ba ni ngang gis mi g.yo ba ngal sos
NK106(me)001:5041: pa la sogs pa'i dus su ngo 'phrod par sla
NK106(me)001:5042: ba yin no // rnal 'byor pas ni 'phros sam
NK106(me)001:5043: gnas kyang rang rang sa bcos bslad med pa'i zhi
NK106(me)001:5044: lhag shes pas grol ba yin no //
NK106(me)001:5046: dmigs pa gcig la sems 'dzin lugs /
NK106(me)001:5047: de yang snang bcas snang med rnam pa gnyis //
NK106(me)001:5048: phyi nang gnyis te bzhi yis zin par 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:5049: snang bcas gzugs sogs sgo lnga'i yul rnams la //
NK106(me)001:5050: snang med mi rtog rtse gcig ngang la 'jog /
NK106(me)001:5051: phyi rol rdo shing sku gzugs la sogs dang //
NK106(me)001:5052: nang nyid snying gar pad+ma 'thur 'phyang sogs //
NK106(me)001:5053: dang po snang bcas la sems gzung tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:5054: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya gang rung la sems
NK106(me)001:5055: ma yengs par gtad pas rtse gcig tu gnas pa'o
NK106(me)001:5056: // de brtan nas snang med la sems gzung ba
NK106(me)001:5057: ni gang du'ang mi rtog pa'i ngang la sems 'dzin
NK106(me)001:5058: // pa'o // de'ang lus kyi nang du lha'i sku'am /
NK106(me)001:5060: snying gar pad+ma 'thur 'phyang dang 'khor lo la sogs pa'i phyag mtshan na /
NK106(me)001:5061: 'od la sogs pa bsgoms pas spros pa zhi nas bde shas che ba'i zhi gnas skye la /
NK106(me)001:5062: phyi rol tu rdo'am shing ngam sku gzugs la sogs
NK106(me)001:5063: pa'i rten zhig las ma yengs par bzung na'ang gsal
NK106(me)001:5064: dngas phyed pa'i zhi gnas skye'o //
NK106(me)001:5065: de'ang spros pa shas che bas phyir bzung na 'phro bas nang du gzung zhing /
NK106(me)001:5066: rtog pa nyung bas nang du bzung na bying ba shas che bas phyir gzung ngo //
NK106(me)001:5067: de'ang dang por mtshan bcas gang rung zhig la sems
NK106(me)001:5068: bzung bas rjes la mtshan med ngang gis 'byung ngo
NK106(me)001:5069: // mi shes pa dag sku gzugs la sogs pa'i yul la sems bzung na spros par 'gro bas /
NK106(me)001:5070: ci yang med pa'i ngang spros med du bzhag zer
NK106(me)001:5071: ba ni gnad ma go zhing nyams myong chung ba'i
NK106(me)001:5072: skad yin te / 'di ltar rang gi sems gang la gtad kyang 'dra ste /
NK106(me)001:5073: gtod dus dang por rtog pa zhig sngon du 'gro yang /
NK106(me)001:5074: de nas yul de snang la der 'dzin ma zhugs
NK106(me)001:5075: pa'i ngang du sems spro bsdu med par dngas sang
NK106(me)001:5076: nge yer re wal le ston ka'i nam mkha' sprin
NK106(me)001:5077: dang bral ba ltar mi gnas mi srid do //
NK106(me)001:5078: snang med kyi ngang du sems gzung yang de las nyams lhag tu mi 'byung la /
NK106(me)001:5079: nyes na bying ba'am rgod pa zhig gis mi mnod mi srid do //
NK106(me)001:5080: mdor na yul snang la der 'dzin ma zhugs pa'i
NK106(me)001:5081: ngang la blo spro bsdu dang bral bar gnas pa
NK106(me)001:5082: la kho bo ni bsam gtan zhes 'dod pas /
NK106(me)001:5083: snang bcas sam snang med gang la sems gzung yang
NK106(me)001:5084: bde gsal mi rtog pa'i nyams mtha' bral 'dzin med
NK106(me)001:5085: chen po'i rtogs pas brgyan pa 'char dgos par 'dod
NK106(me)001:5086: de / de ma shar na skyon bcas /
NK106(me)001:5087: shar na yang dag pa'i bsam gtan thabs shes gnyis
NK106(me)001:5088: med kyi ting nge 'dzin rgyud la skyes par 'dod
NK106(me)001:5089: do // thabs kyi yan lag ni /
NK106(me)001:5091: dmigs yul gcig la rtse gcig sems 'jog pa //
NK106(me)001:5092: zhi gnas bsgrub pa'i thabs kyi yan lag yin //
NK106(me)001:5093: dmigs pa gang la 'jog par 'dod pa de la sems rtse gcig tu gzung ngo //
NK106(me)001:5094: de nas sems gnas pa'i thabs dgus de brtan par bya ste /
NK106(me)001:5095: dmigs pa de la sems 'jog pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5097: phyir 'phro na sems bslan te 'jog pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5098: phyi phyir brtun te nye bar 'jog pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5099: de la dga' ba bskyed nas 'dul ba dang /
NK106(me)001:5100: rnam g.yeng gi nyes pa zhi bar byed pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5101: gnyid rmugs la sogs bsal nas rnam par zhi bar byed pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5102: gzhan la mi 'phro bar rtse gcig tu byed pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5103: de la mi rtsol bar mnyam par 'jog pa ste dagu'o //
NK106(me)001:5113: mnyam par 'jog par byed do zhes pa'i don to //
NK106(me)001:5116: de yis rtse gcig zhi gnas skyes pa'i tshe //
NK106(me)001:5117: spel zhing brtan phyir lhag mthong ye shes spro //
NK106(me)001:5118: bogs 'byin spyod lam kun dang bsre ba gces //
NK106(me)001:5119: stengs na lus sems gsengs la sngar bzhin bsgom //
NK106(me)001:5120: 'dis ni myur du 'grub par 'gyur ba yin //
NK106(me)001:5121: sems rtse gcig tu zin pa tsam gyis rkyen mi
NK106(me)001:5122: thub cing lhag mthong gang dang yang 'drer mi rung
NK106(me)001:5123: bas / rtse gcig pa'i dus der snang ba sgyu
NK106(me)001:5124: ma la sogs pa'i lhag mthong dang bsre ba dang
NK106(me)001:5125: bas / / 'gro 'dug la sogs pa zhi gnas dang bsres la sgom zhing /
NK106(me)001:5126: skyed med na sems spro lus ngag g.yengs pa'i rjes la snga ma ltar bsgoms pas /
NK106(me)001:5127: de nas dmigs pa gang la 'jog par 'dod pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5128: dus nam gyi tshe 'jog par 'dod pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5129: yun ji srid 'jog par 'dod pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5130: tshul ji lta bus 'jog par 'dod pa la rang dbang thob pas 'jug ldog nus pa 'byung ste /
NK106(me)001:5132: de yis de ni 'phel byas nas //
NK106(me)001:5134: dngos gzhi'i gnas pa nges 'thob bo //
NK106(me)001:5137: yan lag gtso 'khor gyi tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:5139: lhag mthong 'dod pas sems gsal dngas pa'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:5140: so sor rtog pa gtso bo'i yan lag la //
NK106(me)001:5141: mi rtog mnyam par 'jog pa 'khor gyi tshul //
NK106(me)001:5143: sems gsal la dngas pa'i ngang las chos rnams kyi
NK106(me)001:5144: rang bzhin la blta ba gtso bo'i yan lag la
NK106(me)001:5145: / blo mi rtog pa'i gsal cha mi 'phro ba de 'khor ram phal pa'i tshul du yod pa'o //
NK106(me)001:5146: so sor rtog pa'i lhag mthong rtsal sbyang ba ni /
NK106(me)001:5147: so sor rtog pa'i lhag mthong /
NK106(me)001:5148: de yang chos can chos nyid rnam pa gnyis //
NK106(me)001:5149: chos can sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad blta bya zhing //
NK106(me)001:5150: chos nyid mkha' ltar stong pa'i rtsal sbyang bya //
NK106(me)001:5151: ji bzhin ngang la bzhag pas ye shes 'char //
NK106(me)001:5152: mnyam gzhag brtan pa'i ngang las /
NK106(me)001:5153: phyi rol gyi snang ba 'di dag chos can rten
NK106(me)001:5154: 'brel rmi lam sgyu ma la sogs pa snang la
NK106(me)001:5155: bden pa med pa'i ngo bor rim gyis brtags pa
NK106(me)001:5156: de'i ngang la ji tsam 'dod par mnyam pa bzhag
NK106(me)001:5157: ste / sa'i snying po 'khor lo bcu pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:5158: chos tshul 'di dag sgyu ma smig rgyu dang //
NK106(me)001:5159: rmi lam mig yor sgra brnyan sprul pa 'dra //
NK106(me)001:5160: gar mkhan tshon 'drar gang gis rtogs gyur pa //
NK106(me)001:5161: bsod nams zhing rab de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK106(me)001:5163: chos nyid rang bzhin gyis ma skyes pa nam mkha'
NK106(me)001:5164: lta bu'i ngang la blo'i tshol khro dang bral bar
NK106(me)001:5165: bzhag ste / skye med rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK106(me)001:5166: gar yang ma rtog cir yang ma bsams shig /
NK106(me)001:5167: bcas bcos ma byed rang bzhin lhug par zhog /
NK106(me)001:5168: ma bcos pa de skye med rin chen mdzod //
NK106(me)001:5169: dus gsum rgyal ba kun gyi gshegs shul yin //
NK106(me)001:5171: de lta mnyam par bzhag pas snang yul sgyu ma ltar rtogs la 'dzin byed ma zhugs pa /
NK106(me)001:5172: rang bzhin nam mkha' ltar rtogs la snang yul ma
NK106(me)001:5173: 'gags pa'i ye shes stong gsal spros pa dang bral
NK106(me)001:5174: ba rang byung gi ye shes 'char te /
NK106(me)001:5176: kye kun byed rgyal po byang chub sems nga ni //
NK106(me)001:5177: chos rnams kun gyi blta ba'i me long ste //
NK106(me)001:5178: gsal la rang bzhin med par kun 'char bas //
NK106(me)001:5179: ma bltas rang bzhin gsal bar lung bstan no //
NK106(me)001:5180: ma skyes de bzhin nyid kyi yul nyid la //
NK106(me)001:5181: blta ba'i yul med mthong ba chen por rtogs //
NK106(me)001:5183: bying rgod rtsal sbyang bogs 'byin pa ni /
NK106(me)001:5184: de ltar bsgoms pa'i lhag mthong de nyid /
NK106(me)001:5185: stengs na sna tshogs chos la rtsal sbyang ste //
NK106(me)001:5186: sgyu ma stong pa gnyis med dag par blta //
NK106(me)001:5187: 'phro na zhi gnas ngang la mnyam par gzhag /
NK106(me)001:5188: de tshe nam mkha' lta bu'i 'od gsal ni //
NK106(me)001:5189: stong gsal spros dang bral ba'i ngo bo mthong //
NK106(me)001:5190: de yis sgrib gnyis sprin las grol ba 'grub //
NK106(me)001:5191: re 'ga' rgya mtsho lta bu'i 'od gsal 'char //
NK106(me)001:5192: shar grol ngang dngas rtog med lhun gyis grub //
NK106(me)001:5193: bogs 'byin spyod lam kun dang de nyid bsre //
NK106(me)001:5194: 'dis ni lhag mthong myur du 'grub par 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:5195: lhag mthong stengs pas skyed med na dgag sgrub la
NK106(me)001:5196: sogs pa'i chos mang po spros te sgyu mar wal
NK106(me)001:5197: wal rtsal sbyang zhing sgyu ma gnyis med du la
NK106(me)001:5198: bzla ba dang / rtog pa 'phro na sngar bzhin zhi gnas la mnyam par bzhag cing /
NK106(me)001:5199: de'i ngang la stengs na yid la byed pa bcu gcig bsgom par bya'o //
NK106(me)001:5200: de'ang rten 'brel la sogs pa'i chos la rtog dpyod du yid la bya'o //
NK106(me)001:5201: des 'phro na zhi gnas la bzhag cing dpyod pa cung zad yid la bya'o //
NK106(me)001:5202: des rtog na rtog dpyod mi 'gyu ba'i ngang du mi rtog pa yid la bya'o //
NK106(me)001:5203: de'i don las ma yengs pa'i zhi gnas yid la bya'o //
NK106(me)001:5204: de yang gsal dngas phyed pa'i lhag mthong yid la bya'o //
NK106(me)001:5205: de'i tshe gsal stong gnyis su med pa'i zung 'brel yid la bya'o //
NK106(me)001:5206: de'i ngang la rgyun bsring ba'i phyir sems rab tu 'dzin pa'i rgyu mtshan yid la bya'o //
NK106(me)001:5207: de'i dus su sems gnas pa'i ngang las mi g.yo ba zhi gnas kyi rgyu mtshan yid la bya'o //
NK106(me)001:5208: gsal dngas phyed pa lhag mthong gi rgyu mtshan yid la bya'o //
NK106(me)001:5209: stong gsal gnyis med du 'dres pa zung 'jug gi rgyu mtshan yid la bya'o //
NK106(me)001:5210: chos thams cad rang bzhin med par mnyam pa btang snyoms kyi rgyu mtshan yid la bya'o //
NK106(me)001:5212: rtog pa dang bcas shing dpyod pa dang bcas pa'i yid la byed pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5213: rtog pa med cing dpyod pa tsam dang bcas pa'i yid la byed pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5214: rtog pa yang med dpyod pa yang med pa'i yid la byed pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5215: zhi gnas yid la byed pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5216: lhag mthong yid la byed pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5217: zung du 'brel pa yid la byed pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5218: sems rab tu 'dzin pa'i rgyu mtshan yid la byed pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5219: zhi gnas kyi rgyu mtshan yid la byed pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5220: lhag mthong gi rgyu mtshan yid la byed pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5221: zung du 'brel ba'i rgyu mtshan yid la byed pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5222: btang snyoms kyi rgyu mtshan yid la byed pas sems sbyang bar bya'o zhes pa'i don to //
NK106(me)001:5225: zhi lhag gnyis su med par rtsal sbyangs pas rgya
NK106(me)001:5226: mtsho dba' rlabs zhi ba lta bu zhi gnas klong
NK106(me)001:5228: sems gang gtad kyi don la gsal dngas 'dzin med du gnas shing /
NK106(me)001:5229: rtog pa 'gyu ba'i dba' rlabs kyis mi gnod par
NK106(me)001:5230: rang shar dus de nyid du grol ba dus mnyam
NK106(me)001:5231: pa 'byung ngo // nam mkha' sprin dang bral ba
NK106(me)001:5232: lta bu lhag mthong gi 'od gsal klong du gyur
NK106(me)001:5234: bcos bslad dang bral ba stong gsal rjen pa'i ngo
NK106(me)001:5235: pa 'byung ngo // pas / bo mthong dus /
NK106(me)001:5236: sems gnas kyang chos nyid kyi ngang du gnas pas
NK106(me)001:5237: yin min gdod nas dag pa'i gdeng thob /
NK106(me)001:5238: 'phro ba chos nyid kyi rol par shar bas gang
NK106(me)001:5239: snang ye shes kyi rtsal du shes te rkyen snang
NK106(me)001:5240: rang byung gi ye shes su grol ba'i dus so
NK106(me)001:5241: // de'i tshe rang sems sku gsum gyi ngo bor
NK106(me)001:5242: mthong bas rtsol sgrub mtshan ma'i chos las grol ba
NK106(me)001:5244: kye sems dpa' chen po nyon cig /
NK106(me)001:5245: chos kyi sku ni byang chub sems //
NK106(me)001:5246: byang chub sems las chos kyi sku //
NK106(me)001:5247: rdul tsam sus kyang bcos su med //
NK106(me)001:5248: des na sangs rgyas sems las med //
NK106(me)001:5249: longs spyod rdzogs sku byang chub sems //
NK106(me)001:5250: byang chub sems las longs spyod sku //
NK106(me)001:5251: sems las byung ba'i gzugs rnams la //
NK106(me)001:5252: longs spyod rdzogs las sku gzhan med //
NK106(me)001:5253: sprul pa'i sku ni byang chub sems //
NK106(me)001:5254: byang chub sems kyi sprul pa las //
NK106(me)001:5255: 'gro ba'i don mdzad gzhan pa med //
NK106(me)001:5256: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyang //
NK106(me)001:5257: byang chub sems las gzhan med de //
NK106(me)001:5258: snga rabs 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK106(me)001:5259: rang sems ma bcos sngar mthong rtogs //
NK106(me)001:5260: da lta bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK106(me)001:5261: ma bcos pa yi rang sems te //
NK106(me)001:5262: da lta 'gro ba'i don yang mdzad //
NK106(me)001:5263: slad nas 'byon pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK106(me)001:5264: rang byung sems nyid 'di la ni //
NK106(me)001:5265: snga ma bcos par lung ma bstan //
NK106(me)001:5267: ma bcos lam du zhugs nas byon //
NK106(me)001:5269: gnyis ka 'byongs nas dbyer med zung 'jug ni /
NK106(me)001:5270: de ltar zhi lhag so sor 'byongs nas de gnyis dbyer med pa'i //
NK106(me)001:5271: zung 'jug shes pa 'phro gnas mnyam pa'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:5272: gnyis kar mi rtog ye shes gtso bo la //
NK106(me)001:5273: yeng med spros dang bral ba 'khor gyi tshul //
NK106(me)001:5274: zung du 'jug pa ni zhi lhag gi ngo bo gsal stong gnyis med du shar ba de'i tshe /
NK106(me)001:5275: 'phro ba dang gnas pa mi 'gal bas yul snang
NK106(me)001:5276: la der mi 'dzin pa'i ye shes rtog bral ma
NK106(me)001:5278: de'i ngang las ma yengs pa'i shes pa'i rang bzhin 'khor du gnas so //
NK106(me)001:5279: de'ang dus thams cad du sems nyid gnyis med gtso bo'i ngang yin yang /
NK106(me)001:5280: de zhi lhag gis mnyam par bzhag dus rtogs par sla bas /
NK106(me)001:5281: thabs yeng med de 'khor ram yan lag tu ldan pa yin no //
NK106(me)001:5283: gang tshe gzung dang 'dzin pa dag /
NK106(me)001:5284: gnyis su med par gyur pa na //
NK106(me)001:5285: rang bzhin tha dad ma yin pas //
NK106(me)001:5286: zung du 'jug par de bshad do //
NK106(me)001:5288: de'i tshe gzhi'i sems nyid du glo bur gyi spros
NK106(me)001:5289: pa nub pas chu la chu bzhag pa ltar ro
NK106(me)001:5290: mnyam dbye ba med pa ni /
NK106(me)001:5292: gnyug ma'i yid ni gcig tu sdod dang rnal 'byor pa //
NK106(me)001:5293: chu la chu bzhag bzhin du shes par byos //
NK106(me)001:5296: zung 'jug de'i ngang la gnas dus /
NK106(me)001:5298: ji ltar shar gnas de yi ngang bzhag pas //
NK106(me)001:5299: shar bas grol la gnas pas mnyam pa nyid //
NK106(me)001:5300: zhi lhag zung 'brel bde gsal mi rtog 'char //
NK106(me)001:5301: snang stong thabs shes bskyed rdzogs lhun gyis grub //
NK106(me)001:5302: chu la rlabs zhi ba ltar /
NK106(me)001:5303: rnam rtog gang shar skad cig gis rang byung rang
NK106(me)001:5304: zhir song nas shar grol dus mnyam pa de'i tshe
NK106(me)001:5305: / shar bas grol ba lhag mthong yin la snang
NK106(me)001:5306: bcas bsod nams kyi tshogs bskyed rim du lhun gyis
NK106(me)001:5307: / grub cing / rang zhi ba'i rang rig pa
NK106(me)001:5308: dngas gsal dang bcas pa la gnas pa zhi gnas
NK106(me)001:5309: te snang med ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs pa'i rim
NK106(me)001:5310: / grub cing / par grub pas / zung 'jug
NK106(me)001:5311: gi rang bzhin du ye nas sems la lhun grub
NK106(me)001:5312: / grub cing / par grub pas / tu gnas pa'o // kun byed las /
NK106(me)001:5313: shes nas ma yengs don la gnas pa las //
NK106(me)001:5314: rtsol ba mi 'jug gnyen pos sems mi sbyong //
NK106(me)001:5315: yul la mi 'jog dran pa'i sems mi sdud //
NK106(me)001:5316: gang ltar byung ba de nyid don yin pas //
NK106(me)001:5317: kun byed nga yi don la 'jug par gyis //
NK106(me)001:5319: rtsal sbyang zlog sgom bya ba ni /
NK106(me)001:5320: de ltar zung 'jug bcos bslad med par bsgoms pas /
NK106(me)001:5321: stengs na zhi lhag so sor rtsal sbyang zhing //
NK106(me)001:5322: bying rgod che na bzlog la bsgom par bya //
NK106(me)001:5323: de'ang zhi gnas stengs na lhag mthong bsgom zhing /
NK106(me)001:5324: lhag mthong stengs na zhi gnas bsgoms la /
NK106(me)001:5326: rgod na zhi gnas bsgoms pas skyon las grol ba'o //
NK106(me)001:5329: bogs 'byin nam mkha' dngas shing sprin med tshe //
NK106(me)001:5330: nyi mar rgyab phyogs mkha' la rab bltas pas //
NK106(me)001:5331: stong gsal shes pa spros dang bral ba 'char //
NK106(me)001:5332: nam mkha' dag pa'i tshe nyi ma la rgyab bstan nas //
NK106(me)001:5333: gtsug tor rnam par blta ba'i lta stangs kyis bltas pas /
NK106(me)001:5334: sems gsal stong gi ngang las skad cig de'i mod
NK106(me)001:5335: la 'char ba ni zung 'jug gi ye shes yin
NK106(me)001:5337: don 'di gang yin nam mkha' dag la brtag par gyis //
NK106(me)001:5339: phyi nang gsang ba'i 'od gsal 'char tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:5341: phyi rol dpe yi nam mkha' dag pa las //
NK106(me)001:5342: nang gi chos nyid don gyi nam mkha' che //
NK106(me)001:5343: gsang ba 'od gsal snying po'i nam mkha' ste //
NK106(me)001:5344: nam mkha' sum sprugs dgongs pa shes par bya //
NK106(me)001:5345: dpe phyi rol gyi nam mkha' la bltas pas /
NK106(me)001:5346: don rang gi rig pa shar te /
NK106(me)001:5347: gsang ba ye shes kyi dgongs pa 'char ba 'di
NK106(me)001:5348: ni mthar thug don gyi gdams pa thams cad 'dir
NK106(me)001:5351: 'on kyang gcig tu bla ma'i zhal la ltos pa yin //
NK106(me)001:5353: bla mas smras pa gang gi snying zhugs pa //
NK106(me)001:5354: lag pa'i mthil na gnas pa'i gter mthong 'dra //
NK106(me)001:5358: dpe ni nam mkha' dag la dris //
NK106(me)001:5361: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa rnal 'byor
NK106(me)001:5362: du byed pa ni nam mkha' rnal 'byor du byed
NK106(me)001:5363: pa yin no zhes pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5365: sems ni nam mkha' 'dra bar gzung bya ste //
NK106(me)001:5366: nam mkha'i rang bzhin nyid du'ang sems gzung bya //
NK106(me)001:5368: dpe nam mkha' stong gsal 'gag pa med pa bzhin du /
NK106(me)001:5369: de dus kyi shes pa'ang stong gsal 'gag pa med pa'i ye shes so //
NK106(me)001:5370: de nyid nang gi nam mkha'o //
NK106(me)001:5371: de las stong gsal spros pa dang bral ba'i ye
NK106(me)001:5372: shes bde gsal mi rtog pa'i nyams dang lhan cig
NK106(me)001:5373: shar bas / chos thams cad nam mkha'i mtshan nyid
NK106(me)001:5374: du rang grol te dngos po dang mtshan 'dzin thams
NK106(me)001:5375: cad las grol ba ni gsang ba 'od gsal chen
NK106(me)001:5376: shar bas / po'i nam mkha'o // de'i dus su du ba la sogs pa'i rtags bcu dang /
NK106(me)001:5377: 'od lnga'i snang ba'ang rlung sems dbu mar chud pas nam mkha'i dbyings kun du snang bar byed do //
NK106(me)001:5379: rang bzhin dmigs su med pa las //
NK106(me)001:5381: la la nam mkha'i dkyil na gsal //
NK106(me)001:5382: sna tshogs brjod kyis mi lang ba'o //
NK106(me)001:5384: 'di dag ni yang dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin brtan
NK106(me)001:5385: pa'i rtags te mi 'dod kyang ngang gis 'byung ba
NK106(me)001:5386: yin no // gnyis med bsgrub pa ngo bo'i yan lag la brgyad las /
NK106(me)001:5387: rdzogs chen spang blang las 'das par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:5389: gnyis med bsgrub pa ngo bo'i yan lag ni //
NK106(me)001:5390: thams cad ro mnyam rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:5391: spang blang mi bya dmigs gtad zhen pa dor //
NK106(me)001:5392: 'dzin zhen thams cad srid pa'i 'du byed la //
NK106(me)001:5393: dmigs gtad med na mkha' bzhin bcings grol med //
NK106(me)001:5394: 'di ltar gshis kyi ngo bo ni rtsol sgrub spang
NK106(me)001:5395: blang las 'das pa nam mkha' lta bu yin la
NK106(me)001:5396: / de'i don rtogs pa lta ba /
NK106(me)001:5397: de'i ngang las ma yengs pa bsgom pa yin pas na /
NK106(me)001:5398: sgom pa de yang yod med spang blang re dogs las 'das par shes nas /
NK106(me)001:5399: bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin 'di bsgoms pas brtan pa
NK106(me)001:5400: thob nas bzang du 'gro snyam pa'ang med pas bsgoms
NK106(me)001:5401: na gzhan lta ci smos te /
NK106(me)001:5403: bde ba 'dod pa chags pa'i nad yin pas //
NK106(me)001:5404: 'dod pa med pas bde ba len par byed //
NK106(me)001:5405: sangs rgyas bsgrubs pas 'grub pa ma yin te //
NK106(me)001:5406: ma btsal rang bzhin gnas pas lhun gyis grub //
NK106(me)001:5407: ma btsal rang bzhin gnas la mi rtog zhog /
NK106(me)001:5409: kye sems dpa' chen po rang sems grub 'dod na //
NK106(me)001:5410: 'dod pa med pas grub pa yin pa'i phyir //
NK106(me)001:5411: rtog med mnyam pa nyid la gnas mi byed //
NK106(me)001:5412: blang dor med pa'i yul la rang bzhin gnas //
NK106(me)001:5413: g.yos pa med pa'i ngang la ngang gis gnas //
NK106(me)001:5414: sems ni ji bzhin pa yi ngo bo ste //
NK106(me)001:5415: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin nyid du grub //
NK106(me)001:5416: ji bzhin pa la 'chos par ma byed cig /
NK106(me)001:5417: ngo bo nyid las gzhan du ma bsgrubs shig /
NK106(me)001:5418: btsal na rgyal bas dbyings nas rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:5419: sngar byas zin pas da ni byed mi dgos //
NK106(me)001:5420: sngar grub zin pas da ni bsgrub mi dgos //
NK106(me)001:5421: mi rtog cir mi dgongs la mnyam par zhog /
NK106(me)001:5423: de'ang 'dzin zhen yod na srid pa las mi grol te /
NK106(me)001:5424: mi zad pa'i gter mdzod man ngag gi glu las /
NK106(me)001:5425: re dang dogs pa'i dug gis rnal 'byor sems myos na //
NK106(me)001:5426: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes gnas der 'ching bar 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:5428: dmigs gtad med na bcing grol las 'das te /
NK106(me)001:5430: re dogs med pa'i mthar thug pa ni rdo rje'i sems //
NK106(me)001:5431: dmyal bar song srid na yang de la sdug bsngal med //
NK106(me)001:5432: 'bras bu'i mchog la gnas kyang lhag pa rnyed min pas //
NK106(me)001:5433: bde dang sdug bsngal nyid kyis phan dang gnod spangs nas //
NK106(me)001:5434: bzang dang dman pa'i spyod pas de la 'phel 'grib med //
NK106(me)001:5435: rtogs pa'i ye shes gnyis bral 'di las ma gtogs pa'i //
NK106(me)001:5436: sangs rgyas che bar 'dod na rmongs par shes par bya //
NK106(me)001:5438: de dag gi don dpes bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:5439: de lta bu'i chos nyid spang blang las 'das pa'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK106(me)001:5441: ji ltar gzugs brnyan sna tshogs me long dang //
NK106(me)001:5442: de ltar chos rnams sna tshogs stong pa'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:5443: gzugs brnyan me long gi ngos las gzhan ma yin par ltar /
NK106(me)001:5444: chos thams cad stong pa'i ngang du shes par bya ste /
NK106(me)001:5446: me long dag cing gsal ba la //
NK106(me)001:5447: gzugs brnyan rang bzhin snang ba ltar //
NK106(me)001:5448: chos rnams thams cad ma skyes pa'i //
NK106(me)001:5449: gzugs brnyan yang dag blta bar byos //
NK106(me)001:5451: dgag sgrub dpes bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:5453: ji ltar sprin rnams sna tshogs nam mkha'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:5454: de bzhin dgag sgrub sna tshogs sems nyid dang //
NK106(me)001:5455: skad cig gis 'khrigs shing dengs pa'i sprin rnams nam mkha'i ngang las ma g.yos pa bzhin du /
NK106(me)001:5456: blo la dgag sgrub ci shar yang sems nyid kyi ngang las ma g.yos te /
NK106(me)001:5458: sprin rnams thams cad nam mkha'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:5459: sems kyi rtog pa chos nyid ngang //
NK106(me)001:5461: nyams rtogs dpes bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:5463: ji ltar chu bo sna tshogs rgya mtsho'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:5464: de bzhin nyams rtogs sna tshogs sgom pa'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:5465: chu bran rgya mtshor ro gcig pa ltar /
NK106(me)001:5466: nyams rtogs sgom par ro gcig pa ni /
NK106(me)001:5468: yon tan rin chen rgya mtsho la //
NK106(me)001:5469: sna tshogs nyams kyi chu rnams kun //
NK106(me)001:5470: 'bab cing ngang gis mi g.yo ba //
NK106(me)001:5471: sems brtan yid bzhin khyad par ro //
NK106(me)001:5475: ji ltar sgyu ma sna tshogs sprul pa'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:5476: de bzhin 'khor 'das sna tshogs chos nyid ngang //
NK106(me)001:5477: sgyu ma thams cad snang dus nas rang bzhin med pa ltar /
NK106(me)001:5478: 'khor 'das chos nyid las mi g.yo bar shes par bya ste /
NK106(me)001:5479: bzang pos zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:5480: chos kun sgyu ma'i rang bzhin du //
NK106(me)001:5481: ngo bo nyid kyis stong par bstan //
NK106(me)001:5484: 'khor ba gang yin mya ngan 'das pa gang //
NK106(me)001:5486: sems dang sems nyid bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:5488: ji ltar phyogs bcu'i nam mkha' gzhi bral ngang //
NK106(me)001:5489: de bzhin ye grol chos rnams lta ba'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:5490: ji ltar chu la chu bzhag gnyis med ngang //
NK106(me)001:5491: de bzhin sems dang sems nyid dbyer med ngang //
NK106(me)001:5492: nam mkha'i dbyings la rang bzhin tha dad pa'i med pa ltar //
NK106(me)001:5493: chos thams cad la rang bzhin gnyis su med de /
NK106(me)001:5495: nam mkha' dbye ba med pa bzhin //
NK106(me)001:5496: de bzhin chos rnams dbyer med do //
NK106(me)001:5498: chu dang chu 'dres dus gnyis su med pa ltar /
NK106(me)001:5499: sems nyid kyi ngang du sems byung gi rtog pa rang zhir thim pas gnyis su med do //
NK106(me)001:5501: ji ltar chu la chu thim ltar //
NK106(me)001:5502: sems dang sems nyid gnyis med do //
NK106(me)001:5504: rtog dang mi rtog dpes bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:5506: ji ltar sna tshogs rmi lam gnyid kyi ngang //
NK106(me)001:5507: de bzhin blang dor gnyis med spyod pa'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:5508: ji ltar mtsho dang dba' rlabs chu bo'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:5509: de bzhin rtog dang mi rtog mnyam pa'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:5510: rmi lam gnyid kyi ngang las ma g.yos pa ltar /
NK106(me)001:5511: blang dor thams cad gnyis su med pa'i ngang du ro gcig pa ni /
NK106(me)001:5513: rmi lam gnyid kyi klong na gsal //
NK106(me)001:5514: chos rnams stong pa gnyis med gsal //
NK106(me)001:5516: dba' rlabs chu'i dbyings dang bcas pa chu las gzhan ma yin pa ltar /
NK106(me)001:5517: rtog pa dang mi rtog pa mnyam pa nyid ni /
NK106(me)001:5519: ji srid sems las rnam 'phros pa //
NK106(me)001:5520: de srid mgon po'i rang bzhin te //
NK106(me)001:5521: chu dang rlabs dag gzhan yin nam //
NK106(me)001:5523: re dogs dpes bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:5525: ji ltar tshong pa don grub bde ba'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:5526: de bzhin re dogs gnyis med 'bras bu'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:5527: thams cad phyam gcig rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:5528: khyab gdal dbyings kyi chos nyid shes par bya //
NK106(me)001:5529: tshod zin nas sems re dogs med pa'i ngang du blo bde ba ltar /
NK106(me)001:5530: sangs rgyas rang sems su thag chod nas de'i ngang du blo bde ba yang /
NK106(me)001:5532: glang chen lom nas sems tshags tshud pa na //
NK106(me)001:5533: der ni 'gro 'ong bcad nas dal ba ste //
NK106(me)001:5534: 'di ltar rtogs na gang du'ang 'dri sa med //
NK106(me)001:5536: de'ang sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes blang dor
NK106(me)001:5537: med pa'i ngang 'dir thams cad rdzogs pas bya btsal
NK106(me)001:5538: mtshan ma'i 'du shes las grol bar bya ste /
NK106(me)001:5540: 'di la ma rdzogs gang yang med //
NK106(me)001:5541: gcig rdzogs gnyis rdzogs kun rdzogs pas //
NK106(me)001:5542: bya ba phun sum tshogs par bde //
NK106(me)001:5543: gcig rdzogs byang chub sems su rdzogs //
NK106(me)001:5544: gnyis rdzogs sems kyis byas par rdzogs //
NK106(me)001:5545: kun rdzogs phun sum tshogs par rdzogs //
NK106(me)001:5546: gcig la rdzogs pa'i lung 'di yis //
NK106(me)001:5547: sangs rgyas dgongs pa 'di la gnas //
NK106(me)001:5548: kun rdzogs pa yi don 'di yis //
NK106(me)001:5549: thams cad phun sum tshogs par byed //
NK106(me)001:5550: bya byed 'di la gang gnas pa //
NK106(me)001:5551: lus 'di gang zag lha mi yang //
NK106(me)001:5552: dgongs pa chos nyid sangs rgyas yin //
NK106(me)001:5553: 'di yis sems can don byas nas //
NK106(me)001:5554: rtsol sgrub mi byed bde bar gnas //
NK106(me)001:5556: spyi don gsum pa skabs kyi dge ba bsngo ba ni /
NK106(me)001:5557: da ni de dag gi dge ba sems can la bsngo ba ni /
NK106(me)001:5559: de ltar sna tshogs gnyis med ro gcig gis //
NK106(me)001:5560: 'gro kun bdag gzhan gzung 'dzin las grol te //
NK106(me)001:5561: 'di zhes dmigs pas 'khrul pa'i srid pa 'dir //
NK106(me)001:5562: dub pa'i sems nyid di ring ngal sos shig /
NK106(me)001:5563: mchog tu rmad du byung ba'i dge ba dri ma
NK106(me)001:5564: med pa nam mkha' ltar yangs shing gnyis su med
NK106(me)001:5565: pa des / 'gro ba'i khams gang rnams ring mo
NK106(me)001:5566: zhig nas gnyis su gzung ba'i 'khrul pas srid par
NK106(me)001:5567: pa des / dub pa las / bsod nams brgya'i
NK106(me)001:5568: 'od zer sa dang lha'i yul du rnam par 'phro
NK106(me)001:5569: ba sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyi me tog brtsegs
NK106(me)001:5570: pa'i skyed mos tshal du ngal sos par shog cig
NK106(me)001:5571: pa des / dub pa las / ces pa'o // lha yul sa steng nam mkha' rnam brgyan pa'i //
NK106(me)001:5572: 'od kyi rkang rten dmar ba las byung ba //
NK106(me)001:5573: 'phags pa'i 'dun sar 'gro kun legs bgrod de //
NK106(me)001:5574: rgyal mdzod 'byor pa rgya chen dang ldan shog /
NK106(me)001:5575: ri rtse nags kyi mthongs ni nyams dga' ba //
NK106(me)001:5576: sman ljongs me tog 'bab chus brgyan pa der //
NK106(me)001:5577: bdag gi tshe 'di don yod 'da' byed cing //
NK106(me)001:5578: rnam grol yon tan mchog rab 'grub par shog /
NK106(me)001:5579: zla ba'i rked ngos sprin gyis mdzes pa gang //
NK106(me)001:5580: ches dkar ku mu ta rnams rgyas byed ltar //
NK106(me)001:5581: 'od bzang zhi ba'i ri bong 'dzin zer gyis //
NK106(me)001:5582: ma lus 'gro kun nyer 'tsho'i gzhir gyur cig /
NK106(me)001:5583: rdzogs pa chen po sems nyid ngal gso las /
NK106(me)001:5584: ting nge 'dzin bsgrub pa'i yan lag thabs la mkhas pa'i le'u ste bcu gnyis pa'i 'grel pa'o ////
NK106(me)001:5585: de ltar rgyu pha rol tu phyin pa'i theg pas
NK106(me)001:5586: rgyud snod rung du byas nas 'bras bu 'od gsal
NK106(me)001:5587: rdo rje snying po'i lam smin grol nye rgyu'i spyod
NK106(me)001:5588: pa dang bcas pa mthar phyin rjes /
NK106(me)001:5589: bcu gsum pa mngon du gyur pa 'bras bu sku
NK106(me)001:5590: dang ye shes kyi le'u la spyi don bzhi ste
NK106(me)001:5591: / lam mthar phyin pas sku dang ye shes 'grub par bstan pa /
NK106(me)001:5592: sku dang ye shes bshad pa /
NK106(me)001:5593: de dag dbyings las byung zhing dbyings su thim pas mjug bsdu ba /
NK106(me)001:5594: skabs kyi dge ba bsngo ba'o //
NK106(me)001:5595: spyi don dang po lam mthar phyin pas sku dang ye shes 'grub par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:5596: de ltar gzhi dang lam gyi rim pa legs par bshad nas /
NK106(me)001:5597: da ni de dag gis grub pa 'bras bu'i don bstan par bya ste /
NK106(me)001:5599: de ltar thabs dang shes rab mthar phyin nas //
NK106(me)001:5600: sku dang ye shes 'phrin las lhun gyis grub //
NK106(me)001:5601: de ltar lam gyi yon tan rdzogs pa na khams
NK106(me)001:5602: kyi dri ma mtha' dag dang bral ba'i sangs rgyas
NK106(me)001:5603: sam byang chub ces bya ba 'thob ste /
NK106(me)001:5604: de'ang sems nyid 'od gsal ba nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor
NK106(me)001:5605: la sgrib pa'i sprin tshogs mtha' dag dengs nas sku
NK106(me)001:5606: dang ye shes 'du 'bral med cing lhun gyis grub
NK106(me)001:5607: pa'i nus pa ci yod pa mngon du thob pa
NK106(me)001:5609: rang bzhin 'od gsal zhes brjod gang yin nyi dang mkha' bzhin glo bur gyi //
NK106(me)001:5610: nyon mongs shes bya'i sprin tshogs stug pos bsgribs pa las ni bral gyur pa //
NK106(me)001:5611: dri med sangs rgyas yon tan kun ldan rtag brtan g.yung drung sangs rgyas nyid //
NK106(me)001:5612: de ni chos la mi rtog rnam 'byed ye shes dag la brten pas 'thob //
NK106(me)001:5614: de'i tshe rang gi don du chos sku dam pa
NK106(me)001:5615: dbyings gdod ma'i ngang na sku gsum 'du 'bral med
NK106(me)001:5616: pa brnyes pas sangs rgyas nyid kyi spyod yul las
NK106(me)001:5617: gzhan gyi ma yin pa rten gyi tshul du gnas
NK106(me)001:5619: thog ma dbus mtha' med cing rnam dbyer med //
NK106(me)001:5620: gnyis med gsum bral dri med rnam rtog med //
NK106(me)001:5621: chos dbyings rang bzhin gang yin de rtogs pa //
NK106(me)001:5622: mnyam par bzhag pa'i rnal 'byor pa yis mthong //
NK106(me)001:5623: gzhal med gang+g+aa'i bye ma las 'das pa //
NK106(me)001:5624: bsam med mnyam med yon tan rnams dang ldan //
NK106(me)001:5625: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dri med dbyings de ni //
NK106(me)001:5626: bag chags bcas pa'i nyes kun rnams spangs pa'o //
NK106(me)001:5628: de'i dbyings na snang ba'i chos sku dang /
NK106(me)001:5629: de las gdul bya'i ngor snang bar 'byung ba'i longs
NK106(me)001:5630: sku yang nam mkha'i zla ba 'phel 'grib med pa
NK106(me)001:5632: sprul pa'i sku 'phro ba'i 'char gzhi mdzad par /
NK106(me)001:5634: sna tshogs dam chos 'od zer snang ba'i skus //
NK106(me)001:5635: 'gro ba'i rnam grol don sgrub la brtson pa //
NK106(me)001:5636: mdzad pa yid bzhin nor bu'i rgyal bzhin te //
NK106(me)001:5637: sna tshogs dngos kyang de yi rang bzhin min //
NK106(me)001:5638: 'jig rten zhi ba'i lam la 'jug pa dang //
NK106(me)001:5639: rab tu smin dang lung ston rgyu yi gzugs //
NK106(me)001:5640: gang yin de yang 'dir ni rtag gnas te //
NK106(me)001:5641: nam mkha'i khams su gzugs kyi khams bzhin no //
NK106(me)001:5644: zhi sku dpag bsam shing ltar gsal gyur cing //
NK106(me)001:5645: yid bzhin nor bu ji bzhin rnam mi rtog /'gro
NK106(me)001:5646: grol bar du 'jig rten 'byor slad rtag /'di ni
NK106(me)001:5647: spros dang bral la snang bar 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:5649: skabs 'dir sangs rgyas kho na'i spyod yul las gdul
NK106(me)001:5650: bya la mi snang ba dbyings kyi sku gsum chos
NK106(me)001:5651: sku nyag gcig tu ro gcig pa nang dbyings phra
NK106(me)001:5652: ba'i ye shes su yod pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5653: de'i byin rlabs dang gdul bya'i smon lam las phyir
NK106(me)001:5654: gzhan snang du shar ba ye shes 'phrin las dag
NK106(me)001:5655: pa'i gzugs sku gnyis snang ba ni mkha' zla dang
NK106(me)001:5656: chu zla ltar shes par bya'o //
NK106(me)001:5658: kha cig gis ma phyed pas sku gsum gcig tu
NK106(me)001:5659: khas blangs dus dbyings kyi yon tan thams cad gdul
NK106(me)001:5660: bya la snang bar thal te /
NK106(me)001:5661: de dang ngo bo gcig pa'i gzugs sku gdul bya la snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)001:5662: 'dod na sangs rgyas khams dang la sogs pas gsal lo //
NK106(me)001:5663: des na 'di gnyis bye brag shes pa gal che'o //
NK106(me)001:5664: de ltar chos sku dang gzugs sku dam pa gnyis
NK106(me)001:5665: brnyes pa ni sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das nyid do
NK106(me)001:5666: // de la theg pa chen po pha rol tu
NK106(me)001:5667: phyin pas ni de lta bu'i sangs rgyas ni sa
NK106(me)001:5668: bcu rgyun matha'i dri ma mtha' dag spangs pa'i rjes
NK106(me)001:5669: la 'og min du sangs rgyas te longs spyod rdzogs
NK106(me)001:5670: pa'i sku byang sems sa bcu pa'i snang ba la
NK106(me)001:5671: // snang zhing / sprul pa du mas sems can
NK106(me)001:5672: gyi khams su gang la gang 'dul du ston to
NK106(me)001:5673: // snang zhing / zhes 'dod do // sngags kha cig de dang mtshungs la /
NK106(me)001:5674: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba chen po las ni de bzhin
NK106(me)001:5675: gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi
NK106(me)001:5676: 'khor lo ni sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan gyi spyod
NK106(me)001:5678: snang na sangs rgyas nyid du 'gyur la /
NK106(me)001:5679: de'i ngang las snang ba sprul pa chen po dang /
NK106(me)001:5680: sprul pa sna tshogs pas gdul bya'i don mdzad pa'o //
NK106(me)001:5681: sprul pa chen po ni sa bcu pa'i sems dpa' la snang ba'i longs sku yin la /
NK106(me)001:5682: sna tshogs pa ni mchog gi sprul pa la sogs
NK106(me)001:5683: pa tha mal pa rnams la snang nas don byed
NK106(me)001:5685: de gnyis ka'i lugs kyis gnas phun sum tshogs pa 'og min du byang chub brnyes par 'dod de /
NK106(me)001:5686: rgyan stug po bkod pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:5687: yang dag sangs rgyas byang chub tu //
NK106(me)001:5689: sangs rgyas ma gyur 'dod khams su //
NK106(me)001:5690: sangs rgyas mdzad pa mi mdzad do //
NK106(me)001:5692: zla gsang thig le'i rgyud las /
NK106(me)001:5693: 'og min gnas mchog nyams dga' bar //
NK106(me)001:5694: yang dag sangs rgyas der sangs rgyas //
NK106(me)001:5696: sangs rgyas phal po che las /
NK106(me)001:5697: 'jig rten gyi khams mi mjed la sogs pa bsam
NK106(me)001:5698: gyis mi khyab pa nang du chud pa ni gzhi
NK106(me)001:5699: dang snying po me tog gis brgyan pa zhes bya
NK106(me)001:5700: la / de lta bu bsam gyis mi khyab pa
NK106(me)001:5701: nang du chud pa ni 'jig rten gyi khams rgya
NK106(me)001:5702: mtsho zhes bya ba yin la /
NK106(me)001:5703: de ni de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par snang mdzad gang chen mtsho'i phyag gi mthil na gnas so //
NK106(me)001:5704: bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad 'khor dang bcas
NK106(me)001:5705: pa gang na bzhugs pa de ni stug po bkod
NK106(me)001:5706: pa'i zhing khams zhes bya ba longs spyod rdzogs pa
NK106(me)001:5708: de'i nang na yod pa'i dum bu thams cad ni sprul pa sku'i gnas yin no zhes bshad pas /
NK106(me)001:5710: gang du glo bur gyi dri ma mtha' dag spangs
NK106(me)001:5711: pas dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med cing sangs rgyas
NK106(me)001:5712: pa gang du brnyes pa de nyid kyi sa la
NK106(me)001:5714: phyogs 'di kho na'o zhes gcig tu chad pa med do //
NK106(me)001:5715: rmi lam yang gnyid du gang song gi gnas der 'ong ba ltar chos mtshungs so //
NK106(me)001:5716: chos kyi dbyings su bstod pa las /
NK106(me)001:5717: dbang phyug chen po'i gnas mchog dang //
NK106(me)001:5718: 'og min de nyid rnam mdzes pa //
NK106(me)001:5719: shes pa gsum pa gcig nyid du //
NK106(me)001:5723: bdag tu 'dzin pa med pa'i phyir //
NK106(me)001:5724: gnas la tha dad yod ma yin //
NK106(me)001:5725: sngon gyi rjes su 'brangs pas na //
NK106(me)001:5726: de la gdags pas tha dad 'byed //
NK106(me)001:5728: gnas der ston pa sh+aakya thub pa 'di sangs rgyas
NK106(me)001:5729: nas dus 'di tsam song zhes bsam par mi nus
NK106(me)001:5730: te / ye shes rol pa'i rgyud las /
NK106(me)001:5731: thog mtha' med pa'i dus dag tu //
NK106(me)001:5732: nga ni mngon par byang chub ste //
NK106(me)001:5734: mi mjed 'dir tshe lo brgya pa'i dus su thog
NK106(me)001:5735: mar gtsang ma'i 'og min du sangs rgyas pa ltar
NK106(me)001:5736: bstan nas / gdod dzam+bu'i gling du sangs rgyas par snang ste /
NK106(me)001:5737: rnam par snang mdzad mngon par byang chub pa'i rgyud las /
NK106(me)001:5738: 'dod pa'i khams dang gzugs med du //
NK106(me)001:5739: sangs rgyas mngon par sangs mi rgya //
NK106(me)001:5740: gzugs kyi khams kyi 'og min du //
NK106(me)001:5741: 'dod chags bral khyod der sangs rgyas //
NK106(me)001:5742: gtsang ma'i gnas dag spangs nas su //
NK106(me)001:5743: 'og min zhes bya nyams dga' bar //
NK106(me)001:5744: yang dag sangs rgyas der sangs rgyas //
NK106(me)001:5747: de yang mi mjed kyi gnas thams cad bkod pa mnyam du snang ste /
NK106(me)001:5748: nam mkha'i zla ba gcig nyid kyi rnam pa chu
NK106(me)001:5749: snod bye ba phrag brgyar dus snga phyi med par
NK106(me)001:5752: nam mkha'i mthas klas pa'i sems can gyi gnas ris
NK106(me)001:5753: so sor mdzad pa bcu gnyis la sogs pa dus
NK106(me)001:5754: mnyam pa dang / mi mnyam pa du mas 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa yin no //
NK106(me)001:5755: gdul bya'i ngor 'og min de lta bur sangs rgyas par snang ngo //
NK106(me)001:5756: bcom ldan 'das nyid kyi rang bzhin ni khams gsum
NK106(me)001:5757: las 'das pas gdul bya'i 'khrul snang gi bag chags
NK106(me)001:5758: kyi 'og min gzugs khams lta bu der bzhugs pa
NK106(me)001:5759: ma yin te bag chags thams cad dang bral ba'i
NK106(me)001:5760: phyir ro // des na rang snang dag pa'i 'og
NK106(me)001:5761: min khams gsum las 'das pa ye shes kyi gzhal
NK106(me)001:5762: yas khang bkod pa tshad med pa can du rtag
NK106(me)001:5763: phyir ro // par bzhugs te / rgyan stug po bkod pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5764: nges pa'i mdo phal la snang zhing 'byung ba ni /
NK106(me)001:5765: gzugs med 'dod dang gzugs khams dang //
NK106(me)001:5766: 'du shes med pa de bzhin te //
NK106(me)001:5767: gnas las 'das te sangs rgyas dbang //
NK106(me)001:5768: bzhugs so stug po'i dkyil 'khor na //
NK106(me)001:5770: brtan pa stug po 'dus ma byas //
NK106(me)001:5773: dri ma mtha' dag dang bral nas brnyes so //
NK106(me)001:5774: de la bral lugs ni glo bur gyi dri ma ste /
NK106(me)001:5776: med pas sangs rgyas zhes tha snyad byas te /
NK106(me)001:5777: de'ang dri ma rang bzhin pa sngar yod gsar du spangs pa'am /
NK106(me)001:5778: yon tan sngar med gsar du bsgrubs pa ni ci yang med do //
NK106(me)001:5780: snga ma phyi mar khyad med kyang //
NK106(me)001:5781: sgrib pa kun gyi dri med pa //
NK106(me)001:5782: de bzhin nyid ni sangs rgyas 'dod //
NK106(me)001:5784: des na glo bur ba mtha' dag spangs par /
NK106(me)001:5786: gang la nyon mongs shes bya'i sgrib pa'i sa bon dus ring rtag ldan pa /
NK106(me)001:5787: spong ba shin tu rgya chen rnam pa kun gyis rab tu bcom gyur cing //
NK106(me)001:5788: gnas gyur chos dkar yon tan mchog rab ldan pa thob pa sangs rgyas nyid //
NK106(me)001:5789: de ni mi rtog shin tu rab dag yul chen ye shes lam gyis 'thob //
NK106(me)001:5791: de'i tshe gnas gyur kyang nyon mongs pa dag stobs kyis yon tan snang ba tsam la brjod kyi /
NK106(me)001:5792: rgyu nyon mongs pa nyid 'bras bu yon tan du
NK106(me)001:5793: gnas gyur te ma dag pa dag par song ba
NK106(me)001:5795: sdig pa dang nyon mongs kun tu dag pa'i rgyu'am ngo bo ma yin pas mi srid do //
NK106(me)001:5796: bral bya'i dri ma bral stobs kyis de'i thad kyi
NK106(me)001:5797: yon tan snang ba la ltos te gnas gyur tsam
NK106(me)001:5798: zhig brjod na / dug lnga gnas gyur pas ye shes lnga'o //
NK106(me)001:5799: kun gzhi gnas gyur pas chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes so //
NK106(me)001:5800: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa gnas gyur pas me long lta bu'i ye shes te /
NK106(me)001:5801: sku gsum la 'jug pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:5802: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa dbyings su nub pa
NK106(me)001:5803: ni me long lta bu'i ye shes so zhes so
NK106(me)001:5804: // de bzhin du lhag ma gsum yang /
NK106(me)001:5806: yid kyi rnam par shes pa dbyings su nub pa ni mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes so //
NK106(me)001:5807: nyon mongs pa can gyi yid dbyings su nub pa ni so sor rtog pa'i ye shes so //
NK106(me)001:5808: sgo lnga'i rnam par shes pa dbyings su nub pa
NK106(me)001:5809: ni bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so zhes so
NK106(me)001:5810: // de'i tshe phyi snang ba zhing khams su gnas gyur /
NK106(me)001:5811: nang phung po lha skur gnas gyur /
NK106(me)001:5812: gsang ba tshogs brgyad ye shes su gnas gyur pas rnam pa kun tu sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK106(me)001:5813: ngo bo'i rgyu ni dang po'i khams la yon tan ye ldan du yod pa'i rigs de gnyis so //
NK106(me)001:5816: dang pos sku ni dang po ste //
NK106(me)001:5817: gnyis pa yis ni phyi ma gnyis //
NK106(me)001:5818: zhes pa la sogs pa bshad zin to //
NK106(me)001:5819: de'ang ngo bo nyid kyi sku sku gzhan gsum gyi chos nyid dri ma med pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5820: chos kyi sku stobs sogs kyi 'byung gnas dam pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5821: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku mtshan dpes gang ba dang /
NK106(me)001:5822: sprul pa'i sku sems can mtha' yas pa'i don mdzad pa ste bzhir gsungs shing /
NK106(me)001:5823: de'i yon tan yang drug cu rtsa bzhi ste /
NK106(me)001:5825: de ltar de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs bcu dang /
NK106(me)001:5827: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa bco brgyad dang /
NK106(me)001:5828: skyes bu chen po'i mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis po
NK106(me)001:5829: de dag rnam pa gcig tu mngon par bsdus te
NK106(me)001:5830: drug cu rtsa bzhi 'gyur ro zhes so //
NK106(me)001:5831: mdo kha cig las sku gsum ye shes dang bcas pa ste /
NK106(me)001:5833: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la sku gsum mnga' ste /
NK106(me)001:5835: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang /
NK106(me)001:5837: chos kyi sku ni yang dag pa'i ye shes nyid tsam du gnas pa la bya'o //
NK106(me)001:5838: sku gnyis po ni btags pa tsam mo //
NK106(me)001:5839: chos kyi sku ni yang dag pa ste sku gnyis kyi gzhi byed pa'o //
NK106(me)001:5841: chos kyi de bzhin nyid dang /
NK106(me)001:5842: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes las gud na sangs rgyas kyi chos med pa'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)001:5844: de bzhin nyid kyi ye shes la rnam par mi
NK106(me)001:5845: rtog bzhin du 'phrin las la mnga' brnyes pa gang
NK106(me)001:5847: dper na nyi zla dang chu dang me long la
NK106(me)001:5848: rtog pa med kyang gzugs brnyan 'byung ba bzhin du
NK106(me)001:5849: / de bzhin nyid kyi ye shes kyang mi rtog
NK106(me)001:5850: pa bzhin du smon lam gyi dbang gis sems can
NK106(me)001:5853: phung po lhag ma dang bcas pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'o //
NK106(me)001:5854: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ni lhag ma med pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'o //
NK106(me)001:5855: chos kyi sku ni mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'o zhes pa dang /
NK106(me)001:5857: sangs rgyas rnams kyi sku dbye ba //
NK106(me)001:5858: rang bzhin longs spyod rdzogs pa dang //
NK106(me)001:5859: gzhan ni sprul pa'i sku yin te //
NK106(me)001:5860: dang po gnyis pa'i rten yin no //
NK106(me)001:5862: sku gsum dag gis sangs rgyas kyi //
NK106(me)001:5863: sku bsdus par ni shes bya ste //
NK106(me)001:5864: sku gsum dag gis rang gzhan gyi //
NK106(me)001:5865: don 'di rten dang bcas par bstan //
NK106(me)001:5867: rgyud bla ma dang mngon rtogs rgyan las sngar smos pa ltar sku bzhir gsungs te /
NK106(me)001:5869: chos dbyings ngo bo nyid kyis ni //
NK106(me)001:5870: dag pa'i phyir na 'od gsal ba //
NK106(me)001:5871: gzhal med grangs med bsam med pa //
NK106(me)001:5872: mnyam med dag pa'i mthar thug pa'i //
NK106(me)001:5873: yon tan rnams dang yang dag par //
NK106(me)001:5874: ngo bo nyid kyi sku ldan te //
NK106(me)001:5876: 'dir ni dang po chos sku ste //
NK106(me)001:5877: phyi ma dag ni gzugs kyi sku //
NK106(me)001:5878: nam mkha' la ni gzugs gnas bzhin //
NK106(me)001:5879: dang po la ni tha ma gnas //
NK106(me)001:5881: gsang sngags kha cig las sku gsum bde ba chen po dang bzhir 'dod de /
NK106(me)001:5883: sku gsum yongs su shes pa ni //
NK106(me)001:5884: bde ba chen po'i 'khor lor brjod //
NK106(me)001:5887: 'jam dpal sgyu 'phrul dra ba las ni sku lngar bshad de 'di skad du /
NK106(me)001:5888: sangs rgyas sku lnga'i bdag nyid can //
NK106(me)001:5889: khyab bdag ye shes lnga yi bdag /
NK106(me)001:5891: de thams cad kyang rigs dang yon tan gyi dbye bsdu tsam las /
NK106(me)001:5892: don la tha dad pa med de sangs rgyas kyi
NK106(me)001:5893: sa'i chos kyi bsdu tshul so so ba tsam las
NK106(me)001:5894: ngo bo gcig yin pa'i phyir ro zhes bshad par
NK106(me)001:5895: bya'o // spyi don gnyis pa sku dang ye shes bshad pa la /
NK106(me)001:5897: dbyings dang ye shes 'du 'bral med par nang gsal du bzhugs tshul /
NK106(me)001:5898: dbye ba rgyas par bshad pa gsum las /
NK106(me)001:5899: zhi ba brnyes pa'i tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:5900: da ni sgyu 'phrul dra ba chen po'i rnam par gzhag pa nyid brjod de /
NK106(me)001:5901: zhi ba brnyes pa'i tshul dang /
NK106(me)001:5902: sku'i rab tu dbye ba las /
NK106(me)001:5903: re zhig dang po bshad pa ni /
NK106(me)001:5904: lam gyi ye shes dag pa mthar thug pa de'i
NK106(me)001:5905: tshe spang bya khams gsum pa'i rgyud kyis bsdus pa'i
NK106(me)001:5906: gzung ba dang 'dzin pa'i rnam pa can rtog pa
NK106(me)001:5907: dang dpyod pa 'i rang bzhin gyi /
NK106(me)001:5908: sems dang sems byung kun gzhir bcas pa kun //
NK106(me)001:5909: chos kyi dbyings su 'jug pa rab zhi'i tshe //
NK106(me)001:5910: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med ro gcig gyur //
NK106(me)001:5911: de tshe dag pa gnyis ldan spros kun zhi //
NK106(me)001:5912: g.yo byed gzung 'dzin gyi rnam pas bsdus pa'i sems sems byung ni khams gsum pa'i sa ba ste /
NK106(me)001:5913: ye shes snying po'i bden gnyis las /
NK106(me)001:5914: sems dang sems byung khams gsum pa //
NK106(me)001:5915: sgro btags rnam pa can rtog yin //
NK106(me)001:5916: zhes pa lta bu rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad
NK106(me)001:5917: kun gzhi dang bcas pa sems nyid 'od gsal ba
NK106(me)001:5918: chos kyi dbyings rang bzhin gyis dag pa'i ngang du
NK106(me)001:5919: zhi zhing thim pa de'i tshe /
NK106(me)001:5920: dbyings gdod ma'i gzhi dang ye shes thim bya'i rig
NK106(me)001:5921: pa gnyis su med par 'dres te ro gcig tu
NK106(me)001:5922: gyur pa ni ye nas dri ma med pa rang
NK106(me)001:5924: glo bur gyi dri ma cha dang bcas pa dag pa nyis ldan gyi chos sku dam pa ste /
NK106(me)001:5925: spring yig bdud rtsi'i thigs pa las /
NK106(me)001:5926: ji ltar chu la chu bzhag dang //
NK106(me)001:5927: mar la mar ni rjes zhugs ltar //
NK106(me)001:5928: shes bya spros bral de nyid dang //
NK106(me)001:5929: dbyer med ye shes rnam 'dres pa //
NK106(me)001:5930: de nyid sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK106(me)001:5931: rang bzhin chos sku zhes byar brjod //
NK106(me)001:5933: de'i dus su sems byung gi 'jug pa rgyun chad nas ye shes chen por ro gcig ste /
NK106(me)001:5935: shes bya'i bud shing skam po ma lus pa //
NK106(me)001:5936: bsregs pas zhi de rgyal rnams chos sku ste //
NK106(me)001:5937: de tshe skye ba med cing 'gag pa med //
NK106(me)001:5938: sems 'gag pa de sku yis mngon sum mdzad //
NK106(me)001:5940: dbyings dang ye shes 'du 'bral med par nang gsal du bzhugs tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:5941: de'i tshe chos sku spros pa'i mtha' bral zhi ba chen po mngon du brnyes pas /
NK106(me)001:5942: shin tu skye med 'od gsal snying po'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:5943: gnam gang zla ba dbyings su nub pa ltar //
NK106(me)001:5944: phra ba'i ye shes mkha' dbyings pad+mora 'khyil //
NK106(me)001:5945: gang du'ang mi rtog zhi ba brnyes pa'i tshe //
NK106(me)001:5946: dag pa mthar thug pa ste /
NK106(me)001:5947: 'od gsal gzhi'i ngang du phyin pas /
NK106(me)001:5948: dbyings nam mkha'i ngang du ye shes gnam gang gi
NK106(me)001:5949: zla ba nang gsal thams cad mkhyen pa'i cha yon
NK106(me)001:5950: tan gyi rten nam 'char gzhir gnas pa las /
NK106(me)001:5951: phyir snang longs sku'am gdul bya'i snang ngor snang ba ni ye yod pa ma yin te /
NK106(me)001:5952: mtha' bzhi'i dri ma las 'das pa chos sku nyag gcig gi dus yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)001:5953: gnam gang na nam mkha' la zla ba yod kyang
NK106(me)001:5954: gzhan gyis bltar rung ba'i mngon gsal du med pa
NK106(me)001:5955: bzhin du chos sku'i ye shes mkha' dbyings su 'khyil
NK106(me)001:5956: ba shin tu phra zhing zab pa'ang de bzhin te
NK106(me)001:5958: dbyings su 'khyil bas mthong du med //
NK106(me)001:5959: med pa min te phra ba'i phyir //
NK106(me)001:5960: chos kyi sngon rol zla ba bzhin //
NK106(me)001:5961: zab pa zhi ba ches phra ba'o //
NK106(me)001:5963: dbye ba rgyas par bshad pa la mi 'gyur rdo rje'i /
NK106(me)001:5967: cir yang sprul pa'i sku dang lnga las /
NK106(me)001:5969: da ni dbye ba rgyas par bshad pa la lnga las /
NK106(me)001:5970: dang po mi 'gyur rdo rje'i sku ni /
NK106(me)001:5971: bsam brjod spros pa'i yul las 'das pa'i /
NK106(me)001:5972: chos nyid mi dmigs dus gsum 'pho 'gyur med //
NK106(me)001:5973: rang bzhin gdod nas dag pa'i cha de la //
NK106(me)001:5974: mi 'gyur rdo rje'i sku zhes brjod pa ste //
NK106(me)001:5975: gzhi dbyings zad pa'i chos nyid mthar thug pa'o //
NK106(me)001:5976: de'ang gzhi gdod ma'i chos dbyings 'od gsal ba sangs
NK106(me)001:5977: rgyas kyi bgrod pa mthar thug de'i chos nyid 'pho
NK106(me)001:5978: 'gyur med pa'i cha de la mi 'gyur rdo rje'i
NK106(me)001:5981: dbyings kyi dag pa rdo rje'i sku //
NK106(me)001:5984: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku ni /
NK106(me)001:5985: sku gnyis pa mngon par byang chub pa ni spangs rtogs mthar thug gi ngo bo ste /
NK106(me)001:5987: rang bzhin glo bur sgrib gnyis rnam dag cing //
NK106(me)001:5988: thams cad mkhyen pa'i chos tshul rgya mtsho brnyes //
NK106(me)001:5989: spangs dang rtogs pa'i yon tan mthar phyin pas //
NK106(me)001:5990: stobs sogs pha rol phyin pa'i chas gzhal na //
NK106(me)001:5991: mngon par byang chub sku zhes btags pa ste //
NK106(me)001:5992: ma 'dres yon tan 'char gzhi mthar thug pa'o //
NK106(me)001:5993: sems nyid 'od gsal ba mthar thug gi tshe dag
NK106(me)001:5994: pa nyis ldan gyi cha la rtogs pa'i yon tan
NK106(me)001:5998: chos sum cu rtsa bdun la sogs pa sngar smos
NK106(me)001:5999: pa'i mkhyen rab dang brtse ba'i nus pa yod pa'i
NK106(me)001:6000: cha nas mngon par rdzogs par byang chub pa'i sku
NK106(me)001:6001: zhes bya ste ma 'dres pa'i yon tan thams cad
NK106(me)001:6004: dri ma bral phyir byang ba ste //
NK106(me)001:6005: yon tan rgyas pa chub pa nyid //
NK106(me)001:6007: mngon par byang chub skur brjod pa'o //
NK106(me)001:6010: ma rig gnyid las sangs phyir dang //
NK106(me)001:6011: shes bya la yang blo rgyas phyir //
NK106(me)001:6015: sangs rgyas nyid ni dbyer med pa //
NK106(me)001:6016: dag pa'i chos kyis rab phye ba //
NK106(me)001:6017: nyi mkha' bzhin te ye shes dang //
NK106(me)001:6018: spangs pa gnyis kyi mtshan nyid do //
NK106(me)001:6019: 'od gsal byas min dbyer med par //
NK106(me)001:6021: rdul las 'das pa'i sangs rgyas kyi //
NK106(me)001:6022: chos rnams kun dang ldan pa nyid //
NK106(me)001:6023: rang bzhin gyis ni ma grub dang //
NK106(me)001:6024: khyab dang glo bur ba nyid kyis //
NK106(me)001:6025: nyon mongs shes bya'i sgrib pa ni //
NK106(me)001:6026: sprin dang 'dra bar brjod pa yin //
NK106(me)001:6027: sgrib pa gnyis dang bral ba yi //
NK106(me)001:6028: rgyu ni ye shes gnyis yin te //
NK106(me)001:6029: mi rtog pa dang de yi ni //
NK106(me)001:6030: rjes thob de ni ye shes 'dod //
NK106(me)001:6032: chos kyi sku la bzhi las /
NK106(me)001:6034: sku gsum pa zhi ba chos kyi sku ni dbyings
NK106(me)001:6035: mtha' las 'das pa'i ngang na shin tu phra ba'i
NK106(me)001:6036: ye shes sku dang ye shes kyi snying po zla
NK106(me)001:6037: ba mkha' dbyings su nub pa'i cha tsam du gnas
NK106(me)001:6038: pa ni / shes bya'i yul la de blo mi 'jug cing //
NK106(me)001:6039: shes byed blo la 'dzin pa mi dmigs kyang //
NK106(me)001:6040: nang gsal mkha' dbyings nub pa'i zla ba ltar //
NK106(me)001:6041: thim la ma rmugs phra ba'i ye shes mchog /
NK106(me)001:6042: thams cad mkhyen chas 'char gzhi ngo bo'i tshul //
NK106(me)001:6043: de las gzugs sku rnam mkhyen mched 'gyur zhing //
NK106(me)001:6044: gzhan la snang mdzad yon tan gter yin phyir //
NK106(me)001:6045: shin tu ches phra'i ye shes rab zhi'i chas //
NK106(me)001:6046: zhi ba chos kyi sku zhes rab tu brjod //
NK106(me)001:6047: dbyings sems nyid nam mkha'i ngang du ye shes ro
NK106(me)001:6048: gcig tu 'dres pa gnam gang lta bu'i tshe na
NK106(me)001:6049: / spros pa'i tshogs rnams zhi la thams cad mkhyen
NK106(me)001:6050: cha ma 'gags pas thim la ma rmugs pa zhes
NK106(me)001:6051: / bya ste / nang gsal gyi ye shes mnyam gzhag gi cha la /
NK106(me)001:6052: phyir gsal gyi ye shes mched pa'i snying po byed pa ste /
NK106(me)001:6053: yul dang yul can gnyis su 'dzin pa med kyang /
NK106(me)001:6054: rtog med kyi ye shes khyad par can ni zhi ba chos kyi sku zhes brjod de /
NK106(me)001:6056: ches phra'i ye shes nang du gsal //
NK106(me)001:6057: dmigs med 'char gzhi chos kyi sku //
NK106(me)001:6060: dri med rnam par rtog med dang //
NK106(me)001:6061: rnal 'byor rnams kyi yul yin phyir //
NK106(me)001:6062: chos dbyings ngo bo nyid kyis ni //
NK106(me)001:6063: dag pa'i phyir na 'od gsal ba //
NK106(me)001:6065: de'ang stong rkyang la chos skur mi 'dod de rig pa'i ye shes ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)001:6066: chos nyid la chos skur 'dod pa ltar na rdo rje'i sku ste bshad zin to //
NK106(me)001:6067: yul la mi 'jug cing mu bzhi las 'das pa ni /
NK106(me)001:6069: 'di dag phyi rol yul la mi 'jug cing //
NK106(me)001:6070: chad pa ma yin shin tu phra ba'i phyir //
NK106(me)001:6071: rtag dang chad sogs mu bzhi'i mtha' las 'das //
NK106(me)001:6072: smra bsam brjod med pha rol phyin pa'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:6073: stong pa'i rang bzhin dmigs pa rab zhi bas //
NK106(me)001:6074: rgyal ba rnams las gzhan gyi spyod yul min //
NK106(me)001:6076: de'ang dbyings nang gsal du gnas pa'i sku 'di gsum
NK106(me)001:6077: ni phyir gsal du 'char ba'i rten yin pa nyid
NK106(me)001:6078: dang / rtag pa ma yin te dmigs bsam gyi yul du med pa'i phyir dang /
NK106(me)001:6079: chad pa ma yin te so so rang gi rig pa'i ye shes yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK106(me)001:6080: gnyis ka dang gnyis ka ma yin pa'i mu ma
NK106(me)001:6081: yin te rtag chad ma grub pas de'i mu khegs
NK106(me)001:6082: pa'i phyir ro // de'ang 'char gzhi byed pas na rgyal sras sar gnas rnams dang /
NK106(me)001:6083: sems can gyi tshogs la gzugs sku mig la snang ba dang /
NK106(me)001:6084: rna bar chos gsung thos pa dang /
NK106(me)001:6085: 'phags pa'i tshul khrims kyi dri snom pa dang /
NK106(me)001:6086: chos kyi ro myong ba dang /
NK106(me)001:6087: ting nge 'dzin bde ba'i reg snang ba dang /
NK106(me)001:6088: rtog dpyod kyi shes rab kyis chos la 'jal ba
NK106(me)001:6089: rnams 'byung ba'i rgyu byed pa yang nang gsal gyi
NK106(me)001:6090: ye shes zla ba dbyings su nub pa lta bu'i
NK106(me)001:6091: nam mkha' bzhin du gnas pa las byung bas sangs
NK106(me)001:6092: rgyas las gzhan gyi spyod yul ma yin te /
NK106(me)001:6094: zag pa med khyab 'jigs med chos can te //
NK106(me)001:6095: brtan zhi rtag pa 'pho med gnas yin no //
NK106(me)001:6096: de bzhin gshegs pa mkha' bzhin dam pa yis //
NK106(me)001:6097: dbang po drug don nyams su myong ba'i rgyu //
NK106(me)001:6098: 'byung med gzugs don blta dang gtam bzang ni //
NK106(me)001:6099: gtsang ma mnyan dang bde gshegs tshul khrims kyi //
NK106(me)001:6100: dri gtsang snom dang 'phags chen dam chos ro //
NK106(me)001:6101: myong dang ting 'dzin reg bde nyams myong dang //
NK106(me)001:6102: rang gi ngo bo nyid kyis zab pa'i tshul //
NK106(me)001:6103: rtogs pa'i rgyur gyur zhib mor bsam pa na //
NK106(me)001:6104: don dam bde mdzad de bzhin gshegs pa ni //
NK106(me)001:6105: nam mkha' bzhin du rgyu mtshan rnams dang bral //
NK106(me)001:6107: rang gzhan don rten de la ni //
NK106(me)001:6108: bsam mi khyab sogs yon tan ldan //
NK106(me)001:6109: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes yul //
NK106(me)001:6110: sangs rgyas shes gsum yul min phyir //
NK106(me)001:6111: ye shes lus can rnams kyis ni //
NK106(me)001:6112: bsam mi khyab par rtogs par bya //
NK106(me)001:6113: phra phyir thos pa'i yul min te //
NK106(me)001:6114: don dam yin phyir bsam pa'i min //
NK106(me)001:6116: chos kyi dbyings su zhi bar bzhugs tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:6117: de lta bu'i ye shes mnga' ba'i cha la mnga'
NK106(me)001:6118: dbang rdzogs pa'i ston pa kun tu bzang po zhes
NK106(me)001:6120: chos dbyings pho brang shin tu skye med na //
NK106(me)001:6121: dus gsum rgyal ba thams cad rtag bzhugs kyang //
NK106(me)001:6122: gcig gis gcig mi gzigs te chos nyid phyir //
NK106(me)001:6123: rang bzhin zab zhir bzhugs zhes gsungs pa yin //
NK106(me)001:6124: de nyid ngang du rgyal rnams dgongs klong gcig /
NK106(me)001:6125: bum mkha' snga phyi'i nam mkha' gcig pa bzhin //
NK106(me)001:6126: de ltar nang gsal gyi dus na chos nyid kyi
NK106(me)001:6127: zhing na ston pa kun du bzang po chos kyi
NK106(me)001:6128: dbyings spros pa dang bral ba'i gzhal med khang par
NK106(me)001:6129: dus gsum mam bzhi'i sangs rgyas thams cad dang dgongs
NK106(me)001:6130: pa snga phyi med par gcig tu bzhugs pa /
NK106(me)001:6131: bum pa snga phyi'i nam mkha' 'dres pa bzhin ye
NK106(me)001:6132: nas dbyer med pa nyid dus der ro gcig tu
NK106(me)001:6133: gyur nas chos nyid dmigs med du bzhugs pas /
NK106(me)001:6134: sangs rgyas rnams kyang gcig gis gcig gi chos nyid
