NK106(me)001:6135: de nyid mi gzigs te gzigs bya gzigs byed kyi
NK106(me)001:6136: yul las 'das pa rtag tu lhun gyis grub par
NK106(me)001:6139: gcig dang du ma bral ba yi //
NK106(me)001:6140: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK106(me)001:6141: sangs rgyas kyis kyang mi gzigs te //
NK106(me)001:6142: rang byung ye shes gnas med snang //
NK106(me)001:6144: chos sku ye shes kyi tshogs su bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:6146: 'di ni chos nyid stong pa shes rab dang //
NK106(me)001:6147: ye shes tshogs dang rdzogs rim mthar thug pa'o //
NK106(me)001:6148: de'ang ye shes kyi tshogs mthar thug pa shes rab
NK106(me)001:6149: rdzogs pa'i rim pa stong pa nyid bsgoms pas sems
NK106(me)001:6150: nyid kyi sgrib pa bsal ba'i tshe nang gsal chos
NK106(me)001:6151: sku mtha' dbus med pa'i dbyings rdzogs par mngon du
NK106(me)001:6154: chos kyi sku ni mdor bsdu na //
NK106(me)001:6155: rgyal po ye shes tshogs las 'khrungs //
NK106(me)001:6157: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la mdor bstan dang rgyas bshad gnyis las /
NK106(me)001:6159: da ni sku bzhi pa lhun grub longs spyod rdzogs
NK106(me)001:6160: pa'i sku bstan pa ni nang gsal gyi dbyings nam
NK106(me)001:6161: mkha' lta bu / de nyid ngang las rang snang longs spyod rdzogs //
NK106(me)001:6162: gnas dus ston pa chos 'khor phun tshogs las //
NK106(me)001:6163: dbyings nang gsal chos nyid kyi ngang las phyir gsal
NK106(me)001:6164: du rang snang ba'i longs sku nges pa lnga ldan
NK106(me)001:6165: snang ba ni rgyal tshab kyi ston pa rigs lnga
NK106(me)001:6166: ste stong gzugs ltar sangs rgyas nyid kyi snang ba
NK106(me)001:6167: las gzhan dang thun mong ma yin pa'o //
NK106(me)001:6168: zhing 'di'i gzhal yas khang pa la sogs pa ni rang snang gzhi'i 'od gsal las grub kyi /
NK106(me)001:6169: gshed na rang mtshan pa yod pa ni ma yin te /
NK106(me)001:6171: lhun rdzogs rig pa rang snang ba'i //
NK106(me)001:6172: zhing dang gzhal yas gdan khri rgyan //
NK106(me)001:6173: 'od zer du mar snang ba ste //
NK106(me)001:6175: rgyas par bshad pa la gnas dus ston pa chos
NK106(me)001:6176: 'khor snang ba mjug bsdu ba dang sa bcu pas
NK106(me)001:6177: kyang mi mthong zhing sangs rgyas kho na'i spyod yul
NK106(me)001:6179: gnas phun sum tshogs pa'ang gsum ste /
NK106(me)001:6182: gnas ni 'od gsal stug po bkod pa'i zhing //
NK106(me)001:6183: lnga ldan 'od kyis lhun stug gsal zhing 'tsher //
NK106(me)001:6184: 'ja' tshon gdangs gsal nam mkha' gang ba bzhin //
NK106(me)001:6185: steng 'og phyogs mtshams nam mkha'i dbyings khyab par //
NK106(me)001:6186: gzhal med khang mdzes sgo bzhi rta babs ldan //
NK106(me)001:6187: rtsig pa lnga dang pha gu dra phyed dang //
NK106(me)001:6188: mda' yab pu shu gtsang khang phyur bus mdzes //
NK106(me)001:6189: rang snang 'od gsal stug po bkod pa rnam dag bde ba'i zhing ni /
NK106(me)001:6190: snying ga'i ye shes kyi 'od lnga rang gsal ba'i gzhi mthar thug pa'i tshe snang ba ste /
NK106(me)001:6191: steng 'og phyogs mtshams kyi nam mkha' thams cad 'od
NK106(me)001:6192: khyim bkod legs pa'i ra ba dang gur gyi snang
NK106(me)001:6193: ba kha dog phyed pas gsal ba dang 'od lnga
NK106(me)001:6194: bkrag tu 'tsher ba me long gi ngos la nyi
NK106(me)001:6195: ma shar ba lta bu'i dbus na /
NK106(me)001:6196: ye shes rin po che'i gzhal med khang 'og gzhi
NK106(me)001:6197: ye shes kyi 'khor lo'i steng na nam mkha'i dbyings
NK106(me)001:6198: khyab par gru bzhi lham par snang ba'i rtse mo
NK106(me)001:6199: bum pa zlum po gatsangakhanga phyur bu'i ya phibs can
NK106(me)001:6200: rin po che 'bar ba'i tog gis brgyan pa'i rdo
NK106(me)001:6202: rtsig pa lnga'i steng na rin po che'i pha gu ser po bsgrigs shing /
NK106(me)001:6203: mda' yab phyir 'phyang gi kha bad kyi gdung sna
NK106(me)001:6204: las nor bu dang mu tig gi dra ba dra
NK106(me)001:6205: phyed nyi zla'i 'phyong dang bcas pa phyir 'phyang ba
NK106(me)001:6206: / mda' yab kyi steng na pu shu mchod rten brtsegs dkar pos mdzes par byas pa /
NK106(me)001:6207: sgo bzhi sgo khyud dang bcas pa phyogs bzhir snang ba'i glo 'bur bzhis brgyan pa /
NK106(me)001:6208: rta babs bang rim bzhi snam phran dang bcas pa 'od lnga'i ra bas mdzes pa ste /
NK106(me)001:6210: 'og min gyi gnas mtha' dang dbus med pa na /
NK106(me)001:6211: gzhi tshad med pa'i ye shes kyi 'khor lo gsal ba la /
NK106(me)001:6212: ye shes rin po che 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK106(me)001:6213: rgya phyogs bcur yongs su ma chad pa /
NK106(me)001:6214: yon tan dpag tu med par rgyas pa'i phyir gru bzhir gyur pa /
NK106(me)001:6215: lhag pa'i ye shes rin po che'i glo 'bur gyis mdzes pa /
NK106(me)001:6216: rtse mo phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams cad dang /
NK106(me)001:6217: so so ma yin ngo bo gcig pa'i ye shes kun du 'khyil ba zhes bya'o //
NK106(me)001:6219: gzhal yas khang de'i rgyan yang /
NK106(me)001:6220: rin po che dang dar gyi /
NK106(me)001:6221: 'phan gdugs rnga yab dril bu'i phreng ba dang //
NK106(me)001:6222: bla re rgyal mtshan la sogs nam mkha' gang //
NK106(me)001:6223: 'dod yon lha mo mchod pa'i sprin 'phro zhing //
NK106(me)001:6224: 'od zer 'khyil bas phyi nang kun tu khyab //
NK106(me)001:6225: dbus dang phyogs bzhi so so'i kha dog la //
NK106(me)001:6226: mthun pa'i rgyan dang kha dog rnam par bkra //
NK106(me)001:6227: che chung ma nges gang bltas de ltar snang //
NK106(me)001:6228: grangs ni tshad med nam mkha'i dbyings kun khyab //
NK106(me)001:6229: ji ltar til gyi gang bu phye ba bzhin //
NK106(me)001:6230: gzhal yas khang pa brgyan pa'i dar zab rin po che'i 'phan dang /
NK106(me)001:6233: rgyal mtshan la sogs pas nam mkha' gang bar brgyan zhing /
NK106(me)001:6234: mchod pa'i lha mos 'dod yon gyi sprin 'khrigs pas phyogs bcu gang bar rang byung ba /
NK106(me)001:6235: gzhal yas khang pa'i dbus mthing ga la sogs pa ye shes kyi phyogs tshon gsal zhing /
NK106(me)001:6236: grangs mang ba til gyi gang bu kha bye ba
NK106(me)001:6237: tsam du nam mkha'i mthas gar khyab thams cad du
NK106(me)001:6238: khyab cing / tshad 'di tsam zhes ma nges pas
NK106(me)001:6239: gang bltas pa de tsam du snang yang mtha' mi
NK106(me)001:6240: khyab cing / mngon la / 'od zer 'khyil bas
NK106(me)001:6241: mig 'phrul ltar snang la rang bzhin med pa ste
NK106(me)001:6242: khyab cing / mngon la / / gsang snying las /
NK106(me)001:6243: ye shes rin po che sna tshogs kyi phreng ba dang /
NK106(me)001:6250: reg bya sna tshogs kyis phyogs bcur 'khrigs par rang byung la /
NK106(me)001:6251: mi sgrib par gsal ba'i rgyan bsam gyis mi khyab pas bklubs pa zhes so //
NK106(me)001:6254: kun gyi nang na seng ge glang chen rta //
NK106(me)001:6255: rma bya shang shang nyi zla pad+mas spras //
NK106(me)001:6256: yon tan gyi brda don du ma mtshon pa'i phyir gdan khri de dag tu snang ba yang /
NK106(me)001:6258: mi 'jigs pa seng ge'i khri dang /
NK106(me)001:6259: stobs glang po che'i khri dang /
NK106(me)001:6262: thogs pa med pa nam mkha' lding gi khri dang /
NK106(me)001:6263: rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK106(me)001:6264: gos pa med pa pad+ma rin po che'i gdan la zhes so //
NK106(me)001:6265: dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK106(me)001:6267: dus ni ma nges gzhi rdzogs 'pho 'gyur med //
NK106(me)001:6268: dus gsum dus med kun tu bzang po'i dus //
NK106(me)001:6269: thams cad mnyam rdzogs chos nyid gdal ba che //
NK106(me)001:6270: rang bzhin gdod nas dag pa'i ngang nyid do //
NK106(me)001:6271: dus phun sum tshogs pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa
NK106(me)001:6272: chos nyid spros pa dang bral ba dus gsum 'pho
NK106(me)001:6273: 'gyur med pa kun tu bzang po'i dus rang bzhin
NK106(me)001:6274: rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang ste /
NK106(me)001:6276: dus gsum dus med rtogs par gnas //
NK106(me)001:6278: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa rang bzhin dbyings sku dang rig pa gdangs kyi sku ni /
NK106(me)001:6280: ston pa mtshan rdzogs dpe byad 'bar ba'i sku //
NK106(me)001:6281: rnam snang mi bskyod rin 'byung 'od dpag med //
NK106(me)001:6282: don grub lnga po lnga lngas bskor ba la //
NK106(me)001:6283: nam mkha' dbyings phyug rdo rje m+aa ma k+ai //
NK106(me)001:6284: sangs rgyas spyan dang gos dkar dam tshig sgrol //
NK106(me)001:6285: yab yum mnyam sbyor so so'i rgyan rnams rdzogs //
NK106(me)001:6286: mthing ga dkar ser dmar ljang 'od zer 'phro //
NK106(me)001:6287: 'og gzhi zhi ba steng gzhi khro bo'i tshul //
NK106(me)001:6289: he ru ka dpal lnga lngas bskor ba yang //
NK106(me)001:6290: kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai lnga dang mnyam par sbyor //
NK106(me)001:6291: de sogs rnam pa brjod kyis mi lang ngo //
NK106(me)001:6292: zhi ba'i sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi gtso
NK106(me)001:6293: bo rigs lnga yab yum 'khril sbyor du bzhugs pa
NK106(me)001:6294: yang tshul dgus 'og gzhi la bzhugs te /
NK106(me)001:6296: de lta'i sku mchog re re la //
NK106(me)001:6297: tshul dgu dag dang ldan pa ste //
NK106(me)001:6298: mnyen dang lcug dang 'khril bag dang //
NK106(me)001:6299: ldem bag chags dang gzhon tshul can //
NK106(me)001:6300: gsal dang 'tsher dang lhun sdug dang //
NK106(me)001:6301: gzi byin 'bar bar rab tu gnas //
NK106(me)001:6303: de'ang mtshan dang dpe byad 'bar bar bzhugs so //
NK106(me)001:6304: steng gzhi la khro bo rigs lnga yang tshul dgus bzhugs so //
NK106(me)001:6307: sgeg pa dpa' ba mi sdug pa //
NK106(me)001:6308: dgod dang drag shul 'jigs su rung //
NK106(me)001:6309: snying rje rngam dang zhi ba ste //
NK106(me)001:6310: gar dgu'i tshul gyis bsgyings pa'o //
NK106(me)001:6314: dur khrod chen po'i gnas chen du //
NK106(me)001:6316: keng rus ri rab 'bar ba'i steng //
NK106(me)001:6317: me 'bar bsregs pa'i klong dkyil na //
NK106(me)001:6318: dur khrod 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK106(me)001:6319: tshad dang rgya yongs ma chad pa //
NK106(me)001:6320: phyi nang med par gsal ba'i 'od //
NK106(me)001:6322: gru chad 'bar ba bzhis brgyan zhing //
NK106(me)001:6323: gru bzhi sgo khyud 'bar bas mdzes //
NK106(me)001:6324: bar khyams gnyis ni 'bar bar gsal //
NK106(me)001:6325: nyi zla sbrul dang thod pas brgyan //
NK106(me)001:6326: khyu mchog dang ni ma he gzig /
NK106(me)001:6327: stag dang gtum po dom dag gi //
NK106(me)001:6328: sder mos dregs pa brgya byin dang //
NK106(me)001:6329: tshangs pa dbang phyug bzung ba yi //
NK106(me)001:6330: gdan chen rnams kyang gsal ba'o //
NK106(me)001:6332: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK106(me)001:6334: stag dang gtum po dom dag ni //
NK106(me)001:6335: zung steng brgya byin tshangs pa yi //
NK106(me)001:6336: gdan chen rnams kyang gsal ba'o //
NK106(me)001:6337: zhes 'byung ba ni shin tu dag par mngon no //
NK106(me)001:6338: zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor ni nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam
NK106(me)001:6339: pa kun du khyab pas bsam gyis mi khyab brjod
NK106(me)001:6340: las 'das pa'o // de la mtshan dpe'i don ni longs sku'i ngo bo yin pas gang zhe na /
NK106(me)001:6341: dang po mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis ni /
NK106(me)001:6343: legs gnas 'khor los mtshan pa dang //
NK106(me)001:6344: yangs dang zhabs long mi mngon dang //
NK106(me)001:6345: sor mo ring dang phyag zhabs ni //
NK106(me)001:6346: dra ba yis ni 'brel ba dang //
NK106(me)001:6347: pags 'jam gzhon sha can legs nyid //
NK106(me)001:6348: sku ni bdun dag mtho ba dang //
NK106(me)001:6349: byin pa e na ya 'dra'i gsang //
NK106(me)001:6350: glang po bzhin du sbubs su nub //
NK106(me)001:6351: ro stod seng ge'i dang 'dra dang //
NK106(me)001:6352: thal gong bar med rgyas pa dang //
NK106(me)001:6353: dpung mgo legs zlum phyag 'jam zhing //
NK106(me)001:6354: zlum zhing mtho dman med pa dang //
NK106(me)001:6355: phyag ring yongs su dag pa'i sku //
NK106(me)001:6357: mgrin pa dri med dung 'dra dang //
NK106(me)001:6359: tshems ni bzhi bcu mnyam pa dang //
NK106(me)001:6360: rab dkar tshems thags bzang ba dang //
NK106(me)001:6361: rnam dag tshems mnyam nyid dang ni //
NK106(me)001:6362: mche ba rab mchog dkar ba nyid //
NK106(me)001:6363: ljags ring mtha' med bsam med pa //
NK106(me)001:6364: ro bro ba yi mchog nyid dang //
NK106(me)001:6365: rang byung ka la ping+ka yi //
NK106(me)001:6366: sgra dang tshangs pa'i dbyangs nyid dang //
NK106(me)001:6367: spyan bzang ut+pala khyu mchog rdzi 'dra dang //
NK106(me)001:6368: zhal mdzes dri med mdzod spu dkar ldan pa //
NK106(me)001:6369: gtsug tor dbur ldan dag cing srab pa dang //
NK106(me)001:6370: pags pa gser gyi mdog 'dra sems can mchog /
NK106(me)001:6371: ba spu legs phra 'jam zhing re re nas //
NK106(me)001:6372: sku yi gyen du g.yas phyogs 'khyil ba dang //
NK106(me)001:6373: dbu skra dri med rin chen mthon mthing bzhin //
NK106(me)001:6374: rgya gro rdzogs pa'i ljon shing dkyil 'khor 'dra //
NK106(me)001:6375: kun du bzang po dpe med drang srong che //
NK106(me)001:6376: sred med bu yi stobs mnga' mkhregs pa'i sku //
NK106(me)001:6377: bsam mi khyab 'bar sum cu rtsa gnyis so //
NK106(me)001:6378: 'di dag ston pas mi dbang mtshan du gsungs //
NK106(me)001:6380: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu ni /
NK106(me)001:6382: thub pa'i sen mo zangs mdog dang //
NK106(me)001:6383: mdog snum mtho dang sor mo rnams //
NK106(me)001:6384: zlum rgyas byin gyis phra ba dang //
NK106(me)001:6385: rtsa mi mngon dang mdud pa med //
NK106(me)001:6386: long bu mi mngon zhabs mnyam dang //
NK106(me)001:6387: seng ge glang chen bya dang ni //
NK106(me)001:6388: khyu mchog stabs gshegs g.yas phyogs dang //
NK106(me)001:6389: mdzes gshegs drang dang 'khril bag chags //
NK106(me)001:6391: gtsang dang 'jam dang dag pa'i sku //
NK106(me)001:6392: mtshan ni yongs su rdzogs pa dang //
NK106(me)001:6393: sku yi kho lag yangs shing bzang //
NK106(me)001:6394: gom snyoms pa dang spyan gnyis ni //
NK106(me)001:6395: dag dang gzhon sha can nyid dang //
NK106(me)001:6396: sku zhum med dang rgyas pa dang //
NK106(me)001:6397: shin tu grims pa'i sku nyid dang //
NK106(me)001:6398: yan lag shin tu rnam 'byes dang //
NK106(me)001:6399: gzigs pa sgrib med dag pa dang //
NK106(me)001:6400: dku zlum skabs phyin ma rnyongs dang //
NK106(me)001:6401: phyang nge ba dang lte ba ni //
NK106(me)001:6402: zab dang g.yas phyogs 'khyil ba dang //
NK106(me)001:6403: kun nas blta na sdug pa dang //
NK106(me)001:6404: kun spyod gtsang dang sku la ni //
NK106(me)001:6405: sme ba gnag bag med pa dang //
NK106(me)001:6406: phyag ni shing bal ltar 'jam dang //
NK106(me)001:6407: phyag ris mdangs yod zabs ring dang //
NK106(me)001:6408: zhal ni ha cang mi ring dang //
NK106(me)001:6409: mchu ni bim pa ltar dmar dang //
NK106(me)001:6410: ljags mnyen pa dang srab pa dang //
NK106(me)001:6411: dmar dang 'brug gi sgra nyid dang //
NK106(me)001:6412: gsung mnyen 'jam dang mche ba zlum //
NK106(me)001:6413: rno dang dkar dang mnyam pa dang //
NK106(me)001:6414: byin gyis phra dang shangs mtho dang //
NK106(me)001:6415: mchog tu dag pa nyid dang ni //
NK106(me)001:6416: spyan yangs pa dang rdzi ma stug /
NK106(me)001:6418: smin tshugs ring dang 'jam pa dang //
NK106(me)001:6419: snum dang spu ni mnyam pa dang //
NK106(me)001:6420: phyag ring rgyas dang snyan mnyam dang //
NK106(me)001:6421: nyams pa rnam par spangs pa dang //
NK106(me)001:6422: dpral ba legs par 'byes pa dang //
NK106(me)001:6423: dbyes che ba dang dbu rgyas dang //
NK106(me)001:6424: dbu skra bung ba ltar gnag dang //
NK106(me)001:6426: mi gshor dri zhim skyes bu yi //
NK106(me)001:6427: yid ni 'phrog par byed pa dang //
NK106(me)001:6428: dpal gyi be'u dang bkra shis ni //
NK106(me)001:6429: g.yung drung 'khyil bas brgyan pa ste //
NK106(me)001:6430: sangs rgyas dpe byad bzang por bzhed //
NK106(me)001:6432: chos phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK106(me)001:6434: chos ni rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:6435: smra bsam brjod du med pa'i klong nyid do //
NK106(me)001:6436: snang ba de'i tshe gcig ngang du ma med pa'i
NK106(me)001:6437: chos phun sum tshogs pa brjod du med pa ni
NK106(me)001:6439: chos ni rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po ste //
NK106(me)001:6440: snying po lhun 'byams smra bsam brjod las 'das //
NK106(me)001:6442: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa la gnyis las /
NK106(me)001:6445: 'khor ni nyid las mi zhan rang snang 'khor //
NK106(me)001:6446: sems dpa' brgyad dang de bzhin sems ma brgyad //
NK106(me)001:6447: sgo ba bzhi dang sgo ma rnam pa bzhi //
NK106(me)001:6448: zhi ba rang bzhin bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis las //
NK106(me)001:6449: drug ni gzhan la snang phyir sprul pa ste //
NK106(me)001:6450: gnyis ni dbyings na gnas phyir chos kyi sku //
NK106(me)001:6451: rang snang zhi ba longs sku sum cu bzhi //
NK106(me)001:6452: khyad par 'khor ni nyi shu bzhir gnas so //
NK106(me)001:6453: rang snang longs sku'i zhing na gtso 'khor du snang
NK106(me)001:6454: yang bzang ngan med pas ye shes gcig gi rol
NK106(me)001:6457: rang snang rgyal ba sems stsogs dang //
NK106(me)001:6458: dang po'i sangs rgyas sa rgyal ba //
NK106(me)001:6459: sems dpa' che dang 'joms pa che //
NK106(me)001:6461: de la zhi ba'i sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis las /
NK106(me)001:6462: kun bzang yab yum ni nang gsal chos sku'i ston par dbyings na bzhugs pas 'dir mi snang ngo //
NK106(me)001:6463: thub pa drug ni gdul bya'i snang bas bsdus pas 'dir mi snang ngo //
NK106(me)001:6464: gtso bo lngar byas na yum dang bcu dbus kyi gtso bo la /
NK106(me)001:6467: sgo ba yab yum brgyad de nyi shu rtsa bzhi yin la /
NK106(me)001:6468: gtso bo rnam snang yab yum du byas dus /
NK106(me)001:6469: rigs bzhi yab yum brgyad dang sum cu rtsa gnyis ni 'khor du rang snang ba'o //
NK106(me)001:6472: khro bo'i 'khor ni koo sing phra men brgyad //
NK106(me)001:6473: sgo skyong bzhi dang dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad //
NK106(me)001:6474: khro bo rang bzhin lnga bcu rtsa brgyad las //
NK106(me)001:6475: khyad par 'khor ni bzhi bcu brgyad dang bcas //
NK106(me)001:6476: 'bar ba'i cha lugs za byed rngam stabs can //
NK106(me)001:6477: shin tu mi bzad gar dgus rol pa'o //
NK106(me)001:6478: gtso bo yab yum lngar byas na 'khor bzhi bcu
NK106(me)001:6479: rtsa brgyad la bud+d+ha he ru ka yab yum dang
NK106(me)001:6480: bcas te gnyis su byas na lnga bcu rtsa drug
NK106(me)001:6481: 'khor du rang snang ba thams cad kyang 'jigs su
NK106(me)001:6482: rung ba'i rngam stabs 'bar bas nam mkha'i dkyil na
NK106(me)001:6483: bzhugs pa ste / slob dpon chen pos /
NK106(me)001:6484: sgeg pa dpa' ba 'jigs su rung ba dang //
NK106(me)001:6485: dgod dang gshe dang drag shul chen po dang //
NK106(me)001:6486: snying rje rngam dang zhi ba'i tshul ston pa //
NK106(me)001:6487: khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa brgyad la phyag 'tshal //
NK106(me)001:6488: zhes gsungs pa ltar gnas so //
NK106(me)001:6489: rang snang gzhan snang bshad pa ni /
NK106(me)001:6490: de ltar sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor bkod pa las /
NK106(me)001:6492: gzhan yang lus grub dkyil 'khor ji snyed pa //
NK106(me)001:6493: de snyed rang snang longs sku'i zhing khams yin //
NK106(me)001:6494: gzhan snang gdul bya'i zhi khro ji snyed pa //
NK106(me)001:6495: sprul skus bsdus phyir rang snang longs sku min //
NK106(me)001:6498: 'khor lo bde mchog la sogs pa'i rgyud bla na
NK106(me)001:6499: med pa las lus grub kyi dkyil 'khor gsungs pa
NK106(me)001:6500: yang rang snang longs sku'i snang ba yin gyi gzhan
NK106(me)001:6501: la snang ba ma yin no //
NK106(me)001:6502: kha cig las bgegs dang log 'dren 'dul ba'i don
NK106(me)001:6503: du khro bo'i dkyil 'khor spros pa dag ni sprul
NK106(me)001:6504: pa'i sku yin gyi 'og min gyi zhing gi dkyil
NK106(me)001:6506: bgegs de dag gi rang snang gi dkyil 'khor yin pa'i phyir rmi lam bzhin no //
NK106(me)001:6507: de dag gi mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK106(me)001:6508: da ni mjug bsdu ba bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:6509: rang snang longs sku'i snang ba chen po rang bkod pa /
NK106(me)001:6510: de ltar phun sum tshogs pa rnam lnga'i zhing //
NK106(me)001:6511: thams cad rang snang yin phyir bzang ngan med //
NK106(me)001:6512: kun kyang gsal 'tsher lhun stug 'od zer 'phro //
NK106(me)001:6513: lham me lhan ne lhang nge'i tshul gyis bzhugs //
NK106(me)001:6514: 'di ni 'dren pa rnams kyi spyod yul te //
NK106(me)001:6515: gcig gis gcig gzigs de yi basngagasa pa brjod //
NK106(me)001:6516: ye shes phyir gsal du snang ba'i zhing gi gtso
NK106(me)001:6517: 'khor la bzang ngan med de rgyud gcig gis bsdus
NK106(me)001:6518: pa'i rmi lam bzang ngan nam gtso 'khor du snang
NK106(me)001:6519: yang don la bzang ngan med pa bzhin /
NK106(me)001:6520: don nang na yod pa'i rtags phyir shar ba'i zhing
NK106(me)001:6521: dang gzhal yas khang dang 'od dang gtso 'khor la
NK106(me)001:6522: sogs pa rnams sgrib pa mtha' dag dang bral ba'i
NK106(me)001:6523: sangs rgyas kyi rgyud gcig gis bsdus pa'i rol pa
NK106(me)001:6525: de dag kyang thugs rnam par mi rtog pas lham me ba dang /
NK106(me)001:6526: gsung brjod bral chen pos lhan ne ba dang /
NK106(me)001:6527: sku gzi brjid chen pos lhang nge bar bzhugs pa yin no //
NK106(me)001:6528: 'di dag phyir snang du mthong ba dag pa'i spyan gyi dkyil 'khor la rang snang ba'i phyir /
NK106(me)001:6529: sangs rgyas thams cad gcig gis gcig bsgribs pa med
NK106(me)001:6530: par gzigs pas yon tan dang basngagasa pa brjod res
NK106(me)001:6532: dag pa sa bcus kyang mi mthong ba'i tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:6533: snang ba 'di nyid sa bcu'i sgrib pa /
NK106(me)001:6534: de ltar yid 'ong kun nas bkod pa'i zhing //
NK106(me)001:6535: dag pa'i gdul bya yis kyang mthong mi nus //
NK106(me)001:6536: sa dang po nas bcu pa'i bar gyi sems dpa'
NK106(me)001:6537: rnams kyis kyang sangs rgyas nyid kyi rang snang ba'i
NK106(me)001:6539: da dung sgrib pa mtha' dag dang ma bral ba'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)001:6540: de lta bu'i sangs rgyas kyi khams dang yon tan
NK106(me)001:6541: 'phrin las la sogs pa nam mkha'i dbyings khyab par
NK106(me)001:6542: mtha' yas pas kyang blta bar mi nus te /
NK106(me)001:6543: rang gi sa pa tsam las yon tan mtha' dag
NK106(me)001:6544: la gzigs pa dag pa'i blo mig ma thob pa'i
NK106(me)001:6546: sangs rgyas khams dang sangs rgyas byang chub dang //
NK106(me)001:6547: sangs rgyas yon tan sangs rgyas 'phrin las te //
NK106(me)001:6548: dag pa'i sems can gyis kyang bsam bya min //
NK106(me)001:6549: 'di ni 'dren pa rnams kyi spyod yul yin //
NK106(me)001:6551: dag yul min phyir don dam gyis bsdus phyir //
NK106(me)001:6552: rtog gnas min phyir dpe las 'das pa'i phyir //
NK106(me)001:6553: bla na med phyir srid zhis ma bsdus phyir //
NK106(me)001:6554: rgyal yul 'phags rnams kyis kyang bsam mi khyab //
NK106(me)001:6556: bla med ye shes thugs rje che sogs yon tan gyis //
NK106(me)001:6557: yon tan pha rol phyin pa'i rgyal ba bsam mi khyab //
NK106(me)001:6558: des na rang byung rnams kyi tha ma'i tshul 'di ni //
NK106(me)001:6559: drang srong chen po dbang thob rnams kyis kyang rig min //
NK106(me)001:6561: sangs rgyas kho na'i spyod yul du bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:6562: 'o na su yi yul yin zhe na /
NK106(me)001:6563: rang snang stong gzugs bzhin du bsam mi khyab //
NK106(me)001:6564: dus gsum rgyal ba rnams kyi rang snang ngo //
NK106(me)001:6565: 'di ltar rlung dbu mar chud pa'i tshe rnal 'byor
NK106(me)001:6566: pa rnams la stong pa nyid kyi gzugs brnyan rang
NK106(me)001:6567: la snang yang gzhan gyis mi mthong ba bzhin du
NK106(me)001:6568: / sangs rgyas la snang ba'i zhing snang de yang
NK106(me)001:6569: byang chub sems dpas mi mthong yang sangs rgyas la
NK106(me)001:6570: rtag pa rgyun gyi khor mor snang ste /
NK106(me)001:6571: lhun gyis grub pa'i dbyings kyi snang ba yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)001:6573: ye shes thig le de nyid la //
NK106(me)001:6574: ye shes thig le nyid snang ba //
NK106(me)001:6575: bsam gyis mi khyab bsam yas mchog /
NK106(me)001:6576: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK106(me)001:6577: zhing khams bsam yas rnam dag dang //
NK106(me)001:6578: rgya dang bral ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK106(me)001:6579: 'khor lo'i rgyan dang rol mo'i tshogs //
NK106(me)001:6580: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsam yas kun //
NK106(me)001:6581: mthong nas nye bar mnyes pa dang //
NK106(me)001:6582: rgya chen gsung las don 'byung ba'ang //
NK106(me)001:6583: mthun pa'i ye shes rang snang ba'o //
NK106(me)001:6585: de la ye shes kyi thig le ni sangs rgyas kyi mthong ba dag pa'i spyan te /
NK106(me)001:6587: ye shes mig gcig dri ma med //
NK106(me)001:6589: ye shes thig le nyid snang ba ni rang snang gi zhing 'ja' 'od gdangs gsal ba'o //
NK106(me)001:6590: bsam gyis mi khyab pa ni snang ba de 'dra
NK106(me)001:6591: ba sangs rgyas gzhan rnams kyi snang ba la snang
NK106(me)001:6592: ba'o // bsam yas mchog kyang de nyid de tshad med pa'o //
NK106(me)001:6593: phyogs bcu ni shar la sogs pa dang /
NK106(me)001:6594: 'das ma 'ongs da ltar gyi sangs rgyas gsum dang
NK106(me)001:6595: ma nges pa 'og min na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK106(me)001:6596: te dus bzhir rdzogs pa'i rang snang ngo //
NK106(me)001:6597: de yang zhing khams bsam yas rnam dag dang zhes
NK106(me)001:6598: pa rang snang gi zhing ste sangs rgyas gcig gis
NK106(me)001:6600: rgya dang bral ba'i gzhal yas la sogs pa ni 'od gsal rang snang gi zhing ngo //
NK106(me)001:6601: gsung las don 'byung ba ni brjod du med pa'i
NK106(me)001:6602: gsung de nyid kho na gsung gi don de go
NK106(me)001:6603: bar mdzad pa'o // mthun pa'i ye shes ni gtso
NK106(me)001:6604: 'khor rtogs pa gcig ngo bo gcig dbyer med par
NK106(me)001:6605: bar mdzad pa'o // mthun pa'o // rang snang ba
NK106(me)001:6606: ni sangs rgyas de nyid kyi spyan la snang gi
NK106(me)001:6607: sems dpa' la sogs pa gzhan la mi snang ngo
NK106(me)001:6609: sprul pa'i sku la yang mdor bstan dang rgyas bshad gnyis kyi /
NK106(me)001:6611: sku lnga pa sprul pa'i sku ni rgyal sras 'phags
NK106(me)001:6612: pa la sogs pa zhi ba'i gling du 'khrid par
NK106(me)001:6613: byed pas ded dpon dam pa'i ston pa zhes bya
NK106(me)001:6614: ste / de'ang gdul bya mchog la snang ba gzugs brnyan longs sku dang /
NK106(me)001:6615: phal pa la snang ba sna tshogs sprul pa gnyis las /
NK106(me)001:6616: dang po ni 'og min la sogs pa'i nges pa lnga ldan du snang la /
NK106(me)001:6617: gnyis pa ni bzo la sogs pa so so'i skye bo dang nyan rang gi don mdzad pa'o //
NK106(me)001:6618: sprul pa de gnyis gang las 'char zhe na /
NK106(me)001:6620: de nyid ngang las gdul bya'i 'jig rten du //
NK106(me)001:6621: 'dul byed ston pa rim gyis snang ba ni //
NK106(me)001:6622: rang bzhin 'gro 'dul sna tshogs sprul pa'i sku //
NK106(me)001:6623: rnam pa gsum gyis 'gro ba'i don mdzad do //
NK106(me)001:6624: rang snang gi ngang las slar 'dul bya la snang ba'i sku mched nas 'gro ba'i don mdzad de /
NK106(me)001:6625: de'ang rang bzhin sprul pa dang /
NK106(me)001:6628: rgyas par bshad pa la rang bzhin 'gro 'dul sna tshogs sprul sku gsum gyi /
NK106(me)001:6629: rang bzhin sprul sku la yang gnas dang ston pa /
NK106(me)001:6636: thog mar sems dpa' rnams la snang ba gzugs brnyan
NK106(me)001:6637: longs sku'i ston pa ni rang snang longs sku dang
NK106(me)001:6638: cha 'dra la dngos ma yin pa bzhin dang me
NK106(me)001:6639: long nang gi gzugs brnyan lta bu ste /
NK106(me)001:6640: phun sum tshogs pa lngas bshad par bya ba'i tshul las /
NK106(me)001:6641: de yang rang bzhin sprul sku'i ston pa ni //
NK106(me)001:6642: 'og min mngon dga' dpal ldan pad+ma brtsegs //
NK106(me)001:6643: las rab grub pa'i 'jig rten rnam pa lngar //
NK106(me)001:6644: rnam snang mi bskyod la sogs rigs lnga'i sku //
NK106(me)001:6645: mtshan dang dpe byad 'od zer 'bar ba la //
NK106(me)001:6646: zhi dang khro tshul dpag med tshul 'char bas //
NK106(me)001:6647: 'gro ba'i don gnyis lhun gyis grub par mdzad //
NK106(me)001:6648: dag pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyang ye shes lnga dang sku lnga thob par byed cing /
NK106(me)001:6649: nyon mongs pa lnga sbyong ba la ltos nas rigs
NK106(me)001:6650: lnga'i ston pa dang zhing dang chos dang grogs la
NK106(me)001:6652: dbus 'og min na ston pa rnam par snang mdzad dang /
NK106(me)001:6653: shar mngon dgar rdo rje sems dpa' dang /
NK106(me)001:6654: lho dpal dang ldan par rin chen 'byung gnas dang /
NK106(me)001:6655: nub pad+ma brtsegs pa'am bde ba can na 'od dpag med dang /
NK106(me)001:6656: byang las rab grub par don yod grub pa rnams
NK106(me)001:6657: mtshan dpe 'bar ba'i sku chu'i zla ba ltar rang
NK106(me)001:6658: snang longs sku'i ci 'dra bar snang ba ste /
NK106(me)001:6660: ji ltar sprin med nam mkha'i zla ba'i gzugs //
NK106(me)001:6661: ston ka'i chu sngon mtshor ni mthong ba ltar //
NK106(me)001:6662: de bzhin rgyal sras tshogs kyis khyab bdag gzugs //
NK106(me)001:6663: rdzogs sangs dkyil 'khor nang du mthong bar 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:6667: mtshan ni sum cu rtsa gnyis dang //
NK106(me)001:6668: dpe byad brgyad cu'i bdag nyid ni //
NK106(me)001:6669: theg chen nye bar longs spyod phyir //
NK106(me)001:6670: thub pa'i longs spyod rdzogs skur bzhed //
NK106(me)001:6672: de'ang nang gsal las rang snang ba'i longs sku nam
NK106(me)001:6673: mkha'i zla ba lta bu'i gzugs brnyan sems dpa' la
NK106(me)001:6674: snang ba ni longs spyod rdzogs sku gnyis pa sems
NK106(me)001:6675: dpa' rnams tshim par byed pa dang /
NK106(me)001:6676: sprul sku rnams rnam par dag pa'i dbyings la brten pas ring ba dang nye ba zhes brjod de /
NK106(me)001:6678: mthong na tshim byed yon tan gang //
NK106(me)001:6679: sum cu rtsa gnyis zhes bya ba //
NK106(me)001:6680: sprul pa chos la rdzogs par ni //
NK106(me)001:6681: longs spyod gzugs sku gnyis la brten //
NK106(me)001:6682: dag las nye dang ring rnams la //
NK106(me)001:6684: chu dang nam mkhar zla gzugs bzhin //
NK106(me)001:6685: de mthong ba ni rnam pa gnyis //
NK106(me)001:6687: de'ang dag dbyings longs sku sangs rgyas kyis mthong ba dang /
NK106(me)001:6688: gzugs brnyan longs sku sems dpas mthong ba gnyis so //
NK106(me)001:6689: zhar la mchog gi sprul pa mtshan dpes brgyan pa
NK106(me)001:6690: yang de'i cha mthun yin pas so so'i skye bo
NK106(me)001:6691: la sogs pas mthong ba la sbyar ba yin no
NK106(me)001:6692: // ye shes la'ang mdor bstan rgyas bshad gnyis las /
NK106(me)001:6694: sems dpa' la snang ba'i longs sku /
NK106(me)001:6695: de yang ye shes lnga lnga'i rang bzhin te //
NK106(me)001:6696: chos dbyings me long mnyam nyid so sor rtog /
NK106(me)001:6697: bya grub ye shes rnam pa lnga po yang //
NK106(me)001:6698: re re'i 'khor du bzhi bzhi ldan pa ste //
NK106(me)001:6699: thams cad ro mnyam gcig gi ngang nyid do //
NK106(me)001:6700: ston pa lnga la ye shes lnga lnga ste nyi
NK106(me)001:6701: shu rtsa lnga ldan pa yang rang bzhin rgyud gcig
NK106(me)001:6702: gi ngang las ma g.yos so //
NK106(me)001:6703: 'di ltar rnam snang la chos dbyings ye shes /
NK106(me)001:6704: mi bskyod pa la me long ye shes /
NK106(me)001:6705: rin 'byung la mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK106(me)001:6706: snang mtha' la kun rtog ye shes /
NK106(me)001:6707: don grub la bya grub ye shes gtso bor ldan
NK106(me)001:6708: la gzhan bzhi po 'khor du ldan pa yin no
NK106(me)001:6709: // rgyas par bshad pa la lnga las /
NK106(me)001:6711: ye shes de dag gang zhe na /
NK106(me)001:6713: chos dbyings ye shes shin tu mi g.yo ba //
NK106(me)001:6714: gzung 'dzin spros pa'i mtha' las 'das pa yin //
NK106(me)001:6715: gti mug dbyings su zhi bas spros pa dang bral ba nam mkha' lta bu'i ye shes te /
NK106(me)001:6716: sangs rgyas kyi sa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:6717: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes ni dper na nam
NK106(me)001:6718: mkha'i gzugs su gyur pa thams cad na yod kyang
NK106(me)001:6719: de'i rang bzhin brjod par bya ba ma yin pas
NK106(me)001:6720: sna tshogs su med par ro gcig go //
NK106(me)001:6721: de bzhin du chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes kyang
NK106(me)001:6722: shes bya thams cad la yod kyang brjod par bya
NK106(me)001:6723: ba ma yin pas sna tshogs ma yin pa'i phyir
NK106(me)001:6727: me long ye shes gsal stong 'char gzhi'i tshul //
NK106(me)001:6728: ye shes kun gyi 'byung gnas chen po yin //
NK106(me)001:6729: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa rnam shes gzhan rnams
NK106(me)001:6730: kyi mched pa'i 'char gzhi can dbyings su nub pa
NK106(me)001:6731: las ye shes lhag ma gsum gyi 'char gzhir gyur
NK106(me)001:6732: pa me long dag pa'i ngos lta bu gzung 'dzin
NK106(me)001:6733: gyi dri ma med pa ni /
NK106(me)001:6735: me long lta bu'i ye shes ni dper na me
NK106(me)001:6736: long gi ngos la gzugs brnyan snang yang yod pa
NK106(me)001:6737: ma yin te rtsol ba yang med /
NK106(me)001:6738: mngon par 'du bya ba yang med do //
NK106(me)001:6739: de bzhin du me long lta bu'i ye shes la
NK106(me)001:6740: thams cad mkhyen pa'i gzugs brnyan sna tshogs byung yang
NK106(me)001:6741: yod pa ma yin te rtsol ba dang mngon par
NK106(me)001:6742: 'du bya ba med do zhes pa dang /
NK106(me)001:6744: me long ye shes mi g.yo ste //
NK106(me)001:6745: ye shes gsum ni de la brten //
NK106(me)001:6746: mnyam pa nyid dang so sor rtog /
NK106(me)001:6747: bya ba grub pa kho na'o //
NK106(me)001:6751: mnyam nyid ye shes chos kun mnyam pa'i ngang //
NK106(me)001:6752: 'khor 'das gnyis med mnyam rdzogs chen po yin //
NK106(me)001:6753: nga rgyal dbyings su zhi bas bdag gzhan mnyam pa
NK106(me)001:6754: nyid du mkhyen cing 'khor 'das gnyis su med pa
NK106(me)001:6756: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes ni chos thams cad
NK106(me)001:6757: mtshan nyid med par mnyam pa nyid khong du chud
NK106(me)001:6758: cing bde ba dang sdug bsngal ro gcig pas mnyam
NK106(me)001:6759: par grub pa'o zhes pa dang /
NK106(me)001:6761: mnyam nyid ye shes sems can la //
NK106(me)001:6762: sgom pa dag pa la 'dod de //
NK106(me)001:6763: mi gnas zhi bar zhugs pa ni //
NK106(me)001:6764: mnyam nyid ye shes yin par 'dod //
NK106(me)001:6768: kun rtog ye shes shes bya ma 'dres mkhyen //
NK106(me)001:6769: ji snyed ji bzhin gzigs pa rnam dag yin //
NK106(me)001:6770: 'dod chags dbyings su nub pas so sor rtog pa'i
NK106(me)001:6771: ye shes shes bya ji lta ba gshis stong pa
NK106(me)001:6772: nyid dang / ji snyed pa snang ba sna tshogs
NK106(me)001:6773: pa'i ngo bo rgyu 'bras thams cad mkhyen pa ste
NK106(me)001:6775: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes ni dper na 'jig
NK106(me)001:6776: rten gyi khams na gling dang nyi zla la sogs
NK106(me)001:6777: pa so sor phye ba yin no //
NK106(me)001:6778: de bzhin du so sor rtog pa'i ye shes kyang
NK106(me)001:6779: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i phun sum tshogs pa thams
NK106(me)001:6780: cad dang / rgyu dang 'bras bur bcas pa dang /
NK106(me)001:6783: byang chub sems dpa' yang dag par grub pa so sor mkhyen to zhes pa dang /
NK106(me)001:6785: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes ni //
NK106(me)001:6786: shes bya kun la rtag mi thogs //
NK106(me)001:6787: ting nge 'dzin dang gzungs rnams kyi //
NK106(me)001:6788: gter dang 'dra ba kho na yin //
NK106(me)001:6790: 'byor pa thams cad ston mdzad cing //
NK106(me)001:6791: the tshom thams cad gcod mdzad pa'i //
NK106(me)001:6792: chos chen char ni rab tu 'bebs //
NK106(me)001:6796: bya grub ye shes 'phrin las phun sum tshogs //
NK106(me)001:6797: shes bya kun la rtag thogs med pa yin //
NK106(me)001:6798: phrag dog dbyings su nub pas 'gro ba'i don mdzad
NK106(me)001:6799: par thogs pa med pa bya ba nan tan gyi
NK106(me)001:6800: ye shes ni / mdo de nyid las /
NK106(me)001:6801: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes ni dper na sems
NK106(me)001:6802: can rnams kyi lus dang ngag dang yid kyi bya
NK106(me)001:6804: de bzhin du bya ba grub pa'i ye shes ni
NK106(me)001:6805: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyis sems can gyi don
NK106(me)001:6806: lhun gyis grub par mdzad pa'o zhes pa dang /
NK106(me)001:6808: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes ni //
NK106(me)001:6809: khams rnams kun tu sna tshogs shing //
NK106(me)001:6810: dpag med bsam yas sprul pa yis //
NK106(me)001:6815: gdul bya'i 'khor ni sa bcu'i sems dpa' la //
NK106(me)001:6816: chos ni ting 'dzin 'od zer rab bkye bas //
NK106(me)001:6817: sa de'i sgrib pa sbyong ba'i blo skyes nas //
NK106(me)001:6818: ser sna la sogs spangs te rgyal la blta //
NK106(me)001:6819: da dung de 'dra'i ston pa rnam dag dang //
NK106(me)001:6820: bdag nyid khyad par mthong nas sgrib pa sbyong //
NK106(me)001:6821: kun tu 'od kyi bar du 'god pa ste //
NK106(me)001:6822: gzugs bzang me long bstan pas don mdzad do //
NK106(me)001:6823: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa ni sa bcu pa'i byang chub sems dpa' ste /
NK106(me)001:6825: byang chub sems dpa' sa chen po la bzhugs pa
NK106(me)001:6826: rnams dang thabs cig tu theg pa chen po'i chos
NK106(me)001:6827: kyi longs spyod kyi dga' ba dang bde ba shin
NK106(me)001:6828: tu kha na ma tho ba med pa nye bar
NK106(me)001:6829: spyod pa'i phyir sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyi longs
NK106(me)001:6830: spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yin no zhes so //
NK106(me)001:6831: de'ang chos phun sum tshogs pa theg pa chen po 'od zer bkye bas snang bar mdzad de /
NK106(me)001:6832: me long bltas pas byad kyi dri ma sel ba ltar /
NK106(me)001:6833: sems dpa' des ston pa longs sku la bltas pas
NK106(me)001:6834: rang gis de'i sgrib pa mthong nas ser sna la
NK106(me)001:6835: sogs pa rim pas sbyangs te ston pa la blta
NK106(me)001:6836: zhing / de dang bdag dag ma dag khyad zhugs par mthong nas /
NK106(me)001:6837: slar yang go ba brdas mtshon pa'i chos nang shar
NK106(me)001:6838: du 'byung bar byin gyis rlob cing 'od zer bkye
NK106(me)001:6839: bas sgrib pa sel bar byed do //
NK106(me)001:6841: 'og min bla med gnas mchog tu //
NK106(me)001:6842: sku ni rnam par snang mdzad tshul //
NK106(me)001:6843: byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor rnams la //
NK106(me)001:6844: de bzhin gsung mchog mi smra ste //
NK106(me)001:6845: sku yis chos rnams 'jal bar ston //
NK106(me)001:6846: me long bstan pa'i tshul bzhin du //
NK106(me)001:6847: dngos kyi mdog ngan thams cad sel //
NK106(me)001:6848: 'khor gyis de bzhin sku bltas na //
NK106(me)001:6849: byang chub sgrib pa gting dpag med //
NK106(me)001:6850: me long bzhin du sku la snang //
NK106(me)001:6851: de nas sa bcu rim gyis 'byang //
NK106(me)001:6852: bla med byang chub yang dag 'thob //
NK106(me)001:6856: dus ni 'gro grol bar du rgyun mi 'chad //
NK106(me)001:6857: longs sku'i zhing na khor mor snang ba yin //
NK106(me)001:6858: sems dpa' sa bcu la bzhugs pa rnams byang chub
NK106(me)001:6859: ma thob pa de srid du bzhugs pas mi zad
NK106(me)001:6860: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i dus te rtag pa rgyun
NK106(me)001:6861: gyi khor mor bzhugs pa yin te /
NK106(me)001:6863: 'gro grol bar du 'jig rten 'byor slad rtag /
NK106(me)001:6866: chos kyi dbang phyug 'chi ba'i bdud bcom dang //
NK106(me)001:6867: ngo bo med phyir 'jig rten mgon po rtag /
NK106(me)001:6869: zhing dang ston pas sbyang bya'i khyad par la gnyis las /
NK106(me)001:6872: de ltar rigs lngar nges pa'i rang bzhin yang //
NK106(me)001:6873: gdul bya gti mug shas cher sbyong ba'i tshe //
NK106(me)001:6874: zhing ni 'og min ston pa rnam snang la //
NK106(me)001:6875: chos ni chos dbyings ye shes rnam par dag /
NK106(me)001:6876: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi dri ma nyon mongs
NK106(me)001:6877: pa lnga'i rim pas ston pa dang chos lngar snang
NK106(me)001:6878: ba'i dang po gti mug gi dri ma sbyong dus
NK106(me)001:6879: rnam snang las chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes kyi
NK106(me)001:6883: de bzhin zhe sdang sbyang phyir mi bskyod zhing //
NK106(me)001:6884: nga rgyal rin 'byung 'dod chags 'od dpag med //
NK106(me)001:6885: phrag dog sbyang phyir don grub snang ba yin //
NK106(me)001:6886: zhe sdang la mi bskyod pas me long ye shes kyi chos ston la /
NK106(me)001:6887: nga rgyal la rin 'byung gis mnyam pa nyid dang /
NK106(me)001:6888: 'dod chags la 'od dpag med kyis so sor rtog pa dang /
NK106(me)001:6889: phrag dog la don yod grub pas bya grub ye shes bstan pas sbyong ba yin no //
NK106(me)001:6890: de'ang sa bcu po la rigs lnga chos lnga gnas gyur lnga gsungs te /
NK106(me)001:6891: mthong lam gyi dus su kun brtags pa'i gti mug
NK106(me)001:6892: gnas gyur chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes rab tu
NK106(me)001:6893: dga' ba'i sa thob rnam snang mthong /
NK106(me)001:6894: sgom lam chung ngu gsum du nga rgyal gnas gyur
NK106(me)001:6895: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes thob rin 'byung mthong
NK106(me)001:6896: / 'bring gsum du rnam pa thams cad pa'i 'dod
NK106(me)001:6897: chags gnas gyur so sor rtog pa'i ye shes thob
NK106(me)001:6899: chen po'i sa brgyad pa la zhe sdang gi sa
NK106(me)001:6900: bon rtog pa'i zug rngu dang kun gzhi'i rnam shes
NK106(me)001:6901: gnas gyur me long lta bu'i ye shes rnam par
NK106(me)001:6902: mi rtog pa thob mi bskyod pa mthong /
NK106(me)001:6903: dgu pa dang bcu par phrag dog gi sa bon
NK106(me)001:6904: dag sgo lnga'i zhing dag par so sor yang dag
NK106(me)001:6905: rig bzhis sems can gyi don byed pa'i 'phrin las
NK106(me)001:6906: phun sum tshogs pa bya ba grub pa'i ye shes
NK106(me)001:6907: thob don grub mthong nas 'od zer chen pos dbang
NK106(me)001:6908: bskur te sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa chen po rdzogs
NK106(me)001:6911: dag pa sa yi dbang nyid phyir //
NK106(me)001:6912: ston pa lnga dang chos rab lnga //
NK106(me)001:6913: ye shes lnga yongs rdzogs pa las //
NK106(me)001:6914: rdzogs pa'i byang chub snying por 'gro //
NK106(me)001:6916: de'i 'grel pa ji lta ba bzhin bkod do //
NK106(me)001:6918: 'khor dang ston pa'i khyad kyis phyed sprul ni /
NK106(me)001:6919: gzhan snang rigs lnga'i zhing dang ston par snang bas sems dpa'i don mdzad pa'i tshul 'di nyid /
NK106(me)001:6920: de ltar ston pa longs spyod rdzogs na yang //
NK106(me)001:6921: 'khor sogs ston pa nyid las gzhan yin pas //
NK106(me)001:6922: thams cad longs spyod rdzogs min de yi phyir //
NK106(me)001:6923: phyed sprul nyid de rang bzhin sprul pa'i sku //
NK106(me)001:6924: dag pa'i 'gro ba rnams la snang ba yin //
NK106(me)001:6925: sar gnas rnams las gdul bya gzhan la min //
NK106(me)001:6926: de phyir phyed snang sprul pa'i sku zhes bya //
NK106(me)001:6927: longs sku mtshan nyid pa'i zhing na thams cad bzang
NK106(me)001:6928: ngan med par rdzogs pas rtag tu 'pho 'gyur med
NK106(me)001:6929: la / sems dpa' la snang ba'i longs sku ni
NK106(me)001:6930: gzugs brnyan du mtshan dpe la sogs pa ston pa'i
NK106(me)001:6931: longs spyod rdzogs par snang yang 'khor dang zhing la
NK106(me)001:6932: sogs pa gzhan du snang zhing sa bcu pa'i snang
NK106(me)001:6933: bas bsdus pa yin pas phyed sprul yongs sku zhes
NK106(me)001:6934: bya bar nyi zla kha sbyor la sogs pa'i rgyud
NK106(me)001:6935: la / du gsungs so // zhing 'di yang sa
NK106(me)001:6936: bcu pa'i sems dpa' las gzhan la mi snang ba'i
NK106(me)001:6937: phyir yang phyed sprul zhes bya la /
NK106(me)001:6938: longs skur snang yang dngos rang snang las gzhan ma
NK106(me)001:6939: yin pas de'i gzugs brnyan phyed pa ltar snang ba'i
NK106(me)001:6940: phyir na'ang phyed sprul zhes bya ste rang snang gi
NK106(me)001:6941: rang bzhin 'phrul pas rang bzhin sprul pa'i sku zhes
NK106(me)001:6942: kyang bshad do // zhi ba'i zhing bzhi ni /
NK106(me)001:6944: zhing de khod mnyam yid 'ong gzhal med khang //
NK106(me)001:6945: rin chen bdun ldan 'od zer phyogs bcur 'phro //
NK106(me)001:6946: pad+ma las skyes rgyal sras dpag tu med //
NK106(me)001:6947: longs spyod sna tshogs 'dod dgu'i char pa 'bab //
NK106(me)001:6948: dus bzhir chos gsung dri med g.yer kha'i sgra //
NK106(me)001:6949: dpag bsam rin chen chu mtshos rab tu mdzes //
NK106(me)001:6950: 'di ni zhi ba rang bzhin sprul pa yin //
NK106(me)001:6951: rigs lnga'i zhing de na rin po che sna bdun
NK106(me)001:6952: gyi sa gzhi la gzhal med khang 'od zer rab
NK106(me)001:6953: tu 'bar ba rin po che'i dra bas brgyan pa
NK106(me)001:6954: dang / ta la'i ljon par dril bu tshar du
NK106(me)001:6955: bsgrengs pa las stong pa nyid dang mtshan ma med
NK106(me)001:6956: pa la sogs pa'i chos kyi sgra sngar ma thos
NK106(me)001:6957: pa nyon mongs pa'i gnod pa zhi bar byed pa
NK106(me)001:6959: rdzing bu yan lag brgyad ldan sprul pa'i chu byas
NK106(me)001:6960: brgyan par rtse ba las nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba
NK106(me)001:6961: sel ba dang / gang ci 'dod pa thams cad
NK106(me)001:6962: nam mkha' las char du 'bab pa la sogs te
NK106(me)001:6963: sangs rgyas kyi mthu dang byang chub sems dpa'i dge
NK106(me)001:6964: ba'i rtsa ba rmad du byung bas bskrun pa'i rgyu
NK106(me)001:6965: las byung ba'i bkod pa tshad med pa ni mi
NK106(me)001:6966: 'khrugs pa'i zhing gi yon tan bkod pa dang bde
NK106(me)001:6967: ba can gyi zhing gi yon tan bkod pa la
NK106(me)001:6968: sogs pa'i mdo las rgyas par 'byung ba bzhin no
NK106(me)001:6969: sel ba dang / // de dag kyang rang gi
NK106(me)001:6970: dge ba'i sems kyi snang ba tsam las gzhan dag
NK106(me)001:6971: rtog 'dod can ma dag pas logs shig tu bgrod
NK106(me)001:6972: nas phyin du yod pa ma yin te /
NK106(me)001:6973: dge ba'i bag chags las rmi lam bzang po 'byung
NK106(me)001:6974: ba ltar sems dpa' rnams la rang snang ba ni
NK106(me)001:6975: sangs rgyas kyi phyed sprul dang thun mong du spyod
NK106(me)001:6978: dpag bsam shing dang yid bzhin gyi //
NK106(me)001:6979: rin po che dang 'byung ba kun //
NK106(me)001:6980: de dag rdzas yod ma yin te //
NK106(me)001:6981: rang sems bsod nams brtas pa yin //
NK106(me)001:6982: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)001:6983: gzhan nas yod 'ongs ma yin te //
NK106(me)001:6984: thabs la brten pa'i shes rab nyid //
NK106(me)001:6985: de la bu yi ngang du byung //
NK106(me)001:6988: zhi ba rang bzhin sprul pa'i sku sems dpa' sar bzhugs pa rnams la snang ba /
NK106(me)001:6989: de bzhin khro tshul dkyil 'khor dpag tu med //
NK106(me)001:6990: mkha' 'gro'i sprin phung 'phro ba'i mkha' spyod gnas //
NK106(me)001:6991: he ru ka dpal rigs lnga'i zhing khams nyid //
NK106(me)001:6992: gsang sngags grub la rab tu snang ba yin //
NK106(me)001:6993: 'di ni ding sang bde chen mkha' spyod ces //
NK106(me)001:6994: mkhas grub rnams la rab tu grags pa yin //
NK106(me)001:6995: nang gsal las rang snang phyir gsal du bzhengs pa
NK106(me)001:6996: khro bo rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor las zla ba'i gzugs
NK106(me)001:6997: brnyan chur snang ba bzhin du gsang sngags kyi rig
NK106(me)001:6998: pa 'dzin pa'i sa la bzhugs pa'i gang zag tshe
NK106(me)001:7000: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin rnams la dug lnga
NK106(me)001:7001: sbyong ba'i phyir sku lnga dang ye shes lnga'i chos
NK106(me)001:7002: rang byung du snang ba las /
NK106(me)001:7003: gti mug 'dul ba'i tshe de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs
NK106(me)001:7004: kyi khro bo bud+d+ha he ru ka'i dkyil 'khor 'og
NK106(me)001:7006: der bgrod nas mkha' 'gro dang rnal 'byor gyi dbang
NK106(me)001:7007: phyug rig pa 'dzin pa gzhan rnams dang skal pa
NK106(me)001:7008: gcig pas tshogs kyi dga' ba dang sngags kyi lta
NK106(me)001:7009: spyod rlabs po che la spyod pa'o //
NK106(me)001:7010: de bzhin du rdo rje'i zhing na badz+ra he ru ka dang /
NK106(me)001:7011: rin po che'i zhing na rat+na he ru ka dang /
NK106(me)001:7012: pad+ma'i zhing na pad+ma he ru ka dang /
NK106(me)001:7013: las kyi zhing na karma he ru ka'i dkyil 'khor dang zhing gi bkod pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7014: mkha' 'gro grub pa can gyi grogs dang /
NK106(me)001:7018: zhing skyes la sogs pa'i rdo rje rnal 'byor ma'i tshogs dang skal pa mnyam zhing /
NK106(me)001:7019: stong grogs byed pas 'chi kar zhing der gdugs dang
NK106(me)001:7020: rgyal mtshan dang rol mo'i sprin phung gis bsu zhing
NK106(me)001:7021: / rig 'dzin gyi bla ma rnams kyis gzigs nas
NK106(me)001:7022: drangs te rig 'dzin gyi gral la 'jog pa'i gnas
NK106(me)001:7023: lnga ni bde chen mkha' spyod ces grags te /
NK106(me)001:7024: sa thob pa rnams dang skal pa mtshungs pa'i zhing
NK106(me)001:7025: dang chos dang ston pa dang grogs su gcig pas
NK106(me)001:7026: rang rang gi lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK106(me)001:7027: dngos grub can gang na spyod pa las gzhan zhig
NK106(me)001:7030: sar bzhugs rnams la snang ba bzhin //
NK106(me)001:7031: rig pa 'dzin la khro bo'i zhing //
NK106(me)001:7032: mkha' spyod yon tan tshogs chen po //
NK106(me)001:7033: grub pa'i mtshan mas brgyan pa zhig /
NK106(me)001:7034: dngos grub ya mtshan chen por snang //
NK106(me)001:7036: 'di nyid du lam sbyong ba'i rig pa 'dzin pa
NK106(me)001:7037: rdo rje bla ma rnams bzhugs so zhes grags pa
NK106(me)001:7038: yin no // 'gro 'dul sprul sku la bdun las /
NK106(me)001:7039: thub pa drug tu bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:7040: gnyis pa 'gro 'dul sprul pa yang 'gro ba so
NK106(me)001:7041: so'i gnas ris su de'i snang ba dang mthun pas
NK106(me)001:7042: don mdzad pa'i ston par snang ba ni /
NK106(me)001:7043: sngar smos pa bzhin 'og min gyi longs spyod rdzogs
NK106(me)001:7044: pa'i sku'i gnas drug nas 'od zer drug 'gro ba
NK106(me)001:7045: drug gi gnas su 'phros pa'i rtse mo las yi
NK106(me)001:7046: ge 'phreng ba'i 'khor lo so so'i ston par snang
NK106(me)001:7047: bas don mdzad do zhes shes par bya ba ni
NK106(me)001:7049: de nyid ngang las 'gro 'dul sprul pa'i sku //
NK106(me)001:7050: 'gro drug gnas su rang rang ston par snang //
NK106(me)001:7051: de yang brgya byin thags bzang ris dang ni //
NK106(me)001:7052: sh+aakya thub pa seng ge rab brtan dang //
NK106(me)001:7053: kha 'bar de ba a wa glang mgo ste //
NK106(me)001:7054: thub pa drug gis phyogs bcu'i zhing rnams su //
NK106(me)001:7055: 'gro ba drug gi rgyud drug so sor sbyong //
NK106(me)001:7056: longs sku'i 'od zer las yi ge 'phreng ba'i 'khor
NK106(me)001:7057: lo 'gro ba drug gi gnas su ston par 'phros
NK106(me)001:7058: te / lha'i gnas su dbang po brgya byin la sogs pa lha'i thub pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7059: lha ma yin gyi gnas su thags bzangs ris la sogs pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7060: mi'i gnas su thub pa chen po la sogs pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7061: dud 'gro'i gnas su seng ge rab brtan la sogs pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7062: yi dgas kyi gnas su kha 'bar de ba la sogs pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7063: dmyal ba'i gnas su a wa glang mgo la sogs
NK106(me)001:7064: pa so so'i 'dul byed gang yin par lhun gyis
NK106(me)001:7065: grub pas / g.yo ba dang 'bad pa'i rtsol ba
NK106(me)001:7066: mi mnga' bzhin du sems can gyi don mdzad pa
NK106(me)001:7067: ni thugs rje chen po'i byin gyis brlabs dang /
NK106(me)001:7068: 'gro ba'i dkar po rnam par 'phel ba'i rgyu las
NK106(me)001:7069: byung ba ste chu dang zla gzugs dang zla ba'i
NK106(me)001:7070: dkyil 'khor gsum dang chos mtshungs par snang ste /
NK106(me)001:7071: zla ba la gzugs brnyan 'jog pa'i nus pa yod
NK106(me)001:7072: pa ltar longs sku'i zla ba la gdul bya'i ngor
NK106(me)001:7073: sprul pa 'byung ba'i nus pa yod pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7074: chu snod la gzugs brnyan 'dzin pa'i nus pa yod
NK106(me)001:7075: pa ltar gdul bya la sprul pa snang ba'i bsod
NK106(me)001:7077: de gnyis 'dzom dus chu zla 'bad rtsol med par
NK106(me)001:7078: 'char ba ltar gdul bya yod dus ston pa'i zla
NK106(me)001:7079: ba las sprul ba'i gzugs brnyan skad cig kyang mi
NK106(me)001:7082: rgya mtsho chu srin gnas kyi rlabs //
NK106(me)001:7083: dus las yol bar 'gyur yang srid //
NK106(me)001:7084: gdul bar bya ba'i sras rnams la //
NK106(me)001:7085: sangs rgyas dus las yol mi mnga' //
NK106(me)001:7086: zhes pa ltar phyogs bzhi steng 'og dang bcas pa'i
NK106(me)001:7087: 'jig rten gyi khams nam mkha'i mthas klas pa drug
NK106(me)001:7088: gi steng 'og phyogs mtshams dang bcas pa na 'gro
NK106(me)001:7089: ba drug ji snyed yod pa dag rang gi las
NK106(me)001:7090: kyis / mtho ris rnams gyen du mgo bstan nas 'gro ba dang /
NK106(me)001:7092: dmyal ba yi dgas 'thur la bstan nas 'gro ba
NK106(me)001:7093: bde sdug sna tshogs la spyod pa ji snyed pa
NK106(me)001:7094: thams cad kyi don mdzad pa la thub pa grangs
NK106(me)001:7095: med tshad med bsam gyis mi khyab pa snang ba
NK106(me)001:7097: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad las thugs
NK106(me)001:7098: rje chen po'i byin gyis brlabs zhes bya ba'i rig
NK106(me)001:7099: pa'i skyes bu thub pa drug /
NK106(me)001:7100: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje las 'thon to //
NK106(me)001:7101: 'thon nas kyang las kyi dbang gis s+n+rel gzhi dang
NK106(me)001:7102: yan man gyi 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha'
NK106(me)001:7103: yas mu med pa'i stong gsum gyi stong chen po
NK106(me)001:7104: re rer / thub pa chen po bcom ldan 'das
NK106(me)001:7105: re res 'dul ba rnam pa bzhis 'gro ba'i don
NK106(me)001:7107: 'dul ba bzhi ni sku bsod nams chen pos 'dul ba dang /
NK106(me)001:7108: gsung theg pa sna tshogs kyi chos kyis 'dul ba dang /
NK106(me)001:7109: thugs mngon par shes pa chen pos 'dul ba dang /
NK106(me)001:7110: 'phrin las bsam gyis mi khyab pas 'dul ba'o //
NK106(me)001:7111: yon tan ni kun la khyab pas logs su ma bgrangs so //
NK106(me)001:7112: dang po ni mdzad pa bcu gnyis la sogs pas 'dul ba ste /
NK106(me)001:7114: thugs rje chen pos 'jig rten mkhyen //
NK106(me)001:7115: 'jig rten kun la gzigs nas ni //
NK106(me)001:7116: chos kyi sku las ma g.yos par //
NK106(me)001:7117: sprul pa'i rang bzhin sna tshogs kyis //
NK106(me)001:7118: skye ba mngon par skye ba dang //
NK106(me)001:7119: dga' ldan gnas nas 'pho ba dang //
NK106(me)001:7120: lhums su 'jug dang bltams pa dang //
NK106(me)001:7121: bzo yi gnas la mkhas pa dang //
NK106(me)001:7122: btsun mo'i 'khor dgyes rol pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7123: nges 'byung dka' ba spyod pa dang //
NK106(me)001:7124: byang chub snying por gshegs pa dang //
NK106(me)001:7125: bdud sde 'joms dang rdzogs par ni //
NK106(me)001:7126: byang chub chos kyi 'khor lo dang //
NK106(me)001:7127: mya ngan 'das par gshegs mdzad rnams //
NK106(me)001:7128: yongs su ma dag zhing rnams su //
NK106(me)001:7129: srid pa ji srid gnas par ston //
NK106(me)001:7133: 'dul ba'i dbang gis lha dang mi'i theg pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7134: nyan thos kyi theg pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7135: rang byang chub kyi theg pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7136: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7137: bla na med pa'i theg pas ma rig pa'i rnam
NK106(me)001:7138: par rtog pa nyon mongs pa stong phrag brgyad cu
NK106(me)001:7139: rtsa bzhi'i gnyen por chos stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa
NK106(me)001:7142: de'ang sh+aakya thub pa lta bu'i 'khor gyi khyams su
NK106(me)001:7143: gsung dbyangs yan lag drug cus rang rang gi mos
NK106(me)001:7144: pa ci yod pa de 'dra ba gsung gcig las
NK106(me)001:7145: dus gcig tu sems can tha dad kyi bsam pas
NK106(me)001:7146: chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong la sogs
NK106(me)001:7147: pa snga phyi med par sgra brnyan bzhin du thos
NK106(me)001:7148: par 'gyur ro // sprul sku'i gsung ltar snang yang sgra tshig rang mtshan pa med de /
NK106(me)001:7149: gdul bya'i blo dang sangs rgyas kyi byin rlabs las rang snang ba nyid /
NK106(me)001:7151: ji ltar sgra brnyan gyi ni sgra //
NK106(me)001:7152: gzhan gyi rnam rig las byung ba //
NK106(me)001:7153: rnam rtog med cing bzo med pa //
NK106(me)001:7154: phyi dang nang na mi gnas ltar //
NK106(me)001:7155: de ltar de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung //
NK106(me)001:7156: gzhan gyi rnam rig las byung ba //
NK106(me)001:7157: rnam par rtog med bzo med cing //
NK106(me)001:7158: phyi dang nang na gnas ma yin //
NK106(me)001:7160: gsung de nyid gdul bya'i rna bar yan lag drug cu'i dbyangs su thob pa ste /
NK106(me)001:7166: ka la ping+ka lta bu dang /
NK106(me)001:7174: mi mthun pa med pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7177: gang gis mi tshugs pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7181: rnam grangs kyi sgo re re gang byung ba de
NK106(me)001:7182: dang der yan lag kun rdzogs par 'byung ngo zhes
NK106(me)001:7183: so // rtsa ba drug la yan lag bcu bcu 'jug pas drug cur 'gyur ro //
NK106(me)001:7184: de ltar drug cu po rnams kyi rang bzhin bcu ni /
NK106(me)001:7187: de la rang bzhin gang zhe na 'di lta ste /
NK106(me)001:7192: gcig la gzigs pa mnyam pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7198: rang bzhin bcu pa re re la rtsa ba'i drug po bsgres na'ang drug cur 'gyur la /
NK106(me)001:7199: drug cu drug cur bsgres pas dbyangs kyi yan lag
NK106(me)001:7200: stong du 'gyur bas dbyangs kyi yan lag rgya mtsho
NK106(me)001:7201: zhes bya'o // de lta sangs rgyas mchog gi sprul
NK106(me)001:7202: pa'i gzugs brnyan mthong ba yang bee d+aur+ya'i sa gzhi
NK106(me)001:7203: la brgya byin gyi gzugs brnyan snang ba ltar 'gro
NK106(me)001:7204: ba'i las dag pa'i sems snang la snang ba ste
NK106(me)001:7206: ji ltar bee d+aur sa gzhi gtsang ma la //
NK106(me)001:7207: lha dbang lus kyi gzugs brnyan snang ba ltar //
NK106(me)001:7208: de bzhin 'gro sems sa gzhi gtsang ma la //
NK106(me)001:7209: thub pa'i dbang po'i sku yi gzugs brnyan 'char //
NK106(me)001:7210: 'gro bar gzugs brnyan 'char nub rnyog med dang //
NK106(me)001:7211: rnyog pa'i rang sems rab 'jug dbang gis 'jug /
NK106(me)001:7215: dus bzhi kun du mkhyen pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7216: thams cad kyi sems kyi rgyud kun du mkhyen pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7217: rdzu 'phrul gyi spyan gyis thams cad kun du gzigs pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7218: rdzu 'phrul gyi snyan gyis kun du gsan pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7219: rdzu 'phrul gyi tshogs kun du don spyod pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7220: zag pa med pa'i kun du bzang po'i spyod pa
NK106(me)001:7221: yongs su rdzogs pa'i mngon par shes pa chen po
NK106(me)001:7223: de'ang gzigs pa lha'i mig gi mngon shes /
NK106(me)001:7224: gsan pa rna ba'i mngon shes /
NK106(me)001:7226: gzhan gyi sems shes pa'i mngon shes /
NK106(me)001:7227: dus bzhi mkhyen pa tshe rabs du ma dran pas sngon gyi gnas dran pa'i mngon shes /
NK106(me)001:7228: rdzu 'phrul gang gis 'gro ba 'dul ba der ston
NK106(me)001:7229: pa rdzu 'phrul gyi mngon shes dang drug gi rim
NK106(me)001:7230: pa thams cad thugs kyi rjes su 'gro zhing mkhyen
NK106(me)001:7231: nas don mdzad pas thugs kyis 'dul ba yin no
NK106(me)001:7234: kun du sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7235: kun du thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7236: kun du zhal bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7237: kun du gsung bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7238: bsam gyis mi khyab pa grangs med pa phyogs bcur snang bar gyur to zhes so //
NK106(me)001:7239: de'ang de lta bu'i sku gsung thugs kyi rim pa
NK106(me)001:7240: re re'ang bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i tshogs can gyis
NK106(me)001:7241: phyogs bcu'i zhing khams thams cad khyab par don mdzad
NK106(me)001:7242: pa'o // de'ang sku gsung thugs gsum gyis dngos su don mdzad pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7243: 'phrin las kyis dngos dang brgyud pa thams cad nas mdzad pas tha dad du bshad pa yin no //
NK106(me)001:7244: sprul pa dang yang sprul bshad pa ni /
NK106(me)001:7245: de ltar 'gro ba'i khams drug tu don mdzad pa'i thub pa drug smos pa /
NK106(me)001:7246: de yang gtso bo'i grangs te sprul pa dang //
NK106(me)001:7247: yang sprul rnams ni bsam gyis mi khyab ste //
NK106(me)001:7248: lha yi gnas su'ang gnas ris so so ru //
NK106(me)001:7249: tshangs dang dbang phyug 'og min par snyed du //
NK106(me)001:7250: rang rang 'dul byed ston pa'i tshul rnams snang //
NK106(me)001:7251: thub pa drug ces smos pa ni sems can gyi
NK106(me)001:7252: rigs drug tu 'dus pa 'dul ba la dgongs la
NK106(me)001:7253: / dbang po brgya byin la sogs pa'i ming drug ni mtshon pa tsam ste /
NK106(me)001:7255: sprul pa des kyang yang sems can gyi ngor sprul pa bkye ba tshad med pas don mdzad de /
NK106(me)001:7256: lha'i gnas su'ang rgyal chen bzhi nas 'og min gyi
NK106(me)001:7257: bar lha gnas so so'i gtso bos 'dul bar byed
NK106(me)001:7258: la / gang la gang 'dul du bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:7260: mi la'ang gang 'dul de la der snang ste //
NK106(me)001:7261: nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK106(me)001:7262: rgyal po la sogs sprul nas mi rnams 'dul //
NK106(me)001:7263: lha min gnas su'ang so so'i 'dul byed dang //
NK106(me)001:7264: dud 'gro'i ris su'ang bya la byar snang zhing //
NK106(me)001:7265: ri dgas rnams la seng ge mchog la sogs //
NK106(me)001:7266: so so'i 'dul byed ston pa bsam mi khyab //
NK106(me)001:7267: de bzhin yi dgas dmyal ba'i 'jig rten du //
NK106(me)001:7268: rang rang mthun pa'i gzugs kyis don mdzad do //
NK106(me)001:7269: 'di ltar mi'i 'jig rten du'ang thub pa gcig pur ma zad de /
NK106(me)001:7272: bud med la sogs pa tshad med pas 'dul zhing /
NK106(me)001:7273: thub pa gcig pus kyang nyan thos dang /
NK106(me)001:7275: rgyal po la sogs par sprul nas don mdzad pa bzhin no //
NK106(me)001:7276: de bzhin du dud 'gro la yang byas 'dul ba la bya //
NK106(me)001:7277: ri dgas kyis 'dul ba la seng ge la sogs pa'o //
NK106(me)001:7278: dmyal ba dang yi dgas na'ang de dang mtshungs te
NK106(me)001:7279: sems can gyis gar khyab tu sangs rgyas kyi sprul
NK106(me)001:7283: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sprul pa ni tshad med de
NK106(me)001:7284: 'gro ba gang dang gang gis 'dul ba de dang
NK106(me)001:7285: de'i gzugs dang kha dog dang ming gis don mdzad
NK106(me)001:7287: dbang sgyur gyi gnas su ni lha'i bdag po dbang
NK106(me)001:7288: sgyur du sprul nas dge ba bcu'i las kyi lam
NK106(me)001:7289: yang dag par len du 'jug go zhes pa nas
NK106(me)001:7293: dmyal ba pa'i gzugs kyis 'dul ba rnams la'ang de'i gzugs su sprul zhing don mdzad do zhes so //
NK106(me)001:7294: ye shes kyis don mdzad tshul la'ang gnyis kyi /
NK106(me)001:7295: so sor don mdzad tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:7297: de ltar 'gro 'dul rnams la ye shes gnyis //
NK106(me)001:7298: ji lta ji snyed mkhyen pa'i rnam pa ste //
NK106(me)001:7299: chos nyid dang ni chos can ma 'dres par //
NK106(me)001:7300: so sor mkhyen nas gdul bya'i don gnyis mdzad //
NK106(me)001:7301: 'gro ba 'dul ba dang mchog gi sprul pa'i ye shes ni //
NK106(me)001:7302: chos nyid la ltos te ji lta ba dang /
NK106(me)001:7303: chos can la ltos te ji snyed pa mkhyen pa ste /
NK106(me)001:7306: ji lta'i ye shes stong pa'i dngos mkhyen nas //
NK106(me)001:7307: 'gro la nye bar zhi ba'i chos ston zhing //
NK106(me)001:7308: ji snyed ye shes sems dang dbang po sogs //
NK106(me)001:7309: ma 'dres mkhyen nas chos tshul bsam yas ston //
NK106(me)001:7310: de'ang chos nyid stong pa'i ngo bo nyid du mkhyen
NK106(me)001:7311: nas sems can rnams la rang bzhin gyis ma skyes
NK106(me)001:7314: kye sems can dag tshur shog /
NK106(me)001:7315: chos thams cad ni rang bzhin gyis ma skyes pa
NK106(me)001:7316: ste khyed ci zhig gis nyon mongs pa zhes chos
NK106(me)001:7317: ston cing stong pa nyid la so sor rtog la
NK106(me)001:7318: zhes so // ji snyed pas gdul bya'i khams dang
NK106(me)001:7319: dbang po dang bag la nyal thams cad gzigs nas
NK106(me)001:7320: de dang mthun pa'i chos ston pa ste /
NK106(me)001:7322: ngas sems can gyi khams la rnam par gzigs nas
NK106(me)001:7323: sems can kun nas nyon mongs pa can de dag
NK106(me)001:7324: gi nyon mongs pa rab tu gdul ba'i phyir chos
NK106(me)001:7325: bstan to zhes pa la sogs pa'o //
NK106(me)001:7326: ma dag pa'i 'gro la snang tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:7327: de ltar thub pa drug gis sprul pa /
NK106(me)001:7328: 'di ni ma dag 'gro la snang ba ste //
NK106(me)001:7329: zhing ni 'gro drug 'jig rten drug rnams su //
NK106(me)001:7330: ston pa 'gro 'dul rang snang mthun pa yis //
NK106(me)001:7331: chos ni ma nges theg pa sna tshogs nyid //
NK106(me)001:7332: dus ni gdul bya'i skal pa mtshungs par nang //
NK106(me)001:7333: de yang sprul sku'i gnas ni sems can gyi snang ba'i gnas gang yin par /
NK106(me)001:7334: ston pa de'i snang ba dang mthun pas /
NK106(me)001:7335: chos kyang sems can gyi blo rtog dang dbang po
NK106(me)001:7336: tha dad pa'i dbang gis theg pa sna tshogs su
NK106(me)001:7337: ston pa gnas dang 'khor rnams tshogs pa'i dus der
NK106(me)001:7339: sprul pa'i sku yis 'dul ba'i zhing khams ni //
NK106(me)001:7340: dzam+bu'i gling ni bye ba phrag brgya sogs //
NK106(me)001:7341: rang byung ye shes thugs rjes rgyud drug 'dul //
NK106(me)001:7343: 'dod chags 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK106(me)001:7344: 'dul ba nyi khri chig stong gsungs pa yin //
NK106(me)001:7345: zhe sdang 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK106(me)001:7346: mdo sde nyi khri chig stong gsungs pa yin //
NK106(me)001:7347: gti mug 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK106(me)001:7348: mngon pa'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK106(me)001:7349: dug gsum cha mnyam 'dul ba'i gnyen po ru //
NK106(me)001:7350: sde snod gsum mnyam nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK106(me)001:7351: spyi ru brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs pa yang //
NK106(me)001:7352: dug gsum gnyen pos 'dul phyir gsungs pa yin //
NK106(me)001:7354: ma dag pa'i snang ba la shar tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:7356: de ltar 'gro drug 'jig rten drug po yang //
NK106(me)001:7357: las dang bag chags dge sdig rgyu 'bras kyis //
NK106(me)001:7358: bde sdug mtho dman rnam pa sna tshogs nyid //
NK106(me)001:7359: ston pa drug kyang 'gro sems rang snang ste //
NK106(me)001:7360: rmi lam nang gi sangs rgyas sems can bzhin //
NK106(me)001:7361: ngo bo dag kyang rnam pa ma dag pas //
NK106(me)001:7362: sna tshogs snang la thugs rje'i rol par shar //
NK106(me)001:7363: 'gro ba'i las dang bag chags dge bas mtho ris dang /
NK106(me)001:7364: mi dge bas ngan song du 'khor zhing bde sdug
NK106(me)001:7365: sna tshogs su myong ba rmi lam nang gi snang
NK106(me)001:7366: ba lta bu 'di ni ma rig pa'i gnyid sangs
NK106(me)001:7367: pa'i sangs rgyas kyi byin rlabs dang /
NK106(me)001:7368: rang rang gi dge ba'i las kyi snang ba la
NK106(me)001:7369: sangs rgyas kyi sprul pa thub pa bcom ldan la
NK106(me)001:7370: sogs pas don mdzad pa de yang rmi lam lta
NK106(me)001:7371: bu ste / sems can gyi rang snang las don
NK106(me)001:7372: la ma grub pa nyid rmi lam du sprul pa
NK106(me)001:7373: bkye ba bzhin snang ba yin te /
NK106(me)001:7375: ngas ni rmi lam lta bu'i 'gro ba las //
NK106(me)001:7376: rmi lam lta bur sprul nas chos bstan yang //
NK106(me)001:7377: ngo bo med de rang bzhin gnyis med med //
NK106(me)001:7378: bdag med stong pa gsog tu rig par bya //
NK106(me)001:7382: chos thams cad rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu /
NK106(me)001:7383: mya ngan las 'das pa yang rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu zhes so //
NK106(me)001:7384: 'khrul snang gi snod bcud brdzun pa ltar de la snang ba'i sangs rgyas la sogs pa'ang brdzun la /
NK106(me)001:7385: yod pa ma yin pa ste med bzhin snang ba'i
NK106(me)001:7386: phyir rmi lam gyi sangs rgyas dang sems can bzhin
NK106(me)001:7387: no // des na 'khor 'das rmi lam lta bur
NK106(me)001:7388: snang dus 'dir ngo bo ye nas dag pa'i sangs
NK106(me)001:7389: no // rgyas yin yang / rnam pa 'gro drug gi sems can dang /
NK106(me)001:7390: de 'dul ba'i ston pa'ang de dag gi gzugs ngan pa la sogs par snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)001:7391: snang yang dbyings gcig gdod nas dag pas gnyis su med pa ste /
NK106(me)001:7392: chos thams cad 'byung ba med pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:7393: sangs rgyas med cing chos dang dge 'dun med //
NK106(me)001:7394: de ltar sus shes de ni mkhas pa yin //
NK106(me)001:7395: sems can rang bzhin byang chub nyid du gsungs //
NK106(me)001:7396: byang chub rang bzhin sems can thams cad de //
NK106(me)001:7397: sems can rnams dang byang chub gnyis ma yin //
NK106(me)001:7398: de ltar sus shes skyes bu mchog tu 'gyur //
NK106(me)001:7400: de lta bu'i sems can la sangs rgyas kyi thugs
NK106(me)001:7401: rjes gzigs pa yang gdul bya dang 'dul byed du
NK106(me)001:7403: log rtog bag chags dang bcas pa dag nas dbyings
NK106(me)001:7404: su zhi ba brnyes kyang ye shes brtse ba chen
NK106(me)001:7405: pos sems can thams cad sa ler gzigs nas /
NK106(me)001:7406: don med pa la bdag tu gzung bas 'khrul pa
NK106(me)001:7407: rnams snying rje'i yul du dgongs te thabs kyis 'dren
NK106(me)001:7408: zhing lhun gyis grub pa'i mdzad pa yang 'bad rtsol
NK106(me)001:7409: med par rang gis 'byung ba'i nus pa ye ldan
NK106(me)001:7410: du shar bas don mdzad pa nyid /
NK106(me)001:7412: log par rtog brtags rnam dag cing //
NK106(me)001:7413: ye shes dbyings las mi gzhan phyir //
NK106(me)001:7414: thugs rje chen pos 'brel bas na //
NK106(me)001:7415: 'gro drug dus gnas ma lus snang //
NK106(me)001:7417: de dag kyang tshad med pa'i thugs rjer ldan pa ni /
NK106(me)001:7418: sprul pa'i sku chen po rnam pa drug po /
NK106(me)001:7419: 'di ni tshad med thugs rje'i sprul pa yin //
NK106(me)001:7420: srid pa ji srid 'phrin las rgyun mi 'chad //
NK106(me)001:7421: dbyings kyi ngang nas ye shes kyi ngo bo tshad
NK106(me)001:7422: med pa'i thugs rje'i byin rlabs las rang snang ba'i
NK106(me)001:7423: sprul pas sems can gyi don mdzad pa de yang
NK106(me)001:7427: dus la bab pa na bsnyel ba mi mnga' bar
NK106(me)001:7428: 'dul bas don mdzad pa yang 'bad rtsol med par
NK106(me)001:7429: chu zla snang ba ltar 'byung ste /
NK106(me)001:7431: gdul bya'i khams dang gdul ba'i thabs dang ni //
NK106(me)001:7432: gdul bya'i khams kyis 'dul ba'i bya ba dang //
NK106(me)001:7433: de yi yul dang dus su gshegs pa la //
NK106(me)001:7434: khyab bdag rtag tu lhun gyis grub par 'jug /
NK106(me)001:7436: de'ang ngan song ba dag mtho ris la bkod nas thar pa'i sar 'dren pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7437: mtho ris pa dag gi'ang gnod 'tshe skyob cing phan bde mdzad nas thar pa la dgod pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7438: lam lam zhugs pa rnams 'jug pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7439: zhugs pa rnams gong nas gong du yon tan la spyor ba dang /
NK106(me)001:7440: sa bcu'i rjes la sangs rgyas la dgod pa ste /
NK106(me)001:7441: mdor na sems can la ji lta bus skad cig
NK106(me)001:7442: tsam bde bar 'gyur ba de yang mdzad nas rim
NK106(me)001:7443: gyis byang chub gsum la so so'i skal pa ji
NK106(me)001:7445: 'khor ba nas 'dren zhing sdug bsngal las skyob pa'i
NK106(me)001:7446: 'phrin las 'khor ba ji srid ma stongs kyi bar
NK106(me)001:7447: du dngos dang brgyud nas mdzad de /
NK106(me)001:7452: rnam pa ni dpe dgus mtshon pa ste /
NK106(me)001:7453: brgya byin mthong dus snon pa skye ba ltar sangs
NK106(me)001:7454: rgyas mthong nas sems dang bas smon zhing tshogs gnyis
NK106(me)001:7455: spyod pa dang / lha'i rnga sgras bag med pa
NK106(me)001:7456: las slong zhing 'jigs pa sel ba ltar chos kyi
NK106(me)001:7457: rnga sgras bag med pa dang 'khor ba'i 'jigs pa
NK106(me)001:7458: spyod pa dang / sel ba dang / sprin ltar
NK106(me)001:7459: chos char 'bebs pas rgyud kyi dge ba spel ba
NK106(me)001:7460: spyod pa dang / sel ba dang / dang /
NK106(me)001:7461: tshangs pa gnas las ma bskyod par lha'i gnas su
NK106(me)001:7462: snang ba ltar chos sku las ma g.yos bzhin du
NK106(me)001:7463: gzugs skus don mdzad pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7464: nyi ma ltar gdul bya'i pad+mo 'dzum zhing mun pa sel ba dang /
NK106(me)001:7465: nor bu ltar rnam par mi rtog pas gzhan don mdzad pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7466: sgra brnyan ltar dbyings gcig drug cur go bas don
NK106(me)001:7467: mdzad dus nyid nas sgra tshig tu med pa dang
NK106(me)001:7468: / nam mkha' ltar rang bzhin spros pa med pa'i
NK106(me)001:7469: chos kyi skus 'char gzhi'i go phye bas don mdzad
NK106(me)001:7470: / pa dang / sa ltar 'gro ba'i dge ba'i
NK106(me)001:7471: lo thog thams cad 'phel ba'i don mdzad pa ste
NK106(me)001:7473: gang zhig brgya byin rnga dang sprin bzhin dang //
NK106(me)001:7474: tshangs nyi rin chen yid bzhin nor rgyal bzhin //
NK106(me)001:7475: sgra brnyan nam mkha' sa bzhin srid pa'i bar //
NK106(me)001:7476: 'bad med gzhan don byed de rnal 'byor rigs //
NK106(me)001:7477: rin chen lha dbang snang bzhin ston pa ste //
NK106(me)001:7478: legs par 'doms mdzad lha yi rnga dang 'dra //
NK106(me)001:7479: khyab bdag mkhyen dang brtse chen sprin tshogs ni //
NK106(me)001:7480: mtha' yas 'gro ba srid rtse'i bar du khyab //
NK106(me)001:7481: tshangs bzhin zag med gnas las mi bskyod par //
NK106(me)001:7482: sprul pa rnam pa du ma rab tu ston //
NK106(me)001:7483: nyi bzhin ye shes snang ba rab spro gang //
NK106(me)001:7484: rnam dag rin chen yid bzhin nor 'dra'i thugs //
NK106(me)001:7485: rgyal ba rnams kyi gsung de brag ca bzhin du yi ge med //
NK106(me)001:7486: sku ni nam mkha' lta bur khyab dang gzugs med rtag pa nyid //
NK106(me)001:7487: sa bzhin 'gro ba'i dkar po'i chos kyi sman rnams ma lus pa'i //
NK106(me)001:7488: rnam pa kun tu gzhir gyur pa ni sangs rgyas sa yin no //
NK106(me)001:7490: sna tshogs sprul sku la gsum las /
NK106(me)001:7491: bzo sprul pas 'gro don phum sum tshogs par mdzad tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:7492: sprul pa'i sku gsum pa ni bems por snang bas
NK106(me)001:7493: don mdzad pa sangs rgyas kyi byin gyis brlabs kyis
NK106(me)001:7494: sprul pa dang / 'gro 'dul la sogs pas de ltar sprul pa yin no zhes bshad pa yang /
NK106(me)001:7495: 'gro 'dul sprul pa'i dus dang ye shes kyis don
NK106(me)001:7496: mdzad pa nam mkha' lta bu'i phrin las phun sum
NK106(me)001:7497: tshogs pa / de nyid ngang las sna tshogs sprul pa'i sku //
NK106(me)001:7498: sems med bems po'i tshul gyis snang ba ste //
NK106(me)001:7499: ris su bris dang 'bur dang rang byon dang //
NK106(me)001:7500: yi ge la sogs mchod pa'i rten dang ni //
NK106(me)001:7501: pad+ma dpag bsam shing dang skyed mos tshal //
NK106(me)001:7502: khang bzangs mchog dang kun dag'i ra ba dang //
NK106(me)001:7503: sprul pa'i grong dang gru gzings zam pa dang //
NK106(me)001:7504: mar me nor bu zas gos bzhon pa sogs //
NK106(me)001:7505: 'gro ba'i don mang byed pa'i bems por snang //
NK106(me)001:7506: ji ltar 'jig rten gyi khams na sangs rgyas kyi
NK106(me)001:7507: rnam par 'phrul pa'i skus don mdzad pa'i bye brag
NK106(me)001:7508: la / ris su bris pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7510: sku gsung thugs kyi rten rang byon du snang ba dang /
NK106(me)001:7512: lha dang mchod rten la sogs pa gang zhig mthong
NK106(me)001:7513: ba tsam gyis dang ba'i gdung shugs g.yo bas thar
NK106(me)001:7515: des mtshon nas de 'dra'i rten gyi rnam pa thams
NK106(me)001:7516: cad kyis 'gro ba'i rgyud la dge ba spel bas
NK106(me)001:7517: sangs rgyas kyi sprul par bsdu ste /
NK106(me)001:7519: da ni snyigs ma'i dus kyi tshe //
NK106(me)001:7520: bzo dang yi ge'i gzugs su 'dug /
NK106(me)001:7521: nga yin snyam du dad par byos //
NK106(me)001:7524: bzo dang skye dang byang chub che //
NK106(me)001:7525: mya ngan 'das pa rtag ston pas //
NK106(me)001:7526: sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku 'di ni //
NK106(me)001:7527: rnam par grol ba'i thabs chen no //
NK106(me)001:7529: bzo ni bzo'i rnam par snang ba bshad ma thag pa rnams so //
NK106(me)001:7530: skye ba ni sems can la dngos su phan pa de'i lus su sprul pa ste /
NK106(me)001:7531: mu ge'i tshe nya po che dang /
NK106(me)001:7532: nad kyi tshe srog chags des pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7533: srin mo'i gling du rta'i rgyal po ba la ha la sogs par sprul nas don mdzad pa'o //
NK106(me)001:7534: mchog gi sprul pa ni mdzad pa bcu gnyis ston pa'o //
NK106(me)001:7539: rab tu byung ba'i kun dga' ra ba dang /
NK106(me)001:7540: tshong pa mya ngam gyi thang la 'khyams dus grong khyer du sprul pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7541: chu chen po la gru dang gzings dang zam par sprul pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7542: gsang chen thabs mkhas las nags su mtshan mo lam
NK106(me)001:7543: 'khyams pa'i tshong pa la sgron mar sprul nas lam
NK106(me)001:7545: mu ge'i tshe nor bur sprul nas kha zas la sogs pa'i char phab pa dang /
NK106(me)001:7546: shing rta'ang glang po che la sogs pa bzhon par
NK106(me)001:7547: sprul nas sems can la gang la gang phan kho
NK106(me)001:7548: na bsgrub pa ni dkon mchog brtsegs pa la sogs
NK106(me)001:7549: pa'i mdo sde rnams las gsungs shing /
NK106(me)001:7551: ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i yul la 'jug pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)001:7553: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gser gyi kha dog tu
NK106(me)001:7554: mthong bas gdul bar bya ba yin na gser gyi
NK106(me)001:7555: kha dog tu snang ngo zhes pa nas /
NK106(me)001:7560: nye bar mkho dgu'i yo byad du snang bas gdul
NK106(me)001:7561: bar bya ba yin na de dang de'i gzugs dang
NK106(me)001:7562: kha dog tu snang ngo zhes rgya cher gsungs te
NK106(me)001:7563: / gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi mngon mtho nges legs lhun grub tu 'byung tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:7565: gnas skabs dga' skyid bde ba'i gnas mdzad nas //
NK106(me)001:7566: mthar thug zhi ba'i lam la 'god pas na //
NK106(me)001:7567: sna tshogs sprul pas 'gro don lhun gyis grub //
NK106(me)001:7568: sprul pa'i rol pa des kyang gnas skabs su sems can so so'i yid dga' ba dang /
NK106(me)001:7569: lus dang ngag bde bas skyid par mdzad pa'i mthar
NK106(me)001:7570: sangs rgyas kyi sa la sbyor bas na sna tshogs
NK106(me)001:7571: sprul pa'i sku yang don dang mdzad pa shin tu
NK106(me)001:7572: chen po lhun gyis grub pa ste /
NK106(me)001:7574: snang ba de ni shin tu yang //
NK106(me)001:7575: rtog pa med cing g.yo ba med //
NK106(me)001:7576: de lta mod kyi sa steng na //
NK106(me)001:7577: don chen gyis ni nye bar gnas //
NK106(me)001:7579: spyi don gsum pa de dag dbyings las byung zhing dbyings su thim pas mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK106(me)001:7580: da ni sku de dag gi bya ba dang mdzad
NK106(me)001:7581: pa dbyings las byung zhing dbyings su thim pa'i tshul
NK106(me)001:7584: gdul bya med na 'dul byed dbyings su nub //
NK106(me)001:7585: rang snang longs sku chos sku'i ngang du thim //
NK106(me)001:7586: chu snod med na chu zla mkha' la thim //
NK106(me)001:7587: tshes kyi dbang gis zla ba dbyings su nub //
NK106(me)001:7588: gnam gang zla ba 'phel 'grib med pa bzhin //
NK106(me)001:7589: gdul bya yod na sngon bzhin rim gyis snang //
NK106(me)001:7590: 'di ni 'bras bu lhun gyis grub pa yin //
NK106(me)001:7591: ji ltar chu snod med dus zla ba'i ngang du
NK106(me)001:7592: chu zla'i gzugs brnyan rang thim pa ltar gdul bya'i
NK106(me)001:7593: chu snod med na de'i ngor snang ba'i sangs rgyas
NK106(me)001:7594: sprul sku'i zla gzugs rang snang longs sku'i ngang tsam
NK106(me)001:7595: las med pas der thim pa'o zhes btags kyang gcig
NK106(me)001:7596: nas 'ongs te gcig tu thim pa ltar ma yin
NK106(me)001:7597: no // zla ba'ang gnam gang gi tshe na nang
NK106(me)001:7598: gsal du thim pa ltar rang snang ga longs sku'ang
NK106(me)001:7599: nang gsal chos sku'i dbyings su thim pas ye shes
NK106(me)001:7600: shes dbyings su 'khyil ba zhes bya'o //
NK106(me)001:7601: de'i tshe so so rang rig pa'i ye shes nyid
NK106(me)001:7602: phra ba'i ye shes su gyur pas shin tu mnyam
NK106(me)001:7603: par gzhag pa'i gnas skabs so //
NK106(me)001:7604: dbu ma las de'i tshe 'jug pa chos kyi dbyings
NK106(me)001:7605: su zhi bas gang du'ang dmigs su med pa 'gog
NK106(me)001:7606: pa dam pa'i ngang la mnyam par gzhag pa'o zhes
NK106(me)001:7607: 'dod la / rgyud bla ma la sogs pa nas mnyam par gzhag pa'i ye shes zhes 'dod do //
NK106(me)001:7608: yang gdul bya yod na g.yo ba dang 'bad pa'i
NK106(me)001:7609: rtsol ba med par skad cig gis phyi gsal du
NK106(me)001:7610: rang snang ba longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang sprul
NK106(me)001:7611: pa'i sku rnams snga phyi med par don mdzad pa
NK106(me)001:7612: snga ma bzhin mi rtog pa'i ngang nas 'byung ngo
NK106(me)001:7613: // 'di la dbu ma nas sngon gyi smon lam las gzhan snang du don mdzad ces 'dod la /
NK106(me)001:7614: rgyud bla ma la sogs pa nas rjes thob tu
NK106(me)001:7615: don mdzad kyang mnyam gzhag gi ngo bo las ma
NK106(me)001:7618: mi rtog pa dang de yi ni //
NK106(me)001:7619: rjes thob de ni ye shes 'dod //
NK106(me)001:7621: byang chub sems dpa'i tshul 'di ni //
NK106(me)001:7622: rjes thob de bzhin gshegs rnams dang //
NK106(me)001:7623: sems can yang dag sgrol ba la //
NK106(me)001:7624: 'jig rten na ni mnyam pa nyid //
NK106(me)001:7625: de lta mod kyi sa rdul dang //
NK106(me)001:7626: rgya mtsho ba lang rmig rjes kyi //
NK106(me)001:7627: khyad par gang yin sangs rgyas dang //
NK106(me)001:7628: byang chub sems dpa'i khyad de nyid //
NK106(me)001:7630: spyi don bzhi pa skabs kyi dge ba bsngo ba ni /
NK106(me)001:7631: da ni dge ba sems can gyi phyir bsngo ba ni /
NK106(me)001:7633: de ltar zhi ba mchog gi rang bzhin gyis //
NK106(me)001:7634: 'gro kun sems nyid 'od gsal dbyings gzhol te //
NK106(me)001:7635: srid zhi'i mthar 'dzin nyes cha'i dri ma yis //
NK106(me)001:7636: dub pa'i sems nyid di ring ngal sos shig /
NK106(me)001:7638: snying po'i de kho na nyid kyi dge bas 'gro
NK106(me)001:7639: ba thams cad srid zhi'i mthar 'dzin pas dub pa'i
NK106(me)001:7640: sems nyid thams cad mkhyen pa'i bde ba tshad med
NK106(me)001:7641: pas dbang 'byor ba'i sa la ngal sos shig ces
NK106(me)001:7642: pa'o // rab dkar ku mu ta rnams rgyas byed pa //
NK106(me)001:7643: ston ka'i mtshan mo dkar ba'i zla gzugs bzhin //
NK106(me)001:7644: dge ba rab mchog nyon mongs gdung sel bas //
NK106(me)001:7645: 'gro kun sems kyi rnyog pa zhi bar shog /
NK106(me)001:7646: nyon mongs mtsho sngon sdug bsngal dbu phreng can //
NK106(me)001:7647: nyes cha'i bzhad rnams lding ba gang yin pa //
NK106(me)001:7648: sems dge'i 'od stong shar bas rab bskams te //
NK106(me)001:7649: rgyal ba'i 'byor pas yongs gang mthong bar shog /
NK106(me)001:7650: sems kyi rab rib glo bur sgrib pa'i sprin //
NK106(me)001:7651: kun sbyor 'ching ba'i rnam 'gros rab brtan pa //
NK106(me)001:7652: ye shes rlung gis phyogs bcur gtor byas te //
NK106(me)001:7653: 'od gsal byang chub nyi ma mthong bar shog /
NK106(me)001:7654: rdzogs pa chen po sems nyid ngal gso las /
NK106(me)001:7655: 'bras bu lhun grub chen po'i le'u ste bcu gsum pa'i 'grel pa'o ////
NK106(me)001:7656: yongs su rdzogs pa mjug gi don la lnga ste /
