NK106(me)001:7657: legs par bshad pa'i dge ba rgya cher bsngo ba ni /
NK106(me)001:7658: de ltar tshig don mtha' dag gi rim pa legs par gtan la phab zin nas /
NK106(me)001:7659: da ni bstan bcos yongs su rdzogs pa'i skabs las /
NK106(me)001:7660: gzhan don du bsod nams bsngo ba ni /
NK106(me)001:7661: thog mar mtshan bshad pa nas brtsams te /
NK106(me)001:7662: 'bras bu mthar thug pa'i don bshad pa'i bar gyi tshig don bkod legs pa /
NK106(me)001:7663: de ltar legs bshad bsod nams sprin chen las //
NK106(me)001:7664: zhi bde'i rang bzhin char gyi tshogs mang pos //
NK106(me)001:7665: sa gsum 'gro ba'i dge legs rab rgyas te //
NK106(me)001:7666: rgyal ba'i 'byor tshogs lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK106(me)001:7668: rab tu yangs shing dri ma med pa'i yid mkhar /
NK106(me)001:7669: legs par bshad pa'i sprin phung chen po /
NK106(me)001:7672: sgom pa las byung ba'i shes rab kyi 'brug stong sgrogs shing /
NK106(me)001:7675: man ngag gi glog phreng bzang po 'gyu ba las 'thon pa'i /
NK106(me)001:7676: zhi bde'i dge ba char gyi tshogs bsil bar 'bab pas /
NK106(me)001:7679: gzugs med pa'i sems can gyi sems kyis gzhi chos
NK106(me)001:7680: khams dge ba snying po'i sa bon can gyi rgyud
NK106(me)001:7681: brlan pas / ches cher gong du 'phel ba'i nus
NK106(me)001:7682: pa mthar phyin pa sangs rgyas kyi byang chub sku
NK106(me)001:7683: gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i yon
NK106(me)001:7684: tan dang 'phrin las chen pos mnga' dbang rdzogs par
NK106(me)001:7686: brtsam dgos pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK106(me)001:7687: brtsams pa'i tshul brjod pa ni /
NK106(me)001:7689: ding sang phal gyi blo mig ma dag pas //
NK106(me)001:7690: sngags dang pha rol phyin gzhung so so'i lam //
NK106(me)001:7691: 'gal bar 'dzin pas gcig tu sdud mi shes //
NK106(me)001:7692: de phyir de dag phyogs re'i mig can yin //
NK106(me)001:7693: sngon gyi mkhas grub chen po rnams ni gshegs la /
NK106(me)001:7694: de dag gi gzhung lugs chen po rnams kyang ring
NK106(me)001:7695: zhig nas rang rang gi don rtog gis dkrugs pas
NK106(me)001:7697: sngags kyi rgyud sde chen po rnams dang /
NK106(me)001:7698: pha rol tu phyin pa'i gzhung so so'i lam gyi dgongs pa shin tu barlinga bas /
NK106(me)001:7699: mang du ma thos shing rtog ge'i ngan rtog tsam
NK106(me)001:7700: gyis dkrugs nas blun po mkhas pa'i mngon rlom can
NK106(me)001:7702: dgongs pa zab mo rnams gcig tu bsdu bar mi shes pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)001:7703: cung zad re'i tshig tsam lhur len pas phyogs re'i mi gcan du gyur pa yin no //
NK106(me)001:7704: mdo sngags gnyis kyi gzhi lam 'bras bu'i don ma nor bar bstan tshul ni /
NK106(me)001:7707: 'dir ni rgyu 'bras theg pa'i zab don mchog /
NK106(me)001:7708: gcig tu bsdus nas nyams su len pa'i thabs //
NK106(me)001:7709: gangs ri thod dkar o rgyan rdzong gnas su //
NK106(me)001:7710: dri med 'od zer shar bas legs par bkod //
NK106(me)001:7711: bstan bcos 'dir ni rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa'i
NK106(me)001:7712: nges don gzhi lam 'bras bu dang bcas pa dang
NK106(me)001:7713: / 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi theg pa'i gzhi lam 'bras bu'i don rnams /
NK106(me)001:7718: man ngag gi gnas bstan pa las ji skad 'byung ba dang /
NK106(me)001:7719: bla ma dam pa las 'ongs pa'i zab mo'i de
NK106(me)001:7720: kho na nyid kyi don rnams gcig tu bsdus te
NK106(me)001:7721: / gangs ri thod dkar gyi mgul o rgyan rdzong gi grub gnas dam par bkod pa yin no //
NK106(me)001:7722: ri de yang 'on cang rdo bkra shis dge 'phel
NK106(me)001:7723: gyi gtsug lag khang gi byang char na yod de
NK106(me)001:7724: / sngon gangs ri'i ze bas brgyan zhing zla ba'i gos dkar gyis g.yogs pa 'dra ba las /
NK106(me)001:7725: dus kyi dbang gis ding sang ni rtse mo brag ri'i ra bas mdzes pa'o //
NK106(me)001:7726: ngogs rnams sman ljongs dang chu gtsang 'bab pa /
NK106(me)001:7727: me tog dang sman dri zhim po rgyas pa'i lho
NK106(me)001:7728: phyogs na rgya shug gi nags tshal ljang gu rma
NK106(me)001:7729: bya'i mgrin pa 'dra bas brgyan pa'i mthongs na /
NK106(me)001:7730: grub pas brten pa'i nags khrod rang byung pad+mas byin
NK106(me)001:7731: gyis brlabs pas o rgyan rdzong zhes btags pa gang
NK106(me)001:7732: yin pa'o // bstan bcos 'di yang snying po'i don
NK106(me)001:7733: gcig tu nges pa bstan pa'i mdzod kyi nor bu
NK106(me)001:7734: yin pas spyi bos blang bar rigs te /
NK106(me)001:7736: de ltar yid ches lung dang rigs pa la //
NK106(me)001:7737: brten nas bdag nyid 'ba' zhig dag phyir dang //
NK106(me)001:7738: gang dag mos dge phun tshogs dang ldan blo //
NK106(me)001:7739: de dag rjes su gzung phyir 'di bshad do //
NK106(me)001:7740: ji ltar sgron glog nor bu nyi zla la //
NK106(me)001:7741: brten nas mig dang ldan pas blta ba bzhin //
NK106(me)001:7742: de bzhin don chen chos spobs 'od mdzad pa //
NK106(me)001:7743: thub la brten nas 'di ni rab tu bshad //
NK106(me)001:7744: gang zhig don ldan chos dang nyer 'brel zhing //
NK106(me)001:7745: khams gsum kun nas nyon mongs srong byed gsung //
NK106(me)001:7746: zhi ba'i phan yon ston par mdzad pa gang //
NK106(me)001:7747: de ni drang srong gsung yin bzlog pa gzhan //
NK106(me)001:7748: gang zhig rgyal ba ston pa 'ba' zhig gi //
NK106(me)001:7749: dbang byas rnam g.yeng med yid can gyis bshad //
NK106(me)001:7750: thar pa thob pa'i lam dang rjes mthun pa //
NK106(me)001:7751: de yang drang srong bka' bzhin spyi bos blang //
NK106(me)001:7753: dge ba rgya cher spel phyir shis brjod kyi rgyan dgod pa ni /
NK106(me)001:7754: de ltar lung dang rigs pa'i rjes su 'brangs te
NK106(me)001:7755: phyin ci ma log par mthong ba'i blo gros kyis
NK106(me)001:7756: / legs par bshad pa'i rgyam mtsho rmad du byung ba'i tshul gang chen mtsho bkod pa'i /
NK106(me)001:7757: dge ba de yis srid pa'i sems can rnams //
NK106(me)001:7758: ma lus nyer zhi'i go 'phang mchog thob nas //
NK106(me)001:7759: sku dang ye shes 'du 'bral med pa yis //
NK106(me)001:7760: phyogs dus kun du bkra shis byed par shog /
NK106(me)001:7761: ces pa ni shis pas brjod pa'i rgyan te /
NK106(me)001:7762: zab cing rgya che ba'i bstan bcos bkod pa las byung ba'i dge ba mchog tu gyur pa des /
NK106(me)001:7763: khams gsum rigs drug srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i
NK106(me)001:7764: 'gro ba ji snyed pa thams cad 'bad pa dang
NK106(me)001:7765: rtsol ba med par zhi ba'i go 'phang kun du
NK106(me)001:7766: bzang po thob nas sku dang ye shes 'du 'bral
NK106(me)001:7769: gnas skabs thams cad du bkra shis pa'i 'od zer
NK106(me)001:7770: brgya stong bye ba khrag khrig dpag gis mi lang
NK106(me)001:7771: bsam gyis mi khyab pa dag kun nas 'phro bar
NK106(me)001:7772: gyur cig ces grags par byas pa yin no //
NK106(me)001:7773: de ltar yon tan mchog rab shin tu rmad byung mtho ris sa steng rnam brgyan pa //
NK106(me)001:7774: legs bshad 'od kyi dkyil 'khor nyi zho dmar bas yid mkha'i lam la rab gnas shing //
NK106(me)001:7775: mtha' yas 'gro bar nyer zhi'i go 'phang bla med snang ba dpe med 'char ba gang //
NK106(me)001:7776: sa gsum skye dgu'i ye shes sgron mar bgyis te ding sang bdag gis sbyar ba lags //
NK106(me)001:7777: chos tshul 'di ni zab cing rgya che chu srin 'dzin khri'i gnas 'dra zhing //
NK106(me)001:7778: legs bshad 'od stong kun nas 'phro ba rta bdun rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor 'dra //
NK106(me)001:7779: 'dod dgu'i re ba mtha' yas rdzogs ldan yid bzhin nor bu'i mchog 'dra zhing //
NK106(me)001:7780: sna tshogs 'dod ster rol pa can te bde gshegs dbang po'i go 'phang bzhin //
NK106(me)001:7781: ma lus mi lus lus pa med pa'i sprin chen snying po dam pa ni //
NK106(me)001:7782: phan mdzad phan bde'i bde legs gyur pa rtag tu byed pa gcig tu gyur //
NK106(me)001:7783: ye shes mtsho bsil sngon med gang de lha brgya'i gang chen mtsho min zhing //
NK106(me)001:7784: mtha' yas 'od zer dra ba spel legs gang yin de yang de bzhin no //
NK106(me)001:7785: 'di ni mdo rgyud blta ba'i me long ste //
NK106(me)001:7786: lung rigs man ngag du ma'i mdzod khang mchog /
NK106(me)001:7787: thar gling snang byed nyi ma'i snying po ste //
NK106(me)001:7788: ma rig mun pa sel ba'i sgron ma yin //
NK106(me)001:7789: phyi rabs skal bzang byang chub 'dod pa dag /
NK106(me)001:7790: yi ge 'di la rtag tu nan tan mdzod //
NK106(me)001:7791: mdo rgyud man ngag snying po 'dir tshang zhing //
NK106(me)001:7792: zab don brgyud pa'i byin rlabs sprin phung mchis //
NK106(me)001:7793: bdag blo'i 'dab bzang snying po'i nam mkha' yangs pa la //
NK106(me)001:7794: thabs dang shes rab tshig don gshog yangs rab brkyang ste //
NK106(me)001:7795: ches cher gong du thar pa'i grong khyer rab 'gro zhing //
NK106(me)001:7796: byang chub zhi ba rdul bral chu ngogs bgrod pa snyam //
NK106(me)001:7797: dpal ldan pad+ma'i mkhyen brtse'i mtsho chen las 'khrungs pa //
NK106(me)001:7798: gang gi rjes zhugs dri med 'od zer stong ldan ni //
NK106(me)001:7799: 'gro kun snang byed yid mkha'i mun pa rab bcom nas //
NK106(me)001:7800: gdod ma'i mkha' dbyings sgrib pa med der gnas pa yin //
NK106(me)001:7801: gang gi mtshan mo zhi dbyings snang ba de mthong tshe //
NK106(me)001:7802: rnga sgra'i dbyangs bzhin sgrib med gsung gi rjes 'gro bas //
NK106(me)001:7803: ri rab mar me'i rgyal mtshan rgyal ba der 'gyur zhes //
NK106(me)001:7804: dbugs chen 'byin pa de yang dpal ldan pad+ma skyes //
NK106(me)001:7805: gang gi mtshan tsam dran pa nyid kyis 'khor ba'i 'jigs las sgrol mdzad pa //
NK106(me)001:7806: de yi byin rlabs zhugs pa nyid kyis dngos po mtshan mar 'dzin pa med //
NK106(me)001:7807: gnyis med chos gsung thos pa nyid kyis mi skye'i bzod la sbyor mdzad pa //
NK106(me)001:7808: de yi dge bas rtag tu skyong zhing 'gro kun nyer 'tsho'i gzhir gyur cig /
NK106(me)001:7809: legs gsungs dpal ldan yon tan mchog mnga' tshangs pa'i rnam grol rab gsal ba //
NK106(me)001:7810: dpag med rgyal ba snga phyi'i gshegs shul rgyu 'bras theg pa zab mo'i don //
NK106(me)001:7811: lung rigs man ngag bzhon pas rab bskyod nges don shing rta chen po'i srol //
NK106(me)001:7812: gang yin 'di ni zab mo'i don te blo chen ldan rnams mgu byed yin //
NK106(me)001:7813: skye ba sngon rabs dus nas chos dkar gyi //
NK106(me)001:7814: dge tshogs rmad byung las bskyed las 'phro can //
NK106(me)001:7815: slob ma bzang po gzhon nu sangs rgyas kyis //
NK106(me)001:7816: bskul ba'i ngor ni bdag gis 'di bkod do //
NK106(me)001:7817: gangs ri'i ra bas legs par bskor ba'i dbus //
NK106(me)001:7818: sngon gyi chos rgyal dam pas bsten pa'i ri //
NK106(me)001:7819: rang byung pad+ma rgyal po'i gnas mchog tu //
NK106(me)001:7820: phyi rabs don phyir phan pa'i chos 'di bkod //
NK106(me)001:7821: dge ba de yis bdag dang 'gro kun 'od gsal snying po'i grur zhugs te //
NK106(me)001:7822: sgrib pa'i rgya mtsho shin tu brgal dka' skad cig yud kyis rab sgrol nas //
NK106(me)001:7823: rgyal ba'i go 'phang shin tu rmad byung rin chen snying po'i gling son te //
NK106(me)001:7824: srid zhi'i rgud pa mtha' dag rab bsal rdzogs sangs yon tan la reg shog /
NK106(me)001:7825: gang yang 'gro bas 'bad ma dgos par bdag gi dge bas yongs grol zhing //
NK106(me)001:7826: cung zad tsam yang bsgrubs pa med par rgyal ba'i 'byor pa phun tshogs ldan //
NK106(me)001:7827: de ltar de bzhin brtson pa med kyang myur du srid pa'i mtsho brgal nas //
NK106(me)001:7828: yong ye phyam gcig 'khor ba stongs nas zhi ba'i grong khyer gang bar shog /
NK106(me)001:7829: gnas skabs kun du dge ba 'di yis ni //
NK106(me)001:7830: 'jig rten khams kun 'byor zhing lha yul bzhin //
NK106(me)001:7831: yid la bsams pa tsam gyis dge 'grub cing //
NK106(me)001:7832: thar pa'i lam bzang snang ba 'dzin par shog /
NK106(me)001:7833: su yang sdug bsngal 'tshe ba mi mthong zhing //
NK106(me)001:7834: rang gi bde ba dam pas nyer 'tsho ba //
NK106(me)001:7835: lha yul sa steng sa 'og kun khyab ste //
NK106(me)001:7836: mthar yang 'od dpag med pa'i gnas thob shog /'gro ba'i don gang chos dang mthun 'grub cing //
NK106(me)001:7837: tshul min yid la byed pa rnam bral te //
NK106(me)001:7838: byams sogs rgyal sras dam pa'i rjes 'gro bas //
NK106(me)001:7839: myur du byams mgon zhabs drung skye bar shog /
NK106(me)001:7840: bdag gi rtsom pa thams cad don yod cing //
NK106(me)001:7841: sems can tshogs rab srid las sgrol ba'i phyir //
NK106(me)001:7842: skad cig mi dal brtson pa mtha' yas kyis //
NK106(me)001:7843: srid gsum zhi ba'i dgon par 'khrid par shog /
NK106(me)001:7844: bdag gi bde bas sems can kun bde zhing //
NK106(me)001:7845: sems can sdug bsngal bdag gis khur khyer te //
NK106(me)001:7846: 'gro ba de kun yongs su stongs kyi bar //
NK106(me)001:7847: bdag gis 'dren pa'i ded dpon byed par shog /
NK106(me)001:7848: nam yang bde med 'khor ba sbrul gdug gling //
NK106(me)001:7849: me chen 'obs dang 'dra ba'i khrod 'di las //
NK106(me)001:7850: lus can bsil ba'i tsan dan nags khrod du //
NK106(me)001:7851: sangs rgyas pad tshal skyong bas nyer gnas shog /
NK106(me)001:7852: mi rtag mi gtsang sdug bsngal bdag tu 'dzin //
NK106(me)001:7853: phyin ci log bzhis rtsen pa'i 'gro ba kun //
NK106(me)001:7854: bdag gi mthu yis rgyal ba'i sar gzhol te //
NK106(me)001:7855: ma lus yon tan tshogs rab rdzogs par shog /
NK106(me)001:7856: nags nang me tog bung ba 'phur lding zhing //
NK106(me)001:7857: rma bya grag pas ze ba bskyod pa der //
NK106(me)001:7858: zhi ba'i bsam gtan bde bas yongs gang zhing //
NK106(me)001:7859: srog dang bcas pa'i lus 'di g.yo bar shog /
NK106(me)001:7860: chu gtsang 'bras bu'i sdang mang grib bsil can //
NK106(me)001:7861: 'khri shing sman ljongs brag ri'i drung der ni //
NK106(me)001:7862: gcig pur yid la byed pa kun spangs te //
NK106(me)001:7863: thar pa'i byang chub bdud rtsi brnyes par shog /
NK106(me)001:7864: nags rlung g.yo bas me tog grib shing bskyod pa yis //
NK106(me)001:7865: lo ma lhags pa lha rdzas char pa 'bab pa bzhin //
NK106(me)001:7866: bsam gtan pa de sgra med zhi ba'i dga' ba yis //
NK106(me)001:7867: ting 'dzin mi brnyings 'od gsal 'dus ma byas 'grub shog /
NK106(me)001:7868: pad+ma la 'khor bung ba dang ni gdangs snyan bya tshogs sgrogs pa las //
NK106(me)001:7869: gzhan pa'i ca co nye bar zhi gyur dben zhing nyams dag'i nags khrod der //
NK106(me)001:7870: 'dris dang 'du 'dzi'i skye bo mi mthong gcig pur zhi la sems gzhol bas //
NK106(me)001:7871: lham me lhan ne lhang nger gnas shing tshe 'di don yod byed par shog /
NK106(me)001:7872: de ltar legs gsungs zhi ba'i chos dang dag pa'i smon lam rgya che bas //
NK106(me)001:7873: mtsho chen yangs gsal srid rtser khyab cing bde dag'i yon tan tshogs rab 'bras //
NK106(me)001:7874: lha yul sa steng mtho ris brgyan pas ngan song pa dag rab stongs te //
NK106(me)001:7875: mngon mtho nges par legs pa'i lam song rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'grub par shog /
NK106(me)001:7876: chos tshul 'di yang mkha' bzhin rgya che kun la khyab cing yid bzhin re ba rnam skong la //
NK106(me)001:7877: sa bzhin 'gro ba'i rten dang nyer 'tsho'i gru chen srid mtsho las sgrol ded dpon bla med bzhin //
NK106(me)001:7878: gdung sel chos char bdud rtsi'i chu bzhin yid mkhar gzungs sprin snyan pas lha yi rnga sgra bzhin //
NK106(me)001:7879: ma rig mun sel thar gling snang bas nyi zla'i mchog bzhin grags pas bkra shis byed par shog //
NK106(me)001:7880: rdzogs pa chen po sems nyid ngal gso zhes bya
NK106(me)001:7881: ba'i 'grel pa shing rta chen po zhes bya ba
NK106(me)001:7882: / dpal o rgyan gyi slob dpon chen po pad+ma
NK106(me)001:7883: sam+b+ha was rjes su gzung zhing bde bar gshegs pa'i
NK106(me)001:7884: bka' rab 'byams la mang du thos pa'i nor gyis
NK106(me)001:7885: phyug pa theg pa mchog gi rnal 'byor pa dri
NK106(me)001:7887: brag dmar zang yag nam mkha'i rdzong bod kyi ri
NK106(me)001:7888: bo rtse lnga gter ka du mas brgyan cing mkha'
NK106(me)001:7889: 'gro rang bzhin gyis 'du ba'i gnas su sbyar ba
